NK123(go)001:1: // ra t+na s+ya so p+aa nam n+aa ma i ti
NK123(go)001:2: h+aa ba kam y+aa na na p+no bi ni k+shi
NK123(go)001:3: pa sam k+she pa sa ma s+t+r+aa b+hi m+aa pa
NK123(go)001:5: snga 'gyur theg pa rim dgu'i rnam gzhag mdor bsdus
NK123(go)001:6: su brjod pa rin po che'i them skas zhes bya
NK123(go)001:7: ba bzhugs so // na mo gu ru many+dzu sh+r+ai ye /
NK123(go)001:8: bsod nams gser gyi shing rtas mngon mtho gdong bzhi pa dang shis brjod nyan //
NK123(go)001:9: grub pa'i mchog gyur rig pa 'dzin dang drang srong tshogs kyis btud gyur cing //
NK123(go)001:10: stobs mchog mthu yis bdud sde'i klad 'gem theg mchog seng ge'i sgra dbyangs kyis //
NK123(go)001:11: sa gsum khyab mdzad kun mkhyen mchog dang des bstan der 'dzin yongs la 'dud //
NK123(go)001:12: khyad par gangs khrod snyigs lnga'i mun rum thub bstan pad ma'i gnyen drangs nas //
NK123(go)001:13: bshad sgrub 'dab stong thog mar bzhad mdzad mkhan slob chos rgyal lo pan tshogs //
NK123(go)001:14: de dag bka' drin gzugs su grub na nam mkha'i ra bar shong srid dam //
NK123(go)001:15: de tshul shes nas byas pa gzo rnams srid pa gsum na basngagasa 'os nyid //
NK123(go)001:16: don gyi dgongs pa rgyal dang mnyam mod bka' drin rgyal las chos 'phags par //
NK123(go)001:17: thub pa mchog gis mdo rgyud kun nas rjes basngagasa dam pa'i mgon rnams la //
NK123(go)001:18: lus srog bye ba phul yang bka' drin shas tsam rjes su 'tshob nus ci //
NK123(go)001:19: de slad byang chub thob kyang rigs kyi bdag por 'bral med bsnyen byas na //
NK123(go)001:20: 'gro kun snying po'i rang bzhin gcig phyir mthar thug theg pa gcig nyid kyang //
NK123(go)001:21: gnas skabs gdul bya'i blo rim dang mtshams 'jug sgo'i tshul 'di rgyal bas bstan //
NK123(go)001:22: de slad bsam 'das theg sgo ji snyed mdor bsdus rnam dgur dbye ba'i tshul //
NK123(go)001:23: snga 'gyur rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal lung mdo tsam 'dir ni brjod par bya //
NK123(go)001:24: de la 'dir 'o skol gyi ston pa thabs mkhas
NK123(go)001:25: shing thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa 'di nyid
NK123(go)001:26: nges don drang thad du ston pa'i dbang du byas
NK123(go)001:27: na bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol du
NK123(go)001:28: ye thog gdod ma'i grol sar mngon par byang chub
NK123(go)001:29: ste / ma rig gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul bas bslad
NK123(go)001:30: pa'i dbang gis med snang srid pa'i btson rar shin
NK123(go)001:31: tu nyam thag pa'i 'gro ba rnams thog mar lam
NK123(go)001:32: ston pa por byung ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:33: mtha' yas pa'i gdul bya rnams kyi so so'i mos
NK123(go)001:34: pa dang skal pa'i khyad par dang rjes su 'tshams
NK123(go)001:35: pa'i gang la gang 'dul gyi rnam 'phrul bsam gyis
NK123(go)001:36: mi khyab pas 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu sgron
NK123(go)001:37: ma rnam par bkod par mdzad pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:38: theg pa thun mong pa'i sde snod kyi lung dam pa'i chos pad ma dkar po las kyang /
NK123(go)001:39: bskal pa bye stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK123(go)001:40: de yi tshad ni nam yang med pa na //
NK123(go)001:41: byang chub mchog rab de ni ngas thob ste //
NK123(go)001:42: nga ni rtag tu chos kyang rab 'chad do //
NK123(go)001:43: byang chub sems dpa' mang 'di yang dag gzung //
NK123(go)001:44: sangs rgyas ye shes la ni de dag dgod //
NK123(go)001:45: sems can bye ba khrag khrig mtha' yas pa //
NK123(go)001:46: bskal pa bye ba mang por smin par byas //
NK123(go)001:47: mya ngan 'das pa'i sa yang bstan byas te //
NK123(go)001:48: sems can rnam par 'dul phyir thabs brjod do //
NK123(go)001:49: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:50: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:51: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas te //
NK123(go)001:52: sems can yongs su smin bya'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:53: bye ba phrag brgya rgyal ba nyid //
NK123(go)001:54: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK123(go)001:55: da dung du yang 'dren pa khyod //
NK123(go)001:56: sangs rgyas mdzad pa mang ston mdzad //
NK123(go)001:59: byang chub rgya mtsho rab brnyes gyur nas kyang //
NK123(go)001:60: sems can rgya mtsho rab tu smin bya'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:61: byang chub sems bskyed rgya mtshor ston mdzad cing //
NK123(go)001:62: mi 'grib spyod pa rgya mtsho kun tu ston //
NK123(go)001:63: bde gshegs rnams kyi rnam 'phrul de 'dra'o //
NK123(go)001:65: yang dag sangs rgyas sku gcig ste //
NK123(go)001:66: 'dren pa thams cad don gcig kyang //
NK123(go)001:67: tshad med gzhan dang gzhan dag tu //
NK123(go)001:68: phyogs bcu kun nas rab tu snang //
NK123(go)001:70: thun mong ma yin pa gsang ba yid bzhin rin po che bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:71: kun gyi sngon rol sangs rgyas pa //
NK123(go)001:72: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal gsang ba che //
NK123(go)001:73: bsam yas zhing du rnam par rol //
NK123(go)001:74: grangs med snga phyi dus kun tu //
NK123(go)001:75: zhi dang khro tshul dpag med cing //
NK123(go)001:76: rngon dang smad 'tshong la sogs gzugs //
NK123(go)001:77: sna tshogs tshul gyis don mdzad kyang //
NK123(go)001:78: da dung bskal pa bzang po 'dir //
NK123(go)001:79: 'dren pa stong du sgyur mdzad cing //
NK123(go)001:80: de bzhin sna tshogs tshul 'chang bas //
NK123(go)001:81: ma lus 'gro ba'i don mdzad do //
NK123(go)001:83: ye shes nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:84: kun bzang longs spyod rdzogs pa las //
NK123(go)001:85: 'dul ba'i sprul pa grangs med cing //
NK123(go)001:86: khyad par mi mjed 'jig rten du //
NK123(go)001:87: stong rtsa gnyis kyi skur snang ngo //
NK123(go)001:89: 'dul byed kyi chos sam theg pa'i sgo yang gdul
NK123(go)001:90: bya rang rang gi skal ba dang 'tshams par mtha'
NK123(go)001:91: yas par ston par mdzad pa ste /
NK123(go)001:92: rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK123(go)001:93: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas su //
NK123(go)001:94: 'dul ba'i don rnams so sor ston //
NK123(go)001:95: theg pa ma tho dman thams cad dang //
NK123(go)001:96: phyin ci log rnams bsam yas su //
NK123(go)001:97: zhi khro'i tshul can thams cad la //
NK123(go)001:98: so sor mthun byas kun tu snang //
NK123(go)001:101: theg pa rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK123(go)001:104: mdo sde lang+kara gshegs pa las //
NK123(go)001:105: sems can rnams ni yongs drang phyir //
NK123(go)001:106: theg pa mtha' dag ngas bshad de //
NK123(go)001:107: 'di zhes dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK123(go)001:109: de dag dus nam gyi tshe tshul ji lta bus gsungs pa'ang /
NK123(go)001:110: mdo sde yon tan bkod pa'i rgyal po las /
NK123(go)001:111: nga yis ci yang ma gsungs par //
NK123(go)001:112: sems can rnams la khyab brdal snang //
NK123(go)001:113: gang tshe rim gyis mngon 'dod pa //
NK123(go)001:114: de dag kun la de bzhin te //
NK123(go)001:115: dus gcig nyid du 'jug pa la //
NK123(go)001:116: chos kyi rnam grangs rdzogs par snang //
NK123(go)001:117: yid bzhin re ba rnam skong ba'i //
NK123(go)001:118: gsung gi che ba de nyid do //
NK123(go)001:119: zhes dang 'phags pa ting 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK123(go)001:120: 'jig rten phan pa khyod kyi gsung gcig la //
NK123(go)001:121: mos pa tha dad bzhin du sgra 'byung ste //
NK123(go)001:122: rgyal bas bdag la ston snyam so sor sems //
NK123(go)001:123: gang gi slad du khyod kyis 'dzum mdzad ston //
NK123(go)001:126: rtog pa med cing 'khrul med pa //
NK123(go)001:127: yid 'ong rdo rje'i gsung gcig la //
NK123(go)001:128: gdul bya'i bsam pa'i dbang gis na //
NK123(go)001:129: bye brag mang po 'byung ba yin //
NK123(go)001:131: des na gdul bya'i zhing dang /
NK123(go)001:134: gang gis 'dul ba bstan pa dam pa'i chos sde
NK123(go)001:135: snod dang theg pa'i rnam grangs sogs tshur mthong gi
NK123(go)001:136: blos gzhal bya'i yul las 'das na'ang /
NK123(go)001:137: re zhig da lta'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i gdul
NK123(go)001:138: bya rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can rnams la ji
NK123(go)001:140: snga 'gyur rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal lung ji lta
NK123(go)001:141: bar theg pa rim pa dgu'i rnam bzhag mdo tsam
NK123(go)001:143: theg pa'i rang bzhin spyir bstan pa //
NK123(go)001:144: bye brag so so'i rnam dbye rgyas par bshad pa /
NK123(go)001:145: rjes su lung gis mtha' bsdu ba'o //
NK123(go)001:149: dbye bsdu'i khyad par spyir bstan pa'o //
NK123(go)001:151: gnas skabs dang mthar thug tu ngan song ngam 'khor
NK123(go)001:152: ba las 'phags te mngon matho'am nges legs myang 'das
NK123(go)001:153: kyi phyogs su 'gro ba'i lam bden gyis bsdus pa'i
NK123(go)001:155: ya na zhes pa'i sgra las theg pa ste /
NK123(go)001:156: de'ang bgrod bya'i shul nyid kyi phyir lam dang /
NK123(go)001:157: khur khyer ba po nyid kyi phyir shing rta la sogs pa'i gzhon pa la 'jug la /
NK123(go)001:158: 'dir de dang 'dra ba'i sgo nas dge bcu'i lam sogs la'ang 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:159: lam gong nas gong du bgrod par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:160: 'dir lam la gtso bor brjod mod /
NK123(go)001:161: 'dis 'degs pa lam gyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:162: 'dir 'degs 'bras bu'i theg pa zhes rnam grangs gnyis su'ang gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:164: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te //
NK123(go)001:165: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par 'thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK123(go)001:166: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan 'da' //
NK123(go)001:169: spyir theg pa'i rnam grangs 'di kho nar nges zhes phyogs gcig tu chad pa med de /
NK123(go)001:170: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa'i gnyen por sangs rgyas kyi
NK123(go)001:171: thugs rjes gang la gang 'dul du bstan pa'i phyir
NK123(go)001:172: gong du drangs pa'i lung rnams kyis gsal por bstan
NK123(go)001:173: pa bzhin la / de yang re zhig bsdu na
NK123(go)001:174: 'bras bu la dgongs te theg pa gcig tu gsung
NK123(go)001:175: pa bzhin la / pa ni / dam chos pad dkar las /
NK123(go)001:176: theg pa gcig ste theg pa gsum du med //
NK123(go)001:177: de dag drang ba'i thabs su bstan pa yin //
NK123(go)001:180: gsang ba'i snying por nges pa ni //
NK123(go)001:181: theg pa'i sgo yang gcig las med //
NK123(go)001:183: yang rgyu 'bras kyi theg par mos pa'i gdul bya la dgongs nas gnyis gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:185: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK123(go)001:186: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK123(go)001:189: mdo sde gdams ngag 'bog pa'i rgyal po las //
NK123(go)001:190: rgyu las mos pa rgyu chos kyi //
NK123(go)001:191: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK123(go)001:192: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK123(go)001:195: yang dman pa dang rgya chen po la mos pa'i
NK123(go)001:196: gdul bya la dgongs nas kyang gnyis su gsungs te
NK123(go)001:198: che chung rim pa blo yod phyir //
NK123(go)001:199: theg pa'i grangs kyang de bzhin te //
NK123(go)001:200: bsdu na che chung rnam gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:201: zhes dang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK123(go)001:202: 'od srung theg pa ni gnyis te chung ngu dang chen po'o //
NK123(go)001:204: yang chung 'bring gi bye bas nyan rang theg chen te gsum du gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:206: rab 'byor nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:207: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:208: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste /
NK123(go)001:210: phyi nang gi rim pas kyang gsum du bshad de /
NK123(go)001:211: gsang ba thig le nor bu'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:212: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:213: dam pa'i chos kyang rab tu gzung //
NK123(go)001:216: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:217: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK123(go)001:219: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum 'bras bu dang bzhir yang bshad de /
NK123(go)001:221: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK123(go)001:222: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK123(go)001:225: theg pa'i sgo ni gsum du gsungs //
NK123(go)001:226: gsang nyid theg pa bsdus rang bzhi //
NK123(go)001:228: yang nges legs kyi theg pa gsum mngon mtho'i gnyis dang bcas lngar yang gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:230: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK123(go)001:231: de bzhin du ni nyan thos dang //
NK123(go)001:232: de bzhin gshegs dang rang rgyal gyi //
NK123(go)001:233: theg pa tha dad par bshad do //
NK123(go)001:235: nges legs gsum gyi steng du bla na med kyi
NK123(go)001:236: theg pa bsnan cing mngo'i mtho'i theg pa gcig tu
NK123(go)001:237: bsdus nas lngar yang bshad de /
NK123(go)001:239: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK123(go)001:240: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK123(go)001:242: yang rgyu 'bras kyi gong 'og dbye bas drug tu bshad de /
NK123(go)001:244: nges pa thob pa'i theg pa drug /
NK123(go)001:248: lha dang mi dang nyan thos dang //
NK123(go)001:249: rang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:250: gsang ba phyi dang nang gnyis te //
NK123(go)001:251: de ltar theg pa bdun du bshad //
NK123(go)001:255: de ltar theg brgyad las 'das pa'i //
NK123(go)001:259: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK123(go)001:261: yang sor bzhag lha ma'i theg pa gnyis /
NK123(go)001:264: 'od gsal rdo rje theg pa dang bcu drug tu bshad de /
NK123(go)001:265: snying po nyi ma snang byed kyi rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:266: theg pa'i dang po bcu drug mgon //
NK123(go)001:268: yang bsam gyis mi khyab par yang gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:270: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK123(go)001:271: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK123(go)001:273: de dag kyang gdul bya'i blo rim la snang ba
NK123(go)001:274: tsam las gnas lugs yang dag pa'i don la gang
NK123(go)001:277: theg pa rnam pa mang bshad pa //
NK123(go)001:278: sems can rnams ni drang ba'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:279: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad de //
NK123(go)001:280: theg pa gcig tu'ang ngas bstan to //
NK123(go)001:282: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK123(go)001:283: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK123(go)001:285: de la kha cig na re /
NK123(go)001:288: sangs rgyas pa la bzhi pa dang //
NK123(go)001:289: lnga pa thub pa'i dgongs pa min //
NK123(go)001:290: zhes pas theg pa bzhi pa dang //
NK123(go)001:291: grub mtha' lnga pa med par gsungs pas theg pa ni gsum kho nar nges pa'i phyir zer /
NK123(go)001:293: rdo rje snying 'grel nyid las kyang /
NK123(go)001:294: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK123(go)001:295: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bu gnas //
NK123(go)001:296: zhes bzhir phye ba'ang mi 'thad par thal /
NK123(go)001:297: gsum kho nar nges pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:299: gsum du phye ba ni nyan rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa gsum yin la /
NK123(go)001:300: de'i phyi ma la rgyu 'bras gnyis su phye nas bzhir gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:301: dbye bsdu'i khyad par tsam ste skyon med do zhe na /
NK123(go)001:302: de 'dra rim dgu la'ang mtshungs te /
NK123(go)001:303: phyi nang gi rgyud sde drug po 'bras theg tu 'du la /
NK123(go)001:304: de'ang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i nang du 'du bas 'dir yang dbye bsdu'i khyad par ro //
NK123(go)001:305: gal te lha ma'i theg pa ma 'dus so zhe na /
NK123(go)001:307: lha ma'i theg pa ni mngon mtho'i theg pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:309: gsum du bsdus pa ni rnam grol gyi theg pa la dgongs pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:310: de bas na khyed cag theg pa gsum kho nar zhen pa ni /
NK123(go)001:311: lang gshegs kyi mdor theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK123(go)001:312: par gsungs pa sogs kyi don la rmongs par zad
NK123(go)001:313: do // des na gnas skabs su theg pa du
NK123(go)001:314: ma'i rnam bzhag mdzad pa'ang de dang de'i gnas skabs
NK123(go)001:315: dang gtso che chung gi dbang gis gdul bya drang
NK123(go)001:316: ba'i thabs su bstan nas de rnams rang rang gi
NK123(go)001:317: 'bras bu rjes mthun re thob tu zin kyang /
NK123(go)001:318: da dung de'i gong du sangs rgyas rnams kyis bgrod
NK123(go)001:319: pa gcig pa'i lam rdo rje theg pa mchog tu
NK123(go)001:320: bstan du yod pa la dgongs pa ste gzhan rnams
NK123(go)001:321: de nyid la dkri ba'i lam stegs tsam du bstan
NK123(go)001:322: cing rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi bar du bgrod bya'i
NK123(go)001:323: lam rnams skas kyi gdang bu ltar gnas te /
NK123(go)001:325: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK123(go)001:326: skas kyi gdang bu lta bur bstan //
NK123(go)001:328: mdo pad ma dkar po las /
NK123(go)001:329: drang srong rnams kyis theg pa gsum bstan pa //
NK123(go)001:330: rnam 'dren rnams kyis thabs la mkhas pa ste //
NK123(go)001:331: theg pa gcig las gnyis su yod ma yin //
NK123(go)001:332: bsti ba'i don du theg pa gsum bstan to //
NK123(go)001:335: srid pa'i lam gyis dub pa rnams //
NK123(go)001:336: ngal gso'i don de de nyid min //
NK123(go)001:338: de'i phyir rang lugs 'dir nyan rang byang sems sngags
NK123(go)001:339: kyi theg pa ste bzhir grangs nges pa'i phyi ma
NK123(go)001:340: la rgyud sde 'og ma gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:341: bla med la bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum du dbye bar mdzad nas /
NK123(go)001:342: de theg pa'i rim pa bzhag pa la 'gal bar
NK123(go)001:343: 'du ba'i cha shas tsam yang gnas pa'i skabs med
NK123(go)001:344: de / sangs rgyas kyi sas bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK123(go)001:345: cad la spyir theg pa gcig gi sgra sbyar ba'am
NK123(go)001:346: de / / bye brag ji snyed pa la theg
NK123(go)001:347: pa so so'i sgra sbyar kyang rung ste thams cad
NK123(go)001:348: mkhyen pa'i bar du bgrod byed kyi lam yin pas
NK123(go)001:349: de / / so // de'ang dang po phyi mtshan
NK123(go)001:350: nyid kyi theg pa gsum pos rim bzhin dgra bcom
NK123(go)001:351: de / / so // pa dang / ne tso'am
NK123(go)001:352: bse ru lta bu'i rang sangs rgyas dang bcu gcig
NK123(go)001:353: kun tu 'od kyi sa mthar 'degs pas na thegs
NK123(go)001:354: de / / so // pa dang / pa dang
NK123(go)001:355: / gnyis pa phyi brgyud kyi theg pa gsum pos
NK123(go)001:356: rim bzhin rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa dang
NK123(go)001:357: de / / so // pa dang / pa dang
NK123(go)001:358: / / rigs bzhi mkha' la spyod pa'i sa dang
NK123(go)001:359: de / / so // pa dang / pa dang
NK123(go)001:360: / / / rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i sar
NK123(go)001:361: 'degs par byed pas na theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:362: gsum pa nang pa thabs kyi rgyud rnam pa gsum
NK123(go)001:363: gyis rim pa bzhin yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK123(go)001:364: gyis sa dang / bde ba chen po'i sa dang
NK123(go)001:365: ye shes bla ma'i sar 'degs par byed pas na
NK123(go)001:366: theg pa'i sgra bshad bzhag la /
NK123(go)001:367: 'di la dgongs nas lang gshegs su //
NK123(go)001:368: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK123(go)001:369: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK123(go)001:371: des na sems kyi rnam par rtog pa ji snyed
NK123(go)001:372: pa dang rjes su 'tshams par theg pa'i sgo yang
NK123(go)001:373: de snyed du yod par gsungs pa'i phyir skabs 'dir
NK123(go)001:374: dbang po 'bring dang rnon po dag la'ang dbye ba
NK123(go)001:375: gsum gsum du phye ba gdul bya'i blo tshod la
NK123(go)001:376: dgongs nas sngags kyi theg pa gong 'og rnams de
NK123(go)001:377: dang mtshungs par bstan nas rang rang gi gzhung lam
NK123(go)001:378: du lta sgom spyod 'bras tshar re tshang bar lam
NK123(go)001:379: so so rang rkya thub pa'i don tsam du bshad
NK123(go)001:380: nas mthar phyin blo zad chos zad 'phags pa'i lam
NK123(go)001:381: bden sgra ji bzhin pa'i mthar thug par bzhag pa
NK123(go)001:382: yin te / de yang gang zhig skye ba gzhan
NK123(go)001:383: du gos pa'i bag chags kyi stobs kyis nags tshal
NK123(go)001:384: dang dben pa la dga' zhing khrus dang man+dala bri
NK123(go)001:385: ba dang mchod pa dang sbyin sreg dang dka' thub
NK123(go)001:386: dang bzlas brjod la sogs pa'i bya ba med par
NK123(go)001:387: yid mnyam pa 'jog mi nus pa /
NK123(go)001:388: de kho na nyid bsgom pa'i nus pa chung ba /
NK123(go)001:389: mtshan ma can gyi spyod pa la dga' ba dag
NK123(go)001:390: la phyi'i spyod pa de dag shas cher ston pa
NK123(go)001:391: bya ba'i rgyud legs grub sogs gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:392: gang zhig bya ba'i khyad par la'ang mos /
NK123(go)001:393: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod pa rgya chen po
NK123(go)001:394: la sbyor ba'i nang gi bdag nyid can gyi tshul
NK123(go)001:395: yang mi 'dor bar spro ba dag la bya ba
NK123(go)001:396: dang rnal 'byor gyi cha gnyis ka dang ldan pa
NK123(go)001:397: gnyis ka'i rgyud rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang
NK123(go)001:398: chub pa la sogs gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:399: de nyid ni gsang sngags dang rjes su mthun pa'i
NK123(go)001:400: spyod pa shes rab dang thabs gtso bor gyur pa
NK123(go)001:401: rgya cher ston pas sngon gyi mkhas pa dag gis
NK123(go)001:402: spyod pa'i rgyud ces bshad do //
NK123(go)001:403: yang gang zhig de kho na nyid la mngon par dga' ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK123(go)001:404: rnal 'byor la lhag par mos pa phyi'i bya ba
NK123(go)001:405: la mi dga' bar ting nge 'dzin gyis rgyud dag
NK123(go)001:406: par byed pa rnams la bya ba'i yan lag nyung
NK123(go)001:407: zhing / rnal 'byor gyi yan lag gtso bor ston
NK123(go)001:408: pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kho na nyid bsdus pa
NK123(go)001:410: rnal 'byor pa gang zhig dbang po rno ba /
NK123(go)001:411: de kho na nyid sgom pa la rab tu 'dun pa /
NK123(go)001:412: sngon goms pa'i stobs kyis bya ba dang dngos po
NK123(go)001:413: thams cad la tha dad pa'i 'du shes mi 'jug
NK123(go)001:414: pa / theg pa chen po la sems rnam par
NK123(go)001:415: sbyangs ba shes rab dang gnyis su med pa'i spyod
NK123(go)001:416: pa la mngon par dad pa'i bdag nyid chen po
NK123(go)001:417: rnams la de kho na nyid kyi rnal 'byor gtso
NK123(go)001:418: bor mdzad de gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis 'jug
NK123(go)001:419: cing spros pa med pa dang shin tu spros pa
NK123(go)001:420: med pa'i spyod pa ston pa /
NK123(go)001:421: rnal 'byor chen po'i rgyud dpal gsang ba 'dus pa
NK123(go)001:422: dang gsang ba snying po la sogs pa gsungs pa
NK123(go)001:423: dang / yang spros pa las 'das pa'i rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:424: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i bdag nyid rtsa
NK123(go)001:425: ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du chos thams
NK123(go)001:426: cad ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs nas nang gi
NK123(go)001:427: rnal 'byor zab mo la mngon par dga' ba dag
NK123(go)001:428: la mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa sogs a nu yo
NK123(go)001:429: ga'i rgyud sde rnams gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:430: yang gang zag dbang po rab rtogs pa dang grol
NK123(go)001:431: ba dus mnyam par gyur pa'i rigs can dag la
NK123(go)001:432: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad spros bral
NK123(go)001:433: thig le nyag gcig rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK123(go)001:434: por ye nas sangs rgyas pas bya rtsol gyi spros
NK123(go)001:435: pa las 'das pa'i theg pa rdzogs pa chen po
NK123(go)001:436: a ti yo ga'i rgyud rnams gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:437: de yang 'og ma 'og ma rnams kyi lam dang
NK123(go)001:438: 'bras bu'i tshul thams cad gong ma gong mar 'du
NK123(go)001:439: zhing / bla med la'ang bskyed rdzogs gnyis po lam
NK123(go)001:440: gang zhig sgrub tshul blos byas las ma 'das pas
NK123(go)001:441: bsgrub bya 'dus byas su 'gyur bas ye shes mthong
NK123(go)001:442: ba la khyad par shin tu che ste /
NK123(go)001:443: rdzogs pa chen po ni blos byas chos kyis rig
NK123(go)001:444: pa'i skabs med pas chos nyid kyi bden pa gnas
NK123(go)001:445: lugs rtogs pa'i stobs kyis thob pa 'phags rgyud kyis
NK123(go)001:446: bsdus pa'i lam bden zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK123(go)001:447: te lam 'og mas mngon du bya rgyu rnam grangs
NK123(go)001:448: mang pos bstan pa'i chos nyid ma nor bar mngon
NK123(go)001:449: sum du mthong bar 'gyur ba'i phyir theg pa ma
NK123(go)001:450: lus pa theg pa chen po bla na med pa
NK123(go)001:451: 'dir 'du ba yin la de'i phyir 'di la ye
NK123(go)001:452: shes kyi theg pa zhes bshad pa'ang yin te /
NK123(go)001:453: sangs rgyas phal po che'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:454: ye shes kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:455: theg pa chen po la rab tu gzhol ba'i sems
NK123(go)001:456: kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba de dag yongs su bsngo'o
NK123(go)001:459: nga yis bstan pa'i theg pa dgu po yang //
NK123(go)001:460: sems can rnams kyis mthu dang mos par bshad //
NK123(go)001:461: 'di ltar thabs kyis mchog gi ye shes la //
NK123(go)001:462: rab tu gzud pa'i phyir na ngas bshad do //
NK123(go)001:464: gzhan yang lha'i bu rab stsal sems kyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:465: theg pa chen po'i theg pa 'di //
NK123(go)001:466: sangs rgyas theg pa bsam mi khyab //
NK123(go)001:467: sems can gyi ni go skabs 'byed //
NK123(go)001:468: theg pa chen po bla na med //
NK123(go)001:469: theg pa ji snyed ci yod pa //
NK123(go)001:470: 'di ni de yi mchog tu dgongs //
NK123(go)001:471: de phyir theg pa chen po las //
NK123(go)001:472: theg pa thams cad rab tu dbye //
NK123(go)001:474: 'phags pa rtogs chen phyag rgyas las kyang /
NK123(go)001:475: theg pa ni gcig kho nar bas te /
NK123(go)001:476: gnyis dang gsum du ma mchis so //
NK123(go)001:479: de yang gdul byar theg pa gsum gyis 'dul ba la nyan thos dang /
NK123(go)001:481: theg pa chen po bstan to //
NK123(go)001:482: yang dag par theg pa gcig ste 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa'o //
NK123(go)001:485: rab 'byor theg pa ni gcig kho na ste /
NK123(go)001:486: bla na med pa sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK123(go)001:489: theg pa gcig las gnyis pa yod ma yin //
NK123(go)001:490: gsum pa nam yang yod min 'jig rten na //
NK123(go)001:491: sna tshogs 'gro ba 'dul bar mdzad ma gtogs //
NK123(go)001:492: zhes pa la sogs skabs 'gar theg pa gcig tu gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:493: kha cig tu gnyis dang gsum dang lnga sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:494: grangs med par yang gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:495: gnas lugs ma 'khrul ba mthong ba'i gang zag la
NK123(go)001:496: dgongs nas theg pa med par gsungs pa sogs gong
NK123(go)001:497: du drangs pa'i lang dkar gshegs pa'i lung sogs kyis
NK123(go)001:498: gsal ba bzhin dgos pa'i dbang gis de lta bur
NK123(go)001:499: bstan pa rnams la mtha' gcig tu 'di tsam zhig
NK123(go)001:500: yin la / 'di tsam zhig min no zhes rnam
NK123(go)001:501: bzhag 'grigs 'grigs ltar smra ba yang yang dag pa'i
NK123(go)001:502: gnas la blo gros kyi 'jug pa ma phyogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:503: rtags su shes par bya zhing /
NK123(go)001:504: yang rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis theg brgyad gol sar bshad pa la /
NK123(go)001:506: chos zab khyad du gsod pa yi /
NK123(go)001:508: zhes kha zer ba'ang gyi na ste /
NK123(go)001:510: a nu man chad gol sgrib kyi theg pa yin pas /
NK123(go)001:511: 'dir rang gi lha ba mchog tu rtogs pa'i slad du /
NK123(go)001:512: de dag gi tshul ngos bzung ba tsam yin la /
NK123(go)001:513: nam yang khyad du gsod par mi 'dod /
NK123(go)001:514: rdzogs pa chen po'i byin rlabs las shar ba'i rtsal
NK123(go)001:515: bstan pa'i sgo sna tshogs pa yin te rol pa'am
NK123(go)001:517: de yang a ti'i lugs kyi rgyu'i theg pa yang sngags su 'dus /
NK123(go)001:518: sngags kyang yo ga rnam pa bzhir 'dus /
NK123(go)001:519: yo ga 'og ma gsum yang a ti yo ga la 'dus /
NK123(go)001:520: a ti ni thig le nyag gcig bya rtsol dang bral ba'i ngang du ye nas gnas te /
NK123(go)001:522: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab cing //
NK123(go)001:523: rgya mtsho'i ngang du rol gcig gnas pa ltar //
NK123(go)001:524: chos rnams rdzogs pa chen por 'dus gsal zhing //
NK123(go)001:525: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK123(go)001:527: theg pa de kun kyang sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje dang /
NK123(go)001:529: dgos ched gnyis kyi dbang gis 'byung ste /
NK123(go)001:530: dgos pa gang la dgos na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa lam lnga dang sa bcu'i sgo nas /
NK123(go)001:531: nyon mongs pa spang ba dang sbyong ba'i rtsol ba byas nas /
NK123(go)001:532: dus bskal pa grangs med pa gsum la sogs pa nas sangs rgyas thob 'dod rnams la dgos /
NK123(go)001:533: ched ni a ti'i grub mtha' sa lam sbyang bgrod pa mi go ba rnams kyi ched du byung /
NK123(go)001:535: gsang sngags phyi nang gi sgor zhugs pa rnams la dgos /
NK123(go)001:536: ched ni bsnyen sgrub bzhis dngos grub sgrub tu med
NK123(go)001:537: de ye grol chen po'i don rtogs pa'i ched du
NK123(go)001:539: sa dang lam la spang zhing sbyang ba dang //
NK123(go)001:540: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis rtsol zhing sgrub pa dang //
NK123(go)001:541: phyi nang sgo phug byed pa'i tshi chad pas //
NK123(go)001:542: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK123(go)001:544: de la a nu man chad kyi gol sgril ni sems kyi rtsal cir yang shar bas te /
NK123(go)001:545: sems skye ba med pa las rtsal 'gag med du
NK123(go)001:546: shar bas rang snang stong pa yin par ma shes
NK123(go)001:547: pas / da lta'i snang ba 'di thams cad sems can spyi mthun gyi las las grub /
NK123(go)001:548: bde sdug thams cad sngon gyi las las byung bar
NK123(go)001:549: lta bas 'jig rten lha mi'i theg par gol lo
NK123(go)001:550: // 'o na rdzogs chen pas lta ba de spong ngam zhe na /
NK123(go)001:551: ched du mi spong ste sems kyi rtsal ma 'gag
NK123(go)001:552: pa so so skye bo lha ma'i theg pa ltar
NK123(go)001:553: shar yang / de ltar ma grub ste /
NK123(go)001:554: de la snang ba dang las rang rgyud pa med de gnyis med rang grol ba'o //
NK123(go)001:555: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK123(go)001:556: ci ste las kyis dbang gyur na //
NK123(go)001:557: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK123(go)001:558: zhes las kyi ngo bo med par gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:560: sems stong pa de'i rtsal ma 'gag pas mu stegs rtag chad ltar shar /
NK123(go)001:561: nyan thos pa'i gang zag gi bdag med /
NK123(go)001:562: rang rgyal gyi bdag med phyed dang gnyis /
NK123(go)001:563: sems tsam pa'i thams cad sems su lta ba /
NK123(go)001:565: kri y+aa pa kun rdzob lha'i dkyil 'khor don dam dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba /
NK123(go)001:567: yo ga'i don dam mtha' bral kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK123(go)001:568: ma h+aa yo ga'i bden gnyis dbyer med /
NK123(go)001:569: a nu'i dbyings dang ye shes te /
NK123(go)001:570: sems kyi rtsal ma 'gag pas theg pa de dag gi lta ba ltar shar ba yin kyang /
NK123(go)001:571: lta ba de dang de dag tu blta ba'i mtha' dang bral te /
NK123(go)001:572: mtha' bral thig le nyag gcig de'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK123(go)001:573: rtsal 'gag pa med pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK123(go)001:574: de theg pa 'og ma de rnams kyi lta spyod
NK123(go)001:578: mi sgrub pa'i don yin no //
NK123(go)001:579: de yang rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs na theg
NK123(go)001:580: pa la mtho dman med pas mnyam pa nyid du
NK123(go)001:582: zhes mkhas mchog sog bzlog pas gsungs shing zhib par mkhas mchog 'di nyid dang /
NK123(go)001:583: thams cad mkhyen pa kahthoga pa tshe dbang mchog grub sogs kyi gsungs las shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:584: gnyis pa bye brag so so'i rnam bzhag rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:585: rdzogs pa chen po'i rgyud rig pa rang shar las /
NK123(go)001:586: kye ho gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK123(go)001:587: nga yi theg pa bsam yas kyang //
NK123(go)001:588: bshad lugs rnam pa gnyis su 'du //
NK123(go)001:592: gnyis ni rnam pa'i bye brag ste //
NK123(go)001:593: theg pa rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK123(go)001:594: 'jig rten pa yi theg pa dang //
NK123(go)001:599: mtha' yas dkyil 'khor ma lus kun //
NK123(go)001:601: 'jig rten pa'i theg pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa dngos bshad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:604: sbyin pa ni 'jig rten pa la'ang yod /
NK123(go)001:605: 'jig rten las 'das pa la'ang yod do //
NK123(go)001:606: de'ang 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK123(go)001:607: gang sbyin pa byin pas 'jig rten las mi g.yo mi 'phag /
NK123(go)001:608: mi 'da' na 'jig rten pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:609: gang sbyin pa byin pas 'jig rten las g.yo 'phags /
NK123(go)001:610: 'da' na 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:612: thabs gang gis mthar phyin par bsgrubs pas 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:613: 'jig rten las 'phags nus mi nus kyi khyad par
NK123(go)001:614: ro // de la thog mar 'jig rten pa'i theg pa la'ang /
NK123(go)001:615: sor bzhag lha ma'i theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:616: 'phros don ma rtogs log rtogs kyi lta ba bshad pa gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:617: dang po ni spyir lang gshegs sogs las lha yi
NK123(go)001:618: theg pa dang tshangs pa'i theg pa zhes gnyis su
NK123(go)001:619: gsungs kyang / 'dir ni rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK123(go)001:620: lha dang mi theg yi pa dang //
NK123(go)001:621: zhes gcig tu bsdus te gsungs pa bzhin du /
NK123(go)001:622: de gnyis mnyam por 'chad pa la /
NK123(go)001:623: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i sgyu 'phrul lam gyi rim pa las /
NK123(go)001:624: gzhi yi theg pa dang por zhog /
NK123(go)001:626: 'di la nges 'byung gzhi yi theg pa zhes kyang
NK123(go)001:627: bya ste theg pa thams cad kyi gazhi'am phyi mi
NK123(go)001:629: yang dag pa'i lta bas ma zin pa dang dngos
NK123(go)001:630: gzhi dge bcu'i las la mi spyod pa'i theg pa
NK123(go)001:631: ni gang yang med pa'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:632: sa snying 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:633: gang la mtho ris theg pa yod min //
NK123(go)001:634: de la nyan thos theg pa med de //
NK123(go)001:635: gang la nyan thos theg pa yod min //
NK123(go)001:636: de la rang rgyal theg pa med de //
NK123(go)001:637: gang la rang rgyal theg pa yod min //
NK123(go)001:638: de la theg pa chen po med de //
NK123(go)001:641: dge ba bcu las brtsam nas ni //
NK123(go)001:642: de yi chos ni rab tu dbye //
NK123(go)001:644: 'phags pa klus rin chen phreng ba las /
NK123(go)001:645: dang po mngon par mtho'i chos //
NK123(go)001:646: phyis ni nges par legs 'byung ba //
NK123(go)001:647: gang phyir mngon par mtho thob nas //
NK123(go)001:648: rim gyis nges par legs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:654: de ltar yang bde gshegs 'dus pa'i rgyud kyi spyi chings chen mo'i le'u dang por /
NK123(go)001:655: re re'ang ngo bo nges tshig dang /
NK123(go)001:656: dbye ba zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:657: de las dang po ngo bo ni spyir 'dod khams
NK123(go)001:658: kyi lha dang mi yi bde ba tsam dang bye
NK123(go)001:659: brag khams gong ma'i bde ba mthar thug pa'i bar
NK123(go)001:660: du 'god pa'i thabs gang zhig 'khor ba las 'phags
NK123(go)001:663: ma nu sha y+aa zhes pa'i sgra las mi'i theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:664: de ba y+aa na las lha'i theg pa zhes 'byung ste /
NK123(go)001:665: de la sgra yangs pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK123(go)001:666: spyir lha mi dang bye brag khams gong ma gnyis
NK123(go)001:667: kyis sa bsdus pa thams cad la tshangs pa'i sgra
NK123(go)001:668: 'jug par 'phags pa rnam grol sdes bshad pa ltar
NK123(go)001:669: de dang de yi bde 'bras tsam la sbyor zhing
NK123(go)001:680: 'jug sgo lta ba tshul khrims dang //
NK123(go)001:681: sgom pa phrin las 'bras bu rnams //
NK123(go)001:682: rim pa bzhin du shes bya ste //
NK123(go)001:683: zhes gsungs te 'og ma rnams la'ang shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:684: de las dang po 'jug sgo ni /
NK123(go)001:685: spyir ngan song gsum sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin can du mthong nas /
NK123(go)001:686: der skye ba'i rgyu mi dge ba'i las spong ba'i
NK123(go)001:687: sgo nas 'jug cing bye brag tu khams gong ma
NK123(go)001:688: rnams su ni 'dod khams sogs sa 'og ma'i skyon
NK123(go)001:689: dang gong ma'i yon tan rnams mthong ba'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:690: / sa 'og ma'i skyon nam sgrib pa rnams 'jig
NK123(go)001:691: rten pa'i lam gyis mgo mnon gyi tshul gyis spong
NK123(go)001:692: ba'i sgo nas rim gyis 'jug par byed de /
NK123(go)001:693: he ru ka gal po che las /
NK123(go)001:694: lha'i theg pas mi dge spang //
NK123(go)001:696: de la mi dge ba bcu ni /
NK123(go)001:698: bcu po de dag gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:699: lus kyi dbye ba rnam pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:700: ngag gi dbye ba rnam pa bzhi //
NK123(go)001:701: yid kyi rab tu dbye ba gsum //
NK123(go)001:702: mi dge bcu ru de dag 'dod //
NK123(go)001:703: de rnams rab tu bshad par bya //
NK123(go)001:704: de la re zhig lus kyi ni //
NK123(go)001:705: srog gcod ma byin len log g.yem //
NK123(go)001:706: ngag gi rdzun tshig phra ma dang //
NK123(go)001:707: tshig rtsub dang ni 'khyal ba rnams //
NK123(go)001:708: yid kyi log lta brnab sems gnod //
NK123(go)001:709: de la srog gcod gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:710: srog dang ldan par gyur pa la //
NK123(go)001:711: srog dang ldan par 'du shes dang //
NK123(go)001:712: gsod sems nye bar gnas pa dang //
NK123(go)001:713: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
NK123(go)001:714: srog ni gcod par gyur pa ste //
NK123(go)001:715: yan lag lnga po de dag dang //
NK123(go)001:716: ldan pa srog gcod yin par bshad //
NK123(go)001:717: ma byin len pa gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:718: gzhan dag gi ni yin pa dang //
NK123(go)001:719: gzhan gyis bdag gir byas pa dang //
NK123(go)001:720: gzhan gyis yin par 'du shes dang //
NK123(go)001:721: rku sems nye bar gnas pa dad //
NK123(go)001:722: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
NK123(go)001:723: gnas nas spags par gyur pa ste //
NK123(go)001:724: yan lag drug po de dag dang //
NK123(go)001:725: ldan pa ma byin len par bshad //
NK123(go)001:726: de la log g.yem gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:727: log par g.yem pa rnam bzhi ste //
NK123(go)001:728: yul min pa dang dus min dang //
NK123(go)001:729: yan lag ma yin bsgrod min yin //
NK123(go)001:730: de la'ang yul min bya ba ni //
NK123(go)001:731: dam chos mchod rten sku gzugs dang //
NK123(go)001:732: byang chub sems dpa'i gzhugs gnas sogs //
NK123(go)001:733: mkhan po dang ni slob dpon dang //
NK123(go)001:734: pha ma drung na gnas pa ni //
NK123(go)001:735: yul min de ru mi bya'o //
NK123(go)001:736: de la dus min bya ba ni //
NK123(go)001:737: zla mtshan 'dzag dang sbrum ma dang //
NK123(go)001:738: bu chung dang bcas mi mo dang //
NK123(go)001:739: sdug bsngal yid mi bde sogs dang //
NK123(go)001:740: yan lag brgyad gnas dus min yin //
NK123(go)001:741: yan lag min pa gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:742: kha dang bshang lam byin pa dang //
NK123(go)001:743: barla bsdam lag par bskyod pa yin //
NK123(go)001:744: bsgrod par bya min zhes bya ni //
NK123(go)001:745: gzhan bzung chos kyi rgyal mtshan ldan //
NK123(go)001:746: rigs kyis bsrung dang rgyal mor gnas //
NK123(go)001:747: gzhan gyis blangs dang smad 'tshong dang //
NK123(go)001:748: nye du dag dang 'brel ba ni //
NK123(go)001:749: de dag bgrod bya min pa yin //
NK123(go)001:750: rnam pa de dag rnams la ni //
NK123(go)001:751: rang gi chung ma brten pa dang //
NK123(go)001:753: brdzun du smra ba gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:754: dngos po gnas par 'gyur ba dang //
NK123(go)001:755: dngos po las ni nyams gyur dang //
NK123(go)001:756: 'du shes gzhan du bsgyur ba dang //
NK123(go)001:757: brdzun du smra bar gyur pa dang //
NK123(go)001:758: rim pa bzhin du byas ldan dang //
NK123(go)001:759: yan lag lnga po de dag dang //
NK123(go)001:760: ldan pa brdzun du smra ba 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:761: de la phra ma gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:762: gzhag dag dbye phyir phra ma yin //
NK123(go)001:763: de la tshig rtsub gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:764: gzhan gyi gnad du bsnun byed pa'i //
NK123(go)001:765: yid du mi 'ong tshig smra yin //
NK123(go)001:766: de la khyab pa gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:767: 'dod pas nye bar blang ba dang //
NK123(go)001:768: chags la yis ni nyer bskyed nas //
NK123(go)001:770: de la brnab sems gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:771: gzhan gyi nor dang longs spyod la //
NK123(go)001:772: mchog tu mngon par chags pa yin //
NK123(go)001:773: gnod sems zhes bya gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:774: sems can rnams la sdang pa yin //
NK123(go)001:775: brdeg dang 'ching dang gsod pa ste //
NK123(go)001:776: de dag sems can la byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:777: log lta zhes bya gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:778: sbyin med mchod sbyin yod min dang //
NK123(go)001:779: 'jig rten pha rol yod min zhing //
NK123(go)001:780: dge sbyor bram ze lha rnams med //
NK123(go)001:781: rdzogs sangs rgyas dang dgra bcom dang //
NK123(go)001:782: rang sangs rgyas dang legs spyod dang //
NK123(go)001:783: nyes pa spyod pa yod min zhes //
NK123(go)001:784: bya ba log par lta ba yin //
NK123(go)001:785: 'phags pa dran pa nyer bzhag dang //
NK123(go)001:786: theg pa chen po'i mdo rnams las //
NK123(go)001:787: bcom ldan 'das kyi rgyas gsungs pa //
NK123(go)001:788: 'di ni mdo ru bsdus pa yin //
NK123(go)001:789: mi dge las kyi lam bcu ni //
NK123(go)001:790: dmyal ba chen po'i rgyu ru bshad //
NK123(go)001:792: de dag rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa gang gis rdzogs par byed na /
NK123(go)001:793: chos mngon pa'i tshig le'u byas pa las /
NK123(go)001:794: gsod dang gnod sems tshig rtsub dag /
NK123(go)001:795: zhe sdang gis ni mthar phyin byed //
NK123(go)001:796: log g.yem brnab sems ma byin len //
NK123(go)001:797: chags pa yis ni mthar phyin byed //
NK123(go)001:798: log par lta ba gti mug gis //
NK123(go)001:799: lhag ma gsum gyis rdzogs par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:801: de'i rnam smin 'bras bu ni ngan song gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:803: srog gcod pas ni sems can dmyal bar 'khrid do //
NK123(go)001:804: byol song gi skye gnas su 'khrid do //
NK123(go)001:806: zhes sogs thams cad la sbyar te gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:807: rgyu mthun la gnyis kyi byed pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK123(go)001:809: de mi dge ba kun tu spyod pa la goms shing 'dris par byas pas /
NK123(go)001:810: phyir yang mi dge ba la brten /
NK123(go)001:812: mi dge ba'i rjes su 'jug pa nyid du skye ste /
NK123(go)001:814: mi dge ba gang la goms pa de la tshe rabs kun tu rang bzhin gyis spro ba'o //
NK123(go)001:818: rnam par 'tshe bas gnod pa mang //
NK123(go)001:819: brku ba yis ni longs spyod phongs //
NK123(go)001:820: byi bo byed las dgra zlar bcas //
NK123(go)001:821: rdzun du smra ba'i skur pa ste //
NK123(go)001:822: phra ma yi ni bshes dang dbye //
NK123(go)001:823: rtsub mo nyid kyi mi snyan thos //
NK123(go)001:824: ma 'brel ba yi tshig mi btsun //
NK123(go)001:825: brnab sems yid la re ba 'joms //
NK123(go)001:826: gnod sems 'jigs pa sbyin pa bshad //
NK123(go)001:827: log par lta bas lta ngan nyid //
NK123(go)001:830: phyi rol yul la smin te /
NK123(go)001:832: phyi rol gzi chung gnod pa mang //
NK123(go)001:833: rdul 'khrigs dri ma mtho dman can //
NK123(go)001:834: tsh+wa sgo can dang log pa dang //
NK123(go)001:835: 'bras bu phra kha chung ngam med //
NK123(go)001:837: zhar byung dge sdig gi 'bras bu rnams smin pa'i snga phyi yang /
NK123(go)001:839: las ni 'khor bar lci gang dang //
NK123(go)001:840: nye ba gang dang goms pa gang //
NK123(go)001:841: sngon byas gang yin de las ni //
NK123(go)001:842: snga ma snga ma rnam smin 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:843: zhes las gang stobs che ba dang /
NK123(go)001:844: de mnyam na 'chi kha'i dge sdig gi sems gang gsal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:845: de mnyam na goms shas gang che dang /
NK123(go)001:846: de yang mnyam na sngar byas pa de'i 'bras bu sngon du smin par gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:848: 'jig rten pa'i yang dag pa'i lta ba zhes bya ba 'jig rten pha rol yod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:849: las rgyu 'bras la mi bslu bar yid ches pa ste /
NK123(go)001:850: ched du brjod pa'i tshom las /
NK123(go)001:851: 'jig rten pa yi yang dag lta //
NK123(go)001:852: chen po gang la yod gyur pa //
NK123(go)001:853: de ni tshe rabs stong du yang //
NK123(go)001:856: de lta bu'i lta ba'am rgyu 'bras yid ches kyi
NK123(go)001:857: dad pa ni las 'bras med par lta ba sogs
NK123(go)001:858: log par lta ba rnams kyi gnyen po yin pas
NK123(go)001:860: de las ldog ste log par lta bas srog gcod
NK123(go)001:861: spangs ba sogs dge ba'i las gzhan la sbyar kyang
NK123(go)001:862: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal du smin par
NK123(go)001:864: gal te mtho ris thar pa mngon bzhed na //
NK123(go)001:865: yang dag lta la goms pa nyid du mdzod //
NK123(go)001:866: gang zag log par lta bas legs spyad kyang //
NK123(go)001:867: thams cad rnam par smin pa mi bzad ldan //
NK123(go)001:870: yang dag pa'i lta ba de nyid kyis zin pa'i
NK123(go)001:871: mi dge bcu spong gi tshul khrims sdom pa'i ngo
NK123(go)001:873: bye brag bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'i dus khrims te /
NK123(go)001:875: 'tshe dang chom rkun 'khrigs pa brdzun dang ni //
NK123(go)001:876: chang dang dus min zas la chags pa dang //
NK123(go)001:877: mal stan mtho la dga' dang glu dag dang //
NK123(go)001:878: gal dang phreng ba'i khyad par rnams spong zhing //
NK123(go)001:879: dgra bcom tshul khrims rjes su byed pa yi //
NK123(go)001:880: yan lag brgyad po 'di dag dang ldan na //
NK123(go)001:881: gso sbyong 'dod spyod lha lus yid 'ong ba //
NK123(go)001:882: skyes pa bud med dag pa stsol bar bgyi //
NK123(go)001:885: dge bcu'i las kyi lam bsten pas //
NK123(go)001:886: dmyal la sogs par ltung ma yin //
NK123(go)001:888: des na blang dor gyi gnas ma 'dzol ba'i tshul khrims la gnas pa gal che ste /
NK123(go)001:890: tshul khrims kyis ni bde 'gro thob //
NK123(go)001:893: mngon mtho'i rgyu ni tshul khrims las gzhan med //
NK123(go)001:896: spyir rang rang gi 'bras bu 'byin nus kyi bar du goms par byed pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:897: bye brag khams gong gnyis su skye ba la /
NK123(go)001:898: rang rang gis 'og ma la chags pa bral byed kyi lam bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:899: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi bsgom pa ste /
NK123(go)001:900: ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:901: bsam gtan dang po la nyer bsdogs dang dngos gzhi gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:902: dang po bsam gtan rang sa'i 'bras bu thob byed
NK123(go)001:903: dngos gzhi la snyoms par 'jug nus pa'i thabs su
NK123(go)001:904: thog mar rgyu bsgrub pa nyer bsdogs sems zhi bar
NK123(go)001:905: gnas pa'i thabs dgus ting nge 'dzin sgrub par gsungs
NK123(go)001:906: te / de la nang nyid du sems 'jog pa zhes pa /
NK123(go)001:907: sems phyi rol du g.yeng ba min par gser ltar
NK123(go)001:908: dwangs pa'i skur snang ba sogs ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK123(go)001:909: spyod yul gyi gzugs brnyan dmigs pa la yid gtad
NK123(go)001:911: rgyun du 'jog pa zhes pa dmigs pa la sems 'jog pa tsam du ma zad rgyun bsring ste /
NK123(go)001:912: skad cig ma snga phyi bar ma chad par 'jog pa dang /
NK123(go)001:913: bslan te 'jog pa zhes pa brjed de dmigs pa
NK123(go)001:914: las sems gzhan du 'phro na'ang de ma thag tu
NK123(go)001:915: slar nang du bkug nas dmigs pa la bslan te
NK123(go)001:916: 'jog pa dang / nye bar 'jog pa zhes pa
NK123(go)001:917: sems phyir 'phros pa de ring du mi 'jog par
NK123(go)001:918: nye bar nang du dmigs pa la 'jog pa dang
NK123(go)001:919: 'jog pa dang / / 'dul bar byed pa zhes
NK123(go)001:920: pa brnab sems la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pas sems
NK123(go)001:921: rgyud rab tu ma zhi ba las dul bar byed
NK123(go)001:922: 'jog pa dang / / pa dang / zhi bar
NK123(go)001:923: byed pa zhes pa rnam par rtog pa'i rba rlabs
NK123(go)001:925: rnam par zhi bar byed pa zhes pa rnam par
NK123(go)001:926: rtog pa phra mo tsam yang zhi bar byed pa
NK123(go)001:927: dang / rtse gcig tu byed pa zhes pa rtsol
NK123(go)001:928: chung ngus sems dang dmigs pa tha dad med par
NK123(go)001:929: rtse gcig tu byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:930: mnyam par 'jog pa zhes pa bying sgod bsal nas
NK123(go)001:931: rtsol ba med par lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du
NK123(go)001:932: mnyam par 'jog pa dang dgus ting nge 'dzin grub
NK123(go)001:933: pa na lus sems shin tu sbyangs pa'i bde ba
NK123(go)001:935: shin sbyang dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin skyes pa
NK123(go)001:936: ni 'jig rten pa'i zhi gnas mtshan nyid par 'jog
NK123(go)001:937: la / de dang mi ldan pa ni zhi gnas rjes mthun pa'am /
NK123(go)001:938: mos pas spyod pa'i sa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:939: de lta bu'i zhi gnas mtshan nyid pa grub nas /
NK123(go)001:940: yid byed bdun gyis 'jig rten pa'i lhag mthong sgrub ste /
NK123(go)001:941: mtshan nyid rab tu rig pa yid la byed pa
NK123(go)001:942: zhes 'dod sa pa'i sems ni rags dang ma zhi
NK123(go)001:943: ba sogs skyon can dang bsam gtan dang po ni
NK123(go)001:944: zhi ba dang bde ba sogs yon tan can du
NK123(go)001:945: thos bsam 'dres ma'i sgo nas rtsing por rtog cing
NK123(go)001:947: mos pa las byung ba yid la byed pa zhes
NK123(go)001:948: pa de nyid sgom byung gi ngo bor skyes pa
NK123(go)001:949: dang / dben pa las skyes pa'i yid la byed
NK123(go)001:950: pa zhes pa 'dod nyon mngon gyur pa chen po
NK123(go)001:952: dga' bsdud pa yid la byed pa zhes pa 'dod
NK123(go)001:953: nyon mngon gyur pa 'bring po gsum spangs pa dang
NK123(go)001:954: / dpyod pa yid la byed pa zhes pa 'dod
NK123(go)001:955: nyon phra mo gsum gyis kyang rgyud la gos ma
NK123(go)001:956: gos rtog cing dpyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:957: sbyor ba'i mtha' yid la byed pa zhes pa de
NK123(go)001:958: ltar dpyod pa las 'dod nyon phra zhing phra ba
NK123(go)001:959: yang gnyen po'i stobs kyis spangs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:960: de ltar yid la byed pa drug gis sbyor ba'i
NK123(go)001:961: matha'i 'bras bu yid la byed pa zhes 'jig rten
NK123(go)001:962: pa'i lhag mthong mthar thug 'grub ste /
NK123(go)001:963: de yang 'dod nyon che 'bring drug spangs pa'i bar ni bsam gtan gyi nyer bsdogs dang /
NK123(go)001:964: chung ngu gsum spangs pa'i tshe na bsam gtan dngos gzhi'i sems thob pa'o //
NK123(go)001:965: de dag ni 'og sa'i ting 'dzin skyon can rags
NK123(go)001:966: par lta zhing sa gong ma skyon med zhi bar
NK123(go)001:967: lta ba zhi rags rnam pa can nyan rang dang
NK123(go)001:968: 'jig rten pa'i thun mong pa'i lam gyis mngon rtogs
NK123(go)001:969: so // gnyis pa dngos gzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:970: rtog dpyod gnyis gnyen po'i yan lag te 'di gnyis
NK123(go)001:971: kyis 'dod khams pa'i sems 'dod 'dun gnod sems rnam
NK123(go)001:973: dga' ba de gnyis phan yon gyi yan lag /
NK123(go)001:974: sems rtse gcig pa gnas kyi yan lag ste /
NK123(go)001:975: de la brten nas phan yon 'byung bas so //
NK123(go)001:976: de ltar yan lag lnga dang ldan pa ni bsam gtan dang po'i mtshan nyid do //
NK123(go)001:977: de la rtog dpyod gnyis ka dang ldan pa dngos gzhi tsam po ba /
NK123(go)001:978: rtog pa med cing dpyod pa dang bcas pa dngos gzhi khyad par can no //
NK123(go)001:981: bsam gtan dang po'i dngos gzhi khyad par can gzhir
NK123(go)001:982: bzhag de nyid skyon can dang bsam gtan gnyis pa
NK123(go)001:983: skyon med yon tan can du mtshan nyid rab tu
NK123(go)001:984: rig pa'i yid byed sogs yid byed bdun gyis dngos
NK123(go)001:985: gzhi'i sems thob par byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:986: des mtshon nas srid rtse'i bar du zhi rags rnam
NK123(go)001:987: can du bltas te yid byed bdun gyis sgrub tshul
NK123(go)001:988: de ltar shes par bya dgos so //
NK123(go)001:989: de la yid byed dang po gnyis rang lam de'i sbyor lam dang /
NK123(go)001:990: rab dben dga' sdud sbyor mtha' gsum gyi nyon mongs
NK123(go)001:991: pa che 'bring chung ngu'i gnyen po byed pas bar
NK123(go)001:994: sbyor 'bras yid byed rnam grol gyi lam mo //
NK123(go)001:995: bsam gtan gnyis pa'i dngos gzhi la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:996: nang rab tu dwangs ba ni rtog dpyod spong ba'i gnyen po'i yan lag ste /
NK123(go)001:997: 'og ma'i skyon las nges par 'byung ba'i rang sa la rab tu dad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:998: ting nge 'dzin las skyes pa'i dga' bde gnyis ni phan yon gyi yan lag /
NK123(go)001:999: ting nge 'dzin ni gnas kyi yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:1000: bsam gtan gsum pa'i dngos gzhi la yan lag lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:1001: 'du byed btang snyoms dang sgom pa mi brjed pa'i dran pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1002: dran bzhin du gnas pa'i shes bzhin gsum ni 'og ma'i dga' ba spong ba'i gnyen pa'i yan lag /
NK123(go)001:1003: lus tshor dang shin sbyang las byung ba'i bde ba phan yon gyi yan lag /
NK123(go)001:1004: ting nge 'dzin gnas kyi yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:1005: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i dngos gzhi la yan lag bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:1006: sa 'og ma'i skyon brgyad dang bral ba'i dran pa yongs su dag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1007: 'du byed btang snyoms yongs su dag pa gnyis ni
NK123(go)001:1008: bsam gtan gsum pa'i bde ba spong ba'i gnyen po'i
NK123(go)001:1009: yan lag / tshor ba btang snyoms pa ni phan yon gyi yan lag /
NK123(go)001:1010: ting nge 'dzin yongs su dag pa brten gyi yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:1011: skyon brgyad ni bsam gtan dang po la yod pa'i rtog dpyod gnyis /
NK123(go)001:1012: gsum pa man chad na yod pa'i dbugs 'byin rngub
NK123(go)001:1013: gnyis 'dod pa na yod pa'i sdug bsngal dang yid
NK123(go)001:1015: gnyis pa man chad du yod pa'i yid bde /
NK123(go)001:1016: gsum pa'i bde ba ste de brgyad dang bral ba'i
NK123(go)001:1017: phyir rlung med pa'i mar me ltar g.yo ba med
NK123(go)001:1018: cing shin tu rnam par dag pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1019: gang smos sems gnas dgu pa 'dod sems rtse gcig pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1020: bsam gtan dang po la tsam khyad gnyis su phye
NK123(go)001:1021: ba'i drug po gang la brten kyang zag med 'jig
NK123(go)001:1022: rten las 'das pa'i lam gyi dngos gzhi sgrub nus
NK123(go)001:1023: pas bsam gtan sa drug zhes kyang bshad do //
NK123(go)001:1024: gzugs med kyi snyoms 'jug bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:1025: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i 'du shes la'ang yid 'byung ba'i mtshan nyid can te /
NK123(go)001:1026: bye brag tu gzugs kyi 'du shes med par nam mkha' tsam mtha' yas so zhes /
NK123(go)001:1027: de tsam la snyoms par 'jug pa goms pa yongs
NK123(go)001:1028: su rdzogs pa nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched kyi
NK123(go)001:1030: nam mkha' tsam gyi 'du shes de yang bkag nas
NK123(go)001:1031: rnam shes tsam du 'du shes pa rnam shes mtha'
NK123(go)001:1032: yas / de yang bkag ste ci yang med pa'i 'du shes la gnas pa ci yang med pa /
NK123(go)001:1033: de yang bkag ste yod min med min tsam du
NK123(go)001:1034: gnas pa 'du shes med 'du shes med min gyi
NK123(go)001:1035: snyoms 'jug gam srid rtse'i snyom 'jug ste de bzhi'o
NK123(go)001:1036: // de ltar bsam gzugs brgyad po de zag med
NK123(go)001:1037: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i shes rab lhag mthong dang
NK123(go)001:1038: ma 'brel na zag bcas 'jig rten pa'i lam ste
NK123(go)001:1039: // / byis pa nyer spyod kyi bsam gtan zhes kyang bya la /
NK123(go)001:1040: bsam gtan bzhi'i dngos gzhi rnams la brten nas /
NK123(go)001:1041: byams sogs tshad med bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:1042: 'jig rten pa'i mngon shes lha'i mig dang lha'i rna
NK123(go)001:1043: ba dang gzhan gyi sems shes pa dang sngon gnas
NK123(go)001:1044: rjes su dran pa dang 'chi 'pho skye ba shes
NK123(go)001:1045: pa ste / lnga ni khams gong ma'i yon tan gyi khyad par rab tu grags pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:1046: theg pa la zhugs pa rnams kyang thog mar ting
NK123(go)001:1047: nge 'dzin de dag dang yon tan de dag bskyed
NK123(go)001:1048: nas / slar gong ma'i khyad par bsgrub dgos pas
NK123(go)001:1049: mngon shes la sogs pa'i yon tan kun gyi gzhir
NK123(go)001:1050: nas / gyur pa dang / khyad par bsam gtan
NK123(go)001:1051: bzhi pa'i dngos gzhi la brten nas zag med 'phags
NK123(go)001:1052: pa'i lam sgrub na gzugs med lta bu ha cang
NK123(go)001:1053: zhi gnas shas che bas mi gsal ba yang min
NK123(go)001:1054: nas / gyur pa dang / la / gsum pa
NK123(go)001:1055: sogs 'og sa ltar g.yo ba phra mo'i skyon kyang
NK123(go)001:1056: med pas rab kyi mtha' zhes bya ste mchog tu
NK123(go)001:1057: nas / gyur pa dang / la / gyur pa
NK123(go)001:1058: dang / der ma zad srid rtse'i dngos gzhi'i sems
NK123(go)001:1059: la brten nas kyang 'phags pa rnams 'du shes dang
NK123(go)001:1060: tshor ba 'gog pa 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug thob pa
NK123(go)001:1061: nas / gyur pa dang / la / gyur pa
NK123(go)001:1062: dang / sogs kyis / phyi rol gyi drang srong
NK123(go)001:1064: nang pa'i theg dman nyan thos dang rang rgyal gyis
NK123(go)001:1065: kyang don du gnyer bya dang bsgrub bya yin la
NK123(go)001:1066: / rgyal ba'i bstan pa la rim par 'jug pa
NK123(go)001:1067: rnams kyi sngon 'gro'i chos kyang yin pas shes nas
NK123(go)001:1068: gom pa'i sbyor ba la bslab par bya ba yin
NK123(go)001:1069: / no // lnga pa spyod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:1070: zag pa dang bcas pa'i dge bcu'i las lam dang 'khor bcas la spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1071: de ni mi dge ba cu spangs pa'i cha nas btags te /
NK123(go)001:1073: mi gsod pa dang rku spong dang //
NK123(go)001:1074: gzhan gyi chung ma spong ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1075: log dang phra ma rtsub nyid dang //
NK123(go)001:1076: ma 'brel smra ba yang dag sdom //
NK123(go)001:1077: chags dang gnod sems med pa pa //
NK123(go)001:1078: nyid kyi lta ba yongs spong ba //
NK123(go)001:1079: 'di dag las lam dkar bcu ste //
NK123(go)001:1081: gzhan yang lus kyi phyag bskor ngag gi kha ton
NK123(go)001:1082: yid kyi phan sems sogs sgo gsum dge la ci
NK123(go)001:1085: bskur bar 'os pa legs khur zhing //
NK123(go)001:1086: mgon med rnams la lhag par byams //
NK123(go)001:1087: byas pa drin lan mi brjed pa //
NK123(go)001:1088: dam pa rnams kyis mdzod spyod yin //
NK123(go)001:1089: zhes pa'i ya rabs dang mthun pa'i spyod pa gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:1091: dkon mchog gsum la dad pa skyo ngal med par byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1092: don dam bar dam pa'i chos brtsal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1093: gtsug lag bzang po la mkhas par slob pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1094: ci la'ang ran cing tshod zin par bya ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1095: ma bcol ba'i las la gtogs 'dod mi byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1096: mig mtho sar blta zhing gong ma rnams kyi rjes snyeg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1097: dus gsum gyi pha ma la drin lan bslan pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1098: phu nu dang pha mtshan nang du shongs yongs che ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1099: rim pas rgan pa la bskur sti bya ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1100: khyim mtshes la byams par bya ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1101: gnyan grogs kyi dge bshes la dka' las kyis phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1102: srid kyis 'brel ba'i nye ring la chab gang mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1103: rig byed bzo la mkhas pas phan pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1104: ltos pa'i mi drin gyis skyabs 'og tu gzhugs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1105: ngan byed kyi gros bkag nas rgyal khams bde yangs kyi gros gzhi 'ding ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1106: las mtha' chos la gtad de phyi mar bu smad
NK123(go)001:1107: kyi zhes pas pha ma sogs khyim gza' tshong tshang
NK123(go)001:1110: bu smad kyis byang chub kyi gzhi thob par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:1111: zhes bshad pa ltar mi chos gtsang ma bcu drug la bslab pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1112: bye brag tu tshangs ris sogs su skye ba la
NK123(go)001:1113: byams snying rje dag 'a ba btang snyoms te tshangs
NK123(go)001:1114: pa'i gnas pa bzhi la spyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1115: yi ge 'dri mchod sogs chos spyod bcu bslab par yang he ru ka gal po las gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:1117: spyir bsam gzugs kyi ting nge 'dzin dang ma 'brel
NK123(go)001:1118: ba'i zag bcas kyi dge ba'i las stobs che chung
NK123(go)001:1120: 'dod lha rigs drug ste mtho ris kyi gnas bcur skye ste /
NK123(go)001:1122: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spongs byed pa //
NK123(go)001:1123: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK123(go)001:1126: dge bcu dag la gtsor len cing //
NK123(go)001:1127: dge dang mi dge mi nyams pas //
NK123(go)001:1128: lha dang mi yi skye gnas te //
NK123(go)001:1129: mnyam nyid ma rtogs 'dod khams khor //
NK123(go)001:1131: de'ang 'dis 'dod pa'i bde ba mthar thug pa mi'i 'khor los bsgyur rgyal dang /
NK123(go)001:1132: lha'i gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bdag po'i bar bgrod pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1133: lang gshegs su bgrod bya'i gtso bo'i sgras smos te lha'i theg pa zhes gsungs /
NK123(go)001:1134: bye brag tu gzugs gzugs med kyi snyoms 'jug la
NK123(go)001:1135: goms pa las ni 'bras bu skye ba'i bsam gtan
NK123(go)001:1136: zhes rang sa'i 'bras bu skyed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1137: de yang bsam gtan bzhi las /
NK123(go)001:1138: bsam gtan dang po'i snyoms 'jug chung ngur goms pas tshangs ris /
NK123(go)001:1139: 'bring du goms pas tshangs pa 'dun na 'don /
NK123(go)001:1140: cher goms pas tshangs chen te bsam gtan dang po'i gnas ris gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:1141: de bzhin du bsam gtan gnyis pa'i snyoms 'jug chung 'bring cher goms pa gsum gyis /
NK123(go)001:1151: 'bras bu che ste so skye'i gnas bcu gnyis su skyes pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:1152: bsam gtan bzhi pa dang zag med 'phags pa'i shes
NK123(go)001:1153: rab spel te bsgoms pa chung 'bring che ba shin
NK123(go)001:1154: tu che ba ches shin tu che ba lnga bsgoms
NK123(go)001:1159: 'og min te gnas gtsang lngar skye bar 'dzin te /
NK123(go)001:1160: 'di lnga la spyir gang zag 'phags pa la /
NK123(go)001:1161: so skye med pa dang zag bcas 'jig rten pa'i
NK123(go)001:1162: lam kho nas bgrod mi nus pas gtsang ma'i gnas
NK123(go)001:1163: ris zhes bshad pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:1164: bye brag yid bzhin mdzod sogs las /
NK123(go)001:1165: sems can rnams thog mar 'khrul ba'i tshe kun gzhi
NK123(go)001:1166: lung ma bstan las rang ngo ma shes pa'i dbang
NK123(go)001:1167: gis 'dzin rtog je rags su gyur pas gong ma
NK123(go)001:1168: las 'oog ma rim gyis mched pa'i phyir 'dir yang
NK123(go)001:1169: so skye'i gang zag yod par bzhed do //
NK123(go)001:1170: gang ltar yang byis pa rnams gzugs la chags bral
NK123(go)001:1171: ma thob cing bsam gtan gyi ro la chags pas
NK123(go)001:1173: tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK123(go)001:1174: rim pas so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK123(go)001:1175: gzugs rnams kun la bdag tu rtog /'di ni tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK123(go)001:1178: lhag mthong gi shes rab kyi dben pas tshor ba dang 'du shes dang /
NK123(go)001:1181: mi bzhi dang ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bdag tu bzung bas gzugs med kyi lhar skye ste /
NK123(go)001:1183: mnyam dang gzugs med ma rtogs nas //
NK123(go)001:1184: ming bzhi med par ma shes te //
NK123(go)001:1185: skye mched bzhi la gnas gyur na //
NK123(go)001:1186: srid pa'i rtse mo'i sa ru skye //
NK123(go)001:1187: zhes gsungs de yang gzugs med khams la gzugs rags
NK123(go)001:1188: pas phye ba'i gnas gzhan tha dad pa med kyang
NK123(go)001:1189: mchog dman dang tshe ring thung dang gong 'og la
NK123(go)001:1190: sogs pa'i sgo nas tha dad du yod la /
NK123(go)001:1191: phal chen dang dus 'khor rdzogs chen sogs nas gnas sogs kyang tha dad du bshad cing /
NK123(go)001:1192: gang ltar gong nas gong du ting nge 'dzin rgya che zhing je brtan du gyur pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1193: tshe ring ba sogs kyi sgo nas mngon mtho'i bde 'bras khyad par du 'phags pa yin zhing /
NK123(go)001:1194: 'di gnyis la lang gshegs las tshangs pa'i theg pa zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:1197: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK123(go)001:1199: 'di la sngon gyi slob dpon rnams dgongs pa mi mthun pa 'ga' zhig snang mod /
NK123(go)001:1201: gu ru rin po ches mdzad pa'i man ngag lta phreng gi dgongs pa ltar na /
NK123(go)001:1202: ma rtogs pa la phyal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1207: de las snga ma gnyis ni so so'i skye bo grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba'i gang zag go //
NK123(go)001:1208: de la 'jig rten phyal ba ni /
NK123(go)001:1209: rten 'byung rgyu 'bras kyi chos yod med gang du'ang
NK123(go)001:1210: mi dpyod cing spong len mi byed pa'i phyir phyal
NK123(go)001:1213: cir yang ma rtogs pa ni 'jig rten phyal ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1215: las rgyu 'bras ye ma rtogs pa'i kun tu rmongs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1217: phyal ba ni chos thams cad rgyu dang 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:1218: yod med du ma rtogs te kun tu rmongs pa'o
NK123(go)001:1221: tshe phyi ma rgyang du bor te tshe 'di'i btsan
NK123(go)001:1222: phyug dang mthu stobs sogs 'jig rten pa'i gsang tshig
NK123(go)001:1223: mo rtsis sogs la brten nas bsgrub pa'i phyir rgyang
NK123(go)001:1225: tshe snga phyi yod med du ma rtogs shing tshe
NK123(go)001:1226: gcig gi phan bde bag tsam sgrub pa'i blo can
NK123(go)001:1227: yin no // de ltar yang lta phreng las /
NK123(go)001:1228: rgyang 'phen pa ni tshe snga phyi yod med du
NK123(go)001:1229: ma rtogs shing tshe gcig gi btsan phyug dang mthu
NK123(go)001:1231: 'jig rten pa'i gsang tshig la brten pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1233: phyi ma gnyis ni rten gyis gang zag gang zhig log pa'i grub mthas blo bsgyur ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1234: de la chad lta mur thug pa ni /
NK123(go)001:1235: chos nyid ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pas 'khrul gzhi byas nas /
NK123(go)001:1236: tshe snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras med par blta ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1237: tshe gcig gi chos thams cad rgyu med glo bur
NK123(go)001:1238: du skye la mtha' chad par blta bas chad pa'i
NK123(go)001:1242: chos thams cad rgyu dang 'bras bu med pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1243: tshe gcig la skyes pa'i chos thams cad glo bur du skyes la mtha' yang chad par blta ba'o //
NK123(go)001:1245: rtag lta mu stegs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:1246: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pas 'khrul gzhi byas nas
NK123(go)001:1247: chos thams cad la bdag yod par blta ba ste
NK123(go)001:1248: / bdag rtag pa gcig pu ba phung po lnga'i rgyun la za ba po dang /
NK123(go)001:1249: byed pa po'i bdag nyid can zhig don dam par yod par 'dod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1250: de yang rang nyid skyed byed kyi rgyu med pa
NK123(go)001:1251: la 'bras bu rtag pa bdag dang gtso bo sogs
NK123(go)001:1253: snod bcud thams cad phya'am dbang phyug la sogs pa
NK123(go)001:1254: rgyu min pa gzhan gyis bskyed par 'dod pa dang
NK123(go)001:1255: / phyugs gsod pa'i mchod sbyin sogs kyis mtho ris
NK123(go)001:1256: thob par 'dod pa sogs rgyu 'bras log par 'dzin
NK123(go)001:1257: / pa dang / rgyu byed pa po rtag gcig rang dbang bar yod pa la /
NK123(go)001:1258: des bskyed pa'i 'bras bu mi rtag pa'i phyir gtan
NK123(go)001:1259: du ba'i ngo bor med par lta ba sogs te
NK123(go)001:1260: / 'di dag ni srid rtsa gcod pa'i lam yang
NK123(go)001:1261: dag dang ma 'brel bar de kho na nyid la
NK123(go)001:1262: rmongs pa'i ma rig pa'i lta ba ngan pa ste
NK123(go)001:1264: mu stegs pa ni chos thams cad la kun tu
NK123(go)001:1265: brtag pas bdag rtag pa zhig yod par lta ba
NK123(go)001:1266: ste / de yang rgyu med la 'bras bu yod par lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1267: rgyu 'bras log par lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1268: rgyu yod pa la 'bras bu med par lta ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1269: 'di dag ni ma rig pa'i lta ba'o //
NK123(go)001:1271: de la ma rtogs pa gnyis ni grub matha'i lta ba ma yin mod kyi /
NK123(go)001:1272: 'on kyang sems kyi gnas tshul bsdu ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1274: log par rtog pa'i lta ba gnyis ni grub mthas
NK123(go)001:1275: blo bsgyur ba'i lta ba yin kyang chos nyid mtha'
NK123(go)001:1276: dang bral ba la sgro skur gyi mtha' la zhen
NK123(go)001:1277: pas log par bsgyur ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1278: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i thabs ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:1279: grub mtha' smra ba rnams kyi nang nas tha chad
NK123(go)001:1280: pa mur thug par ma zad mu stegs pa'ang bdag
NK123(go)001:1281: 'dod pas 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag 'dzin gyis bcings
NK123(go)001:1284: ji srid bdag la mngon chags pa //
NK123(go)001:1288: 'jig tshogs sum brgya dang drug cur gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:1290: log pa'i theg pa 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:1292: sum brgya dbyings la bshad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1293: drug bcu'i lta ba 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:1294: grangs can log par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1295: bye brag rang gi rgyu smra dang //
NK123(go)001:1296: ku m+aa ra la chen po dang //
NK123(go)001:1297: rna ma phug pa'i gzhung 'dzin dang //
NK123(go)001:1298: gsang ba me lnga brten pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1299: me ras til mar lus bsreg dang //
NK123(go)001:1300: mdung rtse'i dka' thub log spyod dang //
NK123(go)001:1301: mchong dang 'tshog pa'i dka' thub dang //
NK123(go)001:1302: sha kor lus la byas thog dang //
NK123(go)001:1303: khyi yi cha byad spyod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1304: de bzhin mngon shes phra mo'i sa //
NK123(go)001:1305: sangs rgyas byin rlabs spyir snang ba //
NK123(go)001:1306: log pa'i dka' thub spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1307: rnam pa'i lta ba 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:1308: byed pa rgyu ru smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1309: byed pa lam du 'khyer ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1310: rtag pa don mtshon chen po dang //
NK123(go)001:1311: ther zug 'gyur med smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1312: gnas skabs rtag par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1313: rgyu la rtag par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1314: 'bras bu rtag par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1315: rtag pa nyid la lam ltos dang //
NK123(go)001:1316: spyod pa rtag par 'dod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1317: don la rtag med chad lta dang //
NK123(go)001:1318: de bzhin rtag pa'i rnam pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1319: tshang med ngan sngags gtsor byed dang //
NK123(go)001:1320: mo dang pra la gtsor byed dang /
NK123(go)001:1321: rdzu 'phrul phra mo gtsor byed dang //
NK123(go)001:1322: rtsod pa lhu ru len pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1323: dka' thub spyod pa dag dang ni //
NK123(go)001:1325: rang gi bya ba 'dzin pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1326: lwa ba can du 'gyur ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1327: mi 'pham ras gos dag dang ni //
NK123(go)001:1328: phyag mtshan gtso bor byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1329: bya ba ltos par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1330: rigs pas pha rol sun 'byin dang //
NK123(go)001:1331: rgyu med chad par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1332: phyam chad stong par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1333: rgyu chad 'bras bu chad lta dang //
NK123(go)001:1334: lam chad ye shes chad lta dang //
NK123(go)001:1335: chad pa ther zug chen po dang //
NK123(go)001:1336: lam chad 'bras bu gtan chad dang //
NK123(go)001:1337: log pa'i sems kyi chad lta dang //
NK123(go)001:1338: chad pa stong pa chen po'o //
NK123(go)001:1339: rig byed gsang bar smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:1340: cha mthun gol ba'i mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1341: mngon snang sems kyi mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1343: zhe sdang skyed pa'i mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1344: bya byed sems kyi mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1345: 'dzin pa don med mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1346: kha tshig gol ba'i mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1347: rtag pa don med mu stegs dang //
NK123(go)001:1348: ka ni dang ni ser sna dang //
NK123(go)001:1349: d+ha si ra dang ka b+hi sha //
NK123(go)001:1350: sin d+ha ra dang d+ha sing dang //
NK123(go)001:1351: ka hi dang ni sang g+ha dang //
NK123(go)001:1352: shang ka ri dang d+ha sha ka'o //
NK123(go)001:1354: 'byung ba dang shes pa'i dbyings las 'khrul nas so
NK123(go)001:1355: sor rtog pas grub mtha' re bzung ba dbyings kyi
NK123(go)001:1358: rgyal dpog pa la sogs pa'i ston pa brgyas 'das pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1360: da ltar gyi dus gsum la log pa'i 'dzin stangs su byed pas sum brgyar bshad pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1363: bye brag pa la sogs drug cu ste /
NK123(go)001:1364: de thams cad bsdu na mur lta dang /
NK123(go)001:1369: bye brag pa la sogs drug cu ste /
NK123(go)001:1370: de thams cad bsdu na mur lta dang /
NK123(go)001:1375: rtag chad gnyis su 'du bar gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:1376: 'di dag gi rnam bzhag zhib par theg mchog rin chen po che'i mdzod dang /
NK123(go)001:1377: chos rje kahthoga pa chen pos mdzad pa'i theg pa
NK123(go)001:1378: spyi ching rtsa 'grel sogs su gsal bas 'dir yi
NK123(go)001:1380: bsdu na rtag chad gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:1381: rtag lta bas ni bdag gam tshangs pa dbang phyug
NK123(go)001:1382: sogs kyi ngo bo rtag cing thams cad des byed
NK123(go)001:1384: chad lta bas 'byung ba bzhi las da lta'i phung
NK123(go)001:1385: po 'di glo bur du skye zhing shi nas rgyun
NK123(go)001:1386: chad pa'i phyir / sems can 'khor bar yang nas yang du 'khor ba ni med par 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:1387: de gnyis kas kyang bdag yod par smra ba ste bdag med mi 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:1388: de la rigs pas brtags na /
NK123(go)001:1389: gang zag gi bdag ni phung po dang gcig tha dad gang du'ang ma grub pas khegs la /
NK123(go)001:1390: tshangs dbang khyab 'jug sogs rtag pa'i skyes bu 'jig
NK123(go)001:1391: rten thams cad skyed pa'i don byed pa de lta
NK123(go)001:1392: bu med de / rtag pa la don byed pas
NK123(go)001:1393: stong pa dang don byed pa la mi rtag pas
NK123(go)001:1394: bu med de / khyab pa dang / gzhan thams
NK123(go)001:1395: cad mi rtag la de gcig pu rtag pa'i bsgrub
NK123(go)001:1396: bu med de / khyab pa dang / byed med
NK123(go)001:1397: de / dngos por yod pa la rgyu las ma
NK123(go)001:1398: skyes pa'i ye yod mi srid pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:1399: chad par smra ba'ang mi rigs te /
NK123(go)001:1400: chos gang yang rgyu med par 'byung ba mi srid do //
NK123(go)001:1401: gal te 'byung na de rtag tu yod pa'am med par thal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1402: rten cing 'brel 'byung gi chos la rgyu tshang bzhin du 'bras bu rgyun chad pa mi srid pas /
NK123(go)001:1403: sems can skye ba'i sems kyi rgyu snga ma'i sems yin pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1404: 'chi dus kyi sems las srid pa phyi ma'i sems
NK123(go)001:1405: 'byung ba la rigs pas gnod pa med cing sgrub
NK123(go)001:1407: de ltar min na da ltar snang ba'i dngos po
NK123(go)001:1408: 'di kun kyang rgyu 'bras su mi rten pas thams
NK123(go)001:1409: cad yod pa'am med par thal ba sogs nyes pa
NK123(go)001:1410: mang po yod pas khegs so //
NK123(go)001:1411: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK123(go)001:1412: rtag chad gnyis la gang gi blo zhen pa //
NK123(go)001:1413: don gyi snying po 'di las gol bar gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1415: 'di dag zhar byung du smos pa'i dgos pa'ang /
NK123(go)001:1417: de bzhin du rigs kyi bu khyod log pa'i lam
NK123(go)001:1418: du zhugs kyis dogs pa'i phyir ngas 'jigs tshogs kyi
NK123(go)001:1419: lta ba mang po bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1421: he ru ka gal po che las /
NK123(go)001:1422: mu stegs theg par rab nges na //
NK123(go)001:1423: mi spyod spang phyir khyod la bshad //
NK123(go)001:1426: cha yod dug la mi reg bzhin //
NK123(go)001:1427: gang gis shes nas der mi gnas //
NK123(go)001:1429: lam log pa ngo shes nas der mi 'jug pa sogs kyi dgos pa du ma yod de /
NK123(go)001:1430: zhib par snying po'i spyi don gsang bdag zhal lung sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:1431: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK123(go)001:1432: chos kyi rnam grangs gang zhig 'khor ba las nges par 'byin pa'i thabs dam par gyur pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1434: mi yi chos lugs legs spyod na //
NK123(go)001:1435: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK123(go)001:1436: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK123(go)001:1439: mngon mtho'i skas la 'dzegs pa las bgrod bya'i gnas
NK123(go)001:1440: dam pa yin pas nges legs sam rnam par grol
NK123(go)001:1442: de phyi rol pa las 'phags pa'i tshul yang /
NK123(go)001:1443: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su bzung nas /
NK123(go)001:1444: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1445: zag pa dang bcas pa sdug bsngal dang /
NK123(go)001:1446: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1447: mya ngan las pa zhi ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1448: lta ba ka rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi khas len pa'am /
NK123(go)001:1452: shes rab ste yang dag pa'i bslab pa gsum la
NK123(go)001:1453: slobs pas 'bras bu srid rtse la brgal nus pas
NK123(go)001:1454: 'phags te / phyi rol pa'i lam la de dag med pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:1455: de ltar yang skyabs 'gro bdun cu pa las /
NK123(go)001:1456: dge bsnyen gsum la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK123(go)001:1457: de ni sdom brgyad rtsa ba yin //
NK123(go)001:1459: sdom pa kun la yod mod kyi //
NK123(go)001:1460: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK123(go)001:1463: bslab pa gsum ni rab ston cing //
NK123(go)001:1464: phyag rgya gsum phyag rgya gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:1470: thog ma bar dang mtha' dge ba //
NK123(go)001:1471: sangs rgyas gsung du mkhas pas rtogs //
NK123(go)001:1474: khyod kyi bstan la mi phyogs pa'i //
NK123(go)001:1475: skye bo gti mug gis ldongs pa //
NK123(go)001:1476: srid rtse'i bar du song nas kyang //
NK123(go)001:1477: sdug bsngal yong 'byung srid pa sgrub //
NK123(go)001:1478: khyod kyi bstan pa'i rjes 'gro ba //
NK123(go)001:1479: bsam gtan dngos gzhi ma thob kyang //
NK123(go)001:1480: bdud kyi mig ras brtsal bzhin du //
NK123(go)001:1481: srid pa dag ni ldog par bgyid //
NK123(go)001:1483: de lta bu'i rnam grol gyi theg pa de la
NK123(go)001:1484: gong du smos pa bzhin dbye bsdu'i khyad par tshad
NK123(go)001:1485: med kyang / 'dir ni gsang chen snga 'gyur ba'i rang skad du /
NK123(go)001:1486: spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK123(go)001:1487: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1488: gsum du nges par snang ba ste //
NK123(go)001:1490: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1491: zhes gsungs pa'i re re la'ang gsum gsum du dbye bas dgur 'gyur te /
NK123(go)001:1493: nyan thos dang ni rang rgyal dang //
NK123(go)001:1494: de bzhin byang chub sems dapa'o //
NK123(go)001:1495: kri y+aa dang ni u pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1496: de bzhin yo ga'i theg par bshad //
NK123(go)001:1497: ma h+aa a nu yo ga dang //
NK123(go)001:1498: de bzhin rdzogs chen a ti'o //
NK123(go)001:1499: de ltar rnam pa dgur bshad de //
NK123(go)001:1500: chos kyi bstan pa chen po yin //
NK123(go)001:1502: de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pa'ang /
NK123(go)001:1503: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK123(go)001:1504: chung ba'i blo dang chen po dang //
NK123(go)001:1505: de bzhin 'bring po'i blo can la //
NK123(go)001:1506: rim pa gsum gyi tshul du bstan //
NK123(go)001:1507: chung ba'i rim pa rnam gsum ste //
NK123(go)001:1508: de yi blo dang mthun pa'i chos //
NK123(go)001:1509: rtogs pas sbags la nyan thos so //
NK123(go)001:1510: 'du shes can la rang rgyal te //
NK123(go)001:1511: rtog 'dzud can la byang sems so //
NK123(go)001:1512: 'bring po gsum la bstan pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1513: rab tu dman la bya ba ste //
NK123(go)001:1514: dman pa rnams la spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1515: rnam shes can la rnal 'byor nyid //
NK123(go)001:1516: chen po rim ldan gsum dag la //
NK123(go)001:1517: sems yas pa la bskyed pa dang //
NK123(go)001:1518: sems bcud can la rdzogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1519: mchog gsang rab la rdzogs pa che //
NK123(go)001:1520: zhes gsungs pa ltar gdul bya dbang po tha ma dang /
NK123(go)001:1522: rab rnams re re la'ang gsum gsum du yod pas
NK123(go)001:1523: de dag gzhug pa'i don du bstan pa yin la
NK123(go)001:1524: / nyon mongs pa so sor 'dul ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK123(go)001:1525: de thams cad kyang sde snod bzhir 'du ste /
NK123(go)001:1526: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:1527: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1528: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1529: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1530: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1531: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1532: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1533: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsung pa ni //
NK123(go)001:1534: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1535: mdor na brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs pa yang //
NK123(go)001:1536: nyon mongs 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs par zad //
NK123(go)001:1539: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por chos de snyed bstan par gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:1540: de lta bu'i rnam grol gyi theg pa dgu po
NK123(go)001:1541: de yang chos tha dad pa rim pa dgu yod
NK123(go)001:1543: nyan rang gi theg pas dngos su lam dang 'bras
NK123(go)001:1544: bu thar pa'i cha shas tsam las rnam grol gyi
NK123(go)001:1545: lam rdzogs par ma bstan cing /
NK123(go)001:1546: rang 'bras mthar phyin nas kyang theg chen la 'jug
NK123(go)001:1547: dgos pas rang rkya ma thub pa'i phyir theg chen
NK123(go)001:1548: du 'dul / theg chen pha rol du phyin pa
NK123(go)001:1549: dang sngags phyi rgyud gsum du mthar thug gi 'bras
NK123(go)001:1551: der bgrod byed kyi lam rdzogs par ma bstan cing /
NK123(go)001:1552: sngags bla med du tshang la /
NK123(go)001:1553: bla med kyi theg pas ni yongs rdzogs bstan pas 'phags par ma zad /
NK123(go)001:1554: yo ga man chad kyi rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa'i lam dang /
NK123(go)001:1555: 'bras bu'i rnam pa thams cad sngags bla med du
NK123(go)001:1556: tshang la bla med kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK123(go)001:1557: khyad chos rnams de dag la med cing /
NK123(go)001:1558: de dang de'i dod thub kyang bzhag tu med pa'i
NK123(go)001:1559: don gyis nang pa bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi nang du
NK123(go)001:1560: thams cad 'du ba yin zhing de'i snga ma gnyis
NK123(go)001:1561: kyi lam mthar thug pa'i 'bras bu'i gtugs dbang bzhi
NK123(go)001:1562: pa'i ye shes ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po
NK123(go)001:1563: yin pas thams cad der 'du ba yin te /
NK123(go)001:1565: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes spyi yi gzugs //
NK123(go)001:1566: zhes pa'i 'grel bar rim pa gnyis pa'i gnyis pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1567: mtshan med kyi rdzogs rim mthar thug la rdzogs pa chen po zhes bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:1569: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK123(go)001:1570: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK123(go)001:1572: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK123(go)001:1573: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK123(go)001:1576: de yang nyan rang 'phags pa rnams thegs chen la
NK123(go)001:1577: gsar du zhugs pa'i tshe theg chen gyi tshogs lam
NK123(go)001:1578: chung ngu nas zhugs dgos te /
NK123(go)001:1579: 'dun ldan gyi sems bskyed nas bzung lam la rim
NK123(go)001:1580: gyis slob dgos pa dang sngar chos bdag med pa
NK123(go)001:1581: rdzogs par ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis shes sgrib phra
NK123(go)001:1582: rags thams cad rdzogs par gdod spong dgos pa'i phyir
NK123(go)001:1584: klu byang gi las mtha' rnam 'byed las /
NK123(go)001:1585: mgo dang rkang lag sogs byin kyang /
NK123(go)001:1586: snang ba rnam par ma dag phyir //
NK123(go)001:1588: zhes gsungs pa bzhin mthar 'bras la dngos su sbyor ba la snang gsum mam /
NK123(go)001:1589: 'pho ba'i sgrib pa ma lus pa spong dgos na /
NK123(go)001:1590: de spang byed lam mdo sogs na ma bshad pa'i phyir ro //
