NK123(go)001:1591: de yang byang chub sems dpa' thog ma nas gsang
NK123(go)001:1592: sngags bla med kyi zab gnad la zhugs pa rnams
NK123(go)001:1593: smos ma dgos / de las gzhan mdo lam gyi nyan rang byang sems dang /
NK123(go)001:1594: sngags kyi rgyud sde 'og ma gsum gyi sgor zhugs te /
NK123(go)001:1595: rang lam mthar phyin par lobs pa'i rang 'bras nyan rang gi dgra bcom dang /
NK123(go)001:1596: byang sems dang rgyud sde 'og ma gsum gyis sa
NK123(go)001:1597: bcu'i byang sems sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab chen po'i
NK123(go)001:1598: go 'phang tsam zhig thob nus kyang /
NK123(go)001:1599: de thams cad mthar rnal 'byor bla med kyi rdzogs
NK123(go)001:1600: rim la brten nas bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK123(go)001:1601: sgrub dgos shing / der ma zad bla med la
NK123(go)001:1602: zhugs pa'i bskyed rim gyi lam mthar phyin pa zhig
NK123(go)001:1603: kyang rdzogs rim la ma zhugs par 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK123(go)001:1604: sgrub dgos shing / thabs med de / bla med
NK123(go)001:1605: byang chub kyi go 'phang mthar thug thob pa la
NK123(go)001:1606: 'khor bar 'ching byed kyi kun rtog phra ba spangs
NK123(go)001:1607: pa tsam du ma zad dkar dmar rlung sems 'gyur
NK123(go)001:1608: bcas kyi cha snang gsum mam 'pho ba'i sgrib pa'ang
NK123(go)001:1609: ma lus par spang dgos na'ang /
NK123(go)001:1610: de spong byed kyi gnyen po dbang bzhi pa'i lam
NK123(go)001:1611: rig stong zung 'jug 'gyur med bde ba chen po'i
NK123(go)001:1613: de phar phyin theg par ma zad sngags phyi rgyud gsum las kyang ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1614: des na phar phyin pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1615: sngags kyi rgyud pa rnams kyang mthar sngags bla med du zhugs dgos shing /
NK123(go)001:1616: de dag lam dang 'bras bu gang nas zhugs kyang
NK123(go)001:1617: rang rang gi mu tshod mthun pa'i sa nas zhugs
NK123(go)001:1621: nyan thos theg pa nyid ni theg pa ma yin te //
NK123(go)001:1622: rang rgyal 'di ltar rgyal ba'i sa ni min par gsungs //
NK123(go)001:1623: dpal ldan rdo rje theg pa rgyal ba'i theg pa nyid //
NK123(go)001:1624: de yang gnyis las theg pa bar dang tha mar byed //
NK123(go)001:1625: de phyir bla na med pa'i theg pa bor nas ni //
NK123(go)001:1626: 'dod pa'i bla med byang chub thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK123(go)001:1630: ngas sems can rnams kyi blo'i khyad par dang rigs
NK123(go)001:1631: kyi bye brag gis theg pa'i khyad par rnams bstan
NK123(go)001:1632: te la la phyi rol pa'i tshul lo //
NK123(go)001:1633: la la nyan thos kyi theg pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1634: la la rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1635: gzhan yang pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1636: rig pa 'dzin pa'i rgyud dpag tu med pa bstan kyang /
NK123(go)001:1637: thig le chen po yi ge med par brda' dang
NK123(go)001:1638: bral bas gnyis su med par sangs rgyas par rig
NK123(go)001:1640: in+d+ra b+hu ti'i dbang 'khor lo'i man ngag las /
NK123(go)001:1641: rang bzhin gyis ni 'od gsal zhing //
NK123(go)001:1642: rdzogs pa chen po'i mthar thug pa //
NK123(go)001:1643: man ngag kun gyi mchog gi mchog /
NK123(go)001:1644: de sgrub thabs su gsungs par zad //
NK123(go)001:1646: de lta bu'i theg pa rim dgu po de yang bsdu na /
NK123(go)001:1648: 'jig rten las 'das pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:1649: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1651: zhes gsungs pas rgyu 'bras gnyis su 'du zhing /
NK123(go)001:1655: rgyu la gsum dang 'bras la gnyis //
NK123(go)001:1656: gnyen po las phye drug tu 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:1657: 'di dag dbang po'i rim pas so //
NK123(go)001:1658: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'chad par bya ba la gnyis /
NK123(go)001:1659: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1660: 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa bshad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1662: so so'i lam des mthar thug gi rang 'bras de mtshan par byed pas mtshan nyid dang /
NK123(go)001:1663: de la sbyor ba'i rgyu yin pas rgyu'i theg pa'am /
NK123(go)001:1664: yang na kun 'byung las dang nyon mongs pa'i lam
NK123(go)001:1665: nas thar bar 'dren par byed pas na kun 'byung
NK123(go)001:1666: 'dren pa'i theg pa zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:1667: gang zag dgu las dbang po tha ma gsum gyi don du dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1671: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1672: de'i dang po nyan thos kyi theg pa ni gang
NK123(go)001:1673: zag tha ma'i tha ma la dgongs nas gsungs te
NK123(go)001:1675: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1682: 'khor ba las rang nyid gcig pu thar 'dod kyi
NK123(go)001:1683: blos gang zag gi bdag med tsam rtogs pa'i thabs
NK123(go)001:1684: su gyur pa / nges tshig ni /
NK123(go)001:1685: sh+ra ba ka zhes pa'i sgra nyan pa dang thos
NK123(go)001:1686: pa gnyis ka la 'jug pas nyan thos zhes bya
NK123(go)001:1689: srid pa tha ma pa'i dus su'ang slob dpon gzhan
NK123(go)001:1690: la bsten zhing de las thos pa dag yul gzhan
NK123(go)001:1691: la sgrog pas thos sgrog gam nyan thos zhes bya'o
NK123(go)001:1692: // dbye ba la sngar ltar drug las /
NK123(go)001:1694: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mtha' dag la yid 'byung ba'i sgo nas /
NK123(go)001:1695: rang nyid zhi bde don gnyer gyi bsam pas 'phags
NK123(go)001:1696: pa'i bden pa bzhi la rgyu 'bras spang blang gi
NK123(go)001:1699: 'jug pa'i sgo nas bden pa bzhi //
NK123(go)001:1700: nyan thos spyi yi 'jug sgo yin //
NK123(go)001:1702: de la bden pa bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:1707: de bshad pa la bden bzhi'i ngo bo ni /
NK123(go)001:1708: skye ba snga ma'i las nyon gyis bskyed pa'i nyer
NK123(go)001:1709: len gyi phung po'i rgyun rnams sdug bsngal gyi bden
NK123(go)001:1710: pa'i ngo bo / de bzhin du 'byung 'gyur nyer
NK123(go)001:1711: len gyi phung po'i rgyun gyur pa'i las nyon rnams
NK123(go)001:1713: gnyen po lam gyis spang bya kun 'byung bcom pa'i spangs ba ni 'gog bden gyi /
NK123(go)001:1714: kun 'byung spong bar nus shing 'gog pa thob par
NK123(go)001:1715: nus pa'i 'phags pa'i ye shes ni lam bden gyi
NK123(go)001:1716: ngo bo'o // bden bzhi'i nges tshig ni /
NK123(go)001:1717: thun mong du rang rang gi ngo bo rnam pa
NK123(go)001:1718: bzhi bzhir bden zhing mi bslu bar gnas pas de
NK123(go)001:1719: rnams kyi rang bzhin ji lta bar mthong na phyin
NK123(go)001:1720: ci ma log pa'i blo skye bas na 'phags pa'i
NK123(go)001:1723: gnod pa'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir sdug bsngal ba'o //
NK123(go)001:1724: kun 'byung ba'i tshul gyis kun 'byung ba'o //
NK123(go)001:1725: phung po zhig pa'i phyir 'gog pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1726: bgrod pa'i don gyis lam mo //
NK123(go)001:1728: de yang bden bzhi rang gi mtshan nyid ji ltar
NK123(go)001:1729: gnas pa de 'phags pa rnams kho nas mkhyen pas
NK123(go)001:1730: na 'phags pa'i bden par bzhag la /
NK123(go)001:1731: so skye rnams sdug bsngal kun 'byung sogs rang la
NK123(go)001:1732: yod kyang de dag gi mtshan nyid ji lta ba
NK123(go)001:1733: bzhin mi shes pas phyin ci log tu 'dzin pas
NK123(go)001:1734: na de dag gi bden par ma bzhag go //
NK123(go)001:1736: sdug bsngal ni 'bras bu'i phung po ste /
NK123(go)001:1739: skye ba ni 'gro ba rigs drug po gcig nas gcig tu 'khor ba'o //
NK123(go)001:1740: gnas ni phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rnams so //
NK123(go)001:1741: de na sdug bsngal gyi rnam grangs ni skye ba la sogs pa mang po dag go //
NK123(go)001:1743: sdug bsngal gyi rgyu'i cha ste /
NK123(go)001:1744: las dang nyon mongs pa gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:1745: nyon mongs pa ni 'dod chags la sogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:1749: dge mi dge mi g.yo ba'i las gsum mo //
NK123(go)001:1751: sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa gtan nas zhi ba ste /
NK123(go)001:1756: kun 'byung spang 'gog pa mngon du byed /
NK123(go)001:1757: lam rgyud la brten pa'i tshul gyis /
NK123(go)001:1758: tshogs sbyor mthong bsgom mi slob pa'i lam ste lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:1761: bstan pa dang mi mthun pa med pa'i mtshan nyid kyi don can /
NK123(go)001:1763: kun 'byung gis bskyed pa'i 'bras bu zag pa dang
NK123(go)001:1764: bcas pa'i phung po bstan pa dang mthun pa sdug
NK123(go)001:1767: sdug bsngal nyer len gyi phung po skyed byed bstan pa dang mthun pa kun 'byung gi /
NK123(go)001:1768: de bzhin nyid glo bur gyi dri mas dag pa bstan pa dang mthun pa 'gog bden gyi /
NK123(go)001:1769: thar par bgrod pa'i 'jug ngogs bstan pa dang mthun pa lam bden gyi mtshan nyid de /
NK123(go)001:1770: 'dir bstan pa dang mthun pa ni bden bzhi'i mtshan
NK123(go)001:1771: nyid 'di ltar yin no zhes sangs rgyas kyis bstan
NK123(go)001:1772: pa'i don ji lta ba bzhin yul bden bzhi rang
NK123(go)001:1773: rang gi ngos nas mi mthun pa med pas na
NK123(go)001:1774: yul gyi ngos nas bden pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1775: bden bzhi'i mtshan nyid ji ltar bstan pa de ltar
NK123(go)001:1776: shes na shes pa'i blo de yang ma nor ba
NK123(go)001:1777: yin pas yul can gyi ngos nas kyang de skad
NK123(go)001:1779: bden pa bzhir byas pa la shes bya'i chos thams
NK123(go)001:1780: cad spang blang du bya ba'i cha nas 'khor 'das
NK123(go)001:1782: de re rer rgyu 'bras phrugs rer yod pas nyis phrugs su nges te /
NK123(go)001:1783: spang bya 'khor ba la'ang 'bras bu sdug bsngal dang rgyu kun 'byung gnyis /
NK123(go)001:1784: blang bya myang 'das la'ang 'bras bu 'gog pa dang
NK123(go)001:1785: rgyu lam bden gnyis su nges pas bden pa bzhir
NK123(go)001:1786: grangs nges pa'o // go rim ni /
NK123(go)001:1787: yul can mngon par rtogs pa'i rim pa dang mthun par yul bden pa bzhi bstan pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:1788: mdzod las bden pa ji ltar mngon rtogs rim //
NK123(go)001:1790: de yang 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi phung po ni nad dang 'dra bar shes par bya ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1791: de'i rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa'i kun 'byung ni
NK123(go)001:1792: nad kyi rgyu dang 'dra bas spang bar bya ba
NK123(go)001:1793: dang / sdug bsngal mtha' dag las grol ba'i 'gog
NK123(go)001:1794: pa ni nad med pa'i bde ba dang 'dra bar
NK123(go)001:1796: de'i thabs su lam zag med sgom pa ni sman
NK123(go)001:1797: bzang po dang 'dra bar brten par bya ba rtogs
NK123(go)001:1798: pa'i phyir te / rgyud bla las /
NK123(go)001:1799: nad ni shes bya nad kyi rgyu ni spang bya la //
NK123(go)001:1800: bder gnas thob bya sman ni brten par bya ba ltar //
NK123(go)001:1801: sdug bsngal rgyu dang de 'gog pa dang de bzhin lam //
NK123(go)001:1802: shes bya spang bya rig par bya zhing brten par bya //
NK123(go)001:1805: gzung yul dngos por rags snang 'di gnyen po dang blos gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:1806: 'dzin pa'i sems kyi rgyun dus gsum gyi chas gzhig tu rung ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1807: gzung 'dzin rags pa 'di kun rdzob tu snang tsam
NK123(go)001:1808: las rang bzhin med pas de la gang zag gi
NK123(go)001:1809: bdag phung po dang gcig tha dad gang du'ang grub
NK123(go)001:1811: gzung yul dngos po rags snang rtsom pa'i gzhi rdul
NK123(go)001:1812: phra rab 'di gnyen po dang blos gzhom du med
NK123(go)001:1813: pa dang / 'dzin sems skad gcig ma dus kyi
NK123(go)001:1814: cha dang bral bas gzung 'dzin phra ba don dam
NK123(go)001:1815: du 'dod pa'i phyir chos kyi bdag med ma rtogs
NK123(go)001:1816: pa dang / te / rgyan sdug po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:1817: phung po gang zag bdag med par //
NK123(go)001:1818: rab tu rnam phye mthong gyur cing //
NK123(go)001:1819: chos kyi dngos yod ma bshig par //
NK123(go)001:1820: nyan thos de dag mngon rtogs 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:1822: rdzogs pa chen po bshad rgyud thig le kun gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:1823: nyan thos g.yag rnga ne'u seng dang //
NK123(go)001:1824: gong bu cha shas med par blta //
NK123(go)001:1825: gzung 'dzin chos kyi bdag tu mthong //
NK123(go)001:1827: man ngag lta ba'i phreng ba las /
NK123(go)001:1828: chos thams cad la mu stegs pa la sogs pas sgro skur bas kun tu brtag pa /
NK123(go)001:1829: ye med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1830: rtag pa la sogs pa yod par blta ba ni /
NK123(go)001:1831: thag pa la sbrul du mthong ba bzhin du med de /
NK123(go)001:1832: phung po dang khams dang skye mched la sogs pa 'byung ba chen po bzhi'i rdul phra rab dang /
NK123(go)001:1833: rnam par shes pa ni don dam pa yod par blta ba /
NK123(go)001:1835: skabs 'dir gong du smos pa ltar bem shes gnyis
NK123(go)001:1836: rdul dang skad cig ma'i chos su mthong bas chos
NK123(go)001:1837: bdag gzung 'dzin rags pa nyid med par rtogs pa
NK123(go)001:1838: des / phyi rol bas kun tu brtag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1839: ngar 'dzin lhan skyes kyi zhen yul du gyur pa'i gang zag gi bdag de /
NK123(go)001:1840: thag pa la sbrul du 'phrul pa bzhin phyin ci
NK123(go)001:1841: log tu blo zhen pa tsam las rang bzhin gyis
NK123(go)001:1842: grub pa med pa'i stong pa nyid de khong chud
NK123(go)001:1843: pas srid rtsa gcod pa yin pas na /
NK123(go)001:1844: chos dang gang zag gi bdag med gnyis po stong
NK123(go)001:1845: gzhi chos can gyi dbye ba tsam las stong tshul
NK123(go)001:1846: la khyad par ci yang med de gnyis ka brten
NK123(go)001:1847: nas brtags pa'i stong nyid tsam gyi ngo bor gcig
NK123(go)001:1848: pa'i phyir / chos kyi bdag med spyi dang /
NK123(go)001:1849: gang zag gi bdag med de'i bye brag yin pa tsam du dgongs nas /
NK123(go)001:1850: nyan thos ma nges pa'i rigs can theg chen la
NK123(go)001:1851: drangs pa'i ched dang stong nyid zhi sgo gcig pur
NK123(go)001:1852: ston pa'i phyir dbu ma'i gzhung kha cig tu nyan
NK123(go)001:1853: rang la chos bdag med rtogs pa yod par gsungs
NK123(go)001:1854: pa dang / yang 'od srung gi zhus pa'i mdo
NK123(go)001:1855: las yung 'bru srin zos kyi nang gi nam mkha'
NK123(go)001:1856: ltar nyan rang gi stong nyid rtogs pa rgya chung
NK123(go)001:1857: bar gsungs pa bzhin dman pa la dgag sgra sbyar
NK123(go)001:1858: pa dang / te / gong du bstan pa'i mdo rgyud man ngag dang bcas dang /
NK123(go)001:1859: gzhan yang lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:1860: dpal ldan zla bas dbu ma 'jug pa'i rang 'grel rang bzhed dngos 'chad pa'i skabs su'ang /
NK123(go)001:1861: de la gang zag gi bdag med par ni rang sangs rgyas rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:1862: nyan thos rnam par grol bar bya ba'i phyir bstan la /
NK123(go)001:1863: byang chub sems dpa' rnams rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK123(go)001:1864: pa nyid thob pas rnam par grol bar bya ba'i
NK123(go)001:1865: phyir ni gnyis ka bstan to //
NK123(go)001:1866: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang rten
NK123(go)001:1867: cing 'brel bar 'byung la rkyen 'di pa tsam mthong
NK123(go)001:1868: mod kyi / de ltar na yang de dag la
NK123(go)001:1869: chos kyi bdag med pa yongs su rdzogs par sgom
NK123(go)001:1870: pa med de khams gsum na spyod pa'i nyon mongs
NK123(go)001:1871: pa spong ba'i thabs tsam zhig ni yod do //
NK123(go)001:1872: de dag la gang zag gi bdag med pa ma
NK123(go)001:1873: lus par sgom pa ni yod par rnam par bzhag
NK123(go)001:1874: go // zhes nyan rang gis chos kyi bdag med
NK123(go)001:1875: ma rtog par dngos su gsal por gsungs yin la
NK123(go)001:1876: go // / khyad par gsang chen snga 'gyur gyi grub mtha' 'dzin pa rnams ni /
NK123(go)001:1877: rdzogs pa chen po'i bshad rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:1878: theg pa so so'i lta ba'i shan 'byed skabs su /
NK123(go)001:1879: kyee sems dpa' chen po gzung 'dzin gnyis su smra na nyan thos lta bar bshad /
NK123(go)001:1880: 'dzin pa yod la gzung ba med na rang rgyal lta bar bshad /
NK123(go)001:1881: sems dang rnam par smra ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1882: don dam dang kun rdzob tu smra na byang chub sems dpa'i lta bar bshad /
NK123(go)001:1884: 'phags chos ngos bzung ba'i skabs su /
NK123(go)001:1885: ma rtogs log par rtog las nyan thos khyad 'phags pa /
NK123(go)001:1886: gang zag bdag med rtogs pas lta bas khyad par 'phags /
NK123(go)001:1888: nyan thos dag las rang rgyal 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:1889: gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi khams dag la //
NK123(go)001:1890: phyogs gcig bdag med lta bas lta ba khyad par 'phags /
NK123(go)001:1892: rang rgyal dag las byang sems 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:1893: bdag med rnam gnyis rtogs pas lta ba khyad par 'phags /
NK123(go)001:1894: zhes so sor gsal bar bstan pa bzhin /
NK123(go)001:1895: kun mkhyen bla mas snyan brgyud zab don gnad kyi me long du /
NK123(go)001:1896: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i ngo bo gang zag gi bdag med rtogs nas lam bsgom pa /
NK123(go)001:1897: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i ngo bo gang zag
NK123(go)001:1898: dang chos kyi bdag phyed bzung ba rang bzhin med
NK123(go)001:1899: par rtogs nas rten 'brel gyi lam bsgom pa /
NK123(go)001:1900: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'i ngo bo bdag med gnyis rtogs nas lam bsgom pa /
NK123(go)001:1901: zhes gsung pa ltar phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg
NK123(go)001:1902: gsum gyi lta ba'i khyad par 'di ltar bzhed pa
NK123(go)001:1903: 'ba' zhig go // des na de gnyis ka don gyi gnad gcig par shes dgos te /
NK123(go)001:1904: de las gzhan du gyur na theg pa che chung
NK123(go)001:1905: dbang po rno rtul sogs gsungs rab kyi rmang 'khrugs
NK123(go)001:1906: par 'gyur ba'i phyir zhib par kun mkhyen bla ma
NK123(go)001:1907: 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i zhal snga nas stsal ba'i nges
NK123(go)001:1908: shes rin po che'i sgron me dang /
NK123(go)001:1909: sher d+aak+ki chen mo yan lag dang bcas pa las rtogs par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:1910: dbye na lo chen ska ba dpal brtsegs kyis mdzad pa'i lta rim snang ba bcu bdun pa las /
NK123(go)001:1911: chos rtsam blta ba'i nyan thos pa //
NK123(go)001:1912: mdo sde pa dang bye brag gnyis //
NK123(go)001:1913: phyi rol rdul la rtsod byed cing //
NK123(go)001:1914: shes pa skad cig snang byed mthun //
NK123(go)001:1917: rags pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa 'di ni g.yag
NK123(go)001:1918: rnga dang ne seng ltar tshogs pa gcig tu snang
NK123(go)001:1919: yang / don dam par rdul phra rab bskor ba
NK123(go)001:1920: bar dang bcas pa cha ldan sil bar 'dod cing
NK123(go)001:1922: rdul phra rab 'byar yang ma 'byar bar yang med pa 'bru'i phung po lta bur 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:1923: phyi ma 'dis rdul phran las gong bu brtsam pa
NK123(go)001:1924: de'ang cha med du rtogs pas bye smra las 'phags
NK123(go)001:1925: te don gyis bltar med pa'i phyir rdul phran khas
NK123(go)001:1927: mdor na chos bdag 'dzin don dam du blta zhing
NK123(go)001:1928: 'khor 'das bden bzhi'i rgyu 'bras la blang dor du
NK123(go)001:1931: gnyis med ma rtogs thams cad la //
NK123(go)001:1932: bden bzhi'i dngos por yod blta zhing //
NK123(go)001:1933: spong dang mi spang byed gyur na //
NK123(go)001:1934: 'di ni nyan thos sa pa yin //
NK123(go)001:1938: so sor thar pa zhes rnam brgyad //
NK123(go)001:1939: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK123(go)001:1940: mtshan las ming ni 'pho ba'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:1941: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK123(go)001:1942: spang bya lnga brgyad bcu dang ni //
NK123(go)001:1943: thams cad spong bar nos pa las //
NK123(go)001:1944: dge bsnyen dang ni bsnyen gnas dang //
NK123(go)001:1945: dge tshul che dang dge slong nyid //
NK123(go)001:1947: so thar rigs brgyad po gang rung ngam /
NK123(go)001:1948: khyad par sangs rgyas kyi rjes su mthun par bslab dgos pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:1949: mchog dge slong gi sdom pa la brten par bya ste /
NK123(go)001:1950: de dag gi srung mtshams zhib par sdom gsum 'grel chen sogs las shes par bya la /
NK123(go)001:1951: mdor bsdus zhe chen ma h+aa pan+di ta 'jam mgon
NK123(go)001:1952: bstan 'dzin 'phel rgyas kyis mdzad pa'i theg dgu'i rnam
NK123(go)001:1953: bshad las / so thar rigs brgyad gang rung ba'i //
NK123(go)001:1954: sdom pa legs bsrung tshul khrims te //
NK123(go)001:1955: bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha ma dang //
NK123(go)001:1956: dge tshul pha ma dge slong ma //
NK123(go)001:1957: dge slong pha ma so thar brgyad //
NK123(go)001:1958: sdom pa gsod rku rdzun smra ba //
NK123(go)001:1959: 'dod log rtsa bzhi spyi'i spang bya //
NK123(go)001:1960: chang dang mal che mtho gar phreng //
NK123(go)001:1961: phyi dro'i kha zas bsnyen gnas khrims //
NK123(go)001:1962: rtsa steng chang bsnan dge bsnyen sdom //
NK123(go)001:1963: bsnyen gnas sdom steng gar phreng dbye //
NK123(go)001:1964: gser dngul spangs pa dge tshul bsrung //
NK123(go)001:1965: de steng gcig 'gro chu skyal ba //
NK123(go)001:1966: skyes reg lhan 'dus smyan byas pa //
NK123(go)001:1967: nyes 'chab rtsa drug gser zung dang //
NK123(go)001:1969: rtsa sngon sogs gcod byin len med //
NK123(go)001:1970: gsog 'jog byas za rjes mthun drug /
NK123(go)001:1971: dge slob khrims yin pha ma bzhi //
NK123(go)001:1972: lhag ma bcu gsum spang ltung grangs //
NK123(go)001:1973: sum cu ltung byed bcu phrag dgu //
NK123(go)001:1974: sor bshags bzhi dang nyes byas pa //
NK123(go)001:1975: brgya dang bcu gnyis dge slong khrims //
NK123(go)001:1979: tshur gnas thos dang bsam ldan pas //
NK123(go)001:1980: sgom pa ni rab tu sbyor //
NK123(go)001:1981: zhes pas gzhi so thar ris bdun gang yang rung
NK123(go)001:1982: ba'i tshul khrims rnam par dag pa la brten nas
NK123(go)001:1983: dge ba'i bshes gnyen las nyan thos kyi sde snod
NK123(go)001:1987: de'ang dang por rang rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa la
NK123(go)001:1988: brtag ste de'i gnyen por 'dod chags la mi sdug
NK123(go)001:1989: pa / zhe sdang la byams snying /
NK123(go)001:1991: rnam rtog gam phrag dog la dbugs bgrang ba /
NK123(go)001:1992: nga rgyal la khams kyi rab dbye rnams bsgoms pas
NK123(go)001:1993: zhi gnas kyi sems las su rung bar byas rjes
NK123(go)001:1995: bden bzhi re re la'ang bzhi bzhir phye ba'i bden chung bcu drug bsgoms pa ste /
NK123(go)001:1996: de la sdug bden gyi bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:1997: rags pa rgyun dang phra ba skad cig gis skye 'jig bye bas mi rtag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:1998: sdug bsngal gsum gyi rang bzhin can yin pas sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:1999: lnga phung la bdag gir byed po gzhan med pas stong pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2000: lnga phung la bdag gi mtshan nyid med pas /
NK123(go)001:2001: bdag med pa dang bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:2002: rdzogs pa chen po lam gyi klong las /
NK123(go)001:2003: rkyen gyis skye zheng rang dbang med mi rtag /
NK123(go)001:2004: gsum mam brgyad kyis gnod pas sdug bsngal lo //
NK123(go)001:2005: bdag gi lta ba'i mi mthun phyogs stong pa //
NK123(go)001:2006: lnga phung bdag tu bltar med stong pa nyid //
NK123(go)001:2012: bdag tu lta ba rnams kyi gnyen po byed do //
NK123(go)001:2013: kun 'byung gi bzhi ni sdug bsngal thams cad bskyed pa'i sa bon lta bur gyur pas rgyu dang /
NK123(go)001:2014: srid pa'i sdug bsngal kun 'byung bas kun 'byung dang /
NK123(go)001:2015: bag chags kyi dbang gis mtshams sbyor bas rkyen dang /
NK123(go)001:2016: rgyu rkyen 'brel ba'i dbang gis sdug bsngal 'phral du bskyed pas rab bskye bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:2018: de rgyu las nyon phung po'i sa bon lha //
NK123(go)001:2019: de la rgyud drug khams gsum 'byung ba'o //
NK123(go)001:2020: bag chags brtas phyir rnams par smin byed rkyen //
NK123(go)001:2021: rgyu rkyen 'brel nas khams gsum rab tu skye //
NK123(go)001:2027: blos g.yo ba sngon du btang ba'i log lta'i gnyen po byed do //
NK123(go)001:2029: rgyu sa bon spangs pas 'bras bu srid pa gtan du mi 'byung bas 'gog pa /
NK123(go)001:2030: sdug bsngal med pas zhi ba /
NK123(go)001:2031: zag med kyi bde ba dang ldan pas gya nam pa /
NK123(go)001:2032: gtan du srid pa las thar bas nges par 'byung ba bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:2034: rgyu rkyen 'bral bas phung khams 'jig phyir 'gog /
NK123(go)001:2035: sdug bsngal med pas gsum mi 'byung zhi ba //
NK123(go)001:2036: phyis kyang khams gsum sdug bsngal bral gya nom //
NK123(go)001:2037: bde bar phyin te skyon las nges par 'byung //
NK123(go)001:2041: sdug bsngal la thar pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:2042: bsam gtan gyi bde ba ni gya nom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2043: thar pa ni gtan du ba ma yin no snyam
NK123(go)001:2044: pa'i log lta las nges par 'byung bar byed do
NK123(go)001:2046: 'phags pa'i sar bgrod par byed pas lam dang /
NK123(go)001:2047: thag bcas las nyon gyi gnyen po byed pas rigs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2048: yang dag pa'i gnas la sems phyin ci ma log par sgrub pas sgrub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2049: srid pa las gtan du nges par 'byin pas nges 'byin bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:2051: 'phags pa'i sar bzhugs mya ngan 'das grol lam //
NK123(go)001:2052: 'khrul pa'i gnyen por tshad mar gyur phyir rigs //
NK123(go)001:2053: phyin ci log spang yang dag thob phyir bsgru //
NK123(go)001:2054: 'khor bar mi skye 'dus par nges par 'byin //
NK123(go)001:2059: lam 'di yang ldog go snyam pa'i log rtog gi gnyen po byed pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:2060: de ltar bden chung bcu drug po dang /
NK123(go)001:2061: tshogs lam chung ngur dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi sogs
NK123(go)001:2062: rang lam gyi byang phyogs so bdun po bsgom par
NK123(go)001:2063: byed do // de'i sgom tshul yang dmigs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2065: 'thob pa gsum gyi sgo nas theg chen las dman te /
NK123(go)001:2066: de'ang dran pa nyer bzhag la mtshon na /
NK123(go)001:2067: dmigs pa gtso bor rang rgyud kyis bsdus pa'i lus tshor sems chos tsam la dmigs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2068: yid byed kyang mi rtag sdug bsngal bdag med sogs bden rnam bcu drug po 'ba' zhig ste /
NK123(go)001:2069: gtso bos gang zag gi bdag med rtog pa'i sgo tsam dang /
NK123(go)001:2070: 'thob pa'ang rang gi lus sogs zag bcas dman pa
NK123(go)001:2071: de dang bral ba'i thar pa thob par 'dod pa
NK123(go)001:2072: yin la / de bzhin du 'bras bu de rtsam 'thob pa ste nyi tshe bas bsdus pa ste /
NK123(go)001:2073: mdor na srid zhi mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i sher phyin
NK123(go)001:2074: ni srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pa'i myang 'das
NK123(go)001:2075: sangs rgyas kyi rgyu mthun min yin na /
NK123(go)001:2076: de nyan rang la med pa'i phyir gnas skabs kyi
NK123(go)001:2077: lam sgom pa dang mthar 'bras gnyis ka theg chen
NK123(go)001:2078: las gzhan du gyur pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:2079: zhib par bden rnam bcu drug dang byang phyogs kyi
NK123(go)001:2080: sgom rim ni mdzod rtsa 'grel dang kun mkhyen bla
NK123(go)001:2081: ma'i grub mtha' mdzod sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:2082: de ltar bsgoms pa'i gzhi de las khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa mthong bas spang ba sogs /
NK123(go)001:2083: spong tshul ye shes bcu drug gis rim par spong ste /
NK123(go)001:2085: mdzod las brgyad cu rtsa brgyad du gsungs kyang 'dir ku btus ltar na /
NK123(go)001:2088: tshul khrims brtul zhugs mchog 'dzin pa //
NK123(go)001:2089: lta min lnga dang lta ba lnga //
NK123(go)001:2090: mthong spang rtsa ba bcu yin no //
NK123(go)001:2091: de dag bden pa bzhi po la //
NK123(go)001:2092: 'jig mthar log rmongs the tshom dngos //
NK123(go)001:2093: khong khro dbang gis log par 'jug /
NK123(go)001:2094: lhag ma rnams ni brgyud nas 'jug /'dod pa'i khams na bcu ka ste //
NK123(go)001:2095: gzugs dang gzugs med khong khro min //
NK123(go)001:2096: de ltar brgya dang bcu ga nyis so //
NK123(go)001:2097: zhes pas mthong spang rtsa ba bcu po bden pa
NK123(go)001:2098: bzhi la log par zhugs tshul gyi sgo nas brgya
NK123(go)001:2099: bcu gnyis te / 'dod khams na bden pa bzhi
NK123(go)001:2100: po re re la log pa bcu re 'jug pas
NK123(go)001:2101: bcu gnyis te / bzhi bcu / khams gong ma
NK123(go)001:2102: gnyis na khong khro ma gtogs gzhan dgu po zhugs
NK123(go)001:2103: pas sum cu rtsa drug pa tshan gnyis te bdun
NK123(go)001:2105: thams cad bsdoms pas khams gsum na mthong bas spang
NK123(go)001:2106: bar bya ba kun brtags kyi cha brgya dang bcu
NK123(go)001:2107: gnyis so // sgom spang yang mdzod las /
NK123(go)001:2108: 'dod chags khong khro nga rgyal ma rig pa bzhi
NK123(go)001:2109: la khams gsum gyi dbye bas bcur bzhed pa sogs
NK123(go)001:2110: yod kyang / 'dir kun btus ltar na /
NK123(go)001:2112: 4 /'jig 5lta mthar 6lta sgom spang drug /'dod par drug yod gzugs gzugs med //
NK123(go)001:2113: khong khro ma gtogs lnga re yod //
NK123(go)001:2114: de la sa dang che 'bring gis //
NK123(go)001:2115: phye bas bzhi brgya bcu bzhi'o //
NK123(go)001:2116: zhes pas sgom spang rtsa ba drug po de la khams dang /
NK123(go)001:2117: sa dang rnam pa'i sgo nas rgyas par dbye na /
NK123(go)001:2118: 'dod par sgom spang chung 'bring chen po gsum la
NK123(go)001:2119: nang gses gsum du dbye ba'i skor dgu re re
NK123(go)001:2120: la sgom spang rtsa ba drug re yod pas lnga
NK123(go)001:2121: bcu nga bzhi / de bzhin du bsam 4gzugs 4kyis brgyad po re rer yang skor dgur phyes nas /
NK123(go)001:2122: de rnams su khong khro ma gtogs lnga re brtsis pas sum brgya drug cu /
NK123(go)001:2123: de gnyis ka bsdom pas khams gsum na sgom pas
NK123(go)001:2124: spang bar bya ba lhan skyes kyi cha bzhi brgya
NK123(go)001:2125: dang bcu bzhi'o // de dag spong tshul ni mthong
NK123(go)001:2126: spang kun brtags yin pas bden bzhi'i rang bzhin mthong
NK123(go)001:2128: sgom spang rnams lhan skyes yin pas bden pa mthong
NK123(go)001:2129: tsam gyis spang mi nus pas mthong zin sgom par
NK123(go)001:2130: byed pa'i sgo nas rim gyis spong dgos /
NK123(go)001:2131: spong tshul dngos la theg pa gong 'og gi bzhed
NK123(go)001:2132: pa mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig yod pa las theg
NK123(go)001:2133: dman ltar na mthong spang skabs ngo bo'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:2134: skad cig ma bcu drug yod pa las /
NK123(go)001:2135: bcu drug pa lam rjes shes sgom lam dang /
NK123(go)001:2136: gzhan bco lnga po mthong ba'i lam ste /
NK123(go)001:2137: dper na sdug bden mthong ba'i lam skad cig bzhi'i
NK123(go)001:2138: dang po sdug bsngal chos bzod kyi skabs su 'dod
NK123(go)001:2139: khams kyi sdug bsngal mthong spang bcu spong /
NK123(go)001:2140: chos shes kyi skabs su gnyen po'i ye shes skye /
NK123(go)001:2141: rjes bzod kyi skabs su gzugs dang gzugs med kyi sdug bsngal mthong spang bco brgyad spong /
NK123(go)001:2142: rjes shes kyi skabs su gnyen po'i ye shes skye /
NK123(go)001:2143: de ltar bden pa gzhan gsum la'ang sbyar te nyi
NK123(go)001:2144: shu rtsa brgyad pa tshan bzhi spangs pas mthong spong
NK123(go)001:2145: brgya dang bcu gnyis po spangs te skad cig bcu
NK123(go)001:2146: drug po 'di la theg dman pa rang la'ang nyan
NK123(go)001:2147: thos sdeb rnams bzhed pa mi 'dra ba du ma
NK123(go)001:2148: yod par gsungs / sgom spang ni /
NK123(go)001:2149: theg chen pa rnams kyis 'das lam kho na las /
NK123(go)001:2150: 'jig rten pa'i lam gyis spang bya rnams gnas skabs
NK123(go)001:2151: mgo gnon tsam las rtsa ba drung nas 'byin mi
NK123(go)001:2152: nus par bzhed pa don la de ltar gnas kyang
NK123(go)001:2153: theg dman pa rnams kyis ni mthong spang 'das lam
NK123(go)001:2155: sgom spang ni 'jig rten pa'i lam gyis kyang spong
NK123(go)001:2156: nus pas mthong spang gi sngon du yang 'dod pa'i
NK123(go)001:2157: sgom spong spong ba srid pas de 'dra de la
NK123(go)001:2158: lam thod rgal ba zhes zer zhing phyir 'ong zhugs
NK123(go)001:2159: pa dang phyir mi 'ong zhugs pa gnyis ka yod
NK123(go)001:2160: par bzhed / spang tshul gnyen po'i ye shes chung
NK123(go)001:2161: rim nas skyes pas spang bya che rim nas rim
NK123(go)001:2162: gyis spong bar 'dod de 'og tu 'chad do //
NK123(go)001:2164: sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la gnas te /
NK123(go)001:2165: rang don gtso bor spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:2166: klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa'i g.yu thang las /
NK123(go)001:2167: spyod pa rang don 'ba' zhig spyod //
NK123(go)001:2171: bsod snyoms stan gcig phyis mi len //
NK123(go)001:2172: phyag dar khrod 'phying chos gos gsum //
NK123(go)001:2173: dgon par bla gam med pa dang //
NK123(go)001:2174: shing drung dur khrod cig pu ba //
NK123(go)001:2175: gzhi ji bzhin te sbyangs yon spyod //
NK123(go)001:2179: 'bras bu thob pa'i lam gyi rgyun la zhugs pa rgyun zhugs dang /
NK123(go)001:2180: 'dod par skye ba lan gcig len pa lan gcig phyir 'ong ba dang /
NK123(go)001:2181: da phyin 'dod pa'i khams 'dir skye ba mi len pa phyir mi 'ong ba ste /
NK123(go)001:2183: mthar thug zad pa shes pa der mi skye ba
NK123(go)001:2184: shes pa'i ye shes gnyis dang ldan pa'i lhag bcas
NK123(go)001:2185: lhag med kyi dgra bcom pa thob cing /
NK123(go)001:2186: 'bras bu bzhi po de re re la zhugs gnas
NK123(go)001:2187: gnyis gnyis su phye bas brgyad de de dag gi
NK123(go)001:2188: sa mtshams ni mngon pa 'og ma ltar na mthong
NK123(go)001:2189: lam skad cig bco lnga la gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2192: mthong lam skad cig bco lnga la gnas pa gnyis ka rgyun du zhugs pa zhugs pa /
NK123(go)001:2193: skad cig ma bcu drug pa lam rjes su shes
NK123(go)001:2194: pa thob nas rgyun du zhugs pa 'bras gnas des
NK123(go)001:2195: 'dod pa'i sgom spang gcig nas lnga'i bar spangs ba
NK123(go)001:2197: 'dod pa'i sgom spang drug pa spangs na phyir 'ong 'bras gnas /
NK123(go)001:2198: 'dod pa'i sgom spang bdun pa dang brgyad pa gang
NK123(go)001:2199: rung spangs dgu pa ma spang na phyir mi 'ong
NK123(go)001:2200: zhugs pa / 'dod pa'i sgom spang thams cad rdzogs par spangs pa phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas so //
NK123(go)001:2201: des khams gong ma'i sgom spang spong ba la zhugs pa nas bzung /
NK123(go)001:2202: srid rtse'i sgom spang brgyad pa spangs ba'i bar 'di dgra bcom pa la zhugs pa /
NK123(go)001:2203: khams gsum ka'i sgrib pa lhag lus med par spangs ba ni dgra bcom pa gnas so //
NK123(go)001:2205: shes rab kyi cha las nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa
NK123(go)001:2206: tsam las rnam par grol yang rnam thar brgyad la
NK123(go)001:2207: snyoms par 'jug mi nus pas mngon shes dang rdzu
NK123(go)001:2208: 'phrul dang mi ldan pa dgra bcom rgyan med dang
NK123(go)001:2209: / snyoms 'jug gi sgrib pa las kyang grol bas
NK123(go)001:2210: bsam gzugs sogs snyoms 'jug dgu ka la snyoms par
NK123(go)001:2211: 'jug nus shing mngon shes rdzu 'phrul sogs dang ldan
NK123(go)001:2212: pa rgyan can te gnyis dang /
NK123(go)001:2213: yang nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs kyang sngar gyi
NK123(go)001:2214: rnam smin nyer len gyi phung po rnams ma dor
NK123(go)001:2215: bas sdug bden gyi lhag ma cung zad lus pa
NK123(go)001:2216: lhag bcas dang / bud shing zad pa'i me bzhin du mya ngan las 'das dus lus med la /
NK123(go)001:2217: sems 'gag pa'i ye shes 'gog pa'i dbyings su zhugs
NK123(go)001:2218: pa lhag med kyi dbye ba gnyis kyang yod do
NK123(go)001:2219: // de ltar dbye gzhi la ltos nas skyes bu zung bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:2220: dbye chos la ltos nas gang zag ya brgyad ces bya'o //
NK123(go)001:2221: de dag dman lam sa brgyad dang sbyar na /
NK123(go)001:2222: sbyor lam du nyan thos kyi rigs nges pa thob pa ni rigs kyi sa /
NK123(go)001:2223: rgyun zhugs zhugs pa ni brgyad pa'i sa ste dgra
NK123(go)001:2224: bcom 'bras gnas nas mar lug ldog tu bgrangs pas
NK123(go)001:2226: rgyun zhugs 'bras gnas ni mthong ba'i sa ste bden bzhi'i don dang por mthong bas so //
NK123(go)001:2227: phyir 'ang 'bras gnas ni srab pa'i sa ste 'dod
NK123(go)001:2228: nyon chung ngu gsum ma gtogs spangs pas 'dod pa'i
NK123(go)001:2230: phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas ni 'dod chags dang bral
NK123(go)001:2231: ba'i sa ste 'dod nyon dgu pa spangs pas 'dod
NK123(go)001:2232: pa'i 'dod chags dang bral bas so //
NK123(go)001:2233: dgra bcom pa ni byas pa rtogs pa'i sa ste
NK123(go)001:2234: rang don gyi bya ba zad dang mi skye shes
NK123(go)001:2235: pa'i ye shes brnyes pas so //
NK123(go)001:2236: zad dang mi skye shes pa ni /
NK123(go)001:2237: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa sngar yod rnams zad pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2238: phyin chad mi skye bar shes pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2241: dgra bcom pa zhugs pa gsum ni nyan thos kyi sa zhes dang /
NK123(go)001:2242: de yi steng du rang rgyal gyi zhugs gnas bka'
NK123(go)001:2243: brgyad ka gcig tu brtsis te rang sangs rgyas kyi
NK123(go)001:2244: sa zhes bya ste de ltar brgyad do //
NK123(go)001:2245: de dag kyang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK123(go)001:2246: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spong ba yis //
NK123(go)001:2247: ye shes bcu drug cha sbyang rab zhi ba //
NK123(go)001:2248: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim pas sbyangs nas ni //
NK123(go)001:2249: nyon mongs dgra rnams zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK123(go)001:2251: gnyis pa gang zag tha ma'i 'bring gi don du
NK123(go)001:2252: dgongs nas bstan pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa ni
NK123(go)001:2254: rang byang chub kyi theg pa dang zhes gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:2259: slob dpon la ma brten par srid pa tha ma'i
NK123(go)001:2260: tshe byang chub mngon du byed pa'i thabs bdag med
NK123(go)001:2261: phyed dang gnyis rtogs kyi sgo nas rten 'brel gyi
NK123(go)001:2262: lam bsgom pa'o // gnyis pa nges tshig ni /
NK123(go)001:2263: pra t+ye ka bud+d+ha'i sgra las /
NK123(go)001:2264: rang gi byang chub rang gi rtogs par byed pa'i phyir ram /
NK123(go)001:2265: so so'am rang gcig pu byang chub sgrub pas rang rgyal lo //
NK123(go)001:2266: gsum pa dbye ba la sngar ltar drug las /
NK123(go)001:2269: 'jug pa'i sgo ni rten 'brel bcu gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:2271: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug /
NK123(go)001:2273: he ru ka gal po las /
NK123(go)001:2274: rang rgyal chos la blo sbyong phyir //
NK123(go)001:2275: phyi dang nang gi rten 'brel chos //
NK123(go)001:2276: zhes pas phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:2277: de la phyi yi rten 'brel ni /
NK123(go)001:2279: de las rim par sdong bu /
NK123(go)001:2282: me tog /'bras bu'i bar rgyu dang 'brel ba drug dang /
NK123(go)001:2288: dus kyi mi rtag par bsgyur nas 'bras bu rnams
NK123(go)001:2289: skyed par byed pas rkyen dang 'brel ba drug ste
NK123(go)001:2291: nang gi rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis ni /
NK123(go)001:2292: ma rig pa las rga shi'i bar te /
NK123(go)001:2294: ma rig pa ni spyir mi shes pa tsam yin yang /
NK123(go)001:2295: skabs 'dir skye ba 'di 'grub pa'i tshe snga ma'i
NK123(go)001:2296: nyon mongs pa rnams tshe 'di la ltos nas ma
NK123(go)001:2298: 'du byed kyi spyir rgyus 'bras bu bskyed pa tsam yin yang /
NK123(go)001:2299: 'dir tshe 'di grub pa'i sngon rol gyi las so //
NK123(go)001:2300: rnam shes ni spyir yul gyi don tsam rig pa yin yang /
NK123(go)001:2301: 'dir ma'i mngal du dang por 'jug pa'i phung po lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:2302: de bzhin du ming gzugs ni spyi ming bzhi'i phung po dang gzugs /
NK123(go)001:2303: 'dir mngal du zhugs nas kha mig ma dod tshun chad kyi phung po lnga /
NK123(go)001:2304: skye mched drug ni spyir mig la sogs pa tsam /
NK123(go)001:2305: 'dir kha mig dong nas bzung ste dri ro reg bya 'dzin mi nus pa tshun chad /
NK123(go)001:2306: reg pa ni spyir yul dbang shes pa gsum 'dus pa tsam /
NK123(go)001:2307: 'dir bde sdug gi rgyu yul 'dzin cing bde sdug dngos ma bskyes pa tshun chad de /
NK123(go)001:2309: tshor ba ni spyir nyams su myong ba tsam /
NK123(go)001:2310: 'dir mngal du bde sdug rags pa myong ba nas
NK123(go)001:2311: bzung ste 'khrig pa spyod mi nus pa'i bar tshun
NK123(go)001:2312: gyi bde sdug / sred pa ni spyir chags pa tsam /
NK123(go)001:2313: 'dir 'khrigs pa spyod nus pa nas bzung ste nor
NK123(go)001:2314: rdzas sam bud med dam skyes pa btsal ba'i 'dun
NK123(go)001:2315: pa med pa tshun chad de dus thung ngo //
NK123(go)001:2316: len pa ni spyir 'dun pa dang 'dod chags tsam /
NK123(go)001:2317: 'dir sred yul tshol cing ma brnyed pa'i bar /
NK123(go)001:2318: srid pa ni spyir las thams cad /
NK123(go)001:2319: 'dir yul de rnyed nas spyad pas tshe phyi ma
NK123(go)001:2320: 'grub pa'i las bsog pa ste 'chi ka ma tshun
NK123(go)001:2321: chad do // skye ba ni spyir rgyu las skye ba thams cad /
NK123(go)001:2322: 'dir las de'i nus pas tshe phyi mar mngal du zhugs ma thag pa /
NK123(go)001:2323: rga shi spyir 'gag par phyogs pa dang 'gag pa
NK123(go)001:2324: thams cad yin yang 'dir mngal der zhugs nas phyi
NK123(go)001:2325: ma'i ming gzugs dang skye mched drug dang reg pa
NK123(go)001:2326: dang tshor ba ste bzhi po rdzogs pa'i bar thams
NK123(go)001:2327: cad do // de'i srid pa nas rten 'brel gzhan gyi mgo 'dzugs pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:2329: ma rig la sogs sngon gnas skabs //
NK123(go)001:2330: 'du byed dag ni sngon las kyi'o //
NK123(go)001:2331: rnam shes mtshams sbyor phung po yin //
NK123(go)001:2332: ming dang gzugs ni de phan chad //
NK123(go)001:2333: skye mched drug dod tshun chad do //
NK123(go)001:2334: de ni gsum 'dus tshun chad do //
NK123(go)001:2335: reg pa bde sdug la sogs kyi //
NK123(go)001:2336: rgyu shes nus pa tshun chad do //
NK123(go)001:2337: tshor 'khrogs tshun chad sred pa ni //
NK123(go)001:2338: longs spyod 'khrig pa'i chags can gyi'o //
NK123(go)001:2339: nye bar len pa longs spyod rnams //
NK123(go)001:2340: thob par bya phyir rgyug pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2342: las byed de ni srid pa yin //
NK123(go)001:2343: nying mtshams sbyor ba skye ba yin //
NK123(go)001:2344: tshor ba'i bar ni rga shi'o //
NK123(go)001:2345: sngon dang phyi ma bar dag la //
NK123(go)001:2346: rmongs pa rnam par bzlog phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:2348: bcu gnyis po de dag las dang nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal gsum du 'dus te /
NK123(go)001:2351: len pa gsum ni nyon mongs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2352: 'du byed dang srid pa gnyis ni las so //
NK123(go)001:2353: rnam shes la sogs lhag ma bdun ni sdug bsngal te /
NK123(go)001:2355: dang po brgyad pa dgu nyon mongs //
NK123(go)001:2356: gnyis pa bcu pa las yin te //
NK123(go)001:2357: lhag ma bdun yang sdug bsngal yin //
NK123(go)001:2359: de rnams skye ba 'grub pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi dbang du bzhag na /
NK123(go)001:2360: gong bshad las nyon lnga dang rgyu dus kyi rnam shes ni rgyu yin la /
NK123(go)001:2361: ming gzugs sogs sdug bsngal drug 'bras dus kyi rnam shes dang bdun ni 'bras bu'o //
NK123(go)001:2362: yang na rnam shes rgyur bgrangs na rgyu drug 'bras drug ces kyang zer ro //
NK123(go)001:2364: mi tshe gsum la rdzogs te mdzod las /
NK123(go)001:2365: srid pa'i 'khor lo thog ma med //
NK123(go)001:2367: yan lag bcu gnyis cha gsum mo //
NK123(go)001:2368: sngon dang phyi mthar gnyis gnyis dang //
NK123(go)001:2369: bar du brgyad kyang rdzogs ldan la //
NK123(go)001:2371: sngon gyi mtha' ma rig 'du byed gnyis //
NK123(go)001:2372: phyi ma'i mthar skye ba rga shi gnyis //
NK123(go)001:2373: bar du rnam shes la sogs pa'i lhag ma brgyad do //
NK123(go)001:2374: de ltar phyi nang gi rten 'brel de rnams ji ltar 'khor na /
NK123(go)001:2375: phyi yi rten 'brel rnams ni mang nyung gi tshul dang /
NK123(go)001:2376: nang gi rten 'brel lus med rnams la bag chags /
NK123(go)001:2377: lus can rnams la dngos su 'khor ro //
NK123(go)001:2378: de'i sgo nas ji ltar 'jug na /
NK123(go)001:2379: spyir rang rgyal gyi rigs nga rgyal dang skyo shas
NK123(go)001:2380: che zhing gzhan don snying rje chung ba ste de
NK123(go)001:2381: las dbang po rnon po rang gcig pur gnas pa
NK123(go)001:2382: la dga' ba bse ru lta bu ni tshogs lam
NK123(go)001:2383: gyi tshogs bskal ba brgya dang /
NK123(go)001:2384: mang po'i tshogs la dga' ba dbang 'bring tshogs spyod
NK123(go)001:2385: che ba bzod 'bring man chad kyis bsdus pa'i tshogs
NK123(go)001:2387: dbang brtul tshogs sbyor chung ba mthong lam skad cig
NK123(go)001:2388: ma bco lnga man chad kyis bsdus pa'i tshogs mi
NK123(go)001:2389: tshe bcu gsum du bsags pa ste /
NK123(go)001:2390: phyi ma 'di gnyis la dbye na /
NK123(go)001:2391: nyan thos sngon du ma song ba dang /
NK123(go)001:2393: de'i phyi ma la nyan thos so skye tsam dang 'phags pa sngon song gnyis /
NK123(go)001:2395: phyir 'ong tsam sngon song gnyis yod cing /
NK123(go)001:2396: de dag rang rgyal gyi lam du zhugs tshe dngos
NK123(go)001:2397: smra ba rnams kyis sngar bgrod zin gyi lam gyi
NK123(go)001:2398: lhag ma nas 'jug par bshad kyang /
NK123(go)001:2399: dbu ma pa'i lugs la rang rgyal gyi tshogs lam
NK123(go)001:2400: nas 'jug dgos te gzug ba chos kyi bdag med
NK123(go)001:2401: rtogs pa mthar thug pa la de rtogs zin rgyun
NK123(go)001:2402: du sgom pa'i lam sngon du 'gro dgos pa'i phyir
NK123(go)001:2403: bzhed / gang ltar yang gsum kas rten de la
NK123(go)001:2404: byang chub thob pa'i skal ba med par shes nas
NK123(go)001:2405: smon lam 'grub par bya ba'i don du nyan thos
NK123(go)001:2406: kyi sde snod la thos bsam byas pa'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:2407: bzhed / phung po dang / khams dang /
NK123(go)001:2412: gnas drug la mkhas par byas te /
NK123(go)001:2413: sangs rgyas mi bzhugs shing nyan thos kyang med pa'i zhing khams su skye bar gyur cig /
NK123(go)001:2414: skyes nas kyang rten de las lam gyi rtogs pa rang byung du rgyud la skye bar gyur cig /
NK123(go)001:2415: gdul bya la lus kyi brdas chos ston cing sgra'i sgo nas ston par ma gyur cig /
NK123(go)001:2416: ces smon lam gsum btab pas sangs rgyas dang nyan
NK123(go)001:2417: thos kyis yongs su ma bzung ba'i 'jig rten du
NK123(go)001:2420: sangs rgyas rnams ni ma byon cing //
NK123(go)001:2421: nyan thos rnams ni zad pa na //
NK123(go)001:2422: rang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes ni //
NK123(go)001:2423: rten pa med par rab tu skye //
NK123(go)001:2425: rten de la mkhan slob med par rang byung gi dge slong du gyur nas /
NK123(go)001:2426: dur khrod du bor ba'i rus pa mthong ba sogs
NK123(go)001:2427: kyi rkyen gyis 'khor ba las yid 'byung zhing phyi
NK123(go)001:2428: nang gi rten 'brel gyi don rtogs pa'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:2430: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa nyan thos dang 'dra la /
NK123(go)001:2431: de'i steng du chos kyi bdag gi phyed bzung cha
NK123(go)001:2432: rdul phra rab cha bcas dang cha med gnyis ka
NK123(go)001:2433: rang bzhin med par rtogs kyang /
NK123(go)001:2434: da dung 'dzin sems skad cig ma don dam du lta zhing /
NK123(go)001:2436: bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:2438: gzung don rtog pa spong phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:2439: 'dzin pa mi spong phyir dang ni /
NK123(go)001:2440: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK123(go)001:2441: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya //
NK123(go)001:2444: de bzhin rang rgyal theg pa yang //
NK123(go)001:2445: phyi rol bcu gnyis sgyu ma tsam //
NK123(go)001:2446: rdul kyang phyogs chas ma grub 'phags //
NK123(go)001:2447: shes pa skad cig rdzas su mthun //
NK123(go)001:2450: las dang nyon mongs thams cad la //
NK123(go)001:2451: mnyam pa nyid du mi shes shing //
NK123(go)001:2453: 'di ni rang sangs rgyas kyi sa //
NK123(go)001:2455: tshul khrims ni nyan thos dang 'dra ste /
NK123(go)001:2457: nyan thos rang rgyal bsrung mtshams ni //
NK123(go)001:2458: nyis brgya lnga bcu'i 'dul khrims yin //
NK123(go)001:2461: sa sde las nyan thos ltar sgom par gsungs kyang /
NK123(go)001:2463: khyad par yod par bzhed pa ltar //
NK123(go)001:2464: bden bzhi mi rtag sogs bcu drug gi steng du /
NK123(go)001:2465: rten 'brel lugs 'byung bkag nas lugs ldog stong pa bcu gnyis khrigs chags su sgom par byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2466: de yang dur khrod kyi rus pa la bltas te /
NK123(go)001:2468: de yang skye ba las byung ba sogs ma rig
NK123(go)001:2469: pa'i bar du shes shing ma rig pa de bdag
NK123(go)001:2470: med rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis spang bar rig nas
NK123(go)001:2471: lam rang rgyud la brten par byed de /
NK123(go)001:2472: 'di ltar rga shi sdug bsngal gyi ngo bo yin pas /
NK123(go)001:2473: de skye ba las byung ba sogs 'byung rim la bsams pas sdug bsngal bden pa rtogs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2474: skye ba 'gags pas rga shi 'gags pa sogs 'gags
NK123(go)001:2475: rim la bsam pas 'gog pa'i bden pa la 'jug
NK123(go)001:2476: / ma rig pa kun 'byung gi rtsa ba yin pas /
NK123(go)001:2477: de las 'du byed sogs 'byung ba'i rim pa la bsam nas kun 'byung gi bden pa rtogs /
NK123(go)001:2478: ma rig pa 'gags pas 'du byed 'gags pa sogs
NK123(go)001:2479: 'gags rim la bsam nas kun 'byung gi gnyen po
NK123(go)001:2480: bdag med bsgom pa sogs lam bden gyi rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:2482: tshul de lta bu'i sgo nas sgom par byed do //
NK123(go)001:2484: gdul bya la ngag gi mi gsungs bar lus kyi brdas chos ston par byed de /
NK123(go)001:2485: de'ang gdul bya dge ba bcu dang /
NK123(go)001:2487: rten 'brel bcu gnyis don du gnyer ba la brda gcig bstan pas so sor go bar 'gyur te /
NK123(go)001:2489: gang gang don gyi gang gang la //
NK123(go)001:2490: ji ltar ji ltar nyan 'dod pa //
NK123(go)001:2491: de de la don de dang de //
NK123(go)001:2492: sgra med kyang de de ltar snang //
NK123(go)001:2495: spyod pa yul gyi rdzu 'phrul gyis //
NK123(go)001:2499: dbang rnon bse ru lta bu gcig pur bzhugs pa
NK123(go)001:2500: ni bsam gtan bzhi pa rab kyi mtha' la brten
NK123(go)001:2501: te / lam lnga stan thog gcig tu rdzogs nas /
NK123(go)001:2502: yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa /
NK123(go)001:2503: zad pa dang mi skye shes pas dgra bcom mngon du mdzad de /
NK123(go)001:2505: ston dang bse ru byang chub pa //
NK123(go)001:2506: bsam gtan mthar rten gcig la kun //
NK123(go)001:2507: de yi sngon du thar cha mthun //
NK123(go)001:2509: 'di'i lugs kyi skye matha'i byang chub sems dpa' gang zag tshogs lam par 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:2510: dbang brtul ne tso lta bu khyus bzhugs pa tshogs sbyor tshogs spyod che chung gnyis ni /
NK123(go)001:2511: rim par lam bzhi dang gsum stan thog gcig tu mngon du mdzad pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:2512: de yang byang sa sogs las nyan rang spangs rtogs khyad du bzhed kyang /
NK123(go)001:2513: 'di mngon rtogs rgyan gyi dgongs pa ltar khyad yod par 'thad de /
NK123(go)001:2514: nyan thos dgra bcom pas gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa mthar thug cing /
NK123(go)001:2515: rang rgyal dgra bcom pas bzung ba chos kyi bdag
NK123(go)001:2516: med rtags pa mthar thug pa'i khyad par yod pa'i
NK123(go)001:2517: phyir zhes kun mkhyen smin gling yab sras bzhed do
NK123(go)001:2520: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes shing /
NK123(go)001:2521: dngos po'i gzugs la thog med rab tu 'jug /
NK123(go)001:2522: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs //
NK123(go)001:2523: byang chub sa bgrod yid bzhin bde ba mchog /
NK123(go)001:2526: gang zag dbang po tha ma'i rab kyi ngo skal
NK123(go)001:2527: du gsungs pa byang chub sems pa'i theg pa ni
NK123(go)001:2528: / dman pa nyan rang gi lam las chen po
NK123(go)001:2529: bdun gyis khyad par du 'phags pas theg pa chen
NK123(go)001:2532: dmigs pa chen po chos nyid nam mkha' dang 'dra ba la dmigs pa /
NK123(go)001:2533: sgrub pa chen po rang gzhan gnyis ka'i don sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:2534: ye shes chen po bdag gnyis kas stong pa'i chos
NK123(go)001:2535: nyid snying rje dang zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes
NK123(go)001:2536: / brtson 'grus chen po skal pa grangs med par sems can gyi don la brtson pa /
NK123(go)001:2537: thabs la mkhas pa chen po srid zhi'i mtha' la mi gnas pa /
NK123(go)001:2538: grub pa chen po stobs sogs sangs rgyas kyi yon tan tshad med pa /
NK123(go)001:2539: phrin las chen po 'khor ba ji srid par gzhan don lhun grub tu 'byung ba rnams so //
NK123(go)001:2541: mgon po byams pas dmigs pa chen po nyid dang ni //
NK123(go)001:2542: de bzhin sgrub pa gnyis dang ni //
NK123(go)001:2543: ye shes brtson 'grus brtsam pa dang //
NK123(go)001:2544: thabs la mkhas pa gang yin dang //
NK123(go)001:2545: yang dag grub pa chen po dang //
NK123(go)001:2546: sangs rgyas phrin las chen po ste //
NK123(go)001:2547: chen po bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:2548: theg chen zhes ni nges par brjod //
NK123(go)001:2550: theg pa 'di gnyis kyi khyad par yang /
NK123(go)001:2552: theg pa'i khyad par shes rab snying rje kho na ste /
NK123(go)001:2553: 'di dag che chung dbang gis theg pa'i khyad par bstan /
NK123(go)001:2555: shes rab chen pos bdag med gnyis rnal mar rtogs
NK123(go)001:2556: nus pa theg chen dang mi nus pa theg dman
NK123(go)001:2557: / snying rje chen pos gzhan don 'ba' zhig spyod nus pa theg chen dang /
NK123(go)001:2558: de ltar mi nus pa dman pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2560: ye shes rnam par bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:2561: thugs rjes sems can la dmigs shing //
NK123(go)001:2562: shes rab chos kyi dbyings su khyab //
NK123(go)001:2563: theg pa chen po zhes bshad de //
NK123(go)001:2564: gzhan dag de las bzlog pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2567: thabs med shes rab bral bas nyan thos nyid du lhung //
NK123(go)001:2569: de lta bu'i theg chen de la'ang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg pa gnyis yod pa'i snga ma ste /
NK123(go)001:2571: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang //
NK123(go)001:2576: ngo bo ni chos thams cad bdag med par rtogs shing /
NK123(go)001:2577: snying rje chen pos gzhan don brlabs po che spyod pa'i thabs dam pa gyur pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2579: bo d+hi sa t+wa'i sgra las /
NK123(go)001:2580: sems stobs chen pos bla med rdzogs pa'i byang chub
NK123(go)001:2581: sgrub pa la dpa' mi zhum zhing brtson pa'i go
NK123(go)001:2582: cha mi 'dod pa'i phyir byang chub sems dpa' zhes
NK123(go)001:2583: bya'o // dbye ba la sngar ltar drug las /
NK123(go)001:2585: bden pa gnyis kyi sgo nas te /
NK123(go)001:2587: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:2588: 'jug pa'i sgo ni bden pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:2590: de yang dbu ma pa'i gzhung ltar na /
NK123(go)001:2591: ma brtags ma dpyad pa'i snang ba 'di rnams snang yang /
NK123(go)001:2592: ngo bo bden med sgyu ma lta bur shes pa'i
NK123(go)001:2593: blos byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems kyis zin
NK123(go)001:2594: par byas nas / dge mi dge'i 'jug ldog gi tshul gyis kun rdzob bden par 'jug la /
NK123(go)001:2595: don dam par gshis kyi gnas lugs spros bral du
NK123(go)001:2596: shes par byas te zung 'jug gi sgo nas 'jug
NK123(go)001:2597: go // de la spyir bden pa gnyis kyi rnam
NK123(go)001:2598: bzhag tsam ni grub mtha' smra ba thams cad kyis
NK123(go)001:2599: go // khas len te / de'ang nyan thos bye brag smra bas /
NK123(go)001:2600: rags pa'i dngos po dang shes pa'i rgyun ni kun rdzob yin la /
NK123(go)001:2601: shes pa'i skad cig cha med dang /
NK123(go)001:2602: dngos po'i rdul phran cha med don dam du 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:2604: gang la bcom dang blo yis gzhan //
NK123(go)001:2605: gsal na de blo mi 'jug pa //
NK123(go)001:2606: bum chu bzhin du kun rdzob tu //
NK123(go)001:2607: yod de don dam yod gzhan no //
NK123(go)001:2609: mdo sde pas don dam par don byed nus pa bum pa'am ka ba lta bu don dam dang /
NK123(go)001:2610: don dam par don byed mi nus pa nam mkha' dang bum spyi lta bu kun rdzob ste /
NK123(go)001:2611: rang mtshan dang spyi mtshan du 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:2613: don dam don byed nus pa gang //
NK123(go)001:2614: de 'dir don dam yod pa yin //
NK123(go)001:2615: gzhan ni kun rdzob yod pa ste //
NK123(go)001:2616: de dag rang spyi'i mtshan nyid 'dod //
NK123(go)001:2618: sems tsam pas gzung 'dzin gnyis su snang ba'i yul dang yul can ni kun rdzob /
NK123(go)001:2619: gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa tsam ni don dam du 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:2620: ye shes snying po kun btus las /
NK123(go)001:2621: cha shas can zhes bya ba med //
NK123(go)001:2622: phra rab rdul yang yod pa min //
NK123(go)001:2623: so sor snang ba'ang dmigs med la //
NK123(go)001:2624: nyams su myong ba rmi lam 'dra //
NK123(go)001:2625: gzung dang 'dzin pa las grol ba'i //
NK123(go)001:2626: rnam shes dam pa'i don du yod //
NK123(go)001:2627: rnal 'byor spyod gzhung rgya mtsho yis //
NK123(go)001:2628: pha rol phyin rnam de skad bsgrags //
NK123(go)001:2630: dbu ma rang rgyud pa rnams kyis /
NK123(go)001:2631: sna ba kun rdzob tu grub pa sgyu ma'i rta glang bzhin dang /
NK123(go)001:2632: don dam par ci'ang ma grub pa nam mkha' lta bur 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:2634: dmigs bcas kun rdzob don dam du //
NK123(go)001:2635: dmigs bya dmigs byed kun las grol //
NK123(go)001:2637: thal 'gyur pas blos smra bsam brjod par brtags pa rnams ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste /
NK123(go)001:2638: 'jig rten na grags pa'i rjes su brjod cing /
NK123(go)001:2639: gshis spros bral bsam brjod thams cad las 'das pa don dam bden pa zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:2641: ngo bo rtogs bya rtogs byed las 'das pas rtogs
NK123(go)001:2642: par bzhag tu med kyang don dam dang mthun pa'i
NK123(go)001:2645: slob dpon zla ba grags pas /
NK123(go)001:2646: stong pa nyid dang rjes su mthun pa'i blo skyes
NK123(go)001:2647: pa la ni stong pa nyid rtogs so zhes brjod
NK123(go)001:2648: kyi / stong pa nyid ni rtogs pa ma yin no //
NK123(go)001:2649: zhes gsungs pa sogs kyis mtshon zhib par kho bo'i
NK123(go)001:2650: bla ma kun mkhyen blo gros mtha' yas kyi zhal
NK123(go)001:2651: snga nas stsal ba'i bstan bcos chen po shes bya
NK123(go)001:2652: kun khyab sogs las rtogs par bya dgos la /
NK123(go)001:2653: 'dir ni rang lugs rgyud kyi dgongs pa kun mkhyen d+harma sh+r+ais 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:2655: he ru ka gal po che las /
NK123(go)001:2656: sangs rgyas rnams kyis chos bstan pa //
NK123(go)001:2657: bden pa gnyis su yang dag 'dus //
NK123(go)001:2659: de yang dbye gzhi shes bya tsam la /
NK123(go)001:2660: snang lugs kun rdzob dang gnas lugs don dam pa'i bden pa gnyis su dbye ste /
NK123(go)001:2662: shes bya tsam gyi snang ba la //
NK123(go)001:2663: bden pa gnyis kyi gzhi yang grub //
NK123(go)001:2666: blo'i yul du gyur po'i chos can mtshan ma can te /
NK123(go)001:2668: bslu zhing blo yi yul gyur pa //
NK123(go)001:2669: kun rdzob spyi yi mtshan nyid do //
NK123(go)001:2672: snang la don byed nus pa mi la mir snang ba lta bu yang dag kun rdzob /
NK123(go)001:2673: snang la don byed mi nus pa tho yor la
NK123(go)001:2674: mir snang ba ltar bu log pa'i kun rdzob ste
NK123(go)001:2676: kun rdzob dbye ba yang dag dang //
NK123(go)001:2677: log pa'i kun rdzob ces bya'o //
NK123(go)001:2678: so so'i mtshan nyid rab bshad na //
NK123(go)001:2679: snang la don byed mi nus log /
NK123(go)001:2680: yang dag snang la don byed nus //
NK123(go)001:2683: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK123(go)001:2684: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK123(go)001:2685: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK123(go)001:2686: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK123(go)001:2689: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK123(go)001:2691: don dam pa yi mtshan nyid ni //
NK123(go)001:2692: spros pa thams cad bral ba yin //
NK123(go)001:2694: dze ta ri'i bde bar gshegs pa'i gzhung rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK123(go)001:2695: yod min med min yod med min //
NK123(go)001:2696: gnyis ka'i bdag nyid du yang med //
NK123(go)001:2697: mtha' bzhi dag las res grol ba //
NK123(go)001:2700: spros pa phyogs re dang bral ba rnam grangs pa'i don dam dang /
NK123(go)001:2701: spros pa mtha' dag dang bral ba rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam ste /
NK123(go)001:2703: dbye ba rnam grangs don dam dang //
NK123(go)001:2704: rnam grangs ma yin mtha' brgyad bral //
NK123(go)001:2706: de ltar bden pa gnyis po de gcig gam tha dad ce na /
NK123(go)001:2707: tha snyad du chu dang chu zla ltar rang bzhin gcig la ldog pa tha dad de /
NK123(go)001:2709: bu ram rang bzhin mngar ba dang //
NK123(go)001:2710: me yi rang bzhin tsha ba dang //
NK123(go)001:2711: de bzhin chos rnams thams cad kyi //
NK123(go)001:2712: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gnas //
NK123(go)001:2714: don dam par gcig tha dad gang du'ang brjod du med de /
NK123(go)001:2716: 'du byed mtshan ma las brjod du med pa'i dbyings
NK123(go)001:2717: de nyid kyang ma yin la gzhan yang ma yin
NK123(go)001:2720: rgyud rang shar gyi lung gi dgongs pa 'di bzhin du 'grel bar mdzod de /
NK123(go)001:2721: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad bden pa gnyis kyi rang bzhin du 'dus la /
NK123(go)001:2722: de yang chos mtshan mar snang ba blo'i yul du snang rung rnams ni kun rdzob bden pa ste /
NK123(go)001:2723: dbye na log pa dang yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:2725: snang srid snod bcud blos bkod pa'i chos so cog
NK123(go)001:2726: dang bcas pa thams cad log pa'i kun rdzob yin
NK123(go)001:2727: te / yul 'khrul snang blo rdzun pa'i ngo bo la snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:2728: de yang ma brtag par snang ba 'di dag blo 'khrul ngo na mthun par snang ba /
NK123(go)001:2730: brtags na ngo bo nyid kyis dben pa /
NK123(go)001:2731: sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad kyi tshul te /
NK123(go)001:2732: med pa gsal snang tsam du shar ba ni /
NK123(go)001:2734: rmi lam ji bzhin sgyu ma bzhin //
NK123(go)001:2735: dri za'i grong khyer ji bzhin du //
NK123(go)001:2736: de bzhin skye dang de bzhin gnas //
NK123(go)001:2737: de bzhin du yang 'jig par gsungs //
NK123(go)001:2740: 'khrul bar snang yang bde 'gro dang thar pa'i rgyu byed la /
NK123(go)001:2741: dge ba bcu'i las rnam par dkar ba /
NK123(go)001:2742: sbyin pa la sogs pa bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK123(go)001:2743: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom bzhi'i sems kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK123(go)001:2744: ye shes kyi rgyur rung blo'i spyod yul lam bden
NK123(go)001:2747: lam bden thams cad ni 'dus byas /
NK123(go)001:2748: 'dus byas thams cad ni kun rdzob ste /
NK123(go)001:2750: chos nyid rang bzhin du gnas pa stong pa nyid
NK123(go)001:2751: kyi ngo bo dang rjes su 'jal ba'i shes rab
NK123(go)001:2752: spros pa zhi ba'i rnam pa dang bcas pa ni
NK123(go)001:2754: dbye na rnam grangs pa mtshan ma tshig gi don dam dang /
NK123(go)001:2755: rnam grangs ma yin pa yang dag gshis kyi don dam gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:2757: rigs pas phye zhing gshigs na gang du'ang ma grub
NK123(go)001:2758: pa'i chos nyid du thams cad ye nas gnas par
NK123(go)001:2759: rtogs pa'i shes rab gshis dang mthun par skye ba
NK123(go)001:2761: skye sogs bkag pa don dam dang //
NK123(go)001:2762: mthun pa'i phyir yang 'dod pa yin //
NK123(go)001:2763: skye med spros kun zhi ba las //
NK123(go)001:2764: don dam zhes pa'i brda' mdzad do //
NK123(go)001:2767: chos rnams gdod ma nyid nas yod mod kyi spros
NK123(go)001:2768: pa las 'das pa'i dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa
NK123(go)001:2770: gzhan las shes min zhi ba dang //
NK123(go)001:2771: rnam rtog med don tha dad med //
NK123(go)001:2772: spros pa rnams kyi ma spros pa //
NK123(go)001:2773: de ni de yi mtshan nyid do //
NK123(go)001:2775: spyir yang bden gnyis dbye ba'i skabs 'dir gzhung chen po rnams su /
NK123(go)001:2777: stong pa don dam du bzhag pa'i tshul gcig dang /
NK123(go)001:2778: gang gnas snang mthun pa'i yul yul can gnyis ka don dam dang /
NK123(go)001:2779: mi mthun pa'i yul yul can la kun rdzob tu
NK123(go)001:2780: bzhag pa ste 'jog tshul mi 'dra ba gnyis su
NK123(go)001:2781: gnas pas / de gnyis skabs don gang yin ma 'dres par /
NK123(go)001:2782: so sor shan phyed dgos pa ni gnad gal po che ste 'phros don no //
NK123(go)001:2784: bdag med pa gnyis ka phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2785: de la kun rdzob tu chos thams cad chu zla ltar snang la /
NK123(go)001:2786: don dam par spros pa thams cad zhi ba'i tshul
NK123(go)001:2787: du rtogs pas bden gnyis kyi gnas lugs rtogs pa
NK123(go)001:2789: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang rnam par byang ba'i
NK123(go)001:2790: chos thams cad don dam par na rang bzhin med
NK123(go)001:2791: pa yin la / kun rdzob tu ni sgyu ma
NK123(go)001:2792: tsam du so so'i mtshan nyid ma 'dres par yod
NK123(go)001:2793: pa yin la / do // zhes dang /
NK123(go)001:2795: mnyam pa'i don nyid ma shes shing //
NK123(go)001:2796: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed pa //
NK123(go)001:2797: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK123(go)001:2798: 'di ni byang chub sa pa yin //
NK123(go)001:2800: skabs 'dir kun mkhyen chen po'i theg mchog mdzod du 'dir ltar gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:2801: theg chen dbu sems gnyis kyi /
NK123(go)001:2802: sems tsam pa la'ang dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang
NK123(go)001:2803: ba shes pa dang bcas pa 'di thams cad rang
NK123(go)001:2804: gi sems kyi rnam par bden par 'dod pa sems
NK123(go)001:2805: tsam rnam bden pa dang shes pa ni rnam par
NK123(go)001:2806: brdzun pa 'dod pa sems tsam rnam brdzun pa gnyis
NK123(go)001:2807: las / dang po ni don du snang ba rang
NK123(go)001:2808: gi shes pa'i rnam pa phyir shar ba tsam ste
NK123(go)001:2809: las / / rdzing 'gram gyi nor bu'i shing gi
NK123(go)001:2810: yal ga la btags pa'i nor bu ke ke ru'i
NK123(go)001:2811: gzugs brnyan chu nang du shar ba na nor bu'i
NK123(go)001:2812: rnam pa phyi rol du shar ba bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:2815: rnam pa'i grangs de snyed la shes pa'i grangs kyang de snyed du 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2816: rnam pa dang shes pa sgo nga bkas pa ltar 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2817: rnam pa dang shes pa sna tshogs gnyis med du 'dod pa gsum las /
NK123(go)001:2819: sgra thos pa'i dus na sgra 'dzin gyi shes pa gcig pu skye yi /
NK123(go)001:2820: gzugs la sogs pa'i 'dzin pa'i shes pa mi skye ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:2821: yul gang la 'jug pa de'i shes pa skye'i gzhan mi skye bas /
NK123(go)001:2822: rnam pa'i grangs ji snyed pa'i shes pa 'dod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2824: phyi rol sna tshogs su snang ba'ang shes pa las byung la /
NK123(go)001:2825: de 'dzin pa'i shes pa'ang sems las byung bas sgo
NK123(go)001:2826: nga bkas pa ltar rnam pa dang shes pa yul
NK123(go)001:2827: yul can sems gcig las shar ba ste /
NK123(go)001:2828: da lta yul 'dzin pa na phyi rnam pa'i shes pa gcig la /
NK123(go)001:2829: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa gcig shar ba yang /
NK123(go)001:2830: thog ma med pa'i bag chags kyis de ltar gnyis
NK123(go)001:2831: snang yang rang rig pa gcig pu las gzhan du
NK123(go)001:2832: grub pa med pa sgo nga bkas pa lta bu'o
NK123(go)001:2833: // 'o na phyi rnam pa'i shes pa gcig la
NK123(go)001:2834: de'i tshe 'dzin pa'i shes pa gcig byung dus rtog
NK123(go)001:2835: gnyis cig char 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK123(go)001:2837: rnam pa'i shes pa de rtog med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:2840: phyi yul gyi rnam pa sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK123(go)001:2841: nang 'dzin byed kyi shes pa gcig gis shes te /
NK123(go)001:2842: mkhar gyi nang na spre'u gcig 'jug pa myur bas /
NK123(go)001:2843: glo skar bzhir ske rib rib byung nas blta ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:2844: sgo lnga la shes pa gcig gis zhugs nas yul rig pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2845: rig dus na'ang rnam pa dang shes pa gnyis ka
NK123(go)001:2846: sems gcig gi rang bzhin du tha mi dad de
NK123(go)001:2847: / rmi lam gyi snang ba dang 'dzin byed rang
NK123(go)001:2848: du snang ba gnyis ka yang gnyid gcig gi shes
NK123(go)001:2849: par tha mi dad pa bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:2851: gnyis pa rnam brdzun pa ni /
NK123(go)001:2852: phyi don gyi rnam par shes pa la 'khrul bar
NK123(go)001:2853: snang ba'i bag chags rdzun pa yin gyi shes par
NK123(go)001:2855: de 'jal byed kyi shes pa yang rdzun pas gzhal gyi /
NK123(go)001:2856: myong ba bden pas gzhal ba ni med de /
NK123(go)001:2857: yul shes gnyis ka yang 'khrul snang rdzun pa'i rang bzhin tsam du 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:2858: 'di la dbye na dri bcas rdzun par 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2859: dri med dag pa bar 'dod pa gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:2861: da lta'i rnam pa sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:2862: de 'jal ba'i shes pa gnyis ka blo'i dri ma nyid snang ba tsam las /
NK123(go)001:2863: don dam par gnyis su med pa'i ye shes khams
NK123(go)001:2864: kyi yon tan dang bcas pa tsam zhig yod kyi
NK123(go)001:2865: / rnam shes su grub pa ni ci yang med do //
NK123(go)001:2866: sangs rgyas kyi chos sku lhag ma med pa ni /
NK123(go)001:2867: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes nyid de /
NK123(go)001:2868: dri ma med pa'i de bzhin nyid yin la /
NK123(go)001:2869: lhag bcas kyi gnas skabs na bag la nyal gyi
NK123(go)001:2870: dri ma cung zad yod pas 'khrul par snang ba
NK123(go)001:2871: gzigs pa dang / ro rgyab snyung ba la sogs pa yod do zhes pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2872: da lta'i sems la nyon mongs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2873: ye shes 'dres par gnas pa'i dri ma nyon mongs pa'i cha rdzun pa bsal bas /
NK123(go)001:2874: lhag ma med pa'i ye shes dag pa mngon du byed pa'o zhes 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:2875: dag pa ba ni rnam pa dang rnam shes rdzun pa tsam du'ang grub pa med de /
NK123(go)001:2876: mngon par chags pa dag gis na chung yid la byed pa goms pa las /
NK123(go)001:2877: ji zhig na bsam ma dgos par /
NK123(go)001:2878: de'i byad bzhin gyi snang ba med pa gsar snang du shar ba bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:2879: des na yul gyi rnam pa dkar dmar sna tshogs su snang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:2880: 'jal byed kyi blo gnyis ka med bzhi na snang ba gzugs brnyan lta bu ste /
NK123(go)001:2881: de'i don nyams su myong ba'i so so rang rig
NK123(go)001:2882: pa'i ye shes tsam zhig yod do zhes 'dod do
NK123(go)001:2883: // gnyis pa dbu ma pa la rang rgyud pa dang thal 'gyur ba gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:2885: 'di ltar sna tshogs su snang ba'i rnam pa dang
NK123(go)001:2886: 'jal byed med pa gsal snang tsam du ma zad
NK123(go)001:2887: don dam par so so rang gi rig pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:2888: shes de yang rang bzhin gyis ngo bo nyid med
NK123(go)001:2890: 'di la dbye na sgyu ma don dam du 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2891: rab tu mi gnas pa gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:2893: yul yul can grub pa med la /
NK123(go)001:2894: ma grub pa rig pa'i ye shes smra brjod med
NK123(go)001:2895: rtsam zhig don dam par sgyu ma'i tshul du yod
NK123(go)001:2896: pas / bsgom pa'i yon tan sa lam /
NK123(go)001:2897: mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK123(go)001:2898: sgyu ma lta bu thob nas chos kyi sku'i ngang
NK123(go)001:2899: nas sgyu ma lta bus don mdzad pa yin te
NK123(go)001:2901: chos thams cad rmi lam lta bu /
NK123(go)001:2903: mya ngan las 'das pa yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu /
NK123(go)001:2904: mya ngan las 'das pa bas chos lhag pa'i chos shig yod na /
NK123(go)001:2905: de yang rmi lam lta bu sgyu ma lta bu zhes so //
NK123(go)001:2906: chos thams cad ni yul shes sna tshogs pa thams cad do //
NK123(go)001:2907: mya ngan las 'das pa ni gzugs sku brnyes nas don mdzad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2908: de bas lhag pa'i chos ni so so rang rig pa'i de bzhin nyid dang chos sku dam pa'o //
NK123(go)001:2910: 'di la sgyu ma rigs grub tu 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2911: sgyu ma ltar snang du 'dod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2912: sgyu ma tsam por 'dod pa la sogs pa rnams grangs rab tu mang ste /
NK123(go)001:2913: rang rgyud 'og ma pa zhes grags pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:2915: don dam par sgyu ma tsam du'ang mi gnas te /
NK123(go)001:2916: yul dang rnam pa med pas de med par myong ba'i so so rang rig kyang med pa ni /
NK123(go)001:2917: mo gsham gyi bu med pas de 'jal byed kyi shes pa med pa bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:2918: kun rdzob la bden par grub par med pas don dam la gang yang mi gnas te /
NK123(go)001:2919: rmi lam sad pa'i dus na rta glang gi snang ba 'gags kyang /
NK123(go)001:2920: dang po nas med pas don la 'gag rgyur ma grub pa bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:2922: don dam par ni 'khor ba yang med /
NK123(go)001:2923: mya ngan las 'das pa yang med /
NK123(go)001:2924: stong pa nyid kyang med de /
NK123(go)001:2925: tshig gi bla dwags tsam du bas lags so //
NK123(go)001:2928: 'di la kun rdzob rab tu mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2929: rgyu mtshan mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2930: ldog cha mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2931: ldog byed mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2933: du ma mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2934: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba mi gnas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2935: snang tsam rab tu mi gnas la sogs pa rnam grangs dpag tu med pa yod de /
NK123(go)001:2936: dbu ma rang rgyud gong ma pa zhes grags so //
NK123(go)001:2938: de ltar don dam par ma grub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:2939: kun rdzob tu snang tsam sgyu mar grub pa sogs thams cad bkag nas /
NK123(go)001:2940: yod med kyi mtha' las 'das pa'i rang bzhin khas len thams cad dang bral bar 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:2942: rtag dang mi rtag 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK123(go)001:2943: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha' //
NK123(go)001:2944: de phyir gnyis ka'i mtha' ni rnam spangs nas //
NK123(go)001:2945: mkhas pa dbus la'ang gnas par mi byed do //
NK123(go)001:2947: dkon mchog ta la'i mdo las /
NK123(go)001:2948: de bzhin gshegs pa rtag tu skye med chos //
NK123(go)001:2949: chos rnams thams cad bde bar gshegs dang 'dra //
NK123(go)001:2950: byis pa'i blo can mtshan mar 'dzin pas na //
NK123(go)001:2951: 'jig rten dag na med pa'i chos la spyod //
NK123(go)001:2955: 'gag pa med pa skye med pa //
NK123(go)001:2956: chad pa med pa rtag med pa //
NK123(go)001:2958: tha dad don min don gcig min //
NK123(go)001:2959: spros pa nyer zhi zhir bstan pa //
NK123(go)001:2960: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas smra rnams kyi //
NK123(go)001:2961: dam pa de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK123(go)001:2964: gal te ngas dam bcas 'ga' yod //
NK123(go)001:2965: de tshe nga la skyon 'di yod //
NK123(go)001:2966: nga la dam bca' med pas na //
NK123(go)001:2967: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK123(go)001:2969: dgag bya ci yang med pas na //
NK123(go)001:2970: nga ni ci yang mi 'gog go //
NK123(go)001:2971: de phyir dgag par byed do zhes //
NK123(go)001:2972: skur ba de ni khyod kyis btab //
NK123(go)001:2974: de yang blos bkod pa'i grub mtha' gang yang med de spros pa zhi ba'i phyir zhes 'dod cing /
NK123(go)001:2975: sna tshogs su snang tsam 'jig rten pas ji ltar
NK123(go)001:2976: 'jog pa ltar brda' shes pa'i yan lag tu bzhag
NK123(go)001:2977: kyang de yang khas len pa med pas /
NK123(go)001:2978: chos su snang ba bden rdzun las 'das pas yod
NK123(go)001:2979: med kyi mtha' dang da lta'i dus nas bral bar
NK123(go)001:2980: 'dod do // 'di ni sangs rgyas pa rnams kyi
NK123(go)001:2981: grub pa'i mtha' smra ba rnams kyi rtse mo yin
NK123(go)001:2983: de yang skabs 'dir shes par bya ba /
NK123(go)001:2984: rgyal gsung 'khor lo bar tha'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel
NK123(go)001:2985: chen po rnams don gyi zab dgongs 'gal med gcig
NK123(go)001:2986: tu 'bab kyang / gnas skabs dgos pa'i dbang gis
NK123(go)001:2987: zhal bzhes kyi khyad par cung zad tsam re la
NK123(go)001:2988: tu 'bab kyang / brten nas / de dag gi
NK123(go)001:2989: go ba len tshul dang rang rang gi 'dod zhen
NK123(go)001:2990: sbyar ba'i grub matha'i dgag sgrub kyi spros pa du
NK123(go)001:2991: ma 'phags bod gnyis ka na 'byung mod /
NK123(go)001:2992: don la de gnyis gnad kyis mi 'gal bar shes dgos te /
NK123(go)001:2993: 'khor lo bar pa'i dngos bstan dbu ma rigs tshogs
NK123(go)001:2994: dang dpal ldan zla ba'i gzhungs rnams kyi rjes su
NK123(go)001:2995: 'brang nas / snying po'i rang bzhin drang don stong
NK123(go)001:2996: nyid tsam du bzhed pa rnams kyi dgongs pa ni
NK123(go)001:2997: 'brang nas / / chos dbyings ngo bo stong phyogs la dgongs shing /
NK123(go)001:2998: snying po'i yon tan rnams da lta so skye'i rgyud la mngon gyur du med pas /
NK123(go)001:2999: tshogs gnyis goms pa'i rgyu las phyis gsar du sgrub
NK123(go)001:3000: pa ltar snang ba'i phyir bskyed bya skyed byed kyi
NK123(go)001:3001: rgyu 'bras mtshan nyid pa ltar snga phyir khas len
NK123(go)001:3002: pa mtshan nyid theg pa spyi'i dbang du mdzad de
NK123(go)001:3003: snang tshul kun rdzob dbang btsan du mdzad pa yin
NK123(go)001:3004: la / 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo dang dbu ma
NK123(go)001:3005: chos dbyings bstod pa rgyud bla sogs byams gzhung phyi
NK123(go)001:3006: ma rnams kyi rjes su 'brang nas /
NK123(go)001:3007: snying po'i rang bzhin sgra ji bzhin par khas len pa rnams kyis ni /
NK123(go)001:3008: 'od gsal ba'i sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK123(go)001:3009: po gdod ma nas bri gang bsal bzhag dang bral
NK123(go)001:3010: bar sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi chos nyid
NK123(go)001:3011: kyi tshul du gnas pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3012: zag pa med pa'i yon tan gyi chos thams cad
NK123(go)001:3013: kyang nyi mkha' bzhin ye nas 'bral mi srid pa'i
NK123(go)001:3014: sems kyi chos nyid kyi tshul du bzhugs pas /
NK123(go)001:3015: rkyen gyis theg pa chen po'i rigs sad nas lam goms pa'i stobs kyis /
NK123(go)001:3016: med snang glo bur gyi sgrib pa'i dri ma dag
NK123(go)001:3017: stobs kyis lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan gyi tshogs
NK123(go)001:3018: rnams mngon gyur lta bur snang na'ang /
NK123(go)001:3019: bral rgyu bral 'bras tsam las bskyed bya skyed byed kyi rgyu 'bras mtshan nyid par mi bzhed de /
NK123(go)001:3021: nyes pa glo bur dang ldan dang //
NK123(go)001:3022: yon tan rang bzhin gyis ldan phyir //
NK123(go)001:3023: ji ltar sngar bzhin phyis de bzhin //
NK123(go)001:3024: 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid do //
NK123(go)001:3026: des chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3027: gnas lugs don dam bden pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3028: rang byung gi ye shes 'dus ma byas sogs sgo
NK123(go)001:3029: du ma nas sems 'grel skor gsum sogs 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:3030: gsang sngags dang sgo mthun par mdo sngags mtshams sbyor
NK123(go)001:3031: gyi tshul gyis mthar thug theg gcig tu sgrub par
NK123(go)001:3032: mdzad pa ni gnas tshul don dam dang mthun pa
NK123(go)001:3033: yin la / rang lugs kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos ni /
NK123(go)001:3034: de gnyis gnad kyis mi 'gal ba la dgongs nas
NK123(go)001:3035: mdo phyogs kyi grub mtha' 'jog pa'i skabs 'dir 'khor
NK123(go)001:3036: lo bar pa'i dngos bstan dbu ma thal 'gyur ba
NK123(go)001:3037: nyid grub matha'i rtse mor zhal gyis bzhes pa ni
NK123(go)001:3038: / gzhi ka dag gi gnas lugs dang mthun zhing
NK123(go)001:3039: dngos smra ba rnams kyi log rtog gi bsgol ba
NK123(go)001:3040: 'joms pa la ches stobs dang ldan pa yin zhing
NK123(go)001:3041: / / sngags mthun min spyi dang khyad par rang
NK123(go)001:3042: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhi'i gnas lugs gtan la
NK123(go)001:3044: 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo dang khyad par rgyud bla
NK123(go)001:3045: ma sogs kyi lung rnams drangs nas nges don gyis
NK123(go)001:3046: mdo rgyud zab mo rnams dgongs pa'i gsang mdzod gcig
NK123(go)001:3047: par yid bzhin mdzod kyi le'u bco brgyad pa rtsa
NK123(go)001:3048: 'grel dang / grub mtha' mdzod sogs mdzod chen bdun /
NK123(go)001:3050: yang tig rnam gsum gyis mtshon gsung rab mtha' dag nas gsal por bstan mdzad pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3051: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas lugs 'od gsal
NK123(go)001:3052: mthar thug gi dgongs pa dang gnad gcig pa'i phyir
NK123(go)001:3053: de nyid nges don mthar thug tu lung rigs tshad
NK123(go)001:3054: ma gsum gyis yang dang yang du sgrub par mdzad
NK123(go)001:3055: pa bzhin / chos kyi rgyal po smin gling pa
NK123(go)001:3056: sku mched gtsos gsang chen snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa'i
NK123(go)001:3057: shing rta ba chen po rnams kyis nges don seng
NK123(go)001:3058: ge'i sgra chen po sgrog par mdzad pa yin la
NK123(go)001:3059: pa bzhin / / de'i tshul mdo tsam ni gzhan du bshad zin la /
NK123(go)001:3060: rtsod dus kyi thams cad mkhyen pa dpal sprul rin
NK123(go)001:3061: po ches kyang snying thig gi rgyud don rnam par
NK123(go)001:3062: dbye ba'i 'phyong mun khang sgron me sogs las gsal
NK123(go)001:3063: bar bstan pas kyang shes par nus la /
NK123(go)001:3064: don la chos dbyings snang stong zung 'jug spros bral
NK123(go)001:3065: mnyam pa chen po'i dgong pa'i gting phyin na dgags
NK123(go)001:3066: sgrub kyi spros pa'i 'dzin stangs thams cad mtha' bral
NK123(go)001:3067: dbu ma chen po'i klong du zhi nas bsam gyis
NK123(go)001:3068: mi khyab pa'i ye shes kyi snang ba rgyas par
NK123(go)001:3069: 'gyur bas / de ltar go zhing legs par khong
NK123(go)001:3070: du chud na dbu phyag rdzogs gsum sogs gang ltar
NK123(go)001:3071: bshad kyang don gyi dgongs pa gcig tu 'babs pas
NK123(go)001:3072: 'gyur bas / / lta sgom grub matha'i 'gags rnams
NK123(go)001:3073: rang sar grol nas dgongs pa'i gsang mdzod ye shes
NK123(go)001:3074: kyi klong du 'gre bar 'gyur ba ni gal che
NK123(go)001:3075: 'phros don du smos pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:3077: sdom sdud don byed kyi tshul khrims gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:3078: de las nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims ni /
NK123(go)001:3079: dbu ma lugs la sems bskyed len pa'i rten du
NK123(go)001:3080: so thar gyi sdom ldan dgos pa ma nges kyang
NK123(go)001:3081: byang sar nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims so thar
NK123(go)001:3082: rig bdun la bshad pa ltar de dag gzhir bzhag
NK123(go)001:3083: gi steng du / byang chub la dmigs pa'i smon sems dang /
NK123(go)001:3084: de'i ched du tshogs dang bya ba la sbyor ba'i 'jug sems te /
NK123(go)001:3085: dbu sems gang rung gi cho gas blang la de'i bslab bya la bslab bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3086: de yang so thar gyi dbang du byas na dus khrims bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3087: gtan khrims so sor thar pa rig bdun te /
NK123(go)001:3088: de rnams kyang bsam pa tshe 'dis rgyal po'i chad
NK123(go)001:3089: pa dang dpya khral sogs la 'jigs nas de las
NK123(go)001:3090: skyob pa'i ched du blang ba 'jigs skyobs /
NK123(go)001:3091: phyi mar lha mi'i go 'phang dang /
NK123(go)001:3092: tshe 'dir zas gos sogs kyi bde skyid la dmigs nas blang ba legs smon te /
NK123(go)001:3093: 'di gnyis mngon mtho tsam las nges legs thar pa'i
NK123(go)001:3094: rgyur mi 'gyur zhing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mtha' dag
NK123(go)001:3095: las rang nyid gcig pu thar 'dod kyis blang ba
NK123(go)001:3096: nges 'byung gi tshul khrims te theg dman gyi so
NK123(go)001:3098: de la byang chub sems kyis zin pa na theg chen so thar du 'gyur la /
NK123(go)001:3099: de yang dang por blang ba'i dus 'jigs skyobs dang legs smon gyi tshul khrims yin yang /
NK123(go)001:3100: phyis nges 'byung nam skyes pa na nges 'byung dang /
NK123(go)001:3101: byang sems nam skyes pa na theg pa chen po'i
NK123(go)001:3102: so thar du 'gro ba yin pas gnad 'di shes
NK123(go)001:3104: byang sems rang gi dbang du byas na /
NK123(go)001:3106: sems tsam gyi bslab bya gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:3109: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog 1dang ni chos spong 2las //
NK123(go)001:3110: tshul ldan tshul 'chal khrims gcod bslab 'bebs 3sogs //
NK123(go)001:3111: mtshams med las byed log 5lta lnga rgyal po //
NK123(go)001:3112: grong ljongs grong khyer grong brdal yul 'khor rnams //
NK123(go)001:3113: 'joms par byed pa'ang blon por nges pa lnga //
