NK123(go)001:3114: ma sbyangs stong nyid brjod sngas nyan thos smon /
NK123(go)001:3116: 1 / rdzogs byang phyir ldog theg dman sems bskyed 2dang //
NK123(go)001:3117: so thar spangs nas theg chen slob pa dang //
NK123(go)001:3118: nyan thos theg pas chags sogs mi zlog pas //
NK123(go)001:3119: de bzlog de yi 'bras bu med par byas /
NK123(go)001:3121: 4 / phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan smod 5dang //
NK123(go)001:3122: rnyed dang bskur sti'i ched du bdag 'tshongs 6dang //
NK123(go)001:3123: dge slong chad pa gcod 'jug sug 'bul 7dang //
NK123(go)001:3124: spong ba'i longs spyod kha ton pa la byin //
NK123(go)001:3125: zhi gnas 'dor bcug phal la 'byung nges brgyad //
NK123(go)001:3126: de der 'byung nyes bzhag gis kun la kun //
NK123(go)001:3127: ming du bco brgyad rdzas su bcu bzhi ste //
NK123(go)001:3128: smon 'jug sems btang de rnams rtsa ltung yin //
NK123(go)001:3129: zhes rtsa ltung nyi shu dang /
NK123(go)001:3131: thogs med lugs kyi smon pa'i bslab bya la //
NK123(go)001:3132: sems can blos mi btang 1dang phan yon 2 dran //
NK123(go)001:3133: tshogs bsags 3byang sems sbyang la 4brtson pa dang //
NK123(go)001:3134: dkar nag chos brgyad blang dor smon pa'i yin //
NK123(go)001:3137: 2 / dam par bskur 'debs 3'gro la g.yo sgyu spyod //
NK123(go)001:3138: nag po'i chos bzhi spong zhing ldog pa ni //
NK123(go)001:3139: dkar po'i chos bzhi yin pas kun tu spyad //
NK123(go)001:3140: rnyed bskur lhag zhen bdag bstod gzhan smod 1dang //
NK123(go)001:3141: se snas zang zing nar dang chos mi ster /
NK123(go)001:3143: 2 / khro bas gzhan 'tshe shad sbyang gis mi ldog /
NK123(go)001:3144: g.yom las chos ltar bcos mas ston bya bzhi //
NK123(go)001:3145: rtsa ltung bzhi ste 'jug pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3146: zhes gsungs pa ltar smon pa'i bslab bya sems can blos mi btang ba sogs bzhi /
NK123(go)001:3147: byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa'i thabs dkar nag chos brgyad la blang dor bya zhing /
NK123(go)001:3148: 'jug pa'i bslab bya rtsa ltung bzhi sogs dran shes
NK123(go)001:3149: bzhin bag yod dang ldan pa'i sgo nas bsrung ba'o
NK123(go)001:3150: // dge ba chos bsdud kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK123(go)001:3151: tshogs gnyis dang 'brel ba'i phar phyin drug sogs dge ba'i chos rgya mtsho lta bu sgrub cing /
NK123(go)001:3152: de'i mi mthun phyogs spang ba la bslab par bya ba'o //
NK123(go)001:3153: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK123(go)001:3154: bsam pa dge ba'i rtsa ba che chung ci sgrub kyang gzhan don la dmigs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3155: sbyor ba bsdu dngos bzhi'i sgo nas sems can gyi don sgrub cing /
NK123(go)001:3156: gzhan don yal bar dor ba'i blo spang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:3159: sbyin 1 pa'i g.yab mos legs bos te //
NK123(go)001:3160: snyan par smra ba'i tshig 2gis bsru //
NK123(go)001:3161: don 3mthun pa yis bag phab ste //
NK123(go)001:3162: don spyod 4gros chen gdab par bya //
NK123(go)001:3165: spyir slob mas bzhi'i byang chub kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun bsgom zhing /
NK123(go)001:3166: bye brag tu thog ma nas ji ltar nyams su
NK123(go)001:3167: len pa'i tshul 'khor lo tha ma nges don gyi
NK123(go)001:3168: mdo sde'i dbang du byas nas /
NK123(go)001:3169: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i tshul khong du chud par byas pa /
NK123(go)001:3170: rigs can des byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas /
NK123(go)001:3171: zhi lhag zung 'jug gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom par byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3172: de la kho bo'i bla ma nges pa don gyi
NK123(go)001:3173: thams cad mkhyen pa 'jam dbyangs mkhyen brtse'i dbang pos
NK123(go)001:3175: tshogs lam chung ngur dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:3176: dran pa ni lus la sogs pa rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid tshul bzhin du shes pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3177: nye bar bzhag pa ni de'i ngang du rtse gcig gis mnyam par bzhag pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3178: 'di la dngos po yongs su rtogs pa'i lam zhes kyang bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3179: ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul la lus dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK123(go)001:3180: mnyam bzhag tu phyi nang gi lus rang bzhin gyis ma grub pa nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK123(go)001:3181: rjes thob tu dur khrod kyi gzugs rnying pa ltar mi gtsang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3182: bden med sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad kyi tshul du gtan la phab nas bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3183: tshor ba ngan pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK123(go)001:3184: mnyam bzhag tu phyi nang gi tshor ba bde sdug
NK123(go)001:3185: bar ma'i rnam par shar ba thams cad gdod nas
NK123(go)001:3187: rjes thob tu tshor ba sdug bsngal ba ni sdug bsngal dang /
NK123(go)001:3188: bde ba ltar snang ba ni 'gyur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3189: btang snyoms ni khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal
NK123(go)001:3190: kho na las ma 'das par shes shing snying po
NK123(go)001:3191: med par gtan la phab nas sgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3192: sems dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK123(go)001:3193: mnyam bzhag tu sems kyi chos nyid rang bzhin gyis
NK123(go)001:3194: stong pa nyid spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral
NK123(go)001:3195: ba dang / rjes thob tu cir yang ma 'gags
NK123(go)001:3196: shing gang du'ang mi gnas par gtan la phab nas
NK123(go)001:3197: ba dang / bsgom pa'o // chos dran pa nyer bzhag ni /
NK123(go)001:3198: mnyam bzhag tu 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK123(go)001:3199: rjes thob tu rang rang gi rgyu rkyen rten 'brel
NK123(go)001:3200: tshogs pa las byung ba sgyu ma lta bur gtan
NK123(go)001:3202: de ltar bsgom pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3203: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi la 'jug par bya ba'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:3204: lus dran pa nye bar bzhag pa las ni sdug bsngal shes pa la 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:3205: lus 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal gyi rab tu phye bar rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3206: tshor ba dran pa nye bar bzhag pa las ni /
NK123(go)001:3208: kun 'byung gi gtso bo sred pa ni tshor ba gsum gyi rgyu can du rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3209: sems dran pa nye bar bzhag pa las ni /
NK123(go)001:3210: 'gog pa mngon du bya ba la 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:3211: de las bdag dang bral ba'i rnam par shes pa
NK123(go)001:3212: skad cig gis 'jig par rtogs pas mya ngan las
NK123(go)001:3213: 'das pa'i tshe bdag chad kyis dog pa'i skrag pa
NK123(go)001:3214: med pa'i phyir / chos dran pa nye bar bzhag pa las ni /
NK123(go)001:3215: lam gyi bden pas bsgom pa la 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:3216: nyon mongs pa'i chos rnams spang bya dang rnam par
NK123(go)001:3217: byang ba'i chos rnams blang byar rtogs pa'i phyir ro
NK123(go)001:3218: // tshogs lam 'bring du yang dag par spong ba bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:3219: brtson 'grus kyis dge ba bskyed cing mi dge ba'i
NK123(go)001:3220: chos rnams spong bas na yang dag par spong ba
NK123(go)001:3221: ste rtsol ba las byung ba'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3223: mi dge ba'i chos sngar ma skyes 1pa rnams mi bskyed cing /
NK123(go)001:3224: skyes pa rnams yang dag par 2spong ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3225: dge ba'i chos sngar ma skyes 3pa rnams bskyed cing /
NK123(go)001:3226: skyes pa rnams gong nas 4gong du yang dag spel ba ste /
NK123(go)001:3232: rab tu 'jog pa'i tshul gyis bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3233: de la 'dun pa bskyed pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3234: dang por blang dor la yid ches pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK123(go)001:3235: 'bad pa ni sems de las gzhan du mi yeng ba'i tshul gyis so //
NK123(go)001:3237: bying sgod la sogs pa zhi bar bya ba'i don du'o //
NK123(go)001:3238: sems rab tu 'dzin pa ni bying rmugs su gyur
NK123(go)001:3239: na rgyal ba'i sku dang yon tan la sogs sems
NK123(go)001:3240: spro bar gyur pa'i gnas la dmigs nas sems rab
NK123(go)001:3241: tu 'dzin pa'o // sems rab tu 'jog pa ni
NK123(go)001:3242: 'phro rgod du gyur na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sogs
NK123(go)001:3243: skyo bar 'gyur ba'i yul dmigs la nas sems rab
NK123(go)001:3244: tu 'dzin pa'o // tu 'jog pa'o // tshogs lam chen por rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:3245: spyan dang mngon shes rdzu 'phrul la sogs pa bsgrub
NK123(go)001:3246: pa'i rgyu zhi lhag zung 'brel gyi ting 'dzin las
NK123(go)001:3247: su rung bar goms par byed pas na rdzu 'phrul
NK123(go)001:3249: ting nge 'dzin yongs su sbyong ba'i lam zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3251: nyes pa lnga'i gnyen por spong pa'i 'du byed brgyad
NK123(go)001:3252: ldan pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom par byed pa ste
NK123(go)001:3255: le lo 1dang ni gdams ngag rnams //
NK123(go)001:3261: le lo'i gnyen po bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:3265: gdams ngag brjed pa'i gnyen po dran pa /
NK123(go)001:3266: 5 bying rgod kyi gnyen por shes bzhin /
NK123(go)001:3267: 6 gnyen po mngon par 'du mi byed pa'i gnyen por mngon par 'du byed pa /
NK123(go)001:3268: 7 bying rgod zhi nas kyang mngon par 'du mi
NK123(go)001:3269: byed pa'i gnyen por 'du byed btang snyoms rnams so
NK123(go)001:3271: bsam gtan gyi 'bras bu la mngon par dad cing
NK123(go)001:3272: gus pa'i 'dun pas ting nge 'dzin la sbyor bas
NK123(go)001:3273: sems las su rung ba thob pa 'dun 1pa'i rdzu
NK123(go)001:3275: de bzhin du rgyun du sbyor ba'i brtson 'grus kyi
NK123(go)001:3276: sems las su rung ba thob pa brtson 'grus kyi
NK123(go)001:3277: / sngon du ting nge 'dzin la sems pa'i bag
NK123(go)001:3278: chags dang ldan pas sems las su rung ba thob
NK123(go)001:3279: pa'i sems kyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen las thos pa'i
NK123(go)001:3280: dmigs pa rnams bsam byung gi shes rab kyis rnam
NK123(go)001:3281: par 'byed pa la bslab pas sems las su rung
NK123(go)001:3282: ba thos pa dpyod pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa
NK123(go)001:3283: / ste bzhi'o // sbyor lam gyi drod dang rtse mo dbang po lnga bsgom ste /
NK123(go)001:3284: 'di lngas bden pa mngon par rtogs pa la dbang byed pas dbang po zhes bya /
NK123(go)001:3286: bden bzhi'i mi rtag pa la sogs pa'am /
NK123(go)001:3287: chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su shes pa'i don la dmigs te /
NK123(go)001:3288: dad 1pa'i dbang pos bden pa'i rnam pa la yid ches pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3289: brtson 'grus kyis bden pa rtogs phyir spro ba 2dang /
NK123(go)001:3290: dran 3pas dmigs pa mi brjed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3291: ting 4nge 'dzin gyis dmigs pa la rtse gcig tu sbyor ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3292: shes rab kyis bden pa rnams kyi rang bzhin shes pa'i tshul gyis bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3293: bzod pa dang chos mchog tu stobs lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:3294: dad pa'i dbang po sogs kyi rgyun goms pas rang rang gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs /
NK123(go)001:3299: shes rab 'chal ba rnams kyis cung zad tsam yang bar du gcod par mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3300: dad pa'i stobs sogs lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:3301: bsgom tshul ni snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK123(go)001:3302: mthong lam du byang chub yan lag bdun te /
NK123(go)001:3303: mthong ba'i lam byang chub zag pa med pa'i yan
NK123(go)001:3304: lag tu 'gyur bas na byang chub kyi yan lag
NK123(go)001:3305: ces bya / chos rab tu rnam par 'byed pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3307: yan lag kyang yin zhing gzhan drug po ni de'i
NK123(go)001:3308: grogs su gyur pas na yan lag ste bdun no
NK123(go)001:3309: // de la dran 1pa ni dmigs pa mi brjed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3310: shes rab kyi gnas yin pas gnas kyi yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:3311: chos rab tu rnam 2 par 'byed pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3312: theg pa chen po'i bden pa bzhi la dmigs pa'i
NK123(go)001:3313: chos bzod chos shes rjes bzod rjes shes 'khor dang
NK123(go)001:3314: bcas pa'i mtshan nyid so sor 'byed pa'i shes rab
NK123(go)001:3316: rang bzhin gyi yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:3317: brtson 'grus ni de'i rang bzhin la spro bas zhugs
NK123(go)001:3318: pa la brten nas so so skye bo'i gnas nas
NK123(go)001:3319: nges par 'byung zhing de las 'da' bar byed pa'i
NK123(go)001:3320: phyir nges par 'byung ba'i yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:3322: sa dang po mthong ba'i dga' ba des lus sems
NK123(go)001:3323: la phan 'dogs shing tshim par byed pa ste phan
NK123(go)001:3326: lus sems las su rung ba ste /
NK123(go)001:3327: gang 'dod du bkol du btub pas nyon mongs pa med pa'i gazhi'o //
NK123(go)001:3329: dmigs pa la sems rtse gcig pa las gzhan du ma 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3330: nyon mongs pa med pa'i gnas so //
NK123(go)001:3331: btang snyoms ni sems dang sems byung gi rnyogs ma
NK123(go)001:3332: bying rgod kyi skyon dang bcas pa rang sar zhi
NK123(go)001:3333: ba ste / nyon mongs med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK123(go)001:3334: de ltar 'di gsum la nyon mongs med pa'i yan lag zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3335: bsgom lam sa dgur 'phags lam yan lag brgyad bsgom ste /
NK123(go)001:3336: 'phags pa rnams kyis bgrod par bya ba'i 'jug ngogs
NK123(go)001:3337: su gyur pa'i lam la 'phags pa'i lam gyi yan
NK123(go)001:3339: de la yang dag pa'i lta ba 1ni /
NK123(go)001:3340: sa gnyis pa yan chad kyi zag med kyi shes rab ste /
NK123(go)001:3341: des sa dang po sogs su chos kyi dbyings la
NK123(go)001:3342: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyis 'di ltar
NK123(go)001:3343: mthong ngo snyam du gcod pas na yongs su gcod
NK123(go)001:3345: yang dag pa'i rtog pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3346: chos rnams ni rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid ma nor
NK123(go)001:3347: bar brtag pa ste gzhan la go bar byed pa'i
NK123(go)001:3348: yan lag / yang dag pa'i ngag gi rang 3gis
NK123(go)001:3349: ji ltar rtogs pa de bzhin du gzhan la 'chad
NK123(go)001:3350: par byed pas ji ltar dris pa de bzhin du
NK123(go)001:3351: lung ston pas na lta ba rnam par dag pa
NK123(go)001:3352: yan lag / dang / yang dag pa'i las kyi mtha' 4ni /
NK123(go)001:3353: srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i mi dge ba cung
NK123(go)001:3354: zad kyang mi byed pas spyod pa phun sum tshogs
NK123(go)001:3355: pa'i phyir tshul khrims rnam par dag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3356: yang dag pa'i 'tsho ba ni log 'tsho spangs te
NK123(go)001:3357: de bzhin gshegs pas ji ltar gnang ba bzhin du
NK123(go)001:3358: longs spyod pas 'tsho ba rnam dag tu yid ches
NK123(go)001:3359: pas na / 'di gsum ni gzhan yid ches par byed pa'i yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:3361: sgom lam gyis spang bar bya ba'i nyon mongs pa rnams spong ba'i ched du brtson 'grus rtsom pa /
NK123(go)001:3363: nye ba'i nyon mongs pa bying rgod kyi gnyen po'i dmigs pa mi brjed pa /
NK123(go)001:3364: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK123(go)001:3365: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i sa la brten nas mngon par
NK123(go)001:3366: shes pa la sogs pa'i yon tan rgya chen po
NK123(go)001:3367: sgrub pa ste / 'di gsum ni mi mthun pa'i gnyen po'i yan lag go //
NK123(go)001:3368: de ltar slob lam du byang phyogs so bdun la
NK123(go)001:3369: goms pa la brten nas mthar phyin mi slob pa'i
NK123(go)001:3370: lam la sbyor bar byed pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:3371: bye brag tu lam sgom pa'i thog mar de bzhin
NK123(go)001:3372: gshegs pa'i snying po'am rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs nyid
NK123(go)001:3373: rang la yod par shes dgos kyi de ma shes
NK123(go)001:3374: na sangs rgyas sgrub 'dod kyi blo mi skye ste
NK123(go)001:3375: / dper na 'og na gser yod par ma nges
NK123(go)001:3376: na gser brko 'dod kyi blo mi skye ba bzhin
NK123(go)001:3378: khams yod na ni las byas pas //
NK123(go)001:3379: sa le sbram dag mthong bar 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:3380: khams med na ni las byas kyang //
NK123(go)001:3381: nyon mongs 'ba' zhig skye bar zad //
NK123(go)001:3382: ces gsungs de la mthar thug chos sku'i yon tan nam mkha' dang mnyam pa de /
NK123(go)001:3383: sngon tha mal 'ching ba kun ldan du gyur pa'i
NK123(go)001:3384: gang zag gi rgyud las phyis mngon du gyur pa
NK123(go)001:3385: yod pa'i phyir dang rigs med na brtson kyang de
NK123(go)001:3387: chos sku'i yon tan de rang bzhin 'dus ma byas rtag pa'i ngo bo yin pa'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:3388: rgyu mtshan gsum gyis sems can gyi rgyud la sangs
NK123(go)001:3389: rgyas kyi snying po yod par ltos pa'i rigs pas
NK123(go)001:3390: grub pa dang / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK123(go)001:3391: gnas lugs stong chen gdod ma'i 'od gsal chen por
NK123(go)001:3392: dbyer med ro gcig pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3393: 'khrul ba glo bur bas sprul pa'i sems can rnams
NK123(go)001:3394: kyang gnas lugs don dam pa'i chos nyid las ma
NK123(go)001:3395: g.yos par chos nyid kyi rigs pas grub pa dang
NK123(go)001:3396: / dri ma glo bur pa spang rung dang /
NK123(go)001:3397: yon tan ye ldan gyi chos sku kun la khyad med du yod pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3399: de yod na lus can de sangs rgyas kyi snying
NK123(go)001:3400: po can du bya ba byed pa'i rigs pas grub
NK123(go)001:3401: pa sogs rnam dag rigs pa'i sgo dang /
NK123(go)001:3402: nges don phyir mi ldog pa'i mdo sde zab mo rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:3403: rje btsun byams pas mdzad pa'i rgyud bla ma /
NK123(go)001:3404: 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa'i chos dbyings bstod pa sogs yid ches pa'i lung dang /
NK123(go)001:3405: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa'i gsar rgyud
NK123(go)001:3406: thun mong ma yin pa rnams kyi man ngag ste
NK123(go)001:3407: / tshad ma gsum la brten nas yid ches pa
NK123(go)001:3408: gal che zhing don gyi gnad 'di la 'phags yul
NK123(go)001:3409: gyi shing rta chen po rnams dgongs pa gcig tu
NK123(go)001:3410: / 'bab na'ang / gnas skabs kyi grub matha'i khas len phra mo tsam la brten nas /
NK123(go)001:3411: gangs can gyi khrod du dgongs pa len tshul tha
NK123(go)001:3412: dad pa'i dbang gis dgag sgrub kyi chu gter rnam
NK123(go)001:3413: par 'khrugs mod / don du khams bde bar gshegs
NK123(go)001:3414: pa'i snying po zab gsal gnyis med kyi ye shes
NK123(go)001:3415: zab mo de nyid gdul bya yongs su ma smin
NK123(go)001:3416: pa rnams kyis thog ma nas thos na skrag par
NK123(go)001:3417: par 'khrugs mod / 'gyur ba'i phyir / rgyal bas 'khor lo dang por dngos su ma bstan cing /
NK123(go)001:3418: bar bar bdag tu lta ba'i gnyen por ngo bo
NK123(go)001:3419: stong phyogs kyi sgo nas rnam thar sum ldan du
NK123(go)001:3420: gsungs pa dang / 'khor lo tha mar yongs su
NK123(go)001:3421: sbyongs bar byas pa'i byang sems skal pa chen po
NK123(go)001:3422: rnams kyi ngor rang bzhin sku dang ye shes sogs
NK123(go)001:3423: snang phyogs kyi cha nas nges don drang thad du
NK123(go)001:3425: rigs khams nor bu sbyang ba'i dpe sogs kyis gsal bar bstan pa bzhin la /
NK123(go)001:3426: mthar thug thun mong ma yin pa'i gnad gsang rnams ni gsang rgyud spyi dang /
NK123(go)001:3427: khyad par dus kyi 'khor lo las gsal bar bstan
NK123(go)001:3428: zhing mthar thug pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK123(go)001:3429: por gtan la phab pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:3430: de dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas pa ni kun mkhyen
NK123(go)001:3431: chos kyi rgyal po'i gsungs kyi gsang mdzod rnams dang
NK123(go)001:3432: / kho bo'i bla ma 'jam dpal dgyes pa'i rdo
NK123(go)001:3433: rje'i zhal snga nas rtsal ba'i bde gshegs snying po'i
NK123(go)001:3434: stong thun seng ge'i nga ro dang gnyug ma 'od
NK123(go)001:3435: gsal gyi don la dpyad pa sogs las rtogs par
NK123(go)001:3436: bya ba las 'dir yi ges 'jigs nas ma spros
NK123(go)001:3439: thar pa dge ba'i rten ni rigs yin la //
NK123(go)001:3440: de yang sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK123(go)001:3441: dri med khams te rang bzhin gnas pa'i rigs //
NK123(go)001:3442: de yi snang cha sku gnyis dpe rnams dgu //
NK123(go)001:3443: snying po'i rang bzhin ye nas gnas pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3444: rgyas 'gyur rigs zhes bde bar gshegs pas gsungs /
NK123(go)001:3445: rtsa ba rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal ba /
NK123(go)001:3446: ngo bo dug gsum med pa'i dge ba yin /
NK123(go)001:3448: de'ang rang bzhin gyis dag cing ngo bo nyid dri
NK123(go)001:3449: ma med pa'i sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi ye shes
NK123(go)001:3450: dam pa ye nas gnas pa'i sems kyi rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:3451: 'od gsal ba'i snang cha nas sangs rgyas kyi gzugs
NK123(go)001:3452: sku'i yon tan lhun grub tu yod pa dpe dgus
NK123(go)001:3453: bstan cing stong cha la chos sku'i yon tan nam
NK123(go)001:3454: mkha' lta bu'i dpe mdo rgyud thams cad nas bshad
NK123(go)001:3455: la / de gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa ni thog ma med pa'i ches khams dge ba ste /
NK123(go)001:3456: 'gyur ba med pas rang bzhin pa'i rigs dang /
NK123(go)001:3457: dri ma sbyangs nas yon rgyas par mngon pas rgyas 'gyur gyi rigs zhes btags kyang /
NK123(go)001:3458: rtsa ba rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal ba nyid do //
NK123(go)001:3460: rigs gnyis su bshad pa'ang ngo bo gcig la ldog
NK123(go)001:3461: pas phye ba tsam las don la ni rang gi
NK123(go)001:3462: sems nyid spros bral rang byung gi ye shes gshis
NK123(go)001:3463: cir yang ma grub la gdangs 'gag med du 'char
NK123(go)001:3464: ba'i gnyug ma'i shes pa dwangs gsal rjen pa 'di
NK123(go)001:3465: nyid rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK123(go)001:3466: sa bon nam bde gshegs snying po yin te /
NK123(go)001:3468: sa yi dkyil na yod pa'i chu //
NK123(go)001:3469: dri ma med par gnas pa ltar //
NK123(go)001:3470: nyon mongs nang na ye shes kyang //
NK123(go)001:3471: de bzhin dri ma med par gnas //
NK123(go)001:3474: sems nyid gcig pu kun gyi sa bon te //
NK123(go)001:3475: gang las srid dang mya ngan 'das 'phro ba //
NK123(go)001:3476: 'dod pa'i 'bras bu ster bar byed pa yi //
NK123(go)001:3477: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i sems la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK123(go)001:3479: de lta bu'i rigs can des lam gyi rtsa ba
NK123(go)001:3480: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas bdag med pa
NK123(go)001:3481: gnyis kyi don tshul bzhin du gtan la phabs te
NK123(go)001:3482: de nyid ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:3483: rdo rje 'chang mkhyen brtse'i dbang pos 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:3484: byang sems smon lam gyi bka' 'grel las /
NK123(go)001:3485: spyir thos bsam gyi sgro 'dogs chod pa'i don rnams
NK123(go)001:3486: blang dor gyi sgo nas rtse gcig tu nyams su
NK123(go)001:3487: len pa dang / khyad par bdag med kyi don
NK123(go)001:3488: gtan la phabs nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:3489: shes sgom pa la 'jug par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3490: 'di la gnyis gang zang gi bdag med bsgom tshul dang /
NK123(go)001:3491: chos kyi bdag med bsgom tshul lo //
NK123(go)001:3493: gang zag gi bdag ces pa phung po la sogs
NK123(go)001:3494: pa la dmigs nas nga dang nga yi bar 'dzin
NK123(go)001:3495: pa'i sems te / de la so so'i skye bo
NK123(go)001:3496: rnams kyis bden par zhen cing mu stegs pa rnams
NK123(go)001:3497: kyis rtag gcig rang dbang can du 'dod pas nyon
NK123(go)001:3498: mongs pa dang las sna tshogs pa bskyed nas 'khor
NK123(go)001:3500: de med par sgrub pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3501: gal te de lta bu'i bdag de rang bzhin gyis grub na /
NK123(go)001:3502: phung po las gcig tu grub pa'am tha dad du grub /
NK123(go)001:3503: gcig tu grub na phung sogs skye 'jig byed pa
NK123(go)001:3504: bzhin du bdag kyang skye 'jig byed par 'gyur la
NK123(go)001:3505: / tha dad du grub na phung po las gzhan pa'i bdag mi rnyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:3506: de bzhin du bdag de yod na lus dang /
NK123(go)001:3508: sems gang rung yin dgos la /
NK123(go)001:3509: lus ni bdag ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:3510: 'byung bzhi 'dus pa las byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:3511: ming ni bdag ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:3512: glo bur du btags pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3513: sems kyang bdag ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:3514: dus gsum gyi ngo bor ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:3515: zhes pa la sogs pa'i rigs pa'i tshul du mas gang zag gi bdag med gtan la phab ste /
NK123(go)001:3516: 'di tsam ni nyan thos bye mdo gnyis kyi lta ba'i dngos gzhi yin no //
NK123(go)001:3518: chos ni phyi gzung ba'i yul dang /
NK123(go)001:3519: nang 'dzin pa'i sems te bdag ni de la dngos po dang mtshan mar zhen pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3520: de med par sgrub pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:3521: gzung ba rang bzhin med par sgrub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3522: 'dzin pa rang bzhin med par sgrub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3523: dang po ni nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha'
NK123(go)001:3524: smra ba la theg dman dang theg chen gnyis las
NK123(go)001:3525: / theg dman la nyan thos bye brag smra ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3527: theg chen la sems tsam pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3529: de la thog mar nyan thos bye brag tu smra bas /
NK123(go)001:3530: shes bya thams cad gzhi lngar gtan la phab ste /
NK123(go)001:3531: snang ba gzugs dang gtso bo sems //
NK123(go)001:3532: de 'khor sems las byung ba dang //
NK123(go)001:3535: gzhi de dag thams cad bden grub tu bzhed de /
NK123(go)001:3536: rdul phra rab 'dus pa'i bdag nyid can gyi phyi don rags pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3537: shes pa'i rgyun gyi dngos po rnams btags yod kun rdzob kyi phung po dang /
NK123(go)001:3538: gzung ba rdul phran cha med dang /
NK123(go)001:3539: shes pa skad cig cha med rdzas yod don dam par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3540: chos kyi bdag gzung 'dzin gnyis ka gtan nas ma spangs la /
NK123(go)001:3542: rig min gzugs ma rtogs sems sems byung gsum bden par 'dod na'ang /
NK123(go)001:3543: rig min gyi gzugs ni gzhig cing gzhom du mi rung ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3544: ldan min 'du byed ni gzugs sems dang sems byung
NK123(go)001:3545: gi gnas skabs la btags pa tsam las rdzas gzhan
NK123(go)001:3547: 'dus ma byas rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3548: de rnams rdzas su mi 'dod pas chos khams phyogs
NK123(go)001:3549: gcig bdag med du rtogs pas khyad par 'phags pa
NK123(go)001:3550: yin no // gang ltar yang de dag gi btags
NK123(go)001:3551: pa'i gzung ba phyi rol gyi don rdul phran cha
NK123(go)001:3552: med du 'dod pa dgag pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3553: de gcig tu yod dam du mar yod /
NK123(go)001:3554: gcig tu yod na phyogs cha'i dbye ba yod dam med /
NK123(go)001:3555: yod na phyogs bzhi steng 'og ste cha drug tu
NK123(go)001:3556: song bas rdul phran cha med kyi dam bca' nyams
NK123(go)001:3557: la / med na dngos po thams cad rdul phran
NK123(go)001:3558: gcig tu 'gyur bas rags pa rtsom mi nus pa'i
NK123(go)001:3559: la / phyir ro // du ma yod do zhe na /
NK123(go)001:3560: rtsom gzhi'i rdul phran gcig ma grub pas /
NK123(go)001:3561: des rtsom pa'i du ma'ang mi 'grub bo //
NK123(go)001:3562: 'o na gzugs sogs mngon sum gyi snang ba 'di rnams ci snyam na /
NK123(go)001:3563: de ni sems 'khrul ba'i dbang gis byung ba rmi
NK123(go)001:3564: lam gyi snang cha bzhin te don la bden par
NK123(go)001:3566: kye rgyal ba'i sras dag khams gsum po 'di ni sems tsam mo //
NK123(go)001:3568: rigs pa'ang dngos gcig yid ni tha dad phyir //
NK123(go)001:3569: don ma grub par 'dod pa yin //
NK123(go)001:3570: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:3571: gnyis pa 'dzin pa rang bzhin med par sgrub pa la /
NK123(go)001:3572: spyir sems tsam pa rnams kyis chos thams cad yul kun brtag dang /
NK123(go)001:3574: gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid yongs grub ste mtshan
NK123(go)001:3575: nyid gsum du gtan la phabs nas snga ma gnyis
NK123(go)001:3576: kun rdzob dang / phyi ma don dam pa'i bden par 'dod /
NK123(go)001:3577: bye brag tu rnam bden pas /
NK123(go)001:3578: sngar smos pa ltar phyi don bden par ma grub kyang /
NK123(go)001:3579: don snang gi sems bden grub tu 'dod pa dgag pa'i tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:3580: gzung ba'i yul ma grub na /
NK123(go)001:3581: der 'dzin gyi shes pa'ang bden par ma grub ste /
NK123(go)001:3582: rmi lam gyi snang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3583: de myong mkhan gyi shes pa gnyis ka sad nas cir yang ma grub pa bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:3584: zhes pa la sogs pas legs par dpyad de bden med du gtan la phab nas /
NK123(go)001:3586: gzung 'dzin gnyis kyis stong pa'i shes pa rang rig rang gsal tsam bden par 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:3588: de lta bu'i gnyis stong gi shes pa de yod na gcig tu yod dam du ma yod /
NK123(go)001:3589: gcig tu yod na dus gsum gyi cha shas yod dam med /
NK123(go)001:3590: yod na gcig tu mi 'thad de du mar 'gyur la /
NK123(go)001:3591: med na dngos med du 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:3592: du mar yod do zhe na /
NK123(go)001:3593: rtsom gzhi gcig ma grub pas /
NK123(go)001:3594: des rtsom pa'i du ma'ang ma grub la /
NK123(go)001:3595: gcig dang du ma gang rung du med na med pas khyab pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:3596: gzhan yang 'das pa'i sems ni zhig pas dngos por mi rung /
NK123(go)001:3597: ma 'ongs pa'i sems ni ma bskyes pas dngos por mi rung /
NK123(go)001:3598: da lta ba'i sems ni kha dog dang dbyibs su ma grub /
NK123(go)001:3600: lus kyi phyi nang gang du'ang mi gnas /
NK123(go)001:3601: btsal na gang yang mi rnyed pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3603: mdor na skye 'gag gnas gsum dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:3604: zhes legs par dpyad pas rtag pa'i mtha' las grol ba na /
NK123(go)001:3606: 'o na sems med pa nyid gnas lugs yin no zhe na /
NK123(go)001:3608: sems de sngar dngos por yod la /
NK123(go)001:3609: phyis med par gyur na dngos med du rung mod kyang gdod nas yod ma myong ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3610: de bkag pa'i med pa'ang ma grub la /
NK123(go)001:3611: yod med gnyis ka las 'das pas mtha' gnyis ka ma grub /
NK123(go)001:3612: de ma grub pas gnyis ka bkag pa'i gnyis min du'ang mi 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3613: gdod nas sems kyi chos nyid mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang bral bar rtogs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:3614: dbu ma rang rgyud pa rnams kyi bzhed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3615: ye shes snying po kun las btus pa las /
NK123(go)001:3616: yod min med min yod med min //
NK123(go)001:3617: gnyis ka'i bdag nyid min pa'ang min //
NK123(go)001:3618: mtha' bzhi rnam par grol ba yi //
NK123(go)001:3619: de nyid dbu ma pa yis rig /
NK123(go)001:3621: mthar thug spros bral du 'dzin pa'ang gnas lugs su 'dod pa ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:3622: dgag bya mtha' bzhi so so nas grub pa med pas /
NK123(go)001:3623: de bkag pa'i mtha' bral zhes bya ba zhig kyang don la grub pa med pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3624: khas len thams cad dang bral ba ni /
NK123(go)001:3625: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i grub mtha' smra ba rnams
NK123(go)001:3626: kyi rtse mor gyur pa dbu ma thal 'gyur pa'i
NK123(go)001:3629: nga la mkhas len med pas na //
NK123(go)001:3630: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK123(go)001:3632: sgra gcan 'dzin gyis yum la bstod par /
NK123(go)001:3633: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK123(go)001:3635: de ltar lung rigs kyis dpyad pa'i mthar brjod bral du gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3636: sgom pas nyams su myong bas brjod bral du gtan
NK123(go)001:3637: la phebs pa gnyis mthar gyi ro gcig tu gyur
NK123(go)001:3638: nas blos byas gzung 'dzin gyi spros pa las grol
NK123(go)001:3639: ba na lta ba'i dpyad pa rdzogs pa'i tshul /
NK123(go)001:3641: sems dang gang shar sems nyid rang lus sogs /
NK123(go)001:3642: phyi nang kun tu rnam par btsal ba na //
NK123(go)001:3643: btsal bas ma rnyed yul can shes rab sogs //
NK123(go)001:3644: gnas skabs shig tu lta bar 'dod na yang //
NK123(go)001:3645: blos byas gzung 'dzin spros pa kun bral ba'i //
NK123(go)001:3646: gnyug ma'i ye shes rang ngo 'phrod pa yi /
NK123(go)001:3647: shes pa gsal dwangs rtog med ye shes de //
NK123(go)001:3648: sgrub brgyud kun gyi lta ba'i gtso bo yin //
NK123(go)001:3650: mdor na blos brtags shing dpyad pas dmigs pa'i yul du snang ba ni kun rdzob bden pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3651: de rnams tha snyad tsam du yang rang gi rgyu
NK123(go)001:3652: la brten nas 'bras bur 'brel bar 'byung ba'i tshul
NK123(go)001:3653: rdzing bur shar ba'i zla ba'i gzugs brnyan nam sgyu
NK123(go)001:3654: ma mkhan gyis sprul pa'i rta dang glang po ltar
NK123(go)001:3655: shes shing / de ltar snang dus nyid nas don
NK123(go)001:3656: dam par mtshan mar grub pa rdul tsam yang ma
NK123(go)001:3657: dmigs pa'i spros bral stong nyid nam mkha'i dbyings lta
NK123(go)001:3658: bur rtogs pa la brten nas snang ba de nyid
NK123(go)001:3660: stong pa'i dus nyid nas snang ba mi 'gags pa
NK123(go)001:3661: zung du 'jug pa'i tshul gyis 'khor 'das snang srid
NK123(go)001:3662: kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad gzhi dbu ma bden
NK123(go)001:3663: gnyis zung 'jug tu rtogs pas rtag chad kyi dra
NK123(go)001:3664: ba mtha' dag cig car du 'jig par byed pa
NK123(go)001:3665: ni / rigs pa'i rgyal pa'i rten 'brel gyi rigs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3668: de ni stong pa nyid du bshad //
NK123(go)001:3669: de ni brten nas gdags pa ste //
NK123(go)001:3670: de nyid dbu ma'i lam yin no //
NK123(go)001:3671: gang phyir rten 'byung ma lags pa'i //
NK123(go)001:3672: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin pa //
NK123(go)001:3673: de phyir stong nyid ma yin pa'i //
NK123(go)001:3674: chos 'ga' yod pa ma yin no //
NK123(go)001:3676: kun rdzob dang ni don dam dag /
NK123(go)001:3677: so sor char ni shes gyur nas //
NK123(go)001:3678: gang du yang dag 'dres gyur pa //
NK123(go)001:3679: zung du 'jug pa zhes bshad do //
NK123(go)001:3683: stong pa nyid kyang gzugs so //
NK123(go)001:3684: gzugs las kyang stong pa nyid gzhan ma yin /
NK123(go)001:3685: stong pa nyid las kyang gzugs gzhan ma yin no //
NK123(go)001:3687: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i bar du gsungs pa
NK123(go)001:3688: rnams la nges shes mchog tu bskyed nas thos bsam
NK123(go)001:3690: sgom pas nyams su len pas ci nus su 'bad pas /
NK123(go)001:3691: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams la snying
NK123(go)001:3692: rje chen po rtsol med du skye bas ci byed
NK123(go)001:3693: gzhan don du 'gyur ba'i thabs la mkhas pa'ang ngang
NK123(go)001:3694: gis 'byung bas na gnas lugs kyi don la ji
NK123(go)001:3696: myong ba skyes pa du tsam du snying rje skye la /
NK123(go)001:3697: des bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs zung 'brel
NK123(go)001:3698: du rdzogs pa ni theg pa chen po'i lam ma
NK123(go)001:3701: stong nyid snying rje snying po can //
NK123(go)001:3702: spyod pas bsod nams dag par 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:3704: de lta bu'i lhag mthong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes nyams su len pa'i tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:3705: sgom bya'i don la thos bsam gyi sgro 'dogs chod nas /
NK123(go)001:3706: dben pa'i gnas su bde ba'i stan la bsam gtan gyi spyod lam dang ldan pas 'dug ste /
NK123(go)001:3707: bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK123(go)001:3708: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK123(go)001:3709: gzung 'dzin gyi mtshan ma 'byung ba'i gzhi gang zag
NK123(go)001:3710: dang chos kyi bdag gnyis po dpyad pa'i yul du
NK123(go)001:3711: byas nas / yul can don dam dpyod pa'i rig
NK123(go)001:3712: shes tshad mas sngar smos pa ltar dpyad pa'i mthar
NK123(go)001:3713: brjod bral du gtan la phebs pa na /
NK123(go)001:3714: de'i ngang du mtshan 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa
NK123(go)001:3715: gzhan spangs te yul yul can ro gcig pa'i gsal
NK123(go)001:3716: stong dbyer med kyi ngang du mnyam par bzhag pa
NK123(go)001:3717: ni / don dam spros bral mkha' ltar rtogs pa'i shes rab ste /
NK123(go)001:3719: sbyor ba'i dus su mtshan mar 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK123(go)001:3720: de nyid dpyad pa'i rten du nges byas nas //
NK123(go)001:3721: mtha' bzhi rnam grol dngos gzhi'i dus su ni //
NK123(go)001:3722: gsal stong 'dzin med sngon rab mkhas pa'i lugs //
NK123(go)001:3724: dpyad dang 'jog pa'i sgom tshul ci yang rung //
NK123(go)001:3725: rang gi mtshan nyid rang bzhin 'od gsal ba //
NK123(go)001:3726: gsal dang shar la sgom med ma yengs pa //
NK123(go)001:3727: sgrub brgyud kun gyi sgom pa'i gtso bo yin //
NK123(go)001:3729: de ltar mnyam par bzhag pa nyid zhi lhag zung 'jug kyang yin te /
NK123(go)001:3730: rigs pas dpyad nas brjod bral du gtan la phabs pa ni lhag mthong /
NK123(go)001:3731: de'i ngang du gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis 'jog pa ni zhi gnas /
NK123(go)001:3732: de gnyis kyang ngo bo dbyer med pa zung 'jug tu shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3733: thun las ldang ba dang dge ba bsngo zhing smon lam gdab /
NK123(go)001:3735: gang shar gyi snang ba thams cad rang rang gi
NK123(go)001:3736: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel tshogs pa las 'byung ba rmi
NK123(go)001:3737: lam dang sgyu ma lta bur shes pas chad mtha'
NK123(go)001:3738: las grol / de yang rten 'brel yin pa'i rtags
NK123(go)001:3739: kyis don dam par rang bzhin ma grub par song
NK123(go)001:3741: snang stong gnyis gdod ma nas zung du 'jug pas
NK123(go)001:3742: brjod bral la nges shes mchog tu 'drong ba ni
NK123(go)001:3743: kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bur shes pa'i shes rab
NK123(go)001:3745: mnyam bzhag dus kyi nyams len de ltar na'ang //
NK123(go)001:3746: rjes thob dus su gang shar snang cha kun //
NK123(go)001:3747: rmi lam sgyu ma'i dran 'dun drag po yis //
NK123(go)001:3748: legs par sgom na snang stong dbyer med 'char //
NK123(go)001:3749: zhes gsungs de'i ngang nas snang cha kun rdzob kyi
NK123(go)001:3750: bden pa la brten nas gnas lugs ma rtogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:3751: 'gro ba rnams bsgral 'dod kyi bsam pas /
NK123(go)001:3752: thabs bsod nams kyi tshogs rgya chen po la 'bad cing /
NK123(go)001:3753: stong cha don dam gyi bden pas de thams cad
NK123(go)001:3754: kyang 'khor gsum gyi bden 'dzin las grol ba ni
NK123(go)001:3755: lam dbu ma thabs shes zung 'jug gi don ma
NK123(go)001:3756: nor ba dang / khyad par gzhan don sgrub tshul
NK123(go)001:3757: la mkhas pa'i shes rab zhes shes rab rnam pa
NK123(go)001:3759: lam dbu ma des tshogs lam nas brtsams te lam
NK123(go)001:3760: lnga rim par bgrod pa'i 'bras bu rang don du
NK123(go)001:3761: chos kyi sku spros pa thams cad dang bral ba
NK123(go)001:3763: gzhan don gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyis 'khor ba
NK123(go)001:3764: ji srid kyi bar du smon lam dang snying rje'i
NK123(go)001:3765: rten 'brel gyis yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar phan
NK123(go)001:3766: bde'i phrin las 'bad med lhun grub tu 'byung ba
NK123(go)001:3767: ni 'bras bu dbu ma sku gnyis zung 'jug gi
NK123(go)001:3769: dge ba 'di yis skye bo kun //
NK123(go)001:3770: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK123(go)001:3771: bsod nams ye shes las byung ba'i //
NK123(go)001:3772: dam pa sku gnyis thob par shog /
NK123(go)001:3774: zhes gsungs pa rnams don che bar sems nas yig tshogs la ma 'dzems par zhib par bris pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3776: rjes thob kyi dus su bdag pas gzhan gces kyi sgo nas sems can gyi don byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3777: de'ang spyod pa'i rang bzhin pha rol du phyin pa drug gam bcu ste /
NK123(go)001:3788: ye shes bzhi bsnan pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3789: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa'i nang du 'adu'o //
NK123(go)001:3791: sbyin pa rang nor yong gtong ba //
NK123(go)001:3792: tshul khrims gzhan phan bya ba'o //
NK123(go)001:3793: bzod pa khro ba spangs ba ste //
NK123(go)001:3794: brtson 'grus dge la spro ba nyid //
NK123(go)001:3795: bsam gtan rtse gcig nyon mongs med //
NK123(go)001:3796: shes rab bden don gtan la 'bebs //
NK123(go)001:3797: zhes rin chen phreng ba las gsungs /
NK123(go)001:3799: byang sems kyi sgrub pa'i bslab bya gang zhig khyad
NK123(go)001:3800: chos bzhi ldan gyi sbyin sogs phar phyin la slob
NK123(go)001:3801: par 'dod pa'i sems pa mtshungs ldan dang bcas pa
NK123(go)001:3804: sbyin pa mi mthun phyogs nyams dang //
NK123(go)001:3805: rnam par mi rtog ye shes ldan //
NK123(go)001:3806: 'dod pa thams cad yongs rdzogs byed //
NK123(go)001:3807: sems can rnam smin byed rnams gsum //
NK123(go)001:3809: sgra don pa r+aa mi ta zhes pa pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3810: 'jig rten dang nyan rang gi dge ba kun las
NK123(go)001:3811: phul du byung ba'i pha rol du 'gro bas so
NK123(go)001:3812: // bye brag so so'i sgra don ni /
NK123(go)001:3814: dbul ba 'dor bar byed pa dang //
NK123(go)001:3815: bsil ba thob dang khro bzod dang //
NK123(go)001:3816: mchog sbyang ba dang yid 'dzin dang //
NK123(go)001:3817: don dam shes pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK123(go)001:3822: mi 'jigs pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa ste gsum /
NK123(go)001:3826: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims te gsum bzod pa la gnod byed la ji mi snyams pa /
NK123(go)001:3828: chos la nges rtog gi bzod pa ste gsum /
NK123(go)001:3832: sems can don byed kyi brtson 'grus gsum /
NK123(go)001:3836: de bzhin gshegs dag'i bsam gtan gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:3838: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab gsum mam /
NK123(go)001:3841: gzhan don shes pa'i shes rab gsum mo //
NK123(go)001:3842: yang na mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK123(go)001:3843: de dag so sor sbyin la sogs //
NK123(go)001:3844: rnam pa drug tu bsdus pa yis //
NK123(go)001:3845: go cha'i sgrub pa gang yin de //
NK123(go)001:3846: drug mtshan drug this ji bzhin bshad //
NK123(go)001:3847: ces pas sbyin sogs re re la'ang sbyin pa'i sbyin pa sogs drug drug tu dbye ba'o //
NK123(go)001:3849: bslab pa gsum gyi dbang gis te //
NK123(go)001:3851: bslab gsum dbang du mdzad nas ni //
NK123(go)001:3852: rgyal bas pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK123(go)001:3853: yang dag bshad de dang po gsum //
NK123(go)001:3854: tha ma gnyis kyis rnam pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:3855: gcig ni gsum char la yang rtogs //
NK123(go)001:3857: de yang tshogs gnyis su bsdu na /
NK123(go)001:3858: sbyin dang tshul khrims bsod nams kyis //
NK123(go)001:3859: tshogs min shes rab ye shes te //
NK123(go)001:3860: gsum ni gnyis char la yang gtogs //
NK123(go)001:3861: lnga char yang ni ye shes tshogs //
NK123(go)001:3864: snga ma la brten phyi ma skye //
NK123(go)001:3865: dman dang mchog tu gnas phyir dang //
NK123(go)001:3866: rags pa dang ni phra ba'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:3867: de dag rim pas bstan pa yin //
NK123(go)001:3870: re ba med pa'i sbyin pa dang //
NK123(go)001:3871: yang srid mi 'dod tshul khrims dang //
NK123(go)001:3872: thams cad la ni bzod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:3873: yon tan kun sdud brtson 'grus dang //
NK123(go)001:3874: de bzhin bsam gtan gzugs med min //
NK123(go)001:3875: shes rab thabs dang ldan pa yis //
NK123(go)001:3876: pha rol phyin pa drug po la //
NK123(go)001:3877: brtan pa rnams kyis yang dag sbyor //
NK123(go)001:3880: rgya che ba dang zang zing med //
NK123(go)001:3881: don che ba dang mi zad pa //
NK123(go)001:3882: sbyin pa la sogs thams cad kyi //
NK123(go)001:3883: yon tan bzhir ni shes par bya //
NK123(go)001:3888: sbyin pas longs spyod khrims kyis bde //
NK123(go)001:3889: bzod pas mdangs ldan brtson pas brjid //
NK123(go)001:3890: bsam gtan gyis zhi blo yis grol //
NK123(go)001:3893: gzugs kyi sku ni mdor bsdu na //
NK123(go)001:3894: bsod nams tshogs las 'khrungs pa ste //
NK123(go)001:3895: chos kyi sku ni mdor bsdu na //
NK123(go)001:3896: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK123(go)001:3898: rgyas par gzhan du shes par bya ste /
NK123(go)001:3901: sa bcu dang lam lnga rim gyis bgrod nas /
NK123(go)001:3902: mi slob pa'i lam bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la /
NK123(go)001:3903: rang don chos skur grol te /
NK123(go)001:3904: gzhan don gzugs sku gnyis la brten nas sems can
NK123(go)001:3905: gyi don 'khor ba ma stong gi bar du mdzad
NK123(go)001:3906: pa ste / de la sa bcu ni /
NK123(go)001:3908: rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi rten du gyur pa /
NK123(go)001:3909: sgra don b+hu mi zhes pa'i sgra las gong ma'i yon tan gyi rten du 'gyur zhing /
NK123(go)001:3910: sa de nyid kyi yon tan gyi gzhi yin pas sa zhes bya /
NK123(go)001:3912: spyir theg pa che chung gi dbye ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3913: theg chen la'ang skye 'phags kyi sa gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:3915: de la slob pa dang mi slob pa'i sa gnyis
NK123(go)001:3916: las dang po rab tu dga' ba sogs bcu ste
NK123(go)001:3917: / de dag gi mtshan nyid dang sgra don zung du 'brel bar bshad na /
NK123(go)001:3918: sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa yongs su rdzogs
NK123(go)001:3919: nas se sna'i rgyu 'bras spong bas dang po'i mtshan
NK123(go)001:3920: nyid / de'i tshe sngon ma mthong ba'i chos nyid mthong bas byang chub tu nye ba dang /
NK123(go)001:3921: sems can gyi don rgya chen po 'grub par mthong
NK123(go)001:3922: bas rab tu dga' ba khyad par can skye ba'i
NK123(go)001:3923: ba'i phyir / raba tu dag'a ba ces bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3925: tshul khrims kyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas 'chal tshul gyi rgyu 'bras spangs ba sa gnyis pa /
NK123(go)001:3926: de'i tshe rmi lam tsam du'ang 'chal tshul gyi dri ma med pas dri meda pa /
NK123(go)001:3927: bzod pa'i phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas khong khro'i rgyu 'bras spang ba sa gsum pa /
NK123(go)001:3928: de'i tshe 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi snang ba tshad med pas na 'od byed pa /
NK123(go)001:3929: brtson 'grus kyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas le lo'i rgyu 'bras spong ba sa bzhi pa /
NK123(go)001:3930: de'i tshe nyon mongs pa'i bud shing ma lus pa
NK123(go)001:3931: bsreg nus pa'i byang chub phyogs chos kyi 'od 'phro
NK123(go)001:3933: bsam gtan gyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas rnam
NK123(go)001:3934: par g.yeng ba'i rgyu 'bras spang ba sa lnga pa
NK123(go)001:3935: / de tshe sems can gyi don kyang rgyun mi 'chad cing /
NK123(go)001:3936: rang gi ngo bo rnam par mi rtogs pa'i ye shes las kyang nyams pa med pa ste /
NK123(go)001:3937: 'di gnyis zung 'bral du spyod pa de shin tu dka' ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3939: shes rab kyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas shes 'chal gyi rgyu 'bras spong ba sa drug pa /
NK123(go)001:3940: de'i tshe so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis 'khor
NK123(go)001:3941: 'das kyi chos thams cad mngon sum du mthong bas
NK123(go)001:3943: thabs kyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas thabs la
NK123(go)001:3944: mi mkhas pa'i rgyu 'bras spong ba sa bdun pa
NK123(go)001:3945: / de'i tshe bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam sa brgyad
NK123(go)001:3946: pa dang 'dab 'brel bas nye zhing 'khor 'das kyi
NK123(go)001:3947: mtha' las ring du song bas na ring du songa
NK123(go)001:3948: / ba / stobs kyi phar phyin rdzogs nas stobs
NK123(go)001:3949: la sgrib pa'i rgyu 'bras spong ba sa brgyad pa
NK123(go)001:3950: / ba / / de'i tshe mnyam rjes kun tu
NK123(go)001:3951: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mtshan ma'i 'du
NK123(go)001:3952: shes dang mtshan ma med pa'i 'du shes kyi chos
NK123(go)001:3953: las 'das shing rtsol bas mi spyod pas mi g.yo
NK123(go)001:3954: / ba / / ba / smon lam gyi phar
NK123(go)001:3955: phyin rdzogs nas smon pa'i don mi 'grub pa'i rgyu
NK123(go)001:3957: de'i tshe so so yang dag par rig pa bzhi
NK123(go)001:3958: la dbang 'byor ba'i blo gros phun sum tshogs pa
NK123(go)001:3959: dang ldan pas legsa pa'i blo gros /
NK123(go)001:3960: ye shes kyi phar phyin yongs su rdzogs nas shes
NK123(go)001:3961: bya'i sgrib pa'i rgyu 'bras yongs su spong ba sa
NK123(go)001:3963: de'i tshe ting nge 'dzin dang gzungs kyi sprin las
NK123(go)001:3964: 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas par gdul bya so
NK123(go)001:3965: so'i skal pa dang mtshams par chos kyi char 'bebs
NK123(go)001:3966: par nus pa'i phyir chos kyi sprin zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:3967: de la'ang nang gses su sa dang po nas bdun
NK123(go)001:3968: pa'i bar la ma dag sa bdun zhes bya ste
NK123(go)001:3969: / mnyam rjes tha dad du 'dzin pa'i dri ma dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:3970: sa brgyad pa nas sa bcu pa'i bar la dag pa sa gsum zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:3971: tha dad du 'dzin pa'i dri ma las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:3973: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob pa'i lam lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:3975: bdag med don spyi'i tshul gyis rtogs pa'i las dang
NK123(go)001:3976: po pa'i mkhyen pa de tshogs lam gyi mtshan nyid
NK123(go)001:3977: / sgra don sam b+ha ra m+aarga zhes pas /
NK123(go)001:3978: gtso bor thos bsam dang bsod nams dang ye shes
NK123(go)001:3979: kyi tshogs gnyis la rten te goms par byed pas
NK123(go)001:3981: thar pa cha mthun gyi lam dang /
NK123(go)001:3982: las dang po pa'i mngon rtogs rnam don gcig go //
NK123(go)001:3983: dbye na chung 'bring che gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:3985: sbyor lam du 'jug pa'i dus ma nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3987: tshe phyi ma phan chad du sbyor lam la 'jug pa'i dus nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3989: tshe de nyid du sbyor lam gyi drod skye bar nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:3990: 'di mthar phyin nas chos rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin thob /
NK123(go)001:3991: sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhal mthong zhing gdams ngag nyan pa sogs la dbang ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:3992: gnyis pa sbyor lam ni tshogs lam gyi rjes las
NK123(go)001:3993: byung ba'i bdag med don spyi'i tshul gyis rtogs pa
NK123(go)001:3994: de sbyor de yang sbyor lam yin min gyi tshad
NK123(go)001:3995: dpe yi ye shes rgyud la skyes ma skyes kyis
NK123(go)001:3998: sgra don pra yo ga m+aarga zhes pas nges par
NK123(go)001:3999: 'byed pa'i mthong lam la dngos su sbyor bar byed
NK123(go)001:4000: pas sbyor lam ste nges 'byed cha mthun nam nges
NK123(go)001:4001: 'byed yan lag mngon rtogs rnams don gcig /
NK123(go)001:4002: dbye na chung 'bring che gsum las /
NK123(go)001:4003: dang po ni drod dang rtse mo gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:4004: mthong lam skye ba'i dus ma nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4005: gnyis pa ni bzod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:4006: tshe phyi ma la mthong lam skye bar nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4009: tshe de nyid la mthong lam skye bar nges pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4010: de yang mthong lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:4011: shes me lta bu'i snga ltas su gyur bas drod
NK123(go)001:4012: / dge ba'i rtsa ba g.yo ba rnams kyi rtse mor gyur pas rtse mo /
NK123(go)001:4013: stong pa nyid la mi skrag pas bzod pa /
NK123(go)001:4014: 'jig rten pa'i chos kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pas chos mchog ste /
NK123(go)001:4015: de so sor drod snang ba thob pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:4016: rtse mor gyur snang ba mched pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:4017: bzod pa de kho na nyid la phyogs gcig la zhugs pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:4018: chos chog de ma thag pa'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya zhing /
NK123(go)001:4019: de re re la'ang nang gses su chung 'bring che
NK123(go)001:4020: gsum gyi dbye bas nges 'byed cha mthun bcu gnyis
NK123(go)001:4022: gzhan yang kun nyon dang rnam byang gi gzung ba
NK123(go)001:4023: rang bzhin med par rtogs pa drod dang rtse mo
NK123(go)001:4024: / gang zag rdzas yod dang btags yod kyi 'dzin
NK123(go)001:4025: pa rang bzhin med par rtogs pa bzod dang chos
NK123(go)001:4028: rtse mo thob pas dge ba'i rtsa ba rgyun mi 'chad /
NK123(go)001:4029: bzod pa thob nas ngan song du mi ltung ba sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:4030: tshogs lam chen po las khyad par du 'phags tshul ni mthong lam la nye ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4031: ye shes kyi drod brtan pas gyur pa sogs kyis phye bar gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:4032: gsum pa mthong la lam ni /
NK123(go)001:4033: bdag med mngon sum du gsal du rtogs pa'i mkhyen pa de mthong lam gyi mtshan nyid /
NK123(go)001:4034: sgra don dar+shana m+aarga zhes pas /
NK123(go)001:4035: sngar ma mthong ba'i chos kyis dbyings dang por mthong bas mthong lam ste /
NK123(go)001:4036: bden pa mngon par rtogs pa dang nges 'byed rnams don gcig go //
NK123(go)001:4037: dbye na ngo bo'i sgo nas skad gcig ma bcu drug ste /
NK123(go)001:4043: de la chos shes pa'i bzod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4044: lam rnams la dmigs nas so so'i mthong spong gi sgrib pa spang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:4046: sgrib pa spangs nas kyang rnam par grol ba nyams su myong ba'o //
NK123(go)001:4047: rjes su shes pa'i bzod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4048: skad cig ma dang po gnyis 'phags pa'i chos kyi rgyur rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4050: de nyid rang rig tshul gyis nges par 'dzin cing myong bar byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4051: 'di la nyan thos bye smra bas skad cig bcu
NK123(go)001:4052: drug tu rim can skye bar 'dod pa sogs dang
NK123(go)001:4053: / theg chen thun mong pa 'ga' zhig kyang bcu
NK123(go)001:4054: drug nas gcig gi bar ci rigs su skye bar
NK123(go)001:4055: / 'dod la / theg chen thun mong ma yin pa ltar na /
NK123(go)001:4057: mi skye ba'i chos la bzod pa thob pa zhes gsungs pas /
NK123(go)001:4058: don dam par mthong lam skye bar mi bzhed cing /
NK123(go)001:4059: kun rdzob tu rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba tsam
NK123(go)001:4060: la dgongs nas mthong lam skye ba'i rnam bzhag byed
NK123(go)001:4061: do // spang bya'i nges nas dbye na /
NK123(go)001:4063: shes sgrib gzung 'dzin rags pa rnams mthong spang ste /
NK123(go)001:4064: zhib par gong smos brgya dang bcu gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:4065: de rnams spong ba'i gnyen po /
NK123(go)001:4067: bar chad med pa'i lam dngos dang /
NK123(go)001:4069: rten gnyen po rnam par grol ba'i lam /
NK123(go)001:4070: rjes bzod bzhi dang rjes shes bzhi ni thag bsring
NK123(go)001:4071: ba'i gnyen po'i khyad par gyi lam ste rtsa 'don
NK123(go)001:4072: gyi tshul du spong bar byed do //
NK123(go)001:4073: rten gyi ngos nas dbye na /
NK123(go)001:4074: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun /
NK123(go)001:4076: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i ye shes thog mar byas
NK123(go)001:4077: pa de'i tshe rang gi ngo skal gyi spong bya
NK123(go)001:4078: spong ba dang / bdag med gnyis mngon du rtogs pas byang chub la nye ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4079: gzhan don 'grub par mthong ba'i rab tu dga' ba
NK123(go)001:4080: rgya chen po sngon chad ma myong ba thob pas
NK123(go)001:4081: sa dang po rab tu dga' ba ste /
NK123(go)001:4082: spang ba'i khyad par mthong spang brgya dang bcu gnyis spangs /
NK123(go)001:4083: rtogs pa'i khyad par chos dbyings kun tu 'gro ba'i don rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4084: yon tan gyi khyad par brgya phrag bcu gnyis la dbang 'byor te /
NK123(go)001:4086: dus skad cig ma gcig la sangs rgyas brgya'i zhal lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4087: sangs rgyas brgyas byin gyis brlabs par shes pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4089: dus skad cig la skal pa brgyar ston pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4090: sngon dang phyi ma'i mtha' brgya la ye shes kyi gzigs pa 'jug pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4091: ting nge 'dzin brgya la dus skad cig mar snyom par 'jug cing ldang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4092: sems can brgya smin par byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4093: zhing khams brgya g.yo bar byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4094: zhing brgya 'od kyis gsal bar byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4095: chos kyi sgo mo brgya 'byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4096: rang gis lus brgyar ston pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4097: lus re re la yang 'khor phun sum tshogs pa brgyas bskor bar ston pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4098: skye ba 'dzin pa'i khyad par 'dzam bu gling gi rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin par nus pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4107: ston pa'i bstan pa las gzhan gyis mi bkri ba
NK123(go)001:4108: chos rnams la mi 'jigs pa thob pa sogs yon
NK123(go)001:4109: tan gyi khyad par mang du gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:4111: bdag med mngon sum du rtogs zin rgyun ldan du
NK123(go)001:4112: goms par byed pa'i mkhyen pa de sgom lam gyi
NK123(go)001:4113: mtshan nyid / sgra don b+ha ga wan m+aarga zhes
NK123(go)001:4114: pas mthong ba'i don sgom par byed pas sgom lam
NK123(go)001:4115: mtshan nyid / ste / rnam dag nges 'byin gyi lam dang don gcig go //
NK123(go)001:4117: spang bya'i ngos nas nyon sgrib lhan skyes dang /
NK123(go)001:4118: shes sgrib gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa phra ba rnams
NK123(go)001:4119: sgom spang ste zhib par gong smos bzhi brgya dang
NK123(go)001:4120: bcu bzhi'o // de'i gnyen por sgom lam chung 'bring che gsum /
NK123(go)001:4121: de re re la'ang chung ngu'i chung du sogs su
NK123(go)001:4122: dbye bas dge ste sa gnyis pa nas bcu pa'i
NK123(go)001:4125: bar chad med pas dngos su spangs te /
NK123(go)001:4126: lam 'di gnyis ni spong ba'i gnyen po'o //
NK123(go)001:4127: rnam grol gyi lam ni rten gyi gnyen po'o //
NK123(go)001:4128: khyad par gyi lam ni thag bsring gi gnyen po'o //
NK123(go)001:4129: de yang theg chen sgom lam chung ngu'i chung ngu'i
NK123(go)001:4130: gnas skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig
NK123(go)001:4131: / sa'i dbang du byas na gnyis pa dri ma med pa /
NK123(go)001:4132: spangs pa'i khyad par khams gsum gyi sgom spang chen po'i chen po zhe drug spangs pa /
NK123(go)001:4133: rtogs pa'i khyad par chos nyid mchog gi don du rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4134: yon tan gyi khyad par stong phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK123(go)001:4135: skye ba 'dzin pa'i khyad par gling bzhi pa'i 'khor
NK123(go)001:4136: los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so
NK123(go)001:4138: sgom lam chung ngu'i 'bring po'i skabs kyi ye shes gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4140: khams gsum gyi sgom spong chen po'i 'bring po zhe drug spang /
NK123(go)001:4141: chos nyid rgyu mthun pa'i don gyi mchog tu rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4142: de'i don sngar thos pa byas pa de chos nyid
NK123(go)001:4143: kyis rtogs pa'i rgyu mthun pa'i don du rtogs nas
NK123(go)001:4144: stong gsum me 'ob kyis gang ba'ang 'bog nas chos
NK123(go)001:4145: 'tshol ba'o // yon tan 'bum phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK123(go)001:4146: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyi skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4147: sgom lam chung ngu'i chen po'i skabs kyi ye shes gang zhig sa bzhi pa 'od 'phro ba /
NK123(go)001:4148: khams gsum gyi sgom spong chen po'i chung ngu zhe
NK123(go)001:4149: drug spangs chos nyid yongs su 'dzin pa med pa'i
NK123(go)001:4151: de'i tshe bdag tu 'dzin pa med pas chos dbyings la bdag gir 'dzin pa med par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4152: yon tan bye ba phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK123(go)001:4153: 'thab bral lha'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4154: sgom lam 'bring po'i chung ngu'i skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4155: sa lnga pa sbyangs dka' ba /
NK123(go)001:4156: khams gsum gyi sgom spang 'bring po'i chen po zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4157: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i don du rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4158: yon tan bye ba stong phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK123(go)001:4159: dga' ldan lha'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4160: sgom lam 'bring po'i 'bring gi skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4161: sa drug pa mngon du gyur pa /
NK123(go)001:4162: khams gsum ka'i sgom spang 'bring po'i 'bring po zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4163: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i don du rtogs //
NK123(go)001:4164: yon tan bye ba 'bum phrag bcu gnyis thob //
NK123(go)001:4165: 'phrul dag'i lha'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4166: sgom lam 'bring po'i chen po'i skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4167: sa bdun pa'i ring du song ba /
NK123(go)001:4168: khams gsum gyi sgom spang 'bring po'i chung ngu zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4169: chos nyid tha dad med pa'i don du rtogs te /
NK123(go)001:4170: sangs rgyas kyi chos mdo dang rgyas pa du mar gsungs kyang /
NK123(go)001:4171: don chos kyi dbyings la tha dad med par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4172: yon tan bye ba khrag khrig 'bum phrag bcu gnyis thob /
NK123(go)001:4173: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4174: sgom lam chen po'i chung ngu'i skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4175: sa brgyad pa mi g.yo ba /
NK123(go)001:4176: khams gsum gyi sgom spang chung ngu'i chen po zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4177: chos nyid bri gang med pa dang rnam par mi
NK123(go)001:4178: rtog pa dang zhing dag pa la dbang ba'i gnas
NK123(go)001:4179: su rtogs / yon tan stong chen 'bum phrag gcig gi rdul dang mnyam par thob /
NK123(go)001:4180: stong gi bdag po tshangs pa'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4181: sgom lam chen po'i 'bring po'i skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4182: sa dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK123(go)001:4183: khams gsum gyi sgom spang chung ngu'i 'bring po zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4184: chos nyid so so yang dag par rig pa'i ye shes la dbang ba'i gnas su rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4185: yon tan stong chen 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam par thob /
NK123(go)001:4186: stong gnyis kyi bdag po tshangs pa chen po'i skye ba 'dzin nus so //
NK123(go)001:4187: ngo bo theg chen sgom lam chen po'i chen po'i skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:4188: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin te /
NK123(go)001:4189: spang ba'i khyad par khams gsum gyi sgom spang chung ngu'i chung ngu zhe drug spangs /
NK123(go)001:4190: rtogs pa'i khyad par chos nyid phrin las la dbang ba'i gnas su rtogs /
NK123(go)001:4191: yon tan gyi khyad par sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK123(go)001:4192: brjod du med pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul
NK123(go)001:4193: gyi grangs dang mnyam pa thob /
NK123(go)001:4194: skye ba 'dzin pa'i khyad par stong gsum gyi stong
NK123(go)001:4195: chen po'i bdag po lha'i bu dbang phyug chen po'i
NK123(go)001:4197: de'ang de dag gi rgyal por skye ba 'dzin pa'i
NK123(go)001:4198: nus pa yod kyi skye ba 'dzin pas ma khyab
NK123(go)001:4199: la / de dag gi rgyal po yin tshad kyang
NK123(go)001:4200: byang chub sems dpa'i sa de dag la gnas pas
NK123(go)001:4201: la / ma khyab ste / kha cig so so'i
NK123(go)001:4202: skye bo bsod nams rlabs chen bsags pa yin la
NK123(go)001:4203: la / ma khyab ste / / kha cig tu
NK123(go)001:4204: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa der snang bas sems
NK123(go)001:4205: can gyi don mdzad tshul gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:4206: gzhan yang dag sa gsum po 'dir dbang bzhi thob ste /
NK123(go)001:4207: sa brgyad pa la nyon yid gnas gyur pas rnam par mi rtog pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4208: sgo lnga gnas gyur pas zhing dag pa la dbang /
NK123(go)001:4209: sa dgu pa rnam par rtog pa yid shes gnas
NK123(go)001:4210: gyur pas ye shes bsam mi khyab pa la dbang
NK123(go)001:4211: 'byor / sa bcu par yid shes kyi 'char gzhi
NK123(go)001:4212: kun gzhi'i shes pa gnas gyur pas phrin las phun
NK123(go)001:4213: sum tshogs pa la dbang 'byor te /
NK123(go)001:4214: gzhan don du mdzad pa bcu gnyis sogs ston par nus pa sangs rgyas dang tshul mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4215: 'on kyang rang ngor spangs rtogs kyi nges nas mnyam pa ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:4216: sa gzhi dang rdul phran gyi dpes rgyud bla ma sogs nas gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:4217: rgyun matha'i ye shes rdo rje lta bus gzhom bya phra mo yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:4218: 'dis gzhal na mdo sngags kyi sangs rgyas dang dngos
NK123(go)001:4219: brtags kyi khyad par sogs kyang shes par nus so
NK123(go)001:4220: // de lta bu'i yon tan yang khams kyi steng
NK123(go)001:4221: gi sgrib pa bral stobs kyis gsar du mthong yang
NK123(go)001:4222: // / sngon med pa phyis gsar du skyes pa
NK123(go)001:4223: ni ma yin te yon tan de lta bu dang
NK123(go)001:4224: gzhan yang tshad med pa nyid ye nas lhun grub
NK123(go)001:4225: tu yod pas so sor khams gsar du mthong ba
NK123(go)001:4226: je dag tu song bas snang ba'i phyir zhes kun
NK123(go)001:4227: mkhyen chen pos grub mtha' mdzod du gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:4228: lnga pa mi slob pa'i lam ni /
NK123(go)001:4229: rang gi rtogs pa mthar thug pa de mi slob pa'i lam gyi mtshan nyid sgra don /
NK123(go)001:4230: nish+tha m+aarga zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK123(go)001:4232: shes bya shes pa mthar phyin par byed pas na mthar phyin pa'am mi slob pa'i lam zhes bya /
NK123(go)001:4234: gnas skabs kyi mi slob pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4235: mthar thug gi mi slob pa gnyis /
NK123(go)001:4237: nyan rang gnyis kyi mi slob pa ste /
NK123(go)001:4238: de ni gong du 'gro ba dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4239: lam mtshan nyid pa dang 'bras bu btags pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4241: theg pa chen po'i mi slob pa'i sa ste /
NK123(go)001:4242: de las gong du spangs rtogs kyi khyab par gzhan
NK123(go)001:4243: thob tu med pa'i phyir lam btags pa ba dang
NK123(go)001:4244: / 'bras bu mtshan nyid pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:4245: de'i ngo bo ni rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge
NK123(go)001:4246: 'dzin la brten nas nyon mongs pa bag chags dang
NK123(go)001:4247: bcas pa gtan nas spangs shing zad pa dang mi
NK123(go)001:4248: skye shes pa'i ye shes mthar thug pa thob pa
NK123(go)001:4249: ste / spangs pa dang ye shes phun sum tshogs
NK123(go)001:4250: pa'i rang bzhin mthar phyin pa ste sangs rgyas kyi
NK123(go)001:4252: ming ni bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:4253: 'di la dbye na rten sku gsum /
NK123(go)001:4255: yon tan dang phrin las kyi tshogs bsam gyis mi
NK123(go)001:4256: khyab pa dang bcas pa la dbang 'byor ba ste
NK123(go)001:4257: / dang po rten sku la'ang dbye na gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:4258: rang don mthar phyin chos sku dang /
NK123(go)001:4259: gzhan don mthar phyin gzugs kyi sku'o //
NK123(go)001:4261: dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK123(go)001:4262: lam glo bur gyi sgrib gnyis dag pa'i ye shes
NK123(go)001:4263: gnyis dbyer med par rang bzhin gyis zung du 'jug
NK123(go)001:4264: cing dri ma thams cad dang bral ba'i dag pa
NK123(go)001:4265: gnyis ldan gyi ye shes nam mkha' lta bu mngon
NK123(go)001:4267: sangs rgyas 'phags pa'i thugs rgyud kyi 'gog lam bden pa rnams dang don gcig go //
NK123(go)001:4269: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK123(go)001:4272: de lta bu'i chos sku'i ye shes las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK123(go)001:4273: gnas 1nges pa 'og min stug po bkod par /
NK123(go)001:4274: ston pa 2nges pa mtshan dang dpe byad kyi dpal
NK123(go)001:4275: du 'bar ba'i longs spyod rdzogs sku rnam par snang
NK123(go)001:4276: mdzad chen pos / 'khor 3nges pa dag pa'i gdul bya sa bcu'i sems dpa' 'ba' zhig la /
NK123(go)001:4277: chos 4nges pa theg pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK123(go)001:4278: dus 5nges pa rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo bskor
NK123(go)001:4279: bar mdzad pa'i phyir nges pa lnga dang ldan pa'o
NK123(go)001:4280: // gnyis pa sprul ba'i sku ni /
NK123(go)001:4281: ngo bo gang du bshad ma thag pa'i longs sku'i bdag rkyen las byung ba /
NK123(go)001:4282: dus rgyun mi 'chad pa srid pa ji srid gnas kyi bar du /
NK123(go)001:4283: yul nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i gdul bya gang
NK123(go)001:4284: du gnas pa na tshul gang la gang mtshams pa'i
NK123(go)001:4285: phan bde'i mdzad pa bla na med pas /
NK123(go)001:4286: phrin las sems can gyi don 'ba' zhig lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa ste /
NK123(go)001:4288: skye ba sprul pa'i sku dga' ldan na bzhugs pa lta bu /
NK123(go)001:4289: mchog gi sprul pa'i sku sh+aakya thub pa lta bu /
NK123(go)001:4290: bzo'i sprul sku dri za'i rgyal po rab dga' gdul
NK123(go)001:4291: ba'i don du pi wam len pa sogs du ma
NK123(go)001:4292: ste / mdor na chos kyi sku rnam par mi rtog pa nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang nas /
NK123(go)001:4293: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zla ba lta bu las /
NK123(go)001:4294: sprul pa'i sku chu zla ltar cir yang 'char bas
NK123(go)001:4295: gdul bya'i 'dod pa rdzogs par mdzad pa ste ngo
NK123(go)001:4297: de las gtso bor sngags kyi sde snod rnams su sku bzhir gsungs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4298: sku gsum po rnam pa tha dad kyang /
NK123(go)001:4299: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa zung du 'jug pa la ngo bo nyid sku'i tha snyad mdzad cing /
NK123(go)001:4301: 'dir bshad pa'i chos sku la ngo bo nyid sku'i
NK123(go)001:4302: tha snyad mdzad de gzugs sku gnyis kyi ngo bor
NK123(go)001:4304: gnyis pa rten pa ye shes la'ang gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:4306: chos gang la sgrib byed kyi dri ma dang bral
NK123(go)001:4307: nas rang gi gnas lugs mngon sum du gyur pa
NK123(go)001:4310: mdo las gsungs pa'i ye shes bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:4311: sngags las thams cad kyi khyab byed chos kyi dbyings la'ang ye shes kyi sgras smos pas lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:4312: de la chos thams cad kyi chos nyid kun gzhi
NK123(go)001:4313: nyid dbyings su nub pa chos kyi dbyings dang ye
NK123(go)001:4316: dbyings rang bzhin rnam par dag pa la spang bya glo bur gyi dri ma phra mo'ang dag pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4317: chos can gsal ba'i cha kun gzhi'i rnam par shes
NK123(go)001:4318: pa dbyings su nub pa me long lta bu'i ye
NK123(go)001:4321: ngo bo nga dang nga yir 'dzin 1pa med pa /
NK123(go)001:4322: yul yongs 2su ris ma chad pa /
NK123(go)001:4323: dus 3rtag tu rgyun mi chad pa /
NK123(go)001:4324: chos can 4shes bya kun la ma rmongs pa /
NK123(go)001:4325: yul gyi rnam pa med pas yul la mngon du
NK123(go)001:4326: mi phyogs pa ste chos lnga dang ldan pa gang
NK123(go)001:4327: zhig / ye shes gzhan thams cad kyi 'char gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4328: yid kyi rnam shes 'di sku gsum la bzhag pa'i mdo'i rjes su 'brang ba ste /
NK123(go)001:4329: gzhan du yid shes gnas gyur pa sor rtog dang /
NK123(go)001:4330: nyon yid gnas 'gyur pa mnyam nyid ye shes su'ang bshad do gsungs /
NK123(go)001:4332: dbyings su nub pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bo /
NK123(go)001:4334: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du thugs su chud pas srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis la mi gnas shing /
NK123(go)001:4335: byams pa dang snying rje chen po mtshungs par ldan
NK123(go)001:4336: las sems can gyi mos pa dang mtshams par sangs
NK123(go)001:4338: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dbyings su nub pa so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK123(go)001:4340: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma 'dres par mkhyen
NK123(go)001:4341: cing gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi 'byung gnas su
NK123(go)001:4342: gyur pas byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la zag
NK123(go)001:4343: med kyi chos ston cing the tshom gyi dra ba
NK123(go)001:4344: gcod pa'o // sgo lnga'i rnam shes dbyings su nub
NK123(go)001:4345: pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo
NK123(go)001:4347: 'jig rten gyi khams kun tu sprul pa dpag tu
NK123(go)001:4348: med pas sems can gyi don bsam gyi mi khyab
NK123(go)001:4350: gsum pa yon tan dang phrin las bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:4352: rang don don dam pa chos kyi sku'am don gyi sku zhes bya ba /
NK123(go)001:4355: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad de
NK123(go)001:4356: spang bya'i nyon mongs pa dang bral ba'i 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:4357: sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4358: gzhan don kun rdzob kyi sku'am /
NK123(go)001:4359: brda' yi sku zhes bya ba bsod nams kyi tshogs
NK123(go)001:4360: rgya mtsho lta bu'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:4361: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang ldan pa
NK123(go)001:4362: ste / rnam pa gnyis po bsdoms pa sku gnyis
NK123(go)001:4363: la mnga' ba'i bral smin gyi yon tan drug cu
NK123(go)001:4366: rang don gzhan don don dam sku dang ni //
NK123(go)001:4367: de la brten pa'i kun rdzob sku nyid de //
NK123(go)001:4368: bral dang rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK123(go)001:4369: yon tan dbye ba drug cu bzhi 'di dag /
NK123(go)001:4370: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa ltar dang /
NK123(go)001:4372: zag pa med pa'i phung po lnga /
NK123(go)001:4375: so sa yang dag par rig pa bzhi /
NK123(go)001:4382: dbang bcu la sogs yon tan gyi rnam grangs mtha' yas pa mnga' ba yin te /
NK123(go)001:4383: 'di dag kyang sngon slob lam du tshogs gnyis rgya
NK123(go)001:4384: mtsho lta bu goms pa'i lhan cig byed rkyen gyis
NK123(go)001:4385: dbyings kyi sgrib byed mtha' dag dang bral ba'i stobs
NK123(go)001:4387: ngo bo ni rang byung zag pa med pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:4388: shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bdag nyid can no
NK123(go)001:4389: // gnyis pa phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4390: de ltar yon tan mtha' yas pa la brten nas
NK123(go)001:4391: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las dus 'khor ba ji
NK123(go)001:4392: srid kyi bar du mdzad pa rgyun mi 'chad pas
NK123(go)001:4393: rtag pa dang / yul nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam
NK123(go)001:4394: pa'i sems can thams cad la snyoms par 'jug pas
NK123(go)001:4395: rtag pa dang / khyab pa dang / ngo bo
NK123(go)001:4396: gnas skabs mngon mtho'i lam la 'god pa'i phyir phan
NK123(go)001:4397: rtag pa dang / khyab pa dang / pa dang
NK123(go)001:4398: / mthar thug nges par legs pa byang chub kyi
NK123(go)001:4399: go 'phang la 'god pa'i phyir bde ba ste /
NK123(go)001:4400: don rnam pa gnyis po 'bad rtsol med par 'byung
NK123(go)001:4401: bas lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las bsam gyis mi
NK123(go)001:4402: khyab pa la dbang 'byor ba'i tshul /
NK123(go)001:4403: rtag cing khyab la lhun grub pa'i //
NK123(go)001:4404: yon tan pha rol phyin pa 'bras //
NK123(go)001:4406: yon tan sogs 'di dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas pa
NK123(go)001:4407: ni rje bla mas mdzad pa'i byang sems smon lam
NK123(go)001:4408: gyi dka' 'grel sogs las shes par bya dgos shing
NK123(go)001:4409: / mdo tsam ni dkon mchog gsum gyi rnam bzhag tu smos zin pas 'dir ma bris so //
NK123(go)001:4412: bdag med gnyis rtogs pha rol phyin rdzogs pa'i //
NK123(go)001:4413: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK123(go)001:4414: sangs rgyas par bgrod go 'phang thob pa'i lam //
NK123(go)001:4415: bden pa gnyis kyis rab tu 'thob par 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:4417: de ltar nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa gsum po'i lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4419: spong tshad gsum gyi khyad par mdor bsdu na /
NK123(go)001:4420: dpal rong zom pa chen pos mdzad pa'i lta ba'i brjed byang las /
NK123(go)001:4421: nyan thos kyi lta ba ni gang zag la bdag med par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4422: ting nge 'dzin dmigs pa dang bcas pa'i sa la gnas pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4423: spong tshad ni srid pa kun tu sbyor ba spang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:4424: rang sangs rgyas kyi lta ba ni /
NK123(go)001:4425: chos la gzugs kyi phung pos bsdus pa'i chos thams cad bdag med par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4426: ting nge 'dzin tshig gi don med par rtogs te brjod du med pa'i tshul gnas pas /
NK123(go)001:4427: gzung ba'i rtogs pa nyams par byas te 'on kyang
NK123(go)001:4428: brjod du med do snyams pa'i 'du shes 'jug pas
NK123(go)001:4429: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa ni ma spangs so //
NK123(go)001:4430: spong tshad ni gang ci yang rung ste /
NK123(go)001:4431: kun 'byung ba'i chos de dag thams cad 'gog pa'i chos su shes so //
NK123(go)001:4432: theg pa chen po spyi'i lta ba ni /
NK123(go)001:4433: chos dang gang zag gnyis las bdag med par rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4434: ting nge 'dzin ni bzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rtog
NK123(go)001:4435: pa thams cad las 'das te rnam par mi rtog
NK123(go)001:4437: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings la gnas so //
NK123(go)001:4438: spong tshad ni bag chags kyi mtshams sbyor ba thams cad yongs su spong ste /
NK123(go)001:4439: rnam pa thams cad mchog gi ye shes thob pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4440: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:4441: des kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa nyan rang byang
NK123(go)001:4442: sems gsum gyi theg pa mdo tsam bshad zin to
NK123(go)001:4443: // gnyis pa 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4445: lta spyod khyad par can gyi sgo nas da lta
NK123(go)001:4446: nas ci rigs par lam du byed pa'i thabs la
NK123(go)001:4447: brten nas sangs rgyas nyid myur du 'grub par byed
NK123(go)001:4448: pa ste / de nyid rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par du 'phags pa'i tshul yang /
NK123(go)001:4449: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa rgyu la 'bad pa cher byas nas tshogs chen pos sgrub dgos pa las /
NK123(go)001:4450: sngags ni rgyu la ltos nas 'bras bu smin zin
NK123(go)001:4451: pas 'bad rtsol chung ngus sangs rgyas thob pas 'phags
NK123(go)001:4452: pa dang / rgyu nas lam lnga sa bcu dka'
NK123(go)001:4453: ba chen pos bskal pa grangs med mang po na
NK123(go)001:4454: pa dang / sangs rgya la / sngags ni rab tshe gcig /'bring bar do /
NK123(go)001:4455: tha mas kyang skye ba brgyud nas sangs rgya bas dus myur bas kyang 'phags pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4456: rgyus sa dang po bden pa mthong ba la'ang tshogs dpag med sogs dgos la /
NK123(go)001:4457: sngags kyi dkyil 'khor tshogs mchod la sogs pa phra mas 'grub pas kyang 'phags pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4458: rgyus lam thad drang du ston par mi byed de /
NK123(go)001:4460: dgongs pa dang ldem dgongs sogs su bstan nas rnam par 'jog la /
NK123(go)001:4461: sngags ni lam cig car thad drang du bstan pas
NK123(go)001:4462: nye zhi ngang bar chad med pa'i phyir 'phags pa
NK123(go)001:4463: dang / gzhan yang rgyu'i theg pa bas sngags kyi theg pa 'dod pa'i don sgrub pa la /
NK123(go)001:4464: thabs mang ba dang dka' ba med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4466: dbang po rnon pos myur du 'grub pa'i tshul gyis 'phags te /
NK123(go)001:4467: tshul gsum pa'i sgron me las /
NK123(go)001:4468: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK123(go)001:4469: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK123(go)001:4470: dbang po rnon pos dbang byas te //
NK123(go)001:4471: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:4473: ci'i phyir 'bras bu'i theg pa dang rdo rje theg pa zhes bya snyam na /
NK123(go)001:4474: he ru ka gal po las /
NK123(go)001:4475: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa yis //
NK123(go)001:4476: sems nyid sangs rgyas rgyu ru gsungs //
NK123(go)001:4477: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa yis //
NK123(go)001:4478: sems nyid sangs rgyas nyid du bsgom //
NK123(go)001:4479: rgyu dang 'bras bu gang yin pa'i //
NK123(go)001:4480: phyogs kyang rab tu shes rab bya //
NK123(go)001:4481: zhes pas mtshan nyid theg par sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rgyu tsam du shes pa de /
NK123(go)001:4482: rkyen tshogs gnyis kyis gong du 'phel bas sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:4483: myang 'das kyi rgyu rnam byang gi chos lam du byed pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4484: rgyu'i theg pa zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:4485: rgyu 'bras snga phyir khas len pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:4486: sngags kyi theg pas sems nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bo
NK123(go)001:4487: sku dang ye shes kyi bdag nyid du ye nas
NK123(go)001:4488: rang la gnas pas thob bya da lta nyid nas
NK123(go)001:4489: rang la yod pa ni gzhi /
NK123(go)001:4490: de shes 'jug gi byed pas gnas skabs glo bur gyi dri ma bsal te /
NK123(go)001:4491: ngo shes par byed pa'i cha nas lam /
NK123(go)001:4492: gzhi de nyid mngon du gyur pa'i cha nas 'bras bur bzhag pas /
NK123(go)001:4493: don la rgyu 'bras snga phyi med pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4494: 'bras bu'i theg pa dang rdo rje theg pa zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:4496: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK123(go)001:4497: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:4498: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te //
NK123(go)001:4499: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma tshol zhig /
NK123(go)001:4501: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK123(go)001:4502: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK123(go)001:4504: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK123(go)001:4505: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK123(go)001:4506: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK123(go)001:4507: de lta bu yi rang du byung //
NK123(go)001:4511: rgyu yi theg pa chen po las //
NK123(go)001:4512: sku gsung thugs kyi lam rnams kyi //
NK123(go)001:4513: gsang ba che las gsang ba mchog /
NK123(go)001:4514: rab tu 'phags par rig par bya //
NK123(go)001:4516: mtshan nyid du sku gsung thugs sgyu ma dang brag
NK123(go)001:4517: cha rmi lam bzhin du rang bzhin med par rgyas
NK123(go)001:4519: rang gi sgo gsum tha mal pas phyag bskor kha
NK123(go)001:4520: ton sogs dge la brtson pa dang rnam rtog bkag
NK123(go)001:4521: pa'i zhi lhag sgrub pa tsam la /
NK123(go)001:4522: sngags su snang grags rig gsum dkyil 'a khor gsum
NK123(go)001:4523: dang sgo gsum rdo rje gsum du legs par rtogs
NK123(go)001:4524: pas cir snang cir spyod thams cad chos nyid kyi
NK123(go)001:4525: rol pa las nam yang 'da' ba med pas te
NK123(go)001:4527: sngags phyi pas lha'i sku gsung thugs su bltas te bsgom pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4528: nang pa ltar na chos thams cad sku gsung thugs
NK123(go)001:4529: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du rtogs nas goms
NK123(go)001:4530: par byed pa'i phyir 'bras bu lam byed dang /
NK123(go)001:4531: rdo rje theg pa'i nges tshig grub ste /
NK123(go)001:4532: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde mig las /
NK123(go)001:4533: 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:4534: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor lam byas nas //
NK123(go)001:4535: 'bras bu de nyid lam du khyer //
NK123(go)001:4536: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum ni //
NK123(go)001:4537: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjer sbyor //
NK123(go)001:4538: de rigs rdo rje theg par btags //
NK123(go)001:4539: zhes gsungs de lta bu'i theg pa de la gsang
NK123(go)001:4540: ba sgyu 'phrul las bla na med pa'i theg pa
NK123(go)001:4543: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK123(go)001:4544: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK123(go)001:4545: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK123(go)001:4546: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK123(go)001:4550: rdo rje theg pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:4551: phyi pa thub pa rgyud dang ni //
NK123(go)001:4552: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud du gsungs //
NK123(go)001:4554: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa'am dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4555: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud dam dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ste gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:4556: de gnyis kyi khyad par la bzhed pa mi 'dra
NK123(go)001:4557: ba 'ga' zhig mthong mod gtso bo gsang bdag dngos
NK123(go)001:4558: byon rje sgro phug pa chen pos ni 'di ltar
NK123(go)001:4559: bzhed de / lta ba'i khyad par /
NK123(go)001:4560: sems nyid bdag nyid chen por rtogs pa nang pa dang ma rtogs pa phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4561: dngos grub len tshul gyi khyad par /
NK123(go)001:4562: ye shes kyi lha la re zhing bka' la sdod pas dngos grub zhu ba phyi pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4563: bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas sems nyid sku dang
NK123(go)001:4564: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i phyir
NK123(go)001:4565: dngos grub rang la yod par mthong ba nang pa
NK123(go)001:4567: mchog dbang gong ma gsum la bskur thob mi nus na phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4568: de gsum la gtso bor 'dzin pa nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4570: 'khor ba'i chos nyi shu la thabs kyis zin nas spyod nus pa nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4573: mi tshe bdun dang lnga dang gsum sogs nas sbyor nus pa phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4574: tshe 'di la sbyor nus pa nang pa'o gsungs /
NK123(go)001:4576: lta spyod ting 'dzin gsum dbyer med du 'dod pa sngags nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4578: 'di dang mtshan nyid gnyis kun rdzob lam du byed nus mi nus kyis 'byed par bzhed /
NK123(go)001:4580: smin byed dbang gi khyad par rgyud sde gong du'ang dbang bzhi tshang bar mi ston zhing /
NK123(go)001:4581: khyad par rigs pa'i dbang tsam las mi ston pa phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4582: dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur ba nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4583: grol byed kyi lam sas rtogs pa lta ba'i khyad par /
NK123(go)001:4584: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor
