NK123(go)001:4585: gsum du shes pas dag mnyam blang dor med par
NK123(go)001:4586: rtogs pa'i dbyings gzhir byed na nang pa mi byed
NK123(go)001:4587: na phyi pa / sgom pa'i lha'i khyad par /
NK123(go)001:4588: lha ci tsam yod kyang zhal sbyor med na phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4592: ri rab kyi steng la sogs pa'i gnas gtsang mar mos pa byed na phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4593: dur khrod dam o rgyan la sogs par mos pa byed na nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4595: khrus dang gtsang sbra la sogs pa gtso bor byed na phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4596: gtsang sbra mi byed cing bza' btung ci dga' la spyod nus na nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4598: rin po che la sogs pa gtsang mar mos pa phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4599: ka p+aa la gtso bor byed pa nang pa /
NK123(go)001:4601: dkar gsum mngar gsum sogs gtsang mi'i zas la spyod pa phyi pa /
NK123(go)001:4602: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga dngos sam bdud rtsi ril
NK123(go)001:4603: bu tsam gyis byin gyis brlabs te mos pa byed
NK123(go)001:4605: mdor na bsgrub bya'i lha dang bdag gnyis bzang ngan
NK123(go)001:4606: tha dad med par mnyam pa'i tshul gyis sgrub pa
NK123(go)001:4608: kun rdzob tu bzang ngan nam tha dad pa'i rnam
NK123(go)001:4609: par bdag gi rgyud lha'i byin gyis rlob pa'i tshul
NK123(go)001:4610: gyis sgrub pa sngags phyi pa'i khyad par ro gsungs
NK123(go)001:4611: / de las dang po phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4612: blang dor dang spang gnyen thams cad phyi mtshan nyid
NK123(go)001:4613: rgyu'i theg pa dang tshul mthun pas phyi thub pa
NK123(go)001:4615: phyi'i dka' thub dang gtsang sbra sogs bral ze rig
NK123(go)001:4616: byed pa ltar brten pas dka' thub rig byed kyi
NK123(go)001:4618: gang zag dbang po 'bring gsum la dgongs te gsungs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4621: phyi pa rgyud la rnam gsum ste //
NK123(go)001:4622: kri ya u pa yo ga'o //
NK123(go)001:4628: gang zag dbang po 'bring gi tha ma'i ngo skal du gsungs pa'i bya ba'i rgyud de la'ang /
NK123(go)001:4633: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK123(go)001:4634: rtogs pas kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re
NK123(go)001:4635: zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK123(go)001:4637: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK123(go)001:4638: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK123(go)001:4639: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK123(go)001:4640: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK123(go)001:4643: kri y+aa'i sgra bya ba ste /
NK123(go)001:4644: phyi'i bya ba gtso bor ston pa'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:4645: bsam gtan phyi ma'i 'grel ba las /
NK123(go)001:4646: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK123(go)001:4648: dbye ba la spyir dpung bzang 'grel bar spyod pa'i sgo bzhir gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:4649: 'jug pa'i spyod pa dbang gis snod rung du byed pa /
NK123(go)001:4650: sbyor ba'i spyod pa rig gsum gang gi lha bsnyen pa /
NK123(go)001:4651: sgrub pa'i spyod pa mtshan ma mthong nas rdzas dang
NK123(go)001:4652: sngags g.yog 'dzom pas brtson 'grus bar ma chad par
NK123(go)001:4654: grub pa'i mtha' 'bras bu'i spyod pa /
NK123(go)001:4655: de ltar sgrubs pas rdzas lus longs spyod rnams 'dod
NK123(go)001:4656: pa'i lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i rig 'dzin nam
NK123(go)001:4658: rten de la brten nas sngags kyi phyin drug gi
NK123(go)001:4659: spyod pa spyad pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu rgyud
NK123(go)001:4660: sde 'dir bshad pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan nyid
NK123(go)001:4661: can gyi byang chub rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK123(go)001:4662: sa mngon du byed par 'dod pa rnams yin yang
NK123(go)001:4663: / 'dir gang smos ltar 'chad pa la drug las /
NK123(go)001:4666: chu dang cod pan gyi dbang 'khor dang bcas pa
NK123(go)001:4667: bskur bas slob ma snod rung du byed pa ste
NK123(go)001:4669: chu yi dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /
NK123(go)001:4670: bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK123(go)001:4672: de yang rigs gsum gang rung gi dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas /
NK123(go)001:4673: gzungs dang dbang sngags bzla bzhin pa'i bum pa'i chu yi dbang gis chos sku dang /
NK123(go)001:4674: rig gang yin gyi dam tshig phyag rgya spyi bor
NK123(go)001:4675: bzhag rin po che'i dar dpyang bcing cod pan gyi
NK123(go)001:4676: dbang gis gzugs sku'i nus pa bzhag pa yin pas
NK123(go)001:4677: de gnyis rtsa ba'i smin byed dngos dang /
NK123(go)001:4678: de'i 'khor du rigs sngags kyi dngos grub sgrub pa
NK123(go)001:4679: me tog gang phog gi lha yi bzlas lung sbyin
NK123(go)001:4680: pa rdo rje slob ma'i dbang /
NK123(go)001:4681: bar chad zhi zhing bgegs gzhom pa khrus bya ba bsrung ba'i dbang /
NK123(go)001:4682: 'byor pa rgyas par byed pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang rnams so //
NK123(go)001:4684: khrus dang gtsang sbra dang dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:4686: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum /
NK123(go)001:4689: de yang dag pa gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:4690: de las dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na /
NK123(go)001:4691: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4692: rdzas dang longs spyod dag pa dang //
NK123(go)001:4695: bdag dang lha yi de kho na nyid bsgom pa lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa /
NK123(go)001:4696: sha chang sgog btsong spang zhing khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK123(go)001:4697: la gnas pa sogs rdzas dang yo byad dag pa
NK123(go)001:4698: / bzlas brjod dang bsam gtan gyi de kho na
NK123(go)001:4699: nyid sngags dang ting 'dzin dag pa ste zhib par
NK123(go)001:4702: phyi'i khrus yan lag lnga khrus /
NK123(go)001:4703: nang gi khrus rtsa ltung dag par byed pa /
NK123(go)001:4704: gsang ba'i khrus mtshan rtog dag par byed pa ste khrus gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:4705: phyis gos ras gsar pa gyon pa /
NK123(go)001:4706: nang gi gos sdom pa bsrung ba /
NK123(go)001:4707: gsang ba'i gos lha bsgom pa ste gos gsum barje ba rnams so //
NK123(go)001:4710: kri ya don dam chos nyid blta //
NK123(go)001:4711: kun rdzob rang rig yon tan lha //
NK123(go)001:4712: rigs gsum dkyil 'khor snang ba la //
NK123(go)001:4714: ces pas bden pa gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:4716: sems nyid dag pas stong gsal gyi ye shes yod
NK123(go)001:4717: med snang stong gi mtha' bzhi dang bral bar 'dod
NK123(go)001:4719: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba //
NK123(go)001:4720: rig phyir ye shes gzhan las min //
NK123(go)001:4722: kun rdzob la yang log gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:4724: dbu ma pa man chad kyis yang dag dang log par brtags pa'i kun rdzob thams cad yin la /
NK123(go)001:4725: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob ni /
NK123(go)001:4726: chos nyid de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan rigs gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:4727: kun rdzob snang ba'i dngos po mtho ba rnams spyan ras gzigs 'jam pa thams cad 'jam dpal /
NK123(go)001:4728: rtsub pa thams cad phyag rdor te /
NK123(go)001:4729: rigs drug gi phyed rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang bar 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:4731: skyon bslang snang ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK123(go)001:4732: snang ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK123(go)001:4733: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK123(go)001:4734: mthong ba rnam par dag ces bya //
NK123(go)001:4736: de yang kun rdzob tu yongs su dag pa'i lha dang ye shes pa nyid sgrub na /
NK123(go)001:4737: dngos grub nges par stsol ba'i mthu dang ldan pa rje bo lta bu dang /
NK123(go)001:4738: rang nyid lha de mnyes par bsgrubs pa'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:4739: dngos grub nod pa po khol po lta bur lta
NK123(go)001:4740: zhing / don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i chos nyid la bzang ngan med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4741: chos can tha snyad du rten cing 'brel bar 'byung
NK123(go)001:4742: ba'i dbang gis lha sngags phyag rgyas rang la rgyas
NK123(go)001:4743: btab ste sgrub na ji ltar dmigs pa'i 'bu bslu
NK123(go)001:4744: med du thob pa'i nges shes khyad par can ni
NK123(go)001:4746: de la mchog dman du blta ba tsam zhig 'di pa'i khyad chos min yang /
NK123(go)001:4747: rje bos khol po la mchog sbyin nus pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:4748: lha dang sngags la brten nas bdag gi rgyud la
NK123(go)001:4749: dngos grub gnyis gdon mi za bar grub pa'i nges
NK123(go)001:4750: shes te / de'i don yang dngos grub stsal nus
NK123(go)001:4751: par shes pa tsam min par rang mtha' thug lha
NK123(go)001:4752: de dang ngo bo dbyer med pa'i 'grub pa'i tshul
NK123(go)001:4753: la yid ches pa ni lta ba'i gnad de /
NK123(go)001:4754: dpal rang zom pa chen pos kyang gsang sngags pas
NK123(go)001:4755: don dam pa skye 'gags med par 'dod pa ni
NK123(go)001:4757: kun rdzob tu phung khams skye mched sgyu ma tsam du lta ba'ang mthun no //
NK123(go)001:4758: bye brag tu sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid de dag kyang
NK123(go)001:4759: yongs su dag pa'i lha'i mtshan nyid du lta ba
NK123(go)001:4760: dang / bden pa gnyis kyang dbyer med par lta bas bye brag tu byas pa'o //
NK123(go)001:4761: de las bye brag tu bya rgyud kyi lhar blta
NK123(go)001:4762: ba yang chos nyid dag pa'i sgo nas lhar blta
NK123(go)001:4763: ba zhes grags te de yang bden gnyis dbyer med
NK123(go)001:4764: du lta ba'i mthus grub ste /
NK123(go)001:4765: chos nyid sangs rgyas yin na chos can sangs rgyas ma yin pa mi rung ste /
NK123(go)001:4766: chos can gyi ngo bo chos nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4767: gnyis ka sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:4768: bdag dang sangs rgyas dbyer med rtogs shing ci la
NK123(go)001:4769: yang mi gnas ci yang mi len pa'i shes rab
NK123(go)001:4770: dang ting nge 'a dzin ni sangs rgyas kyi lam
NK123(go)001:4771: yin par nges don gyi mdo sde las kyang 'byung
NK123(go)001:4772: ste / gang zhig bdag dang sangs rgyas rnams //
NK123(go)001:4773: rang bazhinamanyama par rab gnas shing //
NK123(go)001:4774: mi gnas len pa med pa ni //
NK123(go)001:4775: de dag bde bar gshegs par 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:4776: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK123(go)001:4777: rnam par shes dang sems pa rnams //
NK123(go)001:4778: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:4779: zhes gsungs pa lta bu yin no //
NK123(go)001:4780: de bas na yongs su dag pa'i lha'i rang bzhin yin pa la /
NK123(go)001:4781: de bzhin du bsgoms shing bsten pas de nyid 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK123(go)001:4782: bdag dang gzhan gyi don spyod par nus so //
NK123(go)001:4783: zhes gsungs shing kahthoga pa'i theg spyi'i 'grel bar /
NK123(go)001:4784: dngos por snang ba 'di rnams kyang /
NK123(go)001:4785: rigs gsum mgon po'i sku ma yin kyang /
NK123(go)001:4786: lta sgom spyod gsum gyi sgo nas sems dag par
NK123(go)001:4787: byas na mkhar chu las lugs sku snang ba bzhin
NK123(go)001:4788: 'khrul ba dag pa nyid 'bras bu'i ngo bor ye
NK123(go)001:4790: zhes mkhar chu lugs sku ma yin yang mkhar chu
NK123(go)001:4791: las gzhan pa'i sku mi 'byung ba dper mdzad nas
NK123(go)001:4792: gsungs te / mdor na rang sems dag pa mtha'
NK123(go)001:4793: bzhir rtogs pa'i kun rdzob yongs su dag pa lha'i
NK123(go)001:4794: mtshan nyid du lta ba ma gtogs ma dag pa'i
NK123(go)001:4795: dngos po nyid kyi rang bzhin ye nas dag pa
NK123(go)001:4799: dkon mchog gsum dang byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:4800: sngags dang phyag rgya mi spang zhing //
NK123(go)001:4801: rdo rje dril bu spang mi bya //
NK123(go)001:4802: lha dang bla ma de bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:4803: de ni yan lag dam tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:4804: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po ni //
NK123(go)001:4805: khri la nyal bar mi bya zhing //
NK123(go)001:4806: sha mi za zhing chang mi btung //
NK123(go)001:4807: sgog pa la phud bza' mi bya //
NK123(go)001:4808: zhes yan lag gi dam tshig drug dang rtsa ba'i lnga sde bcu gcig tu gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4810: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK123(go)001:4811: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK123(go)001:4812: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang ni //
NK123(go)001:4813: gsang sngags rig sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK123(go)001:4814: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK123(go)001:4815: zhes dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba /
NK123(go)001:4816: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gsum la slob pa /
NK123(go)001:4817: gsang sngags te lha pho dang rig sngags te lha
NK123(go)001:4818: mo'i tshogs kyis bsdus pa'i bya rgyud kyi lha la
NK123(go)001:4819: dad pa ste rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum dang /
NK123(go)001:4820: rtag par phyag rgya chen po la sogs kyis bstan don bye brag gi dam tshig bcu gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:4821: rang gi lha la lha gzhan las gus pa bya ba /
NK123(go)001:4822: bya rgyud kyi sgor zhugs pa'i dam tshig can la gus pa /
NK123(go)001:4823: bstan sgor zhugs pa'i grogs mdza' bo rnams la gus pa /
NK123(go)001:4824: rang la dbang dang man ngag sbyin pa'i bla ma la gus pa /
NK123(go)001:4825: las ma grub pa sogs kyis lha la khro bas sdang bar mi bya /
NK123(go)001:4826: tshes brgyad sogs dus mtshams su rang gi lha mchod pa /
NK123(go)001:4827: phyi rol pa sogs ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod pa /
NK123(go)001:4828: glo bur gyi mgron mchod pa /
NK123(go)001:4829: sems can la byams pa mi gtong ba /
NK123(go)001:4830: gzhan don la brtson pa mi 'dor ba /
NK123(go)001:4831: bzlas brjod la tshul bzhin du brtson pa /
NK123(go)001:4832: dam tshig gsum bkod sogs las bstan pa'i dam tshig gzhan yang ci nus su bsrung ba /
NK123(go)001:4833: dbang bskur ma thob pa'am thob kyang nyams pa'i dam
NK123(go)001:4834: tshig med pa la sngags dang phyag rgya mi sbyin
NK123(go)001:4835: zhing rgyud dang man ngag sba bar bya ba rnams
NK123(go)001:4836: so // de ltar rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum dang
NK123(go)001:4837: bye brag gi dam tshig bcu gsum du dbye ba'i
NK123(go)001:4838: tshul 'di ni snying po'i spyi don gsang bdag zhal
NK123(go)001:4839: lung du gsungs pa bzhin rigs gsum spyi'i dkyil chog
NK123(go)001:4840: gi sdom bzung ltar bkod pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:4841: gzhan du sdom gsum 'brel chen du rtsa ltung bcu bzhir grangs nges mdzad pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4842: rdor brag zhabs drung pad phrin gyis mdo dbang du
NK123(go)001:4843: rnam grangs bcu gsum du bsdu bar mdzad de don
NK123(go)001:4845: sgom pa la mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las dang po mtshan bcas ni /
NK123(go)001:4846: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing dbang
NK123(go)001:4847: nod la dam tshig dang ldan pa'i sgrub bo des
NK123(go)001:4848: lha dang sngags la sems pa 'ba' zhig ma gtogs
NK123(go)001:4849: pa'i bsams pa gzhan spangs nas lha yi sku dang
NK123(go)001:4850: sngags kyi tshul la dmigs pa las su rung ba'i
NK123(go)001:4851: sgo nas sgom pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:4853: lag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:4854: bdag gi lha dang bdag gi gzugs tha mi dad
NK123(go)001:4855: par byas pas mtshan ma ma byung gi bar du
NK123(go)001:4857: zhi ba'i blo gros gang gi tshe byang chub sems dpa' spyod pa gsang sngags kyi sgor spyod la /
NK123(go)001:4858: bdag nyid rang gi lha'i gzugs su byas la the tshom med pa'i yid kyis /
NK123(go)001:4859: nga rgyal bskyed cing 'gro yang rung /
NK123(go)001:4863: rtag tu dus thams cad du /
NK123(go)001:4864: bskyod kyang mi g.yo ba de'i tshe /
NK123(go)001:4866: 'jam dpal gang gi tshe rang gi gzugs yongs su spangs te /
NK123(go)001:4867: lha'i nga rgyal la the tshom med pa thob pa
NK123(go)001:4868: de'i tshe gsang sngags kyi chos nyid des chos nyid
NK123(go)001:4869: stan te / zhes sogs mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK123(go)001:4870: 'jig rten gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtog pa las /
NK123(go)001:4871: sems can kun gyi bdag che ni //
NK123(go)001:4872: bdag nyid la yang gnas so zhes //
NK123(go)001:4873: byin gyis brlabs nas sems dpa' bdag /
NK123(go)001:4874: yin zhes nga rgyal bsgom par bya //
NK123(go)001:4876: rang sems so sor brtag pa ni //
NK123(go)001:4877: sangs rgyas byang chub de nyid yin //
NK123(go)001:4879: 'jig rten gsum po de nyid do //
NK123(go)001:4881: 'byung ba che rnams de nyid do //
NK123(go)001:4883: de nyid phyag na rdo rje yin //
NK123(go)001:4885: sangs rgyas rigs kyang de nyid de /
NK123(go)001:4886: zhes rdo rje pad ma nor bu'i rigs kyang de nyid yin par gsungs /
NK123(go)001:4887: sems dpar byin brlabs sbyor ba yi //
NK123(go)001:4888: rdo rje sems dpa' yang 'gyur ro //
NK123(go)001:4889: bcom ldan rdo rje de nyid ni //
NK123(go)001:4890: bsgom pas sems dpa' nyid du 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:4892: yang rnam pa thams cad du rtag par bdag gi lus dang lha'i gzugs su /
NK123(go)001:4893: bdag gi ngag dang lha'i ngag tu /
NK123(go)001:4894: bdag gi yid dang lha'i yid du mthong ba de'i tshe mnyam par bzhag pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:4896: bya spyod kyi rgyud rnams su /
NK123(go)001:4897: bdag nyid lhar sgom pa mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:4898: mang du gsungs pas bya rgyud khyad par can gyi
NK123(go)001:4900: bdag nyid lhar bsgoms zhing nga rgyal byed pa med du mi rung ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:4901: spyir bya rgyud la tsam po pa dang khyad par can gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:4902: dang po dpung bzang gis zhus pa'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:4903: gsang sngags mdo sde'i tshul du ngas bshad do //
NK123(go)001:4904: zhes gsungs pa ltar thun mong mdo sde'i gzungs rnams dang tshul 'dra bar gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4905: rtog pa phra mo'i sngags phal che ra la rang
NK123(go)001:4906: lhar mi bsgoms par lha ye shes pa mdun du
NK123(go)001:4907: spyan drangs la mchod cing bzlas pa byed pa dang
NK123(go)001:4908: / ras bris la rten byas te sgrub pa sogs kyi tshul gsungs pa yod la /
NK123(go)001:4909: de dag gi cho ga pan grub rnams kyis gsang sngags mdo sde'i tshul du bkral ba'ang yod cing /
NK123(go)001:4910: de dag bya rgyud du gtogs par yang bzhed do //
NK123(go)001:4911: yang ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa'i rgyud la /
NK123(go)001:4912: bya rgyud la ye shes sems dpa'i bde ba med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:4913: bdag nyid lha'i snyems pa med pa zhes gsungs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:4914: 'di las rnal 'byor rgyud bzhin du rang lha dang
NK123(go)001:4915: tha mi dad du byas te rang la ye shes
NK123(go)001:4917: mdun bskyed gtso bor byas pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:4918: rnal 'byor rgyud ltar lha'i snyems pa mi bya ba'i don yin gyi /
NK123(go)001:4919: bdag nyid lhar bsgom pa gtan med pa'i don ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:4920: bya rgyud pas kun rdzob tu bdag dang lha la
NK123(go)001:4921: bzang ngan du lta ba'i phyir bdag nyid lha'i nga
NK123(go)001:4922: rgyal gyi gsal snang bskyed cing lha dngos yin pa'i
NK123(go)001:4923: 'du shes rgyud sde gong ma ltar mi nus pa'i
NK123(go)001:4924: don to // de ltar na bdag gi sgo gsum
NK123(go)001:4925: dang lha'i gsang gsum dbyer med du snang ba'i tshe
NK123(go)001:4926: sngags 'grub par gsungs pa'i lung rang gis drangs pa
NK123(go)001:4928: kun rdzob tu lha dngos kyi rang bzhin min yang
NK123(go)001:4929: yin pa'i nga rgyal sgom nas gsal snang byung nas
NK123(go)001:4930: / lha'i gsang gsum gyi dngos grub thob pa mi 'gal te /
NK123(go)001:4931: deng sang gi sngags gsar ma pa phal mo ches /
NK123(go)001:4932: sngags bla med kyi bskyed rim 'chad pa'i tshe /
NK123(go)001:4933: rang gdod nas lha'i rang bzhin du rnam par dag
NK123(go)001:4934: pa min yang lha yin par bsgoms pa go chod
NK123(go)001:4935: par khas len pa yin na /
NK123(go)001:4936: bya rgyud la'ang de lta bu 'ong ba ci la 'gal /
NK123(go)001:4937: gzhan yang rang nyid lha'i rnam par sgom pa dang
NK123(go)001:4938: ma bral ba'i sgo nas bltas pas bde ba lam
NK123(go)001:4940: gzhan la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:4941: phyogs bcings pa sogs kyi las phal mo che dang /
NK123(go)001:4942: rig 'dzin gyi 'khor los bsgyur ba sogs dngos grub
NK123(go)001:4943: chen po dang mngag gzhug pa sgrub pa sogs dngos
NK123(go)001:4944: grub sna tshogs bsgrub pa yin gyi /
NK123(go)001:4945: tha mal rang ga ma'i blo ma bor bas de ltar byas kyang don chung bar zad do //
NK123(go)001:4946: gal te rang tha mal pa lha min pa'i gnad kyis lhar sgom mi rung na /
NK123(go)001:4948: bris sku dkyil 'khor sogs lhar bskyed mi rung bar mtshungs te /
NK123(go)001:4949: de dag kyang lha dngos min pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:4950: mdun gyi lha bsgoms pa de yang rang sems kyis brtag ste byas mod /
NK123(go)001:4951: de la gsar snang grub rgyu yod na rang sems
NK123(go)001:4952: dang rang lus lhar gsal kyang gsal snang grub pa
NK123(go)001:4954: mdun gyi lha'i rnam pa de yang rang sems kyi
NK123(go)001:4955: gsal cha tsam gyi rnam pa snang ba yin na'ang
NK123(go)001:4956: / de bdag dang rgyud tha dad pa'i lha ye shes pa dngos su zhen cing /
NK123(go)001:4957: rang dngos grub nod pa po'i tshul gyis mchog dman
NK123(go)001:4958: gyi 'du shes shas che ba'i gdul bya dag gi
NK123(go)001:4959: ngor / re zhig mdun bskyed gtso bor byed pa'i bya rgyud rnams bstan pa yin kyang /
NK123(go)001:4960: rnam pa kun tu tha mal pa dang lha ye shes pa 'dre mi rung bar bzung na /
NK123(go)001:4961: tha mal pa'i snang ba gang yang lhar bsgom mi
NK123(go)001:4962: rung ba'i gnyis snang dam po des dngos grub 'byung
NK123(go)001:4963: ba la gegs byed pa yin cing /
NK123(go)001:4964: bya rgyud pa la'ang nam zhig lha dang rang gnyis
NK123(go)001:4965: su med pa'i nges pa skyes pa'i tshe blo na
NK123(go)001:4966: 'phar te / rgyud sde gong ma'i dgongs don la 'jug pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:4967: des na sngags bla med nas ji ltar gsungs pa'i
NK123(go)001:4968: dgongs don nyams su ma lon par du 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:4970: gnas skabs su gdul bya'i blo dang mthun par 'jug
NK123(go)001:4971: pa'i mdo dang rgyud 'og ma rnams kyi lam la
NK123(go)001:4972: zhugs pa'ang rim gyis mthar 'bras 'thob pa yod mod
NK123(go)001:4973: kyi lam la nye ring gi khyad par gong nas
NK123(go)001:4974: gong du 'phags pa dang lta ba shes rab dang
NK123(go)001:4975: lam sgom pa'i thabs gnyis kas 'phags pa yin pa'i
NK123(go)001:4976: phyir ro // rnam snang dang 'jam dpal sogs lha'i
NK123(go)001:4977: ngo bo la rgyud gong 'og gi khyad par gyi
NK123(go)001:4978: mchog dman med pas 'phags yul gyi slob dpon chen
NK123(go)001:4979: po kun dga' snying po sogs kyi rgyud sde 'og
NK123(go)001:4980: ma la'ang gong ma skyor rung bar bzhed la /
NK123(go)001:4981: sa skya pa dag gis bya rgyud gcig la rgyud sde bzhi kar bkral rung bar bzhed /
NK123(go)001:4982: 'on kyang gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun par tha mal pa'i dngos zhen che chung dang bstun te /
NK123(go)001:4984: bdag nyid lha'i snyems pa don mthun lam du byed
NK123(go)001:4985: nus mi nus sogs kyi rgyud sde bzhi'i cho ga'i
NK123(go)001:4986: sgrub tshul tha dad du phye ba bzhin du /
NK123(go)001:4987: rgyud gang nas de ltar dngos su bstan la de
NK123(go)001:4988: dang de'i rgyud kyi rnam bzhag byed dgos pa yin
NK123(go)001:4989: no // de ltar rigs pas dpyad na bya rgyud
NK123(go)001:4990: yin na bdag bskyed med pa'i nges pa mi 'grub
NK123(go)001:4991: no // la / bdag skyed yod na 'thad pa
NK123(go)001:4992: du ma yang yod mod mang du ma smos so
NK123(go)001:4993: no // la / // lung gi dbang du byas
NK123(go)001:4994: na yang bya rgyud la bdag bskyed mi bzhed pa
NK123(go)001:4995: de dag gis bya rgyud dngos gnas par zhal gyis
NK123(go)001:4996: bzhes pa'i lag na rdo rje dbang bskur ba sogs
NK123(go)001:4997: kyi lung sngar drangs pa dang bya rgyud kyi spyi
NK123(go)001:4998: rgyud bzhir bzhed pa'i nang mtshan bsam gtan phyi ma
NK123(go)001:4999: no // la / // las / gzhi gnyis gsungs
NK123(go)001:5000: pa'i gzhi gcig ni rang nyid lhar sgom pa yin
NK123(go)001:5001: no // la / // las / pa sogs dang
NK123(go)001:5002: / bya rgyud 'ba' zhig tu 'dod pa'i gar mkhan
NK123(go)001:5003: mchog gi brtag pa phyi ma las /
NK123(go)001:5004: bdag nyid phyag rdor du bskyed par gsungs pa sogs
NK123(go)001:5005: de 'dra 'ga' yod pa dang gal te bdag lhar
NK123(go)001:5006: bsgom pa gsungs pa med kyang /
NK123(go)001:5007: de tsam gyis bya rgyud yin nges su mi 'grub ste /
NK123(go)001:5008: bla med rgyud kyi sngags khol phyung dang /
NK123(go)001:5009: rtog pa'i rgyud 'ga' zhig la sogs pa bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:5010: gzhan yang bya rgyud lugs kyi chu cod pan gyi dbang bskur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5011: gtsang sbra dang khrus sogs kyang bya rgyud du gtogs
NK123(go)001:5012: tshad la de dag gi gsal kha ma byung yang
NK123(go)001:5013: bya rgyud yin par 'dod dgos pa bzhin /
NK123(go)001:5014: bdag bskyed ma bstan pas bdag bskyed sgom mi rung
NK123(go)001:5015: na dbang sogs la'ang mtshungs par khas len dgos so
NK123(go)001:5016: // bdag bskyed dngos su ma bstan pa'i rgyud phal che na /
NK123(go)001:5017: mdun bskyed kyang dngos su ma bstan pa yod pas
NK123(go)001:5018: de dag kyang bya rgyud min par yang 'gyur ba'i
NK123(go)001:5019: phyir dang / rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang bla med
NK123(go)001:5020: kyi rgyud yin pa 'ga' la'ang sngags dang cho ga
NK123(go)001:5021: sogs bstan gyi bdag bskyed sogs lha'i mngon rtogs med
NK123(go)001:5023: sngags bzla rgyu yod pa tsam gyis rgyud sde'i khongs su gtogs nges pa'ang min te /
NK123(go)001:5024: dper na chu cod pan gyi dbang nod pa sogs sngon du 'gro ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5025: mdun bskyed sogs mi dgos par /
NK123(go)001:5026: dad pas bzla rung ba 'dul ba dang mdo las
NK123(go)001:5027: byung ba'i sngags dang drang srang sogs bden tshig grub
NK123(go)001:5028: pa dang / lha mthu bo che sogs kyis byin
NK123(go)001:5029: gyis brlabs pas nad zhi ba dang mig 'phrul ston
NK123(go)001:5030: pa sogs kyi sngags mtha' yas pa yod pa bzhin
NK123(go)001:5031: pa dang / no // de yang sangs rgyas dang
NK123(go)001:5032: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la dkyil 'khor gang rung
NK123(go)001:5033: du lha sogs kyi rig sngags phal mo che rgyud
NK123(go)001:5034: dang dkyil 'khor de la brten pa'i rigs sngags kyi
NK123(go)001:5035: 'khor yin pas de'i rigs su gtogs la /
NK123(go)001:5036: de ltar min pa rnams ni /
NK123(go)001:5038: gzhan yang kha cig gnas med rnam par 'khyams //
NK123(go)001:5040: des na rgyud kyi tshig ris la bdag bskyed yod
NK123(go)001:5041: med tsam zhig gis bya rgyud yin min dpyad dka'
NK123(go)001:5042: bas sngags phal mo che dang /
NK123(go)001:5043: bla med kyi rdzogs rim sogs phal che ba rgyud der dngos su gsal bar bstan pa med kyang /
NK123(go)001:5044: de dag gi bshad rgyud rgyas pa sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:5045: rgyud gzhan na gsal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5046: rgyud kyi bka' bsdu ba po gsang bdag dang mkha'
NK123(go)001:5047: 'gro ma sogs kyi man ngag la brten te bkral
NK123(go)001:5048: ba'i lung zab mo shin tu mang ba'i phyir na
NK123(go)001:5049: / lam 'di'i shing rta chen po'i dngos grub brnyes
NK123(go)001:5050: shing mkhas pa'i dpa' bo 'dzam gling na yongs su
NK123(go)001:5051: / grags pa / slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba
NK123(go)001:5052: sogs kyi rjes su 'brang ba ni shin tu rig
NK123(go)001:5053: pa dang ldan zhing dngos grub kyi lam po che
NK123(go)001:5054: yin pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:5055: zhes kun mkhyen bla ma 'jal dpal rjes pas gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:5056: de ltar nges par byas nas sgom pa dngos la 'jug pa la /
NK123(go)001:5057: spyir de kho na nyid bzhir gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:5058: de la bdag gi de kho na nyid ni gzhi gnas lugs lta bas gtan la 'bebs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5059: zhib par gong du song la /
NK123(go)001:5060: de yang slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK123(go)001:5061: bdag gi de kho na nyid ni rig pas dpyad pa'i stong pa tsam la mi bya yi /
NK123(go)001:5062: bdag gi de kho na nyid gnyis su med pa'i
NK123(go)001:5063: ye shes kyi mtshan nyid de thob na sangs rgyas
NK123(go)001:5064: su 'gyur bas de 'dzin zhes gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:5065: mdor na rnam par shes pa'i mtshan nyid kyi chos
NK123(go)001:5066: las 'das te snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:5067: shes kyi bzhugs tshul gtan la phebs na /
NK123(go)001:5068: bdag gi de kho na nyid kyang de yin la /
NK123(go)001:5069: don dam pa'i lha yang der tshul gcig ste chos
NK123(go)001:5070: thams cad kyi gnas lugs dang don dam byang chub
NK123(go)001:5072: lha'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK123(go)001:5073: rnam 'joms kyi rgyud rgyas pa'i tshigs drangs te sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK123(go)001:5074: dang po khrus byas rnal 'byor pas /
NK123(go)001:5075: rdo rje'i gdan la 'dug nas ni /
NK123(go)001:5076: mchod dang gsol bas lha drug sgom /
NK123(go)001:5077: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang /
NK123(go)001:5078: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin no //
NK123(go)001:5079: zhes pas bdag gi de kho na nyid mtha' bzhi dang bral bar bsgoms pa stong pa'i lha /
NK123(go)001:5080: de nyid kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par sgom pa yi ge'i lha /
NK123(go)001:5081: de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags gzugs rang sgra sgrogs pa sgra'i lha /
NK123(go)001:5082: sngags de nyid zla dkyil la 'dres nas slar yang
NK123(go)001:5083: sngags phreng bkod pa las 'od zer spro bsdus sangs
NK123(go)001:5084: rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs te zla ba sngags phreng
NK123(go)001:5085: dang bcas pa yongs su gyur pa las rigs gsum
NK123(go)001:5086: gyi lha de dang de'i gzugs su bsgoms pa gzugs
NK123(go)001:5087: kyi lha / de la rigs gang yin de dang de'i dam rgyas rgyas 'debs pa phyag rgya'i lha /
NK123(go)001:5088: dus kun tu ting nge 'dzin gyi lha'i 'du shes dang mi 'bral ba mtshan ma'i lha ste /
NK123(go)001:5089: lha ma bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor drug sogs 'og tu
NK123(go)001:5090: gal po'i dgongs pa bshad pa dang don gcig go
NK123(go)001:5091: // bzlas brjod kyi de kho na nyid la thun mong dang khyad par gnyis kyi /
NK123(go)001:5092: thun mong pa 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur la /
NK123(go)001:5095: sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol //
NK123(go)001:5096: gsang sngags mi 'gyur gzhi la gnas //
NK123(go)001:5097: yan lag ma nyams gsang sngags bzlas //
NK123(go)001:5098: ngal na bdag la ngal gsos shig /
NK123(go)001:5100: sgra ni sngags kyi yi ge'i phreng ba'i sgra'o //
NK123(go)001:5101: sems ni byang chub kyi sems rnam par rtog pa
NK123(go)001:5102: dang bral ba shin tu rnam dag dri med brtan
NK123(go)001:5103: zhing mi g.yo ba zab cing phra ba me long
NK123(go)001:5104: lta bu de nyid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam
NK123(go)001:5105: par snang ba'o // gzhi la gzhol ni mdun du
NK123(go)001:5106: bzhugs pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la dmigs pa
NK123(go)001:5108: gsang sngags mi 'gyur zhes pa ni gzhi bzhi po gsal zhing brtan par gyur pa la bya'o //
NK123(go)001:5109: gzhi la gnas zhes pa'i gzhi phyi ma ni bdag
NK123(go)001:5110: gi gzhi sde bdag lhar gsal ba la dmigs pa
NK123(go)001:5112: de ltar yan lag bzhi po ma nyams pa'i ting
NK123(go)001:5113: nge 'dzin dang ldan pa'i sgo nas gsang sngags bzla
NK123(go)001:5115: de yang mig sogs dbang po dang ba spu'i mthar
NK123(go)001:5116: thug par rgyu ba'i rlung thams cad lus kyi nang
NK123(go)001:5117: du slar sdud pa yis bkug nas /
NK123(go)001:5118: srog ces pa rlung dang rtsol ba zhes pa yid kyi dran pa 'gyu ba ste /
NK123(go)001:5119: de gnyis ka bsdom nas bzla bar gsungs te mdor na /
NK123(go)001:5120: gzhi bdag mdun lhar bsams pa /
NK123(go)001:5121: sems thugs kar zla dkyil bsam pa /
NK123(go)001:5122: sgra de'i steng sngags kyi sgra gdangs bsam pa /
NK123(go)001:5123: srog rtsol bsdams nas mdun gyi lha bzla ba sngags dang bcas la dmigs nas bzla ba /
NK123(go)001:5124: srog dbyung ba'i tshe rang gi lha bzla ba sngags phreng la dmigs pa /
NK123(go)001:5125: sngags bzla ba'ang skyon dang bral bar ma nyams par bzla zhing /
NK123(go)001:5126: des skyon mi rtog pa'i ngang la ngal gso ba rnams so //
NK123(go)001:5127: bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid ni /
NK123(go)001:5129: gsang sngags mer gnas dngos grub ster //
NK123(go)001:5130: sgra gnas rnal 'byor ster bar dran //
NK123(go)001:5131: sgra mthas thar ba ster bar byed //
NK123(go)001:5132: 'di dag de nyid gsum po yin //
NK123(go)001:5134: de nyid gsum gyi dang po gsang sngags mer gnas ni /
NK123(go)001:5135: rang nyid dang mdun gyi lha'i thugs kar rnam par
NK123(go)001:5136: mi rtog pa'i gzugs can thog reg dang bral bar
NK123(go)001:5137: dwangs zhing 'od gsal la dri ma med pa zla
NK123(go)001:5139: mi gnod cing zug rngu med la yid du 'ong ba'i rang bzhin can /
NK123(go)001:5140: rab tu zhi ba'i me lce 'od rab tu bzang bar bsam pa yin /
NK123(go)001:5141: me lce de'i nang na gnas pa /
NK123(go)001:5142: de nyid gnyis pa sgrar gnas zhes pa ni /
NK123(go)001:5143: sngags kyi yi ge'i phreng ba brgyud mar gnas pa'i
NK123(go)001:5144: sgra gdangs gsal zhing zur phyin pa dril bu'i sgra
NK123(go)001:5145: lta bur bar ma chad du yid ngor snang ba
NK123(go)001:5146: la sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa la gsal snang
NK123(go)001:5147: brtan pa ni gsang sngags mi 'gyur ba'i gzhi zhes
NK123(go)001:5148: gsungs te / ngag gi bzlas brjod med par lha'i
NK123(go)001:5149: ngo bo sngags kyi sgra yid la zhen par bsam
NK123(go)001:5150: gsungs te / pa'o // de nyid gsum pa sgra mtha' ni /
NK123(go)001:5151: sgra snang yal zhing mi dmigs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5152: yal ba'i gnas ni mtha' dang bral ba chos kyi dbyings so //
NK123(go)001:5153: ji ltar sgrar snang yal bar gtong na /
NK123(go)001:5154: sgrar snang gi gnas yig 'bru'i gzugs kyi rnam par snang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5155: sgra mngon du byed pa yi bzlas dang shub bzlas kyang btang /
NK123(go)001:5156: rang bzhin sgrar snang ba de yang yal te mi dmigs pa /
NK123(go)001:5157: zhi ba gdod nas ma skyes pa'i don la bsam gtan byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5158: rtsol ba dang bcas pa thams cad spangs ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:5159: de yang dang po ni las thams cad sgrub pa'i gzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:5160: gnyis pa ni zhi gnas skye ba'i rten dang /
NK123(go)001:5161: gsum pa ni lhag mthong gi ye shes 'char ba'i
NK123(go)001:5162: nyer len du gsungs pa ste zhib par kun mkhyen
NK123(go)001:5163: bla ma 'jal dpal dgyes pas stsal ba'i bsam gtan
NK123(go)001:5164: phyi ma'i rgyud don rnam bshad sogs las shes par
NK123(go)001:5165: bya la / 'dir ni snying po'i spyi don las gsungs pa ltar na /
NK123(go)001:5166: he ru ka gal po las /
NK123(go)001:5167: chos nyid sgra dang yig gzugs thugs //
NK123(go)001:5168: ye shes yongs rdzogs skur sgrub sgom //
NK123(go)001:5169: zhes pas kri y+aa don gyi lha drug gi sgo nas dam tshig pa bskyed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5170: de yang dang po stong pa 'i lha ni bdag
NK123(go)001:5171: dang lha'i de kho na nyid rnam par mi rtog
NK123(go)001:5172: pa chos kyi dbyings su dbyer med pa'i nges shes
NK123(go)001:5173: sam nga rgyal du bya ba snang ba med pa'i
NK123(go)001:5175: de'i ngang las lha gang yin gyi sngags kyi yi
NK123(go)001:5176: ge'i sgra gdangs tsam nam mkha' las grags par bsam
NK123(go)001:5177: pa sgra'i lha'o // gdangs de las sngags kyi yi
NK123(go)001:5178: ge'i gzugs kyi rnam par nam mkha' la snang ba
NK123(go)001:5179: pa sgra'i lha'o // yi ge'i lha'o // de nas
NK123(go)001:5180: gzugs kyi lha sku mngon du rdzogs pa'i phyir bdag
NK123(go)001:5181: gi de kho na nyid zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK123(go)001:5182: rnam par 'gyur ba'i steng du lha'i ngo bo sngags
NK123(go)001:5183: kyi yi ge nam mkhar gnas pa de dag 'dus
NK123(go)001:5184: te dag pa'i dngul chu gser gyi phye mar zhen
NK123(go)001:5186: bdag dang lha gnyis su med pa gcig tu gyur
NK123(go)001:5187: pa'i rang bzhin las 'od zer 'phro 'dus don gnyis
NK123(go)001:5188: byas nas lhag pa'i lha yi gzugs gang yin pa
NK123(go)001:5189: gsal zhing de nyid du nga rgyal bya ba gzugs
NK123(go)001:5191: de nas mtshog ma dang spyi gtsug sogs su lha
NK123(go)001:5192: gang yin pa'i rigs kyis phyag rgyas btab pas brten
NK123(go)001:5193: zhing byin gyis brlabs pa ni phyag rgya'i 5lha'o //
NK123(go)001:5194: de nas de lta bu'i lha de'i sku dang yan
NK123(go)001:5195: lag gi cha shas re re nas kyang gsal btab
NK123(go)001:5196: la / de'i mtshan ma la sems gzung zhing 'di
NK123(go)001:5197: dang 'di lta bu zhes brtag cing rgyun du zhen
NK123(go)001:5199: de ltar rang dam tshig par gsal ba'i mdun du
NK123(go)001:5200: yang dag pa'i smon lam gyi stobs las byung ba'i
NK123(go)001:5201: zhing khams pho brang gdan dang bcas pa gsal btab
NK123(go)001:5202: pa'i nang du ye shes kyi lha spyan drangs nas
NK123(go)001:5203: bzhugs su gsol ba la mchod bstod rgyun bshags sogs
NK123(go)001:5204: byas rjes / bo d+hi tsi rgyal ba'i rigs /
NK123(go)001:5205: pad ma'i snying po pad ma'i rigs ru rak+sha rdo rje'i rigs sogs lha so sor basngagasa pa'am /
NK123(go)001:5206: dung sogs las bye brag par basngagasa pa'i bgrang phreng
NK123(go)001:5207: cho ga bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa zhi bal
NK123(go)001:5208: mtheb mdzub sogs las so sor gsungs pa'am /
NK123(go)001:5209: mthun mong du mtheb srin gyis bzung nas /
NK123(go)001:5210: rigs so so'i thugs kar kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems zla ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK123(go)001:5211: de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags sgra gdangs dang bcas
NK123(go)001:5212: pa bkod nas gsang sngags kyi lha rnams mngon sum
NK123(go)001:5213: 'dra bar bltas pa yang dang yang du bsam pa'i
NK123(go)001:5214: dran pa rgyun mi chad pas yul la phyin ci
NK123(go)001:5215: log gi ngan rtog gsal ba'i sems rtse gcig pa
NK123(go)001:5216: bsgrubs te rigs sngags bzla ba sogs byas la sgrub
NK123(go)001:5217: bya'i lha dang rang nyid rje khol gyi tshul du
NK123(go)001:5218: bltas te dngos grub blang ste /
NK123(go)001:5220: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:5221: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du lta //
NK123(go)001:5223: rigs thams cad pa'i dngos grub len pa'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:5224: rje dpon rgyal po'i tshul bltas la //
NK123(go)001:5225: rang nyid dran gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK123(go)001:5226: sngags sgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK123(go)001:5227: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blangs //
NK123(go)001:5230: mtshan bcas lha dang yig 'bru la sogs par bsgom
NK123(go)001:5231: pa'i snang ba de'ang mi dmigs pa dag pa mtha'
NK123(go)001:5232: bzhi dang bral ba'i ngang du 'jog pas bden gnyis
NK123(go)001:5235: snang stong rim gyis brtan par byed //
NK123(go)001:5241: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK123(go)001:5242: shin tu skarma rgyal rnams la //
NK123(go)001:5243: gza' skar shis pas blang par bya //
NK123(go)001:5247: dkar gsum mngar gsum bza' ba dang //
NK123(go)001:5248: chang sha sgog btsong bsrung ba'o //
NK123(go)001:5249: gos 2ni ras kha tshar ma nyam pa gyon pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5251: lus dang ngag gi gtsang sbra dang //
NK123(go)001:5252: gsum pa yid kyi gtsang sbra dang //
NK123(go)001:5253: bzhi pa bden par smra ba dang //
NK123(go)001:5254: lnga pa phyi yi gtsang sbrar bzhed //
NK123(go)001:5256: yang na khrus kyi bya ba bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:5257: nyon mongs mngon gyur rags pa'i bag chags lta ba 1rtogs pas 'dag /
NK123(go)001:5258: bag la nyal gyi bag chags ting nge 'dzin 2bsgom pas 'dag /
NK123(go)001:5259: spyod lam ma nyams pa'i dri ma lha'i dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing ye shes pa gshegs pas 'dag /
NK123(go)001:5260: tha mal ba'i dri ma sngags kyi btab pa'i chus 'dag pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5261: dmigs rten ni mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bris sku
NK123(go)001:5262: sogs yi dam lha'i sku gzugs gtsang sbras bzhengs pa'o
NK123(go)001:5263: // bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba /
NK123(go)001:5265: gsang ba gsum ldan skyon bcu spangs te blangs //
NK123(go)001:5266: mtshams med lnga dang mi dge bcu spyod dang //
NK123(go)001:5267: sdig pa gang byas bzlas brjod byas pas 'byangs //
NK123(go)001:5268: zhes lha dang bdag dang 'phro 'du'i de nyid gsum
NK123(go)001:5269: dang ldan pa'i sgo nas sngags kyi skyon bcu spangs
NK123(go)001:5270: la ji ltar dbang gi dus su dam bcas pa'i
NK123(go)001:5271: grangs bzhin du bzla bar gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5273: bzlas brjod byed tshe mi nyul mi dal zhing //
NK123(go)001:5274: sgru cher mi dbyung ha cang chung ba'ang min //
NK123(go)001:5275: smra bzhin ma yin gzhan du g.yeng bzhin min //
NK123(go)001:5277: gug skyed klad kor tsheg tshang zur phyin la //
NK123(go)001:5278: gsang sngags dag cing shin tu cho gar bcas //
NK123(go)001:5281: gza' skar dus tshigs zas gos gtsang //
NK123(go)001:5282: brtul zhugs dka' thub spyad pa spyod //
NK123(go)001:5287: bzlas brjod dang zhes sogs gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:5289: bya rgyud rang lam gyis tshogs lam chen po'i bar
NK123(go)001:5290: bgrod nas sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhal mthong ste gnas
NK123(go)001:5291: skabs su 'dod pa'i lha dang skal pa mnyam pa'i
NK123(go)001:5292: rig 'dzin nam mkha' spyod grub nas /
NK123(go)001:5293: rten de la brten nas sngags kyi phyin drug gi dpyod spyad pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu /
NK123(go)001:5294: mi tshe bdun na sku rigs rnam par snang mdzad /
NK123(go)001:5295: gsungs rigs snang ba mtha' yas /
NK123(go)001:5296: thugs rigs rdo rje mi bskyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5297: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa sku gsum ye
NK123(go)001:5298: shes lnga yi bdag nyid can thob par 'dod de
NK123(go)001:5300: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas pa //
NK123(go)001:5304: rig 'dzin grub nas ring por 'tsho ba'i dbang du byas pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5305: bya rgyud rang lam gyis skal chen brgyad nas 'bras
NK123(go)001:5306: bu la sbyor bar bshad pa dang mi 'gal bar
NK123(go)001:5307: shes par bya'o // de yang spyir sngags rgyud phyi
NK123(go)001:5308: nang kun nas rig 'dzin gyi rnam bzhag mang du
NK123(go)001:5309: gsungs kyang bsdu na 'jig rten las 'das pa dang
NK123(go)001:5311: snga ma ni mthong lam nas gzung mi slob pa'i bar gyi bsdus pa mchog gi grub pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5312: rnying lugs kyi rig 'dzin bzhi lta bu yin la /
NK123(go)001:5313: 'dir bstan pa ni phyi ma'i khongs su gtogs pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5314: de la'ang thun mong gi dngos grub pa brgyad kyi
NK123(go)001:5315: nang mtshan ral gri dang ril bu la sogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:5316: rdzas la brten nas grub pa des lus de nyid
NK123(go)001:5317: kyis lha dang mi'i gnas su thog med du rgyu
NK123(go)001:5318: zhing nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5319: rig sngags kyis sems can la phan 'dogs shing tshar
NK123(go)001:5320: gcod pa sogs nus pa ni rdzas la brten pa'i
NK123(go)001:5321: rig 'dzin zhes thun mong gi grub pa chung ngu
NK123(go)001:5323: tshogs lam chen po des drod thob pa na spyod pa spyad de sgrub pas /
NK123(go)001:5324: lus 'dod khams kyi lha dang skal ba mnyam pa /
NK123(go)001:5325: rig sngags dang dngos grub sna tshogs byed pa tshe la dbang bar 'gyur ro //
NK123(go)001:5326: 'di ni lus kyi rig pa 'dzin pa zhes lus
NK123(go)001:5327: phra yang sogs yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa yin
NK123(go)001:5328: te / de la gzugs phra ba ni rtsi shing
NK123(go)001:5329: nags tshal la sogs pa snod kyi chos ji snyed
NK123(go)001:5330: sprul zhing bsdu par byed pas phra ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5331: sems can sna tshogs pa sprul bsdu byed pas yang pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5332: gnyis ka sprul bsdu byed pas yang dag par thob
NK123(go)001:5333: pa'am bdag por gyur pa dang yid kyis bsam pa
NK123(go)001:5334: tsam gyis gar yang phyin pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5335: 'byung po kun gyi mchod pa'i 'os su rab tu gsal ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5336: ji tsam 'dod pa thams cad 'byung bas 'dod dgur sgyur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5337: gang thob par 'dod pa de thob nus pas dga' mgur gnas pa ste de nyid brten pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5338: tshar gcod rjes 'dzin gyi dbang yod pa ni dbang du gyur pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5340: phra ba ni 'ja' lus su gyur pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5341: yang pa ni rdul rags pa'i khams med pas thogs
NK123(go)001:5342: bcas kyi lus min pas 'byung ba lnga la ci
NK123(go)001:5345: de ltar 'jig rten gyi dbang phyug yon tan brgyad dang ldan pas 'dod khams 'og ma 'dir /
NK123(go)001:5346: mi'i nang du 'ong yang yal pas mthong ba med la /
NK123(go)001:5347: sprul pa sna tshogs kyis don mdzad par gsungs /
NK123(go)001:5348: chen po gzugs kyi rig 'dzin zhes lus tshangs ris
NK123(go)001:5349: nas 'og min gyi bar gyi gzugs khams kyi lha
NK123(go)001:5350: dang skal pa mnyam zhing dbang phyug gi yon tan
NK123(go)001:5351: shin tu phra bas gong du bshad pa las khyad
NK123(go)001:5352: par 'phags pa can du gyur te /
NK123(go)001:5353: de'i lus 'dod khams su mi 'byung yang sprul pa sna tshogs pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5354: de ltar thun mong gi dngos grub la 'dun pa'i
NK123(go)001:5355: spyod pa des 'phrul du mchog gi dngos grub thob
NK123(go)001:5356: pa min kyang tshe la dbang thob pa yin pas
NK123(go)001:5357: rim gyi lus brten de la brten nas lam gong
NK123(go)001:5359: mkha' spyod yang spyir sngags kyi rig pa bzung ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5360: skye bdun gyi sha zos pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5361: las stobs kyi skye bas lus nam mkha' la 'gro ba tsam la'ang 'jug pa yin zhing /
NK123(go)001:5362: bye brag bskyed rim sogs la brten pa'i dngos grub mchog dang /
NK123(go)001:5363: chen po sogs dang 'brel ba'i mkha' spyod ces pa de la'ang gnyis kyi /
NK123(go)001:5365: phra mo'i gzugs dang reg yang ba /
NK123(go)001:5366: khyab dang yang dag thob pa nyid //
NK123(go)001:5367: rab tu gsal dang brtan pa nyid //
NK123(go)001:5368: dbang ldan 'dod dgur sgyur mtha' can //
NK123(go)001:5369: zhes pa'i yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5370: 'di'i yon tan brgyad ni gang smos 'jig rten pa'i
NK123(go)001:5371: dbang phyug brgyad dang ming tha dad pa tsam las
NK123(go)001:5372: don la gcig pa nyid do //
NK123(go)001:5373: 'di ni bskyed rim gyi 'bras bu mthar phyin /
NK123(go)001:5374: rdzogs rim gyi rtogs pa mngon du gyur pas rang
NK123(go)001:5375: snang rnam par dag pa'i zhing du lam gyi rtogs
NK123(go)001:5377: mkha' spyod chung ngu la rnam grangs shin tu mang yang rigs bsdu na gzugs khams bcu bdun /
NK123(go)001:5379: mi yul gyi nam mkha' spyod pa phyogs gcig tu nges pa med pa rnams so //
NK123(go)001:5380: de la mi yul gyi mkha' spyod ni /
NK123(go)001:5381: mi'i nang du gnas kyang yang dag pa'i gang zag
NK123(go)001:5382: re re tsam gyis mthong ba dang 'phrad pa srid
NK123(go)001:5383: kyi / gzhan phal pa rnams kyis mthong bar mi nus so //
NK123(go)001:5384: lha yul gyi mkha' spyod ni 'dod gzugs gang dang
NK123(go)001:5385: gang du spyod nus pa der de dang de'i longs
NK123(go)001:5387: de dang de'i tshe tshad dang mnyam pa'am lhag par spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5388: de dag la'ang lus ma spang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5389: spangs nas mkha' spyod du song ba gnyis yod cing /
NK123(go)001:5390: lus ma spang ba la'ang lam bsgom pa'i stobs kyis mkha' spyod thob pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5391: gnod sbyin mo dang grub pa ste rig 'dzin la
NK123(go)001:5392: sogs pa bsgrubs pa'i stobs kyis bgrod pa'i mkha' spyod
NK123(go)001:5393: du khrid pa gnyis las phyi ma ni 'phral snang
NK123(go)001:5394: snang tsam ste mtho dman gang du spyod cing yun
NK123(go)001:5395: ji tsam spyod kyang phugs kyi btsan sa zin pa
NK123(go)001:5396: med do // lam zab mo bsgoms pa'i stobs kyi bgrod pa'i mkha' spyod ni /
NK123(go)001:5397: lus spangs ma spang gang yin yang rung ste /
NK123(go)001:5398: lus 'ja' lus 'od kyi rang bzhin du dwangs shing /
NK123(go)001:5399: ting nge 'dzin mchog tu gyur pa la longs spyod
NK123(go)001:5400: pa'i phyir sa lam gyi dam pa gang du 'phel
NK123(go)001:5401: zhing bgrod pas btsan sa zin pa'i mkha' spyod ces
NK123(go)001:5402: bya'o // des na lus 'od du dwangs ba dang
NK123(go)001:5403: mi snang ba tsam ni spyir bcud len sogs rdzas
NK123(go)001:5404: la brten nas kyang bsgrub nus la /
NK123(go)001:5405: bskyed rim mthar phyin pa sogs kyi rgyu las byung
NK123(go)001:5406: ba'ang rags lus dwangs mar gyur pa tsam yin pas
NK123(go)001:5407: 'di la sngags kyi sku zhes brjod rung gi 'di
NK123(go)001:5408: nyid rdzogs rim zab mo'i thabs kyis ma zin na
NK123(go)001:5409: rdzogs rim gyi sku tsam yang ma yin na mthar
NK123(go)001:5410: lam rdzogs chen gyi 'ja' lus sogs su lta ci
NK123(go)001:5411: smos te / kha cig 'di la 'khrul nas /
NK123(go)001:5412: 'phags skor gyi sgyu lus sgrub tshul shes na rnying
NK123(go)001:5413: ma'i 'ja' lus zer ba bye ma'i 'chang bu ltar
NK123(go)001:5414: 'jig zer ba ni rang mtshangs ngoms pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5415: sngags kyi rgyud kyi skabs 'dir ni sngags kyi lhan cig byas rkyen byas pa'i mthus /
NK123(go)001:5416: rags lus 'di nyid dwangs mar gnas gyur pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:5417: dper na gser 'gyur gyi rtsis lcags nyid gser du bsgyur ba'am /
NK123(go)001:5418: bcud len gyi mthus rgas lus gzhon nur bsgyur ba lta bu yin la /
NK123(go)001:5419: der ma zad gsang 'dus kyi rim lnga'i phra ba'i
NK123(go)001:5420: rlung sems las sgyu ma'i sku grub tshul de yang
NK123(go)001:5421: / rnam shes dang ye shes las rlung dang ye
NK123(go)001:5422: rlung byed pa 'dres pa las sgrub pa yin pas
NK123(go)001:5423: / / 'di yang ma dag pa dag pa dang
NK123(go)001:5424: slob pa mi slob pa'i zung 'jug gi skur rim
NK123(go)001:5425: bzhin gnas 'gyur dgos pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:5426: rdzogs chen gyi snang bzhi mthar phyin tshe /
NK123(go)001:5427: gdos bcas rags pa'i lus 'di 'od du yal te /
NK123(go)001:5428: rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal shin tu rnam dag
NK123(go)001:5429: gi sku mi slob pa'i zung 'jug nyid mngon du
NK123(go)001:5431: des na 'di dag gi khyad par phyed pa'ang gal
NK123(go)001:5432: che bas zhal byung du smos pa ste zhib par
NK123(go)001:5434: gnyis pa gang zag 'bring gi 'bring la dgongs te gsungs pa u pa ya yi theg pa ni /
NK123(go)001:5439: spyod pa bya ba ltar spyod pas dngos grub bsgrub pa'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5441: gnyis ka la brten pas grub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5445: phyi lus ngag gi bya ba dang nang rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:5446: gnyis ka cha mnyam du spyod pa'i phyir gnyis ka'i
NK123(go)001:5449: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:5450: lta ba yo ga lta ba la //
NK123(go)001:5451: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5452: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK123(go)001:5455: 'jug sgo'i dbang ni dkyil 'khor du bcug nas chu
NK123(go)001:5456: dang cod pan gyi steng du spyod rgyud kyi dgongs
NK123(go)001:5459: me long thur ma chos 'chad kyi rjes gnang sogs te /
NK123(go)001:5461: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK123(go)001:5462: spyod pa'i rgyud du rab tu gsal //
NK123(go)001:5464: de yang rnam snang mngon byang la dper mtshon na /
NK123(go)001:5465: bum dbang dang pos ngan song gi dri ma sbyong /
NK123(go)001:5466: gnyis pas 'khor ba'i sa bon bkru /
NK123(go)001:5467: gsum pas sa dang po nas bcu pa'i bar gyi tshogs gnyis kyi sa bon bkrun /
NK123(go)001:5468: bzhi pas rgyal tshab kyi sa bon bzhag /
NK123(go)001:5469: dbu rgyan gyis sku mtshan dpe /
NK123(go)001:5471: rdo rjes thugs ji lta ji snyed /
NK123(go)001:5472: ming dbang gis mtshan khams gsum khyab pa'i sa bon bzhig cing /
NK123(go)001:5473: mig thur me long chos bshad rjes gnang sogs kyis gzhan don phrin las rjes su gnang ba ste /
NK123(go)001:5474: rigs dbang lnga rgyud sde gong ma dang ming 'dra yang don tha dad pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:5475: bya ba'i 'jug sgo dang tshul khrims dang /
NK123(go)001:5476: spyod pa rnams bya rgyud dang /
NK123(go)001:5478: sgom pa yo ga dang shas cher mthun pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5480: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK123(go)001:5481: spyod pa bya ba'i rjes mthun yang //
NK123(go)001:5482: lta ba rnal 'byor rjes mthun phyir //
NK123(go)001:5483: rig dang lta bas khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:5486: gnyis ka'i rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK123(go)001:5487: lta spyod gang 'og rjes su mthun //
NK123(go)001:5489: 'on kyang lta ba chos kyi dbyings mtha' thams cad
NK123(go)001:5490: dang bral ba dang gnyis su med pa rig pa'i
NK123(go)001:5491: ye shes kyi byin rlabs rnam snang sogs rigs bzhir
NK123(go)001:5492: lta ba dang / sgom pa'i lha la /
NK123(go)001:5494: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK123(go)001:5495: de bzhin gzhi la gzhi gyur nyid //
NK123(go)001:5496: shin tu bsdoms pa'i yid las ni //
NK123(go)001:5500: gzugs kyi lha gsum du gsungs shing de re re la'ang gnyis gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:5501: yi ge la byang chub sems kyi lha dang sgra'i lha gnyis /
NK123(go)001:5502: phyag rgya la 'khor lo sogs gzugs dbyibs su byas
NK123(go)001:5503: pa dang chos 'byung sngo skyas mtshon pa'i stong pa
NK123(go)001:5504: nyid gzugs dbyibs med pa gnyis /
NK123(go)001:5505: gzugs la yongs su dag pa mtshan ma'i spros pa
NK123(go)001:5506: mtha' dag nye bar zhi bar rtogs pa'i ngo bo
NK123(go)001:5507: nyid bde gshegs snyiing po so so rang rig gis
NK123(go)001:5509: ma dag pa rnam par rtog pas kha dog zhal phyag sogs gzugs su sgom pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5510: mdor na yi ge phyag rgya sku gzugs gsum po
NK123(go)001:5511: sgra dang mtshan ma dang gzugs su snang ba ni
NK123(go)001:5513: byang chub sems kyi yi ge ste sgra med pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5514: mtshan ma'i gzugs med pa'i phyag rgya /
NK123(go)001:5515: yongs su dag pa'i lha mtshan ma med pa mi
NK123(go)001:5516: rtog pa'i ngo bo gsum ni mtshan med yin pas
NK123(go)001:5518: de ltar shes par byas nas mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor la /
NK123(go)001:5519: bdag dang gnas dang rnal 'byor srung ba gsum sngon
NK123(go)001:5520: du 'gro bas yi ge dang po don dam byang
NK123(go)001:5521: chub sems stong pa nyid kyi ngang las kun rdzob
NK123(go)001:5522: tu de'i snang cha zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du sgom
NK123(go)001:5523: pa / yi ge gnyis pa de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra grags par bsam pa /
NK123(go)001:5524: gzhi dang po de thams cad yongs su dag pa'i
NK123(go)001:5525: rang bzhin bdag nyid lhar bsgom la sngags rgya sogs
NK123(go)001:5527: gzhi gnyis pa me long la gzugs brnyan gyi tshul
NK123(go)001:5528: du de las shar ba'i gzugs brnyan mdun du bsgom
NK123(go)001:5529: la / de'i thugs kar zla ba la sngags bltas
NK123(go)001:5530: te srog bsdam zhing rtse gcig pa'i sbyor bas gsal
NK123(go)001:5531: snang thob kyi bar du slob cing yid bzlas byed
NK123(go)001:5532: la / pa sogs dang / mtshan med kyi rnal
NK123(go)001:5533: 'byor phung po la sogs pa'i chos thams cad la
NK123(go)001:5534: mtha' bzhis dpyad pas skye med du rtogs pa 'jug
NK123(go)001:5535: la / pa sogs dang / pa'i sems / de
NK123(go)001:5536: nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngo bor mngon sum
NK123(go)001:5537: du rtogs pa gnas pa'i sems /
NK123(go)001:5538: de ltar ma rtogs te sdug bsngal ba'i sems can
NK123(go)001:5539: rnams la snying rje chen po rjes su 'jug pa
NK123(go)001:5541: ngo bo byang chub kyi sems de nyid rnam pa 'jug gnas ldang ba'i sems gsum dang sbyar te /
NK123(go)001:5542: rnal 'byor du bya ba sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:5543: tshul khrims yang thun mong pa mi dge bcu'i steng du thun min dam pa'i chos spong ba /
NK123(go)001:5544: byang chub kyi sems spong ba /
NK123(go)001:5545: ser snas chos nor mi sbyin pa /
NK123(go)001:5546: sems can la gnod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5548: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi gsungs pas mtshon /
NK123(go)001:5549: khyad par cung zad snang ngo //
NK123(go)001:5551: phyi nang gi rdzas la brten nas gnas skabs su
NK123(go)001:5552: ral gri la sogs pa'i rig 'dzin grub cing rten
NK123(go)001:5553: de la brten nas sngags kyi spyod pa spyad pas
NK123(go)001:5555: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:5557: sngar gyi rigs gsum gyi steng du rin po che'i
NK123(go)001:5558: rigs bsnan nas las kyi rigs rin po che'i rigs
NK123(go)001:5560: 'gro ba'i bsam pa rdzogs par byed pa'i sgo nas rin po che'i rigs yin la /
NK123(go)001:5561: las su bya ba'i sgo nas las kyi rigs yin
NK123(go)001:5562: pa'i phyir las dang byed pa po gnyis gcig tu
NK123(go)001:5565: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang sar gnas //
NK123(go)001:5567: gnyis su med la mi tshe lngas sgrib grol //
NK123(go)001:5569: 'di'i mi tshe'ang gang smos bzhin te /
NK123(go)001:5570: gzhan du dbang brtul ring mtha' skal ba brgyad dang /
NK123(go)001:5571: rnon po skal chen gsum sogs gsungs pa dang mi 'gal lo //
NK123(go)001:5572: gsum pa dbang po 'bring gi rab la dgongs pa yo ga'i theg pa la gsum /
NK123(go)001:5577: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:5578: ye shes kyi byin brlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings
NK123(go)001:5579: kyi lhar brtags te rtog pa bzang ngan blang dor
NK123(go)001:5580: gyi rtsol bas 'bras bu bsgrub par 'dod pa ste
NK123(go)001:5582: lhun grub mnyam pas ma mthong bas //
NK123(go)001:5583: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK123(go)001:5584: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul pa //
NK123(go)001:5588: yo ga'i sgra las nang gi rnal 'byor gtso bor byed pa'am /
NK123(go)001:5589: ston pas na rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ces bya ste /
NK123(go)001:5591: rnal 'byor gtso bor byas pas 'grub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5595: rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang drug bskur te /
NK123(go)001:5597: phyir mi ldog pa bum pa'i dbang //
NK123(go)001:5598: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK123(go)001:5599: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK123(go)001:5601: de la rig dbang ngam slob ma'i dbang lnga ni /
NK123(go)001:5602: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs shing dam tshig dang sdom pa bzung /
NK123(go)001:5603: ye shes pa dbab cing me tog dor bas rang gi lha nges par byas nas /
NK123(go)001:5604: las bum gyi khrus sngon du 'gro bas lha bum rnams kyi dbang dang /
NK123(go)001:5605: rigs so so'i cod pan dang /
NK123(go)001:5607: des yu ba byas pa'i dril bu dang /
NK123(go)001:5608: rang rigs kyi ming gdags pas dbang bskur ba ste de lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:5609: slob dpon gyi dbang drug ni /
NK123(go)001:5610: phyir mi ldog pa'i dbang dam tshig gsum gzung ba /
NK123(go)001:5616: bsdam pas dbang bskur bcu gcig go //
NK123(go)001:5617: 'dir gsang ba'i dbang yang bla med dang mi mtshungs te /
NK123(go)001:5618: dkyil 'khor du gsang ba'i 'jug pa zhugs shing mthong ba la dkyil 'khor dang /
NK123(go)001:5619: lha'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK123(go)001:5620: dkyil 'khor gyi de nyid bcu dang las kyi rim
NK123(go)001:5621: par bstan par bya ba la gsang dbang du btags
NK123(go)001:5622: pa dang / rnal 'byor rgyud kha cig tu shes
NK123(go)001:5623: rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba zhes gsung pa'ang
NK123(go)001:5624: sngags sbyin nas phyag rgya bzhi la slob tu zhugs
NK123(go)001:5625: pa la der btags pas ming tsam kho nar zad
NK123(go)001:5626: pa dang / do // bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK123(go)001:5627: mtshan bcas dang mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:5629: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pa //
NK123(go)001:5630: mtshan ma yod med sgor zhugs nas //
NK123(go)001:5634: chos thams cad spros pa'i mtshan ma dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od gsal ba'i stong pa nyid de /
NK123(go)001:5636: chos rnams rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK123(go)001:5637: ngo bo nyid kyis gdod nas dag /
NK123(go)001:5639: kun rdzob la gnyis kyi log pa'i kun rdzob sngar dang 'dra /
NK123(go)001:5641: cir snang thams cad chos nyid rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK123(go)001:5642: kyi byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK123(go)001:5643: snang ba'i phyir / skye bos snang ba rang rgyud du brtags pa 'di med par 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:5646: yo ga'i theg par gnas 'dod pas //
NK123(go)001:5647: 'og min rdo rje dbyings su lta //
NK123(go)001:5649: yo ga don dam rnam dag pa'i //
NK123(go)001:5650: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su //
NK123(go)001:5651: rtogs pa'i byin rlabs lhar snang ba //
NK123(go)001:5652: de phyir skye bo lhar snang 'khrul //
NK123(go)001:5655: rang gi dngos mthong mtshan ma gnyis //
NK123(go)001:5656: dbyer med dbyings dang ye shes las //
NK123(go)001:5657: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi lha //
NK123(go)001:5658: shar ltar grol ba'i tshul du lta //
NK123(go)001:5660: de yang don dam mnyam pa nyid la bya rgyud
NK123(go)001:5661: pa las nges pa je bzang du song ba'i gnad
NK123(go)001:5662: kyi bdag dang lha yang mnyam pa spun grogs kyi
NK123(go)001:5663: tshul te / rten 'brel gyi snang cha ma 'gag
NK123(go)001:5664: pas ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du gnas skabs dang
NK123(go)001:5665: mthar thug gi don lha la brten nas grub pa
NK123(go)001:5666: tshul te / dang / bden gnyis zab mo'i tshul
NK123(go)001:5667: la yid ches kyi lta ba dang ldan pa ste
NK123(go)001:5668: tshul te / dang / / 'dir bshad pa ni
NK123(go)001:5669: spyod rgyud dang thun mong pa yo ga tsam po
NK123(go)001:5671: yo ga khyad par ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK123(go)001:5672: mnyam nyid kyi lta ba bshad ma thag pa las
NK123(go)001:5673: kyang khyad par du 'phags pa'i dbang gis bdag dang
NK123(go)001:5674: lha don la mnyam par mthong ba'i nges shes kyis
NK123(go)001:5675: kun rdzob tu yang chu la chu bzhag pa bzhin
NK123(go)001:5676: mnyam par byas te bsgoms na /
NK123(go)001:5677: chos thams cad rang sems kyi snang ba tsam yin
NK123(go)001:5678: pas ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang bsgyur na ci ltar
NK123(go)001:5679: dmigs pa'i lhar mngon du grub pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:5680: lha'i sku gsung thugs phrin las kyi bdag nyid phyag
NK123(go)001:5681: rgya bzhi yi ngo bor 'bad pas bsgrub pas de
NK123(go)001:5682: yi ngo bor 'grub pa'i nges pa khyad par can
NK123(go)001:5683: gyi lta ba ste snga ma ni sgyu 'phrul zur
NK123(go)001:5685: phyi ma ni kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos bzhed do //
NK123(go)001:5687: rtse mor gsungs pa'i rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig /
NK123(go)001:5688: byang chub kyi sems dang por bskyed cing /
NK123(go)001:5689: de'i rjes su tshul khrims gsum gyi bslab pa la nan tan du bya dang /
NK123(go)001:5691: snang mdzad kyi dam tshig gsum /
NK123(go)001:5692: mi bskyod rin 'byung gnyis la bzhi bzhi /
NK123(go)001:5694: don grub kyi gnyis te bcu bzhir gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5696: sngar smos pa'i bya rgyud kyi dam tshig gcig po'i steng du /
NK123(go)001:5697: lung gcig gi chu la mi btung ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5698: nyams dang kha mi bsre ba gnyis bsnan pas bcu gsum du bshad de /
NK123(go)001:5699: de dag zhib par theg dgu las /
NK123(go)001:5700: tshul khrims rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig /
NK123(go)001:5701: byang chub sems mchog dang por bskyed //
NK123(go)001:5702: de rjes tshul khrims gsum la bslab //
NK123(go)001:5703: bye brag snang mdzad dam tshig gsum //
NK123(go)001:5705: mi bskyod rdo dril phyag rgya dang //
NK123(go)001:5706: slob bzung bzhi rin chen la //
NK123(go)001:5707: nor chos mi 'jigs byams sbyin bzhi //
NK123(go)001:5708: pad mar theg pa kun 'dzin gcig /
NK123(go)001:5709: las rigs kun 'dzin mchod brtson gnyis //
NK123(go)001:5710: gzhan yang bya rgyud dam tshig la //
NK123(go)001:5711: lung gcig chu la mi btung zhing //
NK123(go)001:5712: nyams dang kha mi bsre ba dang //
NK123(go)001:5713: yi dam lha dang slob dpon mched //
NK123(go)001:5714: rang sems ma khrel sogs kyang bshad //
NK123(go)001:5716: sgom pa la mtshan bcas mtshan med gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:5717: dang po 'jug tu rung ba'i gang zag theg chen
NK123(go)001:5718: gyi 'jug sgo smon 'jug gi byang chub kyi sems
NK123(go)001:5719: gnyis tshul bzhin du bskyed pa /
NK123(go)001:5720: rgyud la yid ches pas the tshom dang yid gnyis med pa /
NK123(go)001:5721: dam tshig rnams gzhung bzhin du bsrung nus pas bka' bzhin du sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:5722: lam dang lam gyi ston pa lha dang bla ma sogs la dad pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5723: yon tan bzhi dang ldan pa des /
NK123(go)001:5724: thob bya'i 'bras bu sgrib pa thams cad dang bral
NK123(go)001:5725: zhing yon tan mthar thug pa'i sangs rgyas rnam par
NK123(go)001:5726: snang mdzad kyi longs sku chen po sku bzhi'i bdag
NK123(go)001:5727: nyid can de la dmigs nas /
NK123(go)001:5728: de thob byed nyer len gyi rgyu thog ma dang
NK123(go)001:5729: tha ma med pa'i byang chub kyi sems kun tu
NK123(go)001:5730: bzang po / rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing so so rang gis rig pa'i mtshan nyid can /
NK123(go)001:5731: lha dang sngags dang phyag rgya thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pa /
NK123(go)001:5732: rang sems gdod ma nas rnam par dag pa'i de
NK123(go)001:5733: kho na nyid rgyu'i rgyud ces bya ba de nyid
NK123(go)001:5734: yin la / rgyu de las 'bras bu mngon du
NK123(go)001:5735: bya ba'i thabs su phyag rgya bzhi dang 'brel bar
NK123(go)001:5736: lha'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa 'khor dang bcas pa ste
NK123(go)001:5737: yin la / / mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul
NK123(go)001:5738: bzhi'i sgo nas lha dang lha mo'i rnal 'byor phyag
NK123(go)001:5739: rgya bzhi ldan du sgom pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5741: phyi yo byad la gtso bor mi 'dzin par don
NK123(go)001:5742: dam par skye 'gag med pa'i lha dang lha mo
NK123(go)001:5743: dang / de dang 'dra ba'i rgyud yongs su dag
NK123(go)001:5744: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku
NK123(go)001:5745: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:5748: de la mngon byang lnga ni /
NK123(go)001:5749: srid pa bskyed pa'i rim pa kun nas nyon mongs
NK123(go)001:5750: pa'i phyogs dang bstun nas sgom pa rgyud sde 'og
NK123(go)001:5751: ma gsum gyi lugs ma yin kyang yar bltas rnam
NK123(go)001:5752: byang gi 'dra 'bag dang bstun nas srid pa tha
NK123(go)001:5753: ma'i byang sems 'tshang rgya ba'i tshul ltar sgrub la
NK123(go)001:5754: / skyabs sems sogs sngon du song nas stong pa'i ngang las /
NK123(go)001:5755: zhing dang gnas phun sum tshogs pa sgrub pa'i rgyud gdan pad ma las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK123(go)001:5756: chos phun tshogs 'byung ba'i rgyu gsung yig 'bru las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK123(go)001:5757: dus phun tshogs rtag pa bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK123(go)001:5758: gnas pa'i rgyu thugs phyag mtshan las mngon par byang
NK123(go)001:5759: chub pa / 'khor dang ston pa phun sum tshogs
NK123(go)001:5760: pa'i rgyu sku yongs rdzogs dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK123(go)001:5761: dang bcas pa la mngon par byang chub pa /
NK123(go)001:5762: sku yi ngo bo'am ye shes phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:5763: rgyu lha ye shes sems dpa' las mngon par byang
NK123(go)001:5764: chub pa ste mngon byang lnga'i tshul gyis bskyed cing
NK123(go)001:5765: / sku yi rnam pa phyag rgya chen po /
NK123(go)001:5766: gsung gi rnam pa chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK123(go)001:5767: thugs kyi rnam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK123(go)001:5768: 'od zer 'phro 'du la sogs pas las sgrub pa
NK123(go)001:5769: las kyi phyag rgya dang bzhis rang gi sgo gsum
NK123(go)001:5770: byed las dang bcas pa lha'i sku gsung thugs phrin
NK123(go)001:5771: las kyi ngo bor rgyas btab ste sgom pa'i rim
NK123(go)001:5772: pa la'ang dbang rnon rnams smos ma thag pa ltar
NK123(go)001:5773: sngon byung ston pa sangs rgyas nas dkyil 'khor sprul
NK123(go)001:5774: bshad dang 'phrin las mngon par 'du mdzad tshul lngar
NK123(go)001:5776: gtso bskyed dang po'i sbyor ba /
NK123(go)001:5777: dkyil 'khor rgyal mchog rdzogs par bskyed pa /
NK123(go)001:5778: las rgyal mchog ye shes gzhug pa sogs las rim
NK123(go)001:5779: gzhan te ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas nyams
NK123(go)001:5781: dbang brtul rnams bdag nyid rang rigs kyi lha dam tshig par sgom pa rnal 'byor /
NK123(go)001:5782: de la ye shes pa bcug ste ro gcig tu bya ba rjes su rnal 'byor /
NK123(go)001:5783: brtan g.yo thams cad rang rigs kyi lha'i rnal 'byor du bya ba thams cad rnal 'byor /
NK123(go)001:5784: de gsum sngon du song ba las sems rtse gcig
NK123(go)001:5785: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mngon du gyur pa shin tu
NK123(go)001:5786: rnal 'byor te rnal 'byor bzhi la brten nas nyams
NK123(go)001:5788: de gnyis gang ltar rung gtso bor ting nge 'dzin la brten nas 'das pa'i dngos grub dang /
NK123(go)001:5789: bzlas brjod la brten nas dngos grub gnyis ka sgrub pa'i tshul sogs zhib par gzhan du shes la /
NK123(go)001:5790: 'dir zur lugs snying po'i spyi don ltar na /
NK123(go)001:5791: he ru ka gal po las /
NK123(go)001:5792: mi rtog zla ba gsung rdo rje //
NK123(go)001:5793: spro bsdus bsgom pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK123(go)001:5794: ting 'dzin byin rlob dbang bskur mchod //
NK123(go)001:5795: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK123(go)001:5796: bsgom zhing mchod pa bya ba yang //
NK123(go)001:5797: bsod nams ldan phyir bya ba yin //
NK123(go)001:5804: sku yongs su rdzogs pa las byang chub pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5805: de'i don yang gal po'i mchan 'grel las /
NK123(go)001:5806: sgom pa ni mngon byang lnga cho 'phrul bzhi bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5807: dang po rnam par mi rtog par sgom pa ni gzugs sku la mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5808: zla ba tshes gcig pa lta bu'i rang sems rig pa mngon par byang chub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5809: zla ba nya ba lta bu sems bskyed mngon par
NK123(go)001:5810: byang chub pa gnyis ni zla ba la mngon par
NK123(go)001:5811: byang chub pa'o // zla ba'i steng du rdo rje
NK123(go)001:5812: rtse lnga pa sgom pa ni chos sku la mngon
NK123(go)001:5814: 'od zer spro bsdus sgrib sbyong dngos sgrub bskul ba ni brtan par bya ba'i mngon byang ngo //
NK123(go)001:5815: de ltar skur gyur pa ni phyag rgya la mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5817: gu ru rin po ches mdzad pa'i dgongs 'dus rtsa rgyud pad sdang brtsegs pa'i 'grel pa las /
NK123(go)001:5818: mngon par byang chub pa lnga yi sgo nas 'jug pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5819: de yang rtsa ba gzhi shes kyi ngo bo stong pa nyid las byang chub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5820: de'i ngang las nyi zla la sogs pa gsal ba ni gdan nyi zla las byang chub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5821: gdan gyi steng du lha yi sa bon gsal ba ni gsung yig 'bru las byang chub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5822: sa bon yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje'am pad+ma
NK123(go)001:5823: sogs sgom pa ni thugs phyag mtshan las byang chub
NK123(go)001:5824: pa dang / phyag mtshan de nyid spro bsdu las
NK123(go)001:5825: byung ba'i lha rang gi ngo bo zhal phyag sku
NK123(go)001:5826: mdog phyag mtshan rgyan cha lugs yongs rdzogs su gsal
NK123(go)001:5827: ba gzugs snang las byang chub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5834: de la ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul ni /
NK123(go)001:5839: byang du don grub rnams la rang rang gi rigs
NK123(go)001:5840: kyi sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba ste gtso 'khor
NK123(go)001:5842: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK123(go)001:5843: bsgom pa'i lha de dag rang rang gi rigs kyi byin can du byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK123(go)001:5845: rang rigs kyi dbang gang yin gyis sku dang ye
NK123(go)001:5846: shes dang ye shes dang gzung dang ting nge 'dzin
NK123(go)001:5847: dang ldan par dbang bskur ba'o //
NK123(go)001:5849: de dag la phyag dang mchod pa bstod pa bya ba rnams so //
NK123(go)001:5851: lus ngag yid dang bya ba bzhi la rim par sku phyag mtshan /
NK123(go)001:5854: phrin las las rgya rnams kyi rgyas btab nas bsgom pa'i phyir phyag rgya ste /
NK123(go)001:5855: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa'i 'khrul ba glo bur ba gsal nas /
NK123(go)001:5856: rang bzhin me long lta bu'i ye shes de mngon
NK123(go)001:5857: du bya ba la sku phyag rgya chen po'i rnal
NK123(go)001:5858: 'byor / nyon yid kyi glo bur 'khrul ba bsal
NK123(go)001:5859: nas rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes de
NK123(go)001:5860: mngon du bya ba la thugs dam tshig gi phyag
NK123(go)001:5861: 'byor / rgya'i rnal 'byor / yid kyi shes pa'i
NK123(go)001:5862: glo bur gyi 'khrul pa bsal nas rang bzhin so
NK123(go)001:5863: sor rtogs pa'i ye shes de mngon du bya ba
NK123(go)001:5864: gsung chos kyi phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor /
NK123(go)001:5865: sgo lnga'i rnam shes 'khrul pa bsal nas rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:5866: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes de mngon du bya
NK123(go)001:5867: ba phrin las las kyi phyag rgya'i rnal 'byor /
NK123(go)001:5868: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes ni de thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5869: mdor na 'khrul ba sbyong byed kyi thabs phyag rgya
NK123(go)001:5870: bzhi dang 'brel ba'i lha'i rnal 'byor sgom pa 'khor
NK123(go)001:5872: de yang dam tshig pa bskyed la /
NK123(go)001:5873: ye shes pa spyan drangs nas spun nam grogs kyi tshul du bzang ngan med par bltas te /
NK123(go)001:5874: mchod bstod bzlas pa sogs bya'o //
NK123(go)001:5875: de ltar yang rang shar las /
NK123(go)001:5876: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK123(go)001:5877: spun nam grogs po'i tshul du 'bod //
NK123(go)001:5879: 'di ni yo ga tsam po pa'i lugs yin la /
NK123(go)001:5880: yo ga khyad par ba'i dbang du byas na bdag
NK123(go)001:5881: nyid lha yi rnal 'byor du bsgoms pa la ye
NK123(go)001:5882: shes pa dgug bstim gnyis med du byas rjes bzlas
NK123(go)001:5884: skabs der dngos grub nod par bya ba dang /
NK123(go)001:5885: mthar gshegs su gsol ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:5887: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang
NK123(go)001:5888: de'i byin rlabs ltar snang ye shes kyi snang cha
NK123(go)001:5889: gnyis su med pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa
NK123(go)001:5891: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings dang /
NK123(go)001:5892: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang /
NK123(go)001:5895: gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i kun spyod kyi grogs dang ldan
NK123(go)001:5896: pa'i sgo nas gtso bor lha'i rnal 'byor la gnas
NK123(go)001:5897: pas rang gzhan gyi don spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:5899: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK123(go)001:5900: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK123(go)001:5901: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK123(go)001:5902: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa mchog /
NK123(go)001:5905: 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub mkha' spyod kyi rig 'dzin dang /
NK123(go)001:5906: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub mi tshe gsum
NK123(go)001:5907: na sngar gyi rigs bzhi'i steng du las rigs bsnan
NK123(go)001:5908: pas rigs lnga stug po bkod pa'i sa la sku
NK123(go)001:5909: gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid du 'tshang rgya bar
NK123(go)001:5911: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK123(go)001:5912: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK123(go)001:5915: gzung 'dzin bag chags lnga byang nas //
NK123(go)001:5916: ye shes lnga yi rtsal dag gis //
NK123(go)001:5917: stug po bkod pa'i sa non nas //
NK123(go)001:5919: skye med chos sku dag pa ni //
NK123(go)001:5920: skye med sgo nas 'gro don mdzad //
NK123(go)001:5921: phyag rgya rigs lnga longs spyod rdzogs //
NK123(go)001:5922: byang chub sems pa'i 'gro don rdzogs //
NK123(go)001:5923: sprul pa bye ba sa ya yis //
NK123(go)001:5924: rigs drug ngo bo cir yang ston //
NK123(go)001:5926: de yang spyir yang yo ga'i rgyud gzhung gzhan rnams
NK123(go)001:5927: nas dbang po rno brtul gyi khyad par gyis lam
NK123(go)001:5928: bgrod pa'i yun la mi tshe mang nyung gi khyad
NK123(go)001:5929: par 'ga' zhig gsungs kyang don la snga ma rnams
NK123(go)001:5930: la ltos nas dus shin tu myur bar bgrod pa
NK123(go)001:5931: yin la / de'ang dbang po rno brtul gang yin
NK123(go)001:5932: kyang sa bcu par 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur
NK123(go)001:5933: ba thob nas bsam gtan bzhi pa'i rab matha'i ting
NK123(go)001:5934: yin la / nge 'dzin sgrub / de thob pa'i
NK123(go)001:5935: rten de la yid kyi rang bzhin gyi lus can
NK123(go)001:5936: yin la / nge 'dzin sgrub / / srid pa tha ma'i byang chub sems dpa'/
NK123(go)001:5937: bya ba thams cad bzhed pa tsam la rags las
NK123(go)001:5938: par 'grub pas byang sems don thams cad grub pa
NK123(go)001:5939: zhes bya'o // don grub kyi rten des 'og min
NK123(go)001:5940: stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams su byang chub kyi
NK123(go)001:5942: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK123(go)001:5943: pa mngon du byas pa'i mthu las mi g.yo ba'i
NK123(go)001:5945: de'i tshe na phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis ting nge 'dzin las bslangs te /
NK123(go)001:5946: mngon par byang chub pa lnga'i gdams ngag bstan /
NK123(go)001:5947: des de bsgoms pas ye shes lnga'i ngo bor mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur ro //
NK123(go)001:5948: sangs rgyas de yang sku gsum gyi mtshan nyid can te /
NK123(go)001:5949: ye shes bzhi chos dbyings ye shes kyi ngo bor ro gcig pa chos sku /
NK123(go)001:5950: 'og min chen por nges pa lnga ldan gyi skur snang ba longs sku chen po /
NK123(go)001:5951: ri rab kyi rtse la sogs par 'khor los bsgyur
NK123(go)001:5952: ba'i cha byad kyis dkyil 'khor sprul bshad mdzad pa
NK123(go)001:5954: dga' ldan gyi gnas na gnas par ston pa la
NK123(go)001:5955: sogs mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston pa sprul
NK123(go)001:5956: pa'i sku'o // de ltar shin tu 'gor yang bskal
NK123(go)001:5957: pa chung ngu gcig la mthar thug gi sangs rgyas
NK123(go)001:5959: zhes bstan bcos chen po shes bya kun khyab las gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:5960: des dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa kri y+aa
NK123(go)001:5961: u pa yo ga gsum gyi theg pa mdo tsam
NK123(go)001:5962: bshad zin to // gnyis pa nang ba thabs kyi rgyud dam dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ni /
NK123(go)001:5963: sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi rol par snang
NK123(go)001:5964: bas dngos grub gzhan nas mi 'tshol bar rang byung
NK123(go)001:5965: gi ye shes su rtogs pas sngags nang pa'am /
NK123(go)001:5966: snod bcud thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK123(go)001:5967: 'khor bden gnyis dbyer med blo'i spyod yul dang bral
NK123(go)001:5968: bar gtan la phab pas chos thams cad mnyam pa
NK123(go)001:5969: nyid du dbang bsgyur ba'i thabs la mkhas pas na
NK123(go)001:5970: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa zhes gsungs te gang
NK123(go)001:5971: zag dbang po rab gsum gyi ngo skal du gsungs
NK123(go)001:5972: pa yin no // de yang 'di ltar rgyu pha rol du phyin pa'i theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5973: der ma zad sngags phyi pa dang bcas pa ni ring ba'i lam yin la /
NK123(go)001:5974: sngags bla med ni nye lam dang 'bras bu'i theg
NK123(go)001:5975: pa mtshan nyid pa yin zhing 'di las gang du
NK123(go)001:5976: gyur pa'i theg pa med de /
NK123(go)001:5977: theg pa gzhan rnams gdul bya'i bsam pa la bltos nas drang ba'i thabs su bstan la /
NK123(go)001:5978: 'dir ni sangs rgyas kyi ye shes kyis gzigs pa
NK123(go)001:5979: ji lta ba bzhin du nges pa'i don mthar thug
NK123(go)001:5980: pa bstan pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:5981: des na theg pa 'og ma kun las bla na
NK123(go)001:5982: med pa'i theg pa 'di nyid thabs dang shes rab
NK123(go)001:5983: kyi sgo nas cher 'phags pa'i tshul de dag 'di'i
NK123(go)001:5984: mtshan gyi rnam grangs lngas bstan pa'i don bzhin du
NK123(go)001:5987: gsang sngags kyi theg pa dang /
NK123(go)001:5991: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa'i theg pa zhes ming lngas bstan to //
NK123(go)001:5992: de la gsang ba zhes pa rgyal ba rnams kyi
NK123(go)001:5993: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor zab mo gang zhig
NK123(go)001:5994: ye nas chos kun gyi rang bzhin du gnas kyang
NK123(go)001:5995: 'khrul ba'i blo can rnams la ye gsang thabs kyis
NK123(go)001:5997: theg pa 'og ma rnams su gdul bya dman pa
NK123(go)001:5998: la de nyid ji bzhin par ma gsungs pas sbas
NK123(go)001:5999: pa'i gsang ba nyid du mdzad pa de'i dbang gis
NK123(go)001:6000: gdul bya thun mong pa'i spyod yul du ma gyur
NK123(go)001:6001: pa yin la / sngags zhes pa de lta bu'i
NK123(go)001:6002: gsang ba gsum gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid sgrub par
NK123(go)001:6003: byed pa la gab sbas med par ye ji bzhin
NK123(go)001:6005: shes rab ma rmongs pa dang sgrub byed kyi thabs mchog tu gyur pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6006: sngags bla med kyi lam 'dis ni yid shes bde
NK123(go)001:6007: myur du skyob pa'i phyir lam gzhan kun las khyad
NK123(go)001:6008: par du 'phags pa'i phyir de skad ces gsungs so
NK123(go)001:6009: // thabs kyi theg pa zhes pa ni thabs che ba dang /
NK123(go)001:6012: thabs myur ba bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6013: de yang lam 'di'i gnad dang ldan na kun byang
NK123(go)001:6014: gi chos kun spang blang med par spyod kyang sgrib
NK123(go)001:6015: par mi 'gyur bar ma zad tshogs chen po rdzogs
NK123(go)001:6016: par 'gyur ba'i phyir thabs che ba zhes bya ste
NK123(go)001:6017: / lam gzhan na de lta bu'i thabs med do //
NK123(go)001:6018: de bzhin du dka' thub dang sdom pa drag pos
NK123(go)001:6019: gzir mi dgos par 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la
NK123(go)001:6020: ji bde bar spyod bzhin du de nyid kyis grol
NK123(go)001:6021: ba nyid du byed pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6023: sems can rnams kyi rgyud kyi chags sdang sogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:6024: nyon mongs pa mtha' yas pa rnams gnyan po gzhan
NK123(go)001:6025: gyis bkag mi dgos par nyon mongs pa de nyid
NK123(go)001:6026: kyi sgo nas grol ba ster ba'i thabs du ma
NK123(go)001:6027: yod pa'i phyir thabs mang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:6028: thabs myur ba ni rgyu mtshan bzhi'i sgo nas te /
NK123(go)001:6030: thog ma med pa'i dus kyi spros pa'i bar chags
NK123(go)001:6031: ma lus pa myur du ldog par byed pa ni
NK123(go)001:6032: / 'di ltar snang ba lhar shes te chos kun
NK123(go)001:6033: spang blang med par spyod pas gzung 'dzin gyi rtog
NK123(go)001:6034: pa rang sar ldog pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:6035: rnam par smin pa las ldog pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6036: lta spyod phul du byung ba'i sgo nas rnam smin
NK123(go)001:6037: gyi lus 'di ma bor bar sangs rgyas kyi sa
NK123(go)001:6038: la sbyor nus pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:6039: bsod nams chen po skyed pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6040: snang ba lha yi dkyil 'khor du lta zhing mnyam pa bzhi'i dag pa dang ma bral bas /
NK123(go)001:6041: ji ltar spyod kyang tshogs chen rdzogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:6042: chos rang bzhin med pa la ngang gis 'jug pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6043: chos nyid cir yang ma yin pa'i gnad kyis cir
NK123(go)001:6044: yang 'char du rung bas ni ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK123(go)001:6045: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub pas ci yang
NK123(go)001:6046: min pa'i chos nyid mngon du rig par 'gyur ba'i
NK123(go)001:6047: phyir de lta rgyu mtshan bzhi'o //
NK123(go)001:6048: rdo rje'i theg pa zhes pa'i don ni /
NK123(go)001:6049: mtshan nyid pa ltar kun rdzob sgyu ma'i chos la blang dor du spyod pa ma yin gyi /
NK123(go)001:6050: kun rdzob don dam dbyer med par spyod cing sgo
NK123(go)001:6051: gsum rdo rje gsum gyi rang gzhin du sbyor bas
NK123(go)001:6052: ye nas blang dor med par sangs rgyas pa'i bdag
NK123(go)001:6053: nyid / rdo rje lta bu dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK123(go)001:6054: don dang ldan pa'i theg pa la rdo rje'i theg
NK123(go)001:6055: pa zhes brjod pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:6057: theg pa gzhan nas rang gi lam de nyid nyams
NK123(go)001:6058: su blang ba'i mthus skye ba gzhan na 'bras bu
NK123(go)001:6059: chos sku stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:6060: bdag nyid can du grags pa de gdod thob byar
