NK123(go)001:6061: 'dod la / 'dir gzhi nyid nas 'bras bu'i ngo
NK123(go)001:6062: bor gnas shing 'bras bu de nyid da lta nas
NK123(go)001:6065: mi mnyam pa dang mnyam pa'i theg pa gang zhe na /
NK123(go)001:6066: gang yang mi mnyam pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6067: mthar thug 'bras bu'i sku brnyes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams te /
NK123(go)001:6069: de dag gi dgongs spyod dang mnyam pa'i de skad ces bya'o //
NK123(go)001:6070: de ltar khyad par 'phags pa de yi phyir na ye shes 'char lugs gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:6071: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum gyi ye shes
NK123(go)001:6072: 'char lugs ni ye shes chen po rgyab nas 'char
NK123(go)001:6074: ji ltar chu rnyogs pa dwangs ba la gzugs brnyan
NK123(go)001:6075: 'char ba ltar rnam par mi rtog pa la yun
NK123(go)001:6076: ring du gnas par byas pas rim gyis nyon mongs
NK123(go)001:6077: pa'i rnam rtog snyigs ma dwangs nas sa bcu'i mthar
NK123(go)001:6078: kun tu 'od kyi sa la sangs rgyas nas thams
NK123(go)001:6080: ye shes de lta bu bskal pa grangs med gsum
NK123(go)001:6081: sogs nas phyis 'byung bar 'dod pas ye shes rgyab
NK123(go)001:6083: sngags phyi rgyud sde gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:6084: ye shes chen po mdun nas 'char ba zhes bya ba ste /
NK123(go)001:6085: da lta nyid du 'og min na bzhugs pa'i rgyal
NK123(go)001:6086: ba rigs gsum mam rigs lnga 'khor bcas spyan drangs
NK123(go)001:6087: te / mdun mkha' sogs su zhugs pa la phyag
NK123(go)001:6088: 'tshal zhing mchod pa phul la dngos grub nod par
NK123(go)001:6089: byas pas lha des dngos grub ster bar lta zhing
NK123(go)001:6090: te / / bdag dang lha dang rdzas kyi rten 'brel zab mo'i thabs kyis bsgrubs pas /
NK123(go)001:6091: mi tshe bdun dang bcu drug la sogs pas mthar
NK123(go)001:6092: thug gi 'bras bu 'grub par 'dod pa de dag
NK123(go)001:6093: gi lam rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa las 'bras
NK123(go)001:6094: bu thob pa la myur ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6095: ye shes mdun nas 'char ba zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:6096: sngags nang ba thabs kyi theg pa gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:6097: ye shes chen po khong nas 'char ba zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:6098: chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes bdag nyid chen po'i ngang las ma 'das pas na /
NK123(go)001:6099: rang gi sems nyid bde ba chen po'i de nyid
NK123(go)001:6100: la gnas bzhin du sangs rgyas gzhan du 'tshol mi
NK123(go)001:6101: dgos par tshe 'di nyid la mngon du char bas
NK123(go)001:6102: na / ye shes khong nas 'char ba zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:6103: zhes kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal rjes pas gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:6104: de lta bu'i khyad par du 'phags pa'i nang pa thabs kyi theg pa de la dbye na /
NK123(go)001:6106: nang pa la ni gsum du 'dod //
NK123(go)001:6107: ma h+aa a nu a ti'o //
NK123(go)001:6111: man ngag a ti yo ga'o //
NK123(go)001:6112: de gsum gyi khyad par la bzhed pa mi 'dra ba mang yang gtso bor /
NK123(go)001:6114: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med kyi cho 'phrul du rtogs pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK123(go)001:6115: chos thams cad sems nyid dbyings ye gnyis su med pa'i rtsal du rtogs pa a nu /
NK123(go)001:6116: chos thams cad sems nyid ye nas skye 'gags med
NK123(go)001:6117: pa'i rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bar rtogs
NK123(go)001:6118: pa a ti ste lta ba'i sgo nas phye bar
NK123(go)001:6119: bzhed / kun mkhyen chen pos ni /
NK123(go)001:6120: gdul bya zhe sdang shas che zhing rtog pa mang
NK123(go)001:6121: ba'i don du snang ba thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:6122: pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /'dod chags shas che
NK123(go)001:6123: zhing sems gnas pa la dga' ba'i don du stong
NK123(go)001:6124: pa de kho na nyid kyi rdzogs rim shes rab
NK123(go)001:6126: gti mug shas che zhing bya rtsol slod pa can
NK123(go)001:6127: gyi don du gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin a
NK123(go)001:6130: sems yas pa la bskyed pa ste //
NK123(go)001:6131: sems bcud can la rdzogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6132: mchog gsang rab la rdzob pa che //
NK123(go)001:6133: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:6134: sems nyid ngal gso las kyang /
NK123(go)001:6135: ma h+aas rlung dang bskyed rim thabs gtso la //
NK123(go)001:6136: a nus khams dang rdzogs rim shes rab gtso //
NK123(go)001:6137: a ti'i thams cad gnyis med ye shes gtso //
NK123(go)001:6139: de las dang po gang zag rab kyi tha ma
NK123(go)001:6140: zhe sdang che ba dang rtog pa mang ba la
NK123(go)001:6141: dgongs nas gsungs pa ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa
NK123(go)001:6142: ni / rgyud seng ge rtsal rdzogs las /
NK123(go)001:6143: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni chos thams cad kyi gzhi lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:6144: zhes gsungs pas rgyud thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am rtsa ba lta bur gyur pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6150: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor bstan pa'i sgo nas /
NK123(go)001:6151: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don la rtogs
NK123(go)001:6152: goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba thob pa'i rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:6154: ma h+aa yo ga'i sgra las rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK123(go)001:6155: gnyis med kyi don la blo 'byor bas yo ga phyi pa las ches 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:6156: dbye na drug las 'jug sgo'i dbang ni /
NK123(go)001:6157: thun mong pa bum dbang gi steng du thun min
NK123(go)001:6158: mchog dbang gong ma gsum bsnan pas dbang bzhi bskur
NK123(go)001:6159: ba ste snying po'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK123(go)001:6160: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK123(go)001:6161: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK123(go)001:6163: de la rgyud sde'i khyad par gyi dbye bsdu mang
NK123(go)001:6164: yang bla med kyi rgyud sde thams cad kyi rtsa
NK123(go)001:6165: bar gyur pa gsang ba rgyu 'phrul ltar na /
NK123(go)001:6167: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK123(go)001:6168: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK123(go)001:6169: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK123(go)001:6170: zhes pas dad pa can la dbu rgyan cod pan sogs phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK123(go)001:6172: bdag don nus pa la nyan sgom /
NK123(go)001:6174: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje slob dpon bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang ste nus dbang lnga /
NK123(go)001:6175: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs can gsum la zab mo'i dbang gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:6176: de ltar bum dbang la phan nus gnyis su phye bas lngar 'gyur te /
NK123(go)001:6178: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:6179: bdag phan nus pa gnyis ka'i las //
NK123(go)001:6181: sgrub sde thams cad kyi spyi bka' bde 'dus ltar na /
NK123(go)001:6183: phyi dbang nang dbang gsang dbang dang //
NK123(go)001:6184: theg pa lta ba spyi 'byams dbang //
NK123(go)001:6185: rim gyis dbang ni rdzogs par bskur //
NK123(go)001:6187: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi dbang bzhi las /
NK123(go)001:6188: gdul bya zhe sdang can sgrol ba lam du khyer
NK123(go)001:6189: ba'i phyir bum pa sogs phyi nang gi rdzas brgya
NK123(go)001:6190: rtsa brgyad la brten nas phyi dbang bskur ba /
NK123(go)001:6191: nga rgyal can lha lam du khyer ba'i phyir nang dbang lus la brten nas bskur ba /
NK123(go)001:6192: 'dod chags can sbyor ba lam du khyer ba'i phyir gsang dbang yum la brten nas bskur ba /
NK123(go)001:6193: gti mug can rnam rtog lam du khyer ba'i phyir
NK123(go)001:6194: de kho na nyid kyi dbang sems la brten nas
NK123(go)001:6196: sgrub sde'i dgos bka' yang phur sogs la thun mong
NK123(go)001:6197: ba bla med spyi bka' ltar dbang bzhi bskur ba
NK123(go)001:6198: dang / zab khyad sgrub dbang gi lugs su bskur
NK123(go)001:6199: ba sogs mang yang spyi ldog nas bla med kyi
NK123(go)001:6200: dbang thams cad dbang bzhir 'du ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:6201: bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni shes rab stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK123(go)001:6203: phyag rgya phra rags te ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:6204: bskyed rim gtso bor bstan pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6206: 'jug pa'i sgo ni ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:6209: ma h+aa yo ga'i 'jug sgo ni //
NK123(go)001:6214: thabs kyi lta spyod chen po ni //
NK123(go)001:6215: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK123(go)001:6216: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK123(go)001:6217: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK123(go)001:6218: yang dag skyes mchog dam pa yis /
NK123(go)001:6219: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med par //
NK123(go)001:6220: yang dag nyid du rab tu rtog /
NK123(go)001:6221: zhes pas spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'i cha nas dbu ma dang /
NK123(go)001:6222: chos can thams cad sems kyi rang rtsal tsam du
NK123(go)001:6223: 'du ba'i cha nas sems tsam pa dang phyogs mtshungs
NK123(go)001:6224: kyang sngags kyi lta ba ni /
NK123(go)001:6225: de las khyad par du gyur pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6226: de yang ye gdod ma nas dbyings /
NK123(go)001:6228: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las te /
NK123(go)001:6229: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pa lhag pa don dam bden pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6230: de nyid kyi rtsal snang phung khams skye mched kyis
NK123(go)001:6231: bsdus pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad sku dang ye shes
NK123(go)001:6232: kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas 'khor 'das bzang
NK123(go)001:6233: ngan med par mnyam pa nyid du rdzogs pa ni
NK123(go)001:6234: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6235: de gnyis kyang snang stong phyogs re ba ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:6236: gser dang gser gyi ser po'am g.yu dang g.yu yi
NK123(go)001:6237: kha dog bzhin du ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa
NK123(go)001:6238: mnyam pa nyid du snang ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6239: tha snyad du dbyer med ces brjod na'ang /
NK123(go)001:6240: der 'dzin pa'i bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba ste /
NK123(go)001:6242: lhag pa'i mnyam nyid dbyer med don //
NK123(go)001:6243: ming grangs cir yang bstan mod kyang //
NK123(go)001:6244: don du smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK123(go)001:6247: de min zhen pa sgrol phyir las //
NK123(go)001:6248: tha snyad gnyis pa bsam brjod las //
NK123(go)001:6250: 'dir lhag pa'i sgras smos pa ni theg pa 'og ma las dpag pa'i don te /
NK123(go)001:6252: bcings med rnam par grol med pa'i //
NK123(go)001:6253: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK123(go)001:6254: zhes pas gzhi 'ching grol med pa'i gnas lugs rang
NK123(go)001:6255: rig pa byang chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med
NK123(go)001:6256: spyod yul dang bral ba ye nas gnas pa la
NK123(go)001:6257: / de nyid sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo yin pa'i cha nas bde gshegs snying po dang /
NK123(go)001:6258: stong chas chos sku'i yon tan dang snang chas gzugs
NK123(go)001:6259: sku'i yon tan 'char rung du gnas pas rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:6260: gnas rigs dang / 'khor 'das gnyis kyi 'byung gzhi yin pas kun gzhi'i ye shes dang /
NK123(go)001:6261: kri y+aa'i bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK123(go)001:6262: u pa dang yo gas don dam mtshan ma med
NK123(go)001:6263: pa'i byin rlabs kyis kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK123(go)001:6265: ma h+aa yo ga'i bden gnyis dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po dang /
NK123(go)001:6266: a nu yo ga'i dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK123(go)001:6267: med pa'i sras rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK123(go)001:6268: 'khor dang / a ti yo ga'i ngo bo rang
NK123(go)001:6269: bzhin thugs rje gsum la sogs pa'i tha snyad gang
NK123(go)001:6270: la 'jug pa gzhi rgyud kyi gnas lugs de nyid
NK123(go)001:6271: rtogs bya'i lta bas gtan la 'bebs par byed pa
NK123(go)001:6272: la rtog ge dang rigs pa ltar snang gis gtan
NK123(go)001:6274: kun khyab tshad ma gsum gyis gtan la phab cing
NK123(go)001:6275: rang rig mngon sum gyis rtogs dgos pa'i phyir ro
NK123(go)001:6276: // gtan la phebs byed kyi gtan tshig kyang /
NK123(go)001:6280: bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshig dang bzhi las dang po ni /
NK123(go)001:6282: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK123(go)001:6283: byin gyis brlabs dang mngon sum pa //
NK123(go)001:6284: rab tu rtogs pa rnam bzhi yis //
NK123(go)001:6285: thams cad mngon rdzogs chen por che //
NK123(go)001:6286: zhes pas 'khor 'das gnyis su snang zhing zhen pa'i
NK123(go)001:6287: gnyis 'dzin gyi blo de nyid gnyis med ye shes
NK123(go)001:6288: su gtan la 'bebs pa'i ched du gnyis 'dzin gyi
NK123(go)001:6289: zhen pa de gzhal byar byas nas 'jal byed rgyu
NK123(go)001:6290: gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis chos thams cad rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:6291: skye med du gtan la phab /
NK123(go)001:6292: de bzhin du snga ma snga mas gtan la pheb
NK123(go)001:6293: pa'i grub matha'i zhen cha de gtan tshigs phyi ma
NK123(go)001:6294: phyi ma'i gzhal byar byas nas /
NK123(go)001:6295: yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gtan tshigs kyis rol pa 'gag med du gtan la phab /
NK123(go)001:6296: byin gyis brlabs kyi gtan tshigs kyis ngo bo dbyer med du gtan la phab /
NK123(go)001:6297: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs kyis mtshan nyid blo bral du gtan la 'bebs pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6298: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos so cog chos can /
NK123(go)001:6299: rang byung gi ye shes skye ba med pa'i dbyings su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6300: rtogs ma rtogs kyi byed pas 'khor 'das gnyis su snang ba tsam las /
NK123(go)001:6301: gnyis su ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6302: sems nyid skye med kyi gdangs chos can /
NK123(go)001:6303: rol pa 'gag med lha yi sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba yin te /
NK123(go)001:6304: mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid mtshon byed
NK123(go)001:6305: yi ge du mar ma 'gag par snang bas mtshon
NK123(go)001:6307: rang bzhin skye med dang rol pa 'gag med gnyis chos can /
NK123(go)001:6308: de dang de dngos su rtogs pa'i mthu las /
NK123(go)001:6309: de gnyis ldog pa so sor snang yang ngo bo
NK123(go)001:6310: dbyer med du rtogs pa'i byin brlabs shugs la 'byung
NK123(go)001:6311: ba yin te / lhag pa don dam dkor bdun
NK123(go)001:6312: ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pas de'i snang
NK123(go)001:6313: ldog kun rdzob sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK123(go)001:6315: bden pa dbyer med chos can /
NK123(go)001:6316: blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6317: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes so so rang rig
NK123(go)001:6318: pa'i mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal du bsam
NK123(go)001:6319: brjod bral bar rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:6321: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing /
NK123(go)001:6323: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis phyi nang snod
NK123(go)001:6324: bcud phung khams skye mched thams cad dag pa chen
NK123(go)001:6326: snod bcud rgyud gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad chos can /
NK123(go)001:6327: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6330: rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga dag pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6331: gang ye nas dag pa'i rang bzhin la sgrib pa
NK123(go)001:6332: mtha' dag gis gos ma myong bas khyab cing de
NK123(go)001:6333: nyid sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bo sangs rgyas
NK123(go)001:6334: pas khyab ste / chos kyi sku bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:6336: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyi //
NK123(go)001:6337: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK123(go)001:6338: zhes pas mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis kun rdzob
NK123(go)001:6339: dang don dam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad mnyam
NK123(go)001:6340: pa chen por gtan la 'beb par byed de /
NK123(go)001:6342: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6343: mnyam pa bzhis 'khor 'das gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6345: thun mong gi mnyam gnyis ni /
NK123(go)001:6346: myu gu bdag las mi skye ba lta bu spros
NK123(go)001:6347: pa phyogs re tsam chod pa rnam grangs pa'i don
NK123(go)001:6348: dam dang / mtha' bzhi'i spros pa dang bral ba
NK123(go)001:6349: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam gnyis chos can
NK123(go)001:6350: dam dang / / mnyam pa yin te /
NK123(go)001:6351: spros pa bkag pa'i stong nyid tsam du mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6352: chu zla lta bu don byed mi nus pa log
NK123(go)001:6353: pa'i kun rdzob dang mkha' zla lta bu don byed
NK123(go)001:6354: nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis chos can
NK123(go)001:6356: bden pas stong pa tsam du mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6357: thun mong ma yin pa'i lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis ni /
NK123(go)001:6358: rnam grangs la chos rnams rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa med dgag dang /
NK123(go)001:6359: rnam grangs min pa sems nyid ci yang ma yin
NK123(go)001:6360: pa'i dbyings ye zung 'jug ma yin dgag gi stong
NK123(go)001:6363: lhag pa'i don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6364: ma dag pa las snang log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK123(go)001:6365: yang dag pa lhar snang ba yang dag pa'i kun rdzob gnyis chos can /
NK123(go)001:6367: lhag pa'i kun rdzob sku dang ye shes su mnyam pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6369: rang byung ye shes gnas med snang //
NK123(go)001:6370: zhes pas bdag nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs kyis chos
NK123(go)001:6371: thams cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK123(go)001:6372: po gcig gi bdag nyid du ye nas gtan la
NK123(go)001:6374: snang lugs nas du mar snang yang yin lugs nas gzhal na de ltar ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:6375: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK123(go)001:6376: po gcig nyid du ye nas gnas pa'i phyir ro
NK123(go)001:6377: // de ltar gtan la phab pas rtogs bya'i lta
NK123(go)001:6378: ba rang bzhin rgyu rgyud gnas lugs kyi don de
NK123(go)001:6379: bzhin nyid de rang rig mngon sum gyis yul med
NK123(go)001:6380: rang gsal du rjen par rtogs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6382: de ltar 'dir bshad pa ni bka' sde zur pa'i
NK123(go)001:6383: dgongs pa kun mkhyen smin gling pa yab sras kyi
NK123(go)001:6385: smra ba'i seng chen rong klong rnam gnyis kyi bzhed
NK123(go)001:6386: pa chos thams cad dag mnyam bden pa dbyer med
NK123(go)001:6387: du sgrub pa'i tshul gyi rigs pa'i sgo gzhan rnams
NK123(go)001:6389: kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam dpal dgyes pas mdzad pa'i
NK123(go)001:6390: snying po'i spyi don sogs las shes par bya ste
NK123(go)001:6391: / mdor na chos nyid lta ba'i lta bas 'khor
NK123(go)001:6392: 'das kyi chos thams cad rang bzhin mnyam pa chen
NK123(go)001:6394: chos can lta ba'i lta bas snang spyod kyi chos
NK123(go)001:6395: thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin dag
NK123(go)001:6396: pa chen por gtan la dbab /
NK123(go)001:6397: rang rig lta ba'i lta bas de gnyis dbyer med
NK123(go)001:6398: mtshan nyid bsam brjod dang bral ba mngon sum rang
NK123(go)001:6399: thog tu gtan la phabs nas chos thams cad ye
NK123(go)001:6400: nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du shes par bya
NK123(go)001:6401: ba ni rdo rje rtse mo'i grub matha'i gnad gsang
NK123(go)001:6404: gsang sngags kyi grub mtha' ni lta ba dbu ma
NK123(go)001:6405: las thabs khyad par du 'phags pa tsam du 'dod
NK123(go)001:6407: dbu ma dang sngags gnyis don dam spros bral dang /
NK123(go)001:6408: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du mnyam par lta ba mthun na'ang /
NK123(go)001:6409: de tsam gyi sngags kyi lta ba gtan la mi phebs te /
NK123(go)001:6410: sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i lta ba ni
NK123(go)001:6411: bden pa dbyer med snod bcud dag mnyam chen por
NK123(go)001:6413: de yang chos nyid lta ba'i ngos nas chos thams
NK123(go)001:6414: cad spros bral dmigs bsam brjod 'das chen por gtan
NK123(go)001:6415: la 'bebs pa'i cha nas mdo sngags kyi lta ba
NK123(go)001:6417: chos can kun rdzob lta ba'i ngos nas phung khams
NK123(go)001:6418: skye mched dag pa lha yi 'khor lor mdo nas
NK123(go)001:6419: bshad pa med cing sngags bla med nas bstan pas
NK123(go)001:6420: khyad par du byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6421: de ltar kun rdzob kyi ngos nas sngags kyi lta ba mdo las 'phags pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis /
NK123(go)001:6422: de nyid kyi snang gzhi stong nyid kyang spros bral yin pa tsam du 'dra yang /
NK123(go)001:6423: 'dir don dam dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun
NK123(go)001:6424: gyis grub pa'i rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid
NK123(go)001:6425: la 'dod pas khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK123(go)001:6426: gal te khyed cag gi rgyu rgyud de rig pa
NK123(go)001:6427: 'gyur med la de bzhin nyid du byed par 'dug
NK123(go)001:6428: pas / de 'dra de 'khor lo tha ma'i nges don gyi mdo zab mo rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:6429: de'i dgongs 'grel rgyud bla ma sogs las kyang 'byung
NK123(go)001:6430: bas rtogs bya'i yul la khyad med dam zhe na
NK123(go)001:6431: / rig pa 'gyur med la rgyu rgyud byed pa
NK123(go)001:6432: 'khor lo tha ma nas gsungs pa dang 'dra ba
NK123(go)001:6433: / bden mod kyi / da dung des sngags kyi
NK123(go)001:6434: thun mong min pa'i lta ba gtan la phebs par
NK123(go)001:6435: / bden mod kyi / mi 'gyur te / de
NK123(go)001:6436: bzhin nyid de bla na med pa'i rgyud 'di rgyud
NK123(go)001:6437: du 'jog pa'i tshe na lhan cig skyes pa mi
NK123(go)001:6438: 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin du byas
NK123(go)001:6439: pa ni sngags kyi khyad chos su de bzhin gshegs
NK123(go)001:6440: pa sras bcas bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:6442: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK123(go)001:6443: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK123(go)001:6444: mi shig thig le bde chen po //
NK123(go)001:6445: nam mkha' lta bur kun khyab pa //
NK123(go)001:6446: mi gnas chos sku'i rang bzhin yin //
NK123(go)001:6449: des na gtso bos gang zhig 'pho med lhan skyes
NK123(go)001:6450: lus kyi bde ba dag ni sngags kyi theg par
NK123(go)001:6452: de yang gnyis snang 'khor ba'i chos 'di rnams thag khra'i sbrul ltar med snang glo bur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:6453: de'i snang gzhi gnas lugs de bzhin nyid yin pa'i gnad kyis /
NK123(go)001:6454: rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag par gsungs pa yang /
NK123(go)001:6455: phung sogs snang gzhi de bzhin nyid kyi rtsal gnyug ma ste /
NK123(go)001:6456: shin tu phra ba'i ye shes kyi rtsa dang /
NK123(go)001:6458: ye shes kyi khams zhes sam /
NK123(go)001:6460: me rlung gnyis mkha' sems gnyis zung du 'jug pa
NK123(go)001:6461: rnams riim par ye nas sku gsum rdo rje gsum
NK123(go)001:6462: gyi ngo bor gzhan gyis ma brtsal bar lhun gyis
NK123(go)001:6463: grub pa dang / khams lnga'i dwangs ma ye ji bzhin rigs lnga dang /
NK123(go)001:6464: ye shes kyi khams rigs drug pa'i bdag nyid du
NK123(go)001:6465: dag pas lha'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa gang yin
NK123(go)001:6466: pa ste / lam rim rim du /
NK123(go)001:6467: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK123(go)001:6468: gzhi rdzogs phyag rgya ma 'dres gsal //
NK123(go)001:6471: zhes rgyal sras rin po che pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtshos gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:6472: des na bla med kyi rgyud rnams su sgo gsum
NK123(go)001:6473: rags phra shin tu phra ba'i sgo gsum du phye
NK123(go)001:6474: ba'i shin tu phra ba'i sgo gsum dang mi shig
NK123(go)001:6475: pa'i thig le sogs don gcig ste /
NK123(go)001:6476: de ni khams drug gi dwangs ma dbyer med cing
NK123(go)001:6477: 'bral mi shes pa 'od gsal gnyug ma'i sems dang
NK123(go)001:6479: shin tu phra ba'i rlung de la ye shes lnga'i
NK123(go)001:6480: cha 'dzin pa 'od lnga'i gting mdangs can du yod
NK123(go)001:6481: pa phra rags kyi rlung sems thams cad gang las
NK123(go)001:6482: mched cing gang du sdud pa'i gzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:6483: de la rtsol ba bcas rlung gi rnal 'byor dang
NK123(go)001:6484: rtsol med rdzogs chen gyi rnal 'byor gang rung gi
NK123(go)001:6485: gnad du bsnun pas sgrib bral du gyur pa na
NK123(go)001:6486: lam dus su sgyu lus dang stong gzugs kyi lha
NK123(go)001:6487: sku 'char zhing 'bras dus su rang snang longs sku
NK123(go)001:6488: chen po dang gzhan snang phyed sprul sogs 'char gzhi
NK123(go)001:6489: byed pa ste / des na shin tu phra ba'i sgo gsum ni sbyang gzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:6490: phra ba'i yid lus rlung sems tsam dang rags pa'i
NK123(go)001:6491: sgo gsum ni sbyang bya yin pas gnad 'di go
NK123(go)001:6492: na 'khor lo tha ma'i mdo'i dgongs don rgyud bla
NK123(go)001:6493: sogs nas gsungs pa 'gal med don gcig tu 'bab
NK123(go)001:6494: pa'ang yin no // tshul khrims ni /
NK123(go)001:6495: gsangs sngags phyi 'gyur ba rnams bsrung bya'i dam tshig /
NK123(go)001:6504: rang bzhin dag pa'i chos la som nyi za ba /
NK123(go)001:6506: don dam la rtog dpyod kyis 'jal ba /
NK123(go)001:6507: dad ldan gyi sems sun 'byin pa /
NK123(go)001:6508: skabs su babs pa'i dam tshig gi rdzas mi brten pa /
NK123(go)001:6509: shes rab ma la smod pa ste rtsa ltung bcu bzhi /
NK123(go)001:6510: ma smin pa'i rigs ma brten pa /
NK123(go)001:6511: tshogs 'khor gyi dus su kyal ka'i rtsod pa /
NK123(go)001:6512: mtshan nyid med pa'i yul las bdud rtsi len pa /
NK123(go)001:6513: snod ldan la gsang sngags mi ston pa /
NK123(go)001:6514: dad ldan la chos mi ston pa /
NK123(go)001:6515: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun bsdad pa /
NK123(go)001:6516: nga rgyal gyi sngags par rlom pa /
NK123(go)001:6517: snod min la chos bshad pa ste yan lag gi ltung ba brgyad rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:6518: spyod bya'i dam tshig sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin shes nas spyod pa gnyis su bzhed /
NK123(go)001:6520: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:6522: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsrung mtshams ni /
NK123(go)001:6523: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum po dang //
NK123(go)001:6524: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga bsrung //
NK123(go)001:6526: bla ma dang mched la gus pa sku /
NK123(go)001:6527: sngags dang phyag rgya la brtson pa gsung /
NK123(go)001:6528: bla med byang chub kyi sems mi spongs shing gsang
NK123(go)001:6529: ba bsrung ba thugs kyi dam tshig ste rtsa ba
NK123(go)001:6530: gsum / ta na ga na ma byin len dang
NK123(go)001:6531: rdzun tshig barlanga ste thabs kyis zin pa'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:6532: gsum / spyad bya lnga / chags sdang gti mug nga rgyal phrag dog ste /
NK123(go)001:6533: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas mi spong ba lnga /
NK123(go)001:6534: dri chen dri chu byang sems dkar dmar mam sa ste /
NK123(go)001:6536: chos nyid ngo bos grub pa /
NK123(go)001:6537: chos can rang bzhin gyis grub pa /
NK123(go)001:6539: byin gyis brlabs kyis grub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6541: nad lnga sel ba'i sman yin pa /
NK123(go)001:6542: thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i dam rdzas yin pa /
NK123(go)001:6543: rigs lnga ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin yin pa rnams so //
NK123(go)001:6545: pa bzhi dang yin pa gsum gyi dbang gis dang du blang bya lnga /
NK123(go)001:6546: phung po 'byung ba yum dbang po kha dog rnams lhar shes pas bya lnga /
NK123(go)001:6551: las kyi rigs lnga phung po sgrub pa sgrub bya lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:6552: yan lag gi dam tshig nyer lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:6553: khyad par gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs ltar na /
NK123(go)001:6554: bla med mi spong bla ma bskur /
NK123(go)001:6555: sngags phyag rgya rgyun mi gcod /
NK123(go)001:6556: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams /
NK123(go)001:6557: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya /
NK123(go)001:6558: zhes rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK123(go)001:6559: dug lnga mi spong ba dang /
NK123(go)001:6560: bdud rtsi lnga po mi 'dor ba ste /
NK123(go)001:6561: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu bcas bco lnga /
NK123(go)001:6562: de dag las kyang spros na sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6564: sgrub sde gtso bor byas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6565: rgyud sde gtso bor byas pa'i lugs gnyis /
NK123(go)001:6567: 'jam dpal sku 'khor lo bzhi'i dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6568: pad+ma gsung rta skad thengs gsum gyi dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6569: yang dag thugs ru lu 'bru brgyad kyi dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6570: che mchog yon tan bdud rtsi rnam dag gi dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6571: phur pa phrin las thal 'byin rnam pa bzhi'i dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6572: ye shes lha yi sgrub lugs lnga dang /
NK123(go)001:6573: mo mo rbod gtong rtsa rlung thig le'i dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6574: 'jig rten mchod bstod brten gsum gyi dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6575: dmod pa drag sngags 'bod rbad bsad gsum gyi dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6576: thun mong gi sgrub lugs gsum bcas brgyad dang /
NK123(go)001:6577: bla ma rig 'dzin bsnyen sgrub rnam pa bzhi'i dgongs pa la brten nas sgrub pa'i tshul te /
NK123(go)001:6578: de rnams ni zhib par kun mkhyen bla ma 'jam
NK123(go)001:6579: dpal dgyes pas mdzad pa'i bka' brgyad rnams bshad chen
NK123(go)001:6582: spyir ma h+aa yo ga la'ang pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum gyi dbye bas /
NK123(go)001:6583: gsang 'dus la sogs pa pha rgyud du bskyed rim thabs kyi cha dang /
NK123(go)001:6584: de'i rdzogs rim kyang rlung gtso bor byed pas /
NK123(go)001:6585: gsal stang rnam par mi rtogs pa'i tshul gyis nyams len par 'dod /
NK123(go)001:6586: bde dgyes yang dag sogs ma rgyud rnams su bskyed rim gyis spros pa shas chung zhing /
NK123(go)001:6587: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa khams byang chub kyi
NK123(go)001:6588: sems thig le gtso bor byed pa'i bde stong rnam
NK123(go)001:6589: par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len par
NK123(go)001:6590: 'dod / sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs ma ning gi rgyud rnams su bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing /
NK123(go)001:6591: de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa thig rlung gsum las skyes pa'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK123(go)001:6592: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK123(go)001:6593: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len par 'dod
NK123(go)001:6594: do // skabs 'dir gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs nyid mdo tsam bshad na /
NK123(go)001:6596: grol lam thabs su rnam par bstan //
NK123(go)001:6597: zhes pas spyir thabs grol gyi lam gnyis gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:6599: mtshan ma sgom pa'i rim pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6600: de bzhin nyid ni sgom pa yi //
NK123(go)001:6601: bye brag rnam pa gnyis su gsungs //
NK123(go)001:6602: zhes pas nyams len la mtshan bcas dang /
NK123(go)001:6604: dang po la bskyed rdzogs gnyis kyi /
NK123(go)001:6607: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK123(go)001:6608: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK123(go)001:6609: rang byung kun bzang lhun gyis grub //
NK123(go)001:6611: gtso bor shes rab rnam pa gsum gyi sgo nas
NK123(go)001:6612: rang rgyud kyi 'ching ba chos nyid du grol bar
NK123(go)001:6613: byed pa ste / rin po che ko stu b+ha
NK123(go)001:6614: dang lhan cig bzhag pa'i rdo'i khams rim gyis gser
NK123(go)001:6615: du 'gyur ba bzhin te thabs lam la ltos nas
NK123(go)001:6616: ring ba'i lam du bzhag ste /
NK123(go)001:6618: ring ba'ang rim dang cig char ba //
NK123(go)001:6619: zhes pas dbang po yang rab in+d+ra b+hu ti lta
NK123(go)001:6620: bu dbang dus su grol ba kha cig dbyer med
NK123(go)001:6621: chig chod du rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa
NK123(go)001:6622: yod de / cig car ba zhes bya zhing /
NK123(go)001:6623: yang rim gyis rtogs goms mthar phyin par byed pa ni rim gyis pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6626: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK123(go)001:6627: nus mthu can du gang gyur pa //
NK123(go)001:6628: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK123(go)001:6630: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK123(go)001:6631: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:6632: lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi ste gsum las /
NK123(go)001:6633: dang po ni gong du smos zin la /
NK123(go)001:6634: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK123(go)001:6635: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas dkyil 'khor rim
NK123(go)001:6636: gyis bskyed pa gtso bor byed pa'i sgo nas lha
NK123(go)001:6637: rtogs dbyer med du bsgoms pa'i nyams len /
NK123(go)001:6641: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang don
NK123(go)001:6642: spyi'i rnam pa tsam de mos pa lam byed kyis
NK123(go)001:6643: sgom pa nub gcig la cho ga'i yan lag tshang
NK123(go)001:6644: bar nyams su len pa lta bu ste /
NK123(go)001:6646: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis bskyed rim gyi khog phub pa /
NK123(go)001:6647: ji ltar bskyed pa'i ngo bor dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba /
NK123(go)001:6648: de ltar bskyed pa de'ang srog sdom gzer bzhi'i rgyas
NK123(go)001:6649: theb pa zhig ni bskyed rim gyi gnad yin pas
NK123(go)001:6651: 'di la bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i tha snyad sbyor na /
NK123(go)001:6653: ting 'dzin gsum bskyed bsnyen pa yin //
NK123(go)001:6654: bdag nyid lhar bskyed nye bsnyen te //
NK123(go)001:6655: yum bskyed sgrub par shes par bya //
NK123(go)001:6656: gzhan rnams sgrub pa chen po yin //
NK123(go)001:6658: ting 'dzin gsum bsgoms pa yan chad bsnyen pa /
NK123(go)001:6659: rang lha gtso bor bsgoms pa nye bsnyen /
NK123(go)001:6660: yum bsgoms te mkha' gsang brlabs pa dang 'khor gyi lha tshang bar bsgoms pa bsgrub pa /
NK123(go)001:6661: dbang bskur rgyas gdabs sogs cho ga'i yan lag gzhan rnams sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK123(go)001:6663: rim pa gnyis po'i ting nge 'dzin nyams lnga mthar phyin gyi bar du slob pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6664: bi ma'i phyag rgya bsam gtan gyi 'grel ba las /
NK123(go)001:6665: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga //
NK123(go)001:6666: bsam gtan nyams kyi skye tshul yin //
NK123(go)001:6668: dang po g.yo ba'i nyams ni /
NK123(go)001:6669: dpe ri gzar gyi 'bab chu ltar sems skad cig
NK123(go)001:6670: kyang mi gnas par rnam rtog snga ma bas mang
NK123(go)001:6671: du song ba lta bu ste rnam rtog ngos zin
NK123(go)001:6672: pa'i nyams so // gnyis pa thob pa'i nyams ni /
NK123(go)001:6673: dper rong khung dogs pa'i 'bab chu ltar rnam rtog
NK123(go)001:6674: 'phro 'du zhi nas yud tsam re rtog med du
NK123(go)001:6675: zhi mal le gnas pa zhig 'byung ste rnam rtog
NK123(go)001:6677: gsum pa goms pa'i nyams ni /
NK123(go)001:6678: dpe g.yo 'gul mang po byed mi nus pa'i rgan po'i spyod pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:6679: phal cher rtog med du gnas pa las res 'ga'
NK123(go)001:6680: rtog pa ban bun tsam re 'byung ba rnam rtog
NK123(go)001:6682: bzhi pa brtan pa'i nyams ni /
NK123(go)001:6683: dper mtsho chung ba ser bus bskyod pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:6684: phal cher rtog med rgya 'byams su gnas pa las
NK123(go)001:6685: rkyen grag po res cung zad g.yo ba 'byung ste
NK123(go)001:6686: rnam rtog gis bskyod du med pa'i nyams so //
NK123(go)001:6687: lnga pa mthar phyin pa'i nyams ni /
NK123(go)001:6688: dpe rgya mtsho rlabs dang bral ba'am ri bo chen
NK123(go)001:6689: po ltar gnas pa rkyen gang gis kyang gnod mi
NK123(go)001:6690: nus par ma zad slar la bogs 'byin zhing btang
NK123(go)001:6691: 'gro bzhag sdod rang dbang du 'byor bas mthar phyin
NK123(go)001:6692: rang dbang 'byor ba'i nyams zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:6693: de lta bu'i tshul gyis bsgom bya dngos la /
NK123(go)001:6695: spang bya 'khor ba'i chos sna tshogs par snang ba
NK123(go)001:6696: 'di dag srid par skye bar blang ba la brten
NK123(go)001:6697: nas 'char bas 'khor ba'i chos kyi gtso bor skye
NK123(go)001:6698: gnas bzhi'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun nas /
NK123(go)001:6699: bskyed rim sgom tshul bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:6701: skye gnas gzhi po dag bya'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:6702: bskyed pa'ang de bzhin rnam pa bzhi //
NK123(go)001:6703: spros bcas spros pa med pa dang //
NK123(go)001:6704: shin tu spros pa med bzhi'o //
NK123(go)001:6705: zhes pas sgong skyes sbyong byed ni /
NK123(go)001:6706: dbang brtul spros pa can gyi dbang du byas te /
NK123(go)001:6707: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bde chen byang chub sems
NK123(go)001:6708: kyi ngo bor zhu ba'i 'od kyi thig le las
NK123(go)001:6709: zhu pa glus bskul gyis slar bzhengs te dkyil 'khor
NK123(go)001:6710: gyi 'khor lo spro ba bdag sras gzhan sras kyi
NK123(go)001:6711: cho ga dang / nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyi
NK123(go)001:6712: nang du rang lha'i phyag mtshan sa bon dang bcas
NK123(go)001:6713: pa zhu zhing 'dres pa las spro bsdus lhar bskyed
NK123(go)001:6714: pa mngon byang lnga'i cho ga lta bu dang /
NK123(go)001:6715: mngal skyes sbyong byed dbang po dang spros pa 'bring gi ngor /
NK123(go)001:6716: 'chi srid bar do dang bcas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6717: dri za'i sems khu khrag gi dbus su zhugs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6718: de las lus grub pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6719: btsas nas dbang po yul la sad pa bzhi rim par sbyong byed /
NK123(go)001:6722: sku yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6723: gnas gsum sogs la yi ge 'god pa ste rdo rje'i cho ga bzhi bskyed dang /
NK123(go)001:6724: sa bon phyag mtshan sku yongs rdzogs te rdo rje'i cho ga gsum bskyed de /
NK123(go)001:6725: de ltar sgong skyes dang mngal skyes sbyong ba'i sgom
NK123(go)001:6726: tshul gnyis po 'di ma h+aa yo ga'i bskyed yul
NK123(go)001:6727: yin la / drod gsher sbyong byed spros med a nu'i lugs dang /
NK123(go)001:6728: bardzusa skyes sbyong byed shin tu spros med a ti'i
NK123(go)001:6729: bskyed tshul gnyis ni 'og tu rang rang gi skabs
NK123(go)001:6731: 'di bzhi yang rim par las dang po pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6733: brtan pa chen po thob pa dang shin tu brtan
NK123(go)001:6734: pa'i gnas skabs na rang rang gi blo tshad dang
NK123(go)001:6735: mthun par sgom par bya ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:6736: de thams cad kyang tha mal gyi snang zhen sbyong ba'i phyir sgom pa yin pas /
NK123(go)001:6737: tha mal gyi snang ba sbyong byed rnam pa gsal ba /
NK123(go)001:6738: bdag tu zhen pa sbyong byed nga rgyal brtan pa /
NK123(go)001:6739: dngos por zhen pa sbyong byed rnam dag dran pa gsum dang ma bral ba'i dang /
NK123(go)001:6740: mar 'khor ba'i gnas skabs na lus ngag yid gsum
NK123(go)001:6741: bya ba dang bcas pa yar sangs rgyas kyi skabs
NK123(go)001:6742: na sku gsung thugs phrin las dang bcas pa dbyer
NK123(go)001:6743: med du lto sbyar nas srog gzer bus bsdams pa
NK123(go)001:6745: sku bskyed pa lha yi gzer /
NK123(go)001:6746: gzung bzlas pa sngags kyi gzer /
NK123(go)001:6747: thugs dgongs pa mi 'gyur ba'i gzer /
NK123(go)001:6748: bya byed 'phro 'du phrin las kyi gzer te srog
NK123(go)001:6749: sdom gyi gzer bzhi'i lta sgom spyod 'bras mthar dbyung
NK123(go)001:6751: de ltar shes par byas nas /
NK123(go)001:6753: srid pa'i rim par smin tshul gyis //
NK123(go)001:6754: 'jug pa'i yan lag lnga ru bzhag /
NK123(go)001:6755: gang dag dngos kun rang rig phyir //
NK123(go)001:6756: shi ba don dam bden pa ste //
NK123(go)001:6757: skye ba bar ma kun rdzob yin //
NK123(go)001:6758: skye ba'i rim gsum gnyis med don //
NK123(go)001:6760: 'chi bar skye gsum gyi srid pa cig car du sbyong ba'i lam rdzogs par ston pa la /
NK123(go)001:6761: 'chi ba 'od gsal dang rjes su mthun pa'i stong pa chen po /
NK123(go)001:6762: bar do dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam snying rje sgyu ma /
NK123(go)001:6763: skye ba'i rim pa gsum dang rjes su mthun pa'i lam phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK123(go)001:6765: tshom bu tshogs sgrub ste zag bcas tshogs sbyor gyi lam lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:6766: de la'ang rags pa bskyed rim dang /
NK123(go)001:6767: phra ba rdzogs rim gyi sbyong tshul gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:6768: dang po ni lus can rnams 'chi 'pho ba'i tshe
NK123(go)001:6769: phyi nang gi thim rim rnams rdzogs pa'i mthar 'chi
NK123(go)001:6771: de nyid lam du khyer ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6772: snang grags kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad chos sku
NK123(go)001:6773: spros bral de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom
NK123(go)001:6774: pa dang 'od gsal de nyid ngos ma zin par
NK123(go)001:6775: bar do'i yid lus sgyu ma lta bu'i gnas skabs
NK123(go)001:6776: kyi bag chags sbyong byed dmigs pa med pa'i kun
NK123(go)001:6777: snang gi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo snying rje
NK123(go)001:6778: chen po mkha' khyab tu bsgom zhing /
NK123(go)001:6779: gzhi de las bar do ma grol bar ma'i mngal
NK123(go)001:6780: du skye ba bzung ba nas btsas pa'i bar gyi
NK123(go)001:6781: bar chags sbyong byed phyag rgya gcig pa phra rags
NK123(go)001:6782: gnyis te / gang du skye bar 'gyur ba'i gnas
NK123(go)001:6783: la sred pa skyes pa'i rkyen gyis der 'jug ma
NK123(go)001:6784: rag gi bar srid kyi gnas skabs sbyong byed phra
NK123(go)001:6785: ba rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngo bo yig 'bru
NK123(go)001:6789: lhang nge ba ste gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:6793: cir yang sgyur du btub pa ste brtan pa'i tshad
NK123(go)001:6794: bzhi bcas gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa
NK123(go)001:6796: de nyid pha ma'i khu rdul gyi bar du zhugs
NK123(go)001:6797: nas phyi rol gyi dbang po'i yul la sad kyi
NK123(go)001:6798: bar gyi gnas skabs sbyong byed rags pa lha sku
NK123(go)001:6799: la bslab pa mngon byang bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:6800: cho ga gsum sogs kyis bskyed pa skye gnas rigs bzhi'i tshul dang mthun pa la bslab pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6801: btsas nas nar son pa'i bar gyi bag chags sbyong
NK123(go)001:6802: byed phyag rgya spros bcas la bslab pa la'ang bzhi
NK123(go)001:6804: 'khor lo tshom bu grangs zhal phyag /
NK123(go)001:6805: ces bshad pa ltar dkyil 'khor spro ba /
NK123(go)001:6808: zhal phyag spro ba ste bzhi las /
NK123(go)001:6810: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6811: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6813: zhi ba la stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong dang /
NK123(go)001:6814: bsam yas lhun grub rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:6816: stong bzhi rgya lnga bcu dang /
NK123(go)001:6817: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu dang /
NK123(go)001:6818: bsam yas lhun grub la bslab pa rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:6819: zhal phyag yang rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gyi tshul lo //
NK123(go)001:6820: nar son nas rgan po'i bar gyi bag chags sbyong byed tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa la /
NK123(go)001:6822: gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus /
NK123(go)001:6823: gang la brten nas sgrub pa'i yo byad /
NK123(go)001:6824: gang gis sgrub pa'i ston pa dang 'khor /
NK123(go)001:6825: ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs te phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung zhing /
NK123(go)001:6826: sgrub pa'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i gzhung bsrangs te /
NK123(go)001:6828: zla gcig phyed zhal nye bsnyen dang //
NK123(go)001:6830: bco lnga ma phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK123(go)001:6832: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK123(go)001:6833: dngos sgrub bzlas bya sgrub chen po //
NK123(go)001:6834: zhes pas cha rkyen rnams tshogs nas sgrub pa la 'jug ma thag pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK123(go)001:6835: zhugs nas zla ba phyed yan chad ni nye bsnyen te /
NK123(go)001:6836: 'di gnyis su 'od dkar po'i 'phro 'du bsnol mas rgyud dag par byed pa dang /
NK123(go)001:6837: tha ma'i zhag gcig ma gtogs pa'i phyed man chad
NK123(go)001:6838: ni sgrub pa ste 'od dmar po'i 'phro 'dus kyis
NK123(go)001:6840: nub tha mar 'od zer mthing ga tshur bsdu ba
NK123(go)001:6841: sogs kyi srod nam gung tho rengs gsum gyi dus
NK123(go)001:6842: gnad dang bstun te lha dang gzas po dang gzungs
NK123(go)001:6843: ma gsum las dngos grub len pa ni sgrub pa
NK123(go)001:6844: chen po ste / 'di ni zla ba gcig la dper mtshon pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6845: de ltar sgrub pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bstan pa ni /
NK123(go)001:6847: zhag ni sum bcu phrag drug gam //
NK123(go)001:6848: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK123(go)001:6849: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK123(go)001:6850: ces gsungs pas zla ba drug spog chog dang bcas
NK123(go)001:6851: pa sogs kyis dbang po'i khyad par dang mthun par
NK123(go)001:6852: 'dod gzugs kyi rig 'dzin grub nas rim gyis lam
NK123(go)001:6853: gong ma la sbyor bar byed do //
NK123(go)001:6854: de ltar zag bcas kyi lam lnga po des mar
NK123(go)001:6855: 'khor ba dang rnam pa mthun pas de'i bag chags
NK123(go)001:6856: sbyong zhing dag / yar sangs rgyas sku gsum dang
NK123(go)001:6857: de'i mdzad spyod kyi rigs kyi nus pa gsos theb
NK123(go)001:6859: bar du lam 'og mas gong ma sgom rung gi
NK123(go)001:6860: gzhi bting bas smin byed du 'gro ba'i thabs so
NK123(go)001:6861: // gnyis pa phra ba rdzogs rim gyi spyod tshul yang /
NK123(go)001:6862: de dang rnam pa mthun pas bsam gtan gyi spyod
NK123(go)001:6863: lam dang ldan pas rig pa ma bcos pa'i ngang
NK123(go)001:6864: du so mar 'jog pa rig pa spyi blugs dang
NK123(go)001:6865: sngar thos bsam gyi lta ba dran par byas nas
NK123(go)001:6866: de'i ngang du 'jog pa mthong ba'i rjes la 'jog
NK123(go)001:6867: pa ste / 'jog thabs gnyis gang rung gi don
NK123(go)001:6868: dam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK123(go)001:6869: mnyam par 'jog pa nyin mo'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK123(go)001:6870: mtshan mo gnyid 'thug gi 'od gsal 'dzin pa'i man ngag gnyis sbrel te /
NK123(go)001:6871: nyin mtshan kha sbyor du nyams su len pa'i sgo
NK123(go)001:6872: nas nyams lnga mthar phyin pa bslab pa stong pa
NK123(go)001:6873: chen po / stong chen 'od gsal de'i ngang du sems 'gags pas /
NK123(go)001:6874: du ba smig rgyu me khyer /
NK123(go)001:6875: mar me sogs stong gzugs kyi snang ba shar ba
NK123(go)001:6876: na nyin gyi rnal 'byor sad pa'i snang ba de
NK123(go)001:6877: dang / mtshan mo rmi lam gyi snang ba thams
NK123(go)001:6878: cad sgyu ma chu zla ltar mthong ba las dmigs
NK123(go)001:6879: med bde chen gyi snying rje ma 'gags par shar
NK123(go)001:6880: ba la goms par byed pa snying rje sgyu ma
NK123(go)001:6881: dang / / snang ba ris med las snying rje
NK123(go)001:6882: chen po'i 'phen pa dang ting nge 'dzin gyi rkyen
NK123(go)001:6883: gyis chu dwangs pa la gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar
NK123(go)001:6884: zhu ba de dang mtshungs ldan du byung ba'i lha
NK123(go)001:6885: sku phyag rgya gcig pas gang shar gyis snang ba
NK123(go)001:6886: thams cad la rgyas theb pa phyag rgya gcig pa
NK123(go)001:6887: dang / / / sngar gyi lha snang de las
NK123(go)001:6888: ches cher 'phel bas snang ba thams cad zung 'jug
NK123(go)001:6889: gi lha gtso 'khor dang tshom bu'i rnam par mngon
NK123(go)001:6890: sum du spros te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'char
NK123(go)001:6891: ba la goms pa phyag rgya spros bcas /
NK123(go)001:6892: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang rung gi sgo
NK123(go)001:6893: nas spros bcas bskyed rim dang phyogs mthun du sgrub
NK123(go)001:6894: pa'am / spros med rnal 'byor pho mo gtso bo yab yum tsam tshogs pa la brten pa'am /
NK123(go)001:6895: shin tu spros med ni yab mi 'gyur ba'i bde
NK123(go)001:6896: chen nyid yum rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa
NK123(go)001:6897: nyid kha sbyor gyis sgrub pa tshom bu tshogs sgrub
NK123(go)001:6898: ste / gang ltar yang dbang po rab 'bring tha
NK123(go)001:6899: gsum gyi dbye bas zla ba drug gam lo gcig
NK123(go)001:6901: lo gcig zla ba bzhi rnams kyis zag med la dngos su sbyor ba byed do //
NK123(go)001:6902: gsum pa lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin ni /
NK123(go)001:6903: de ltar bsgoms pas zag pa med pa'i lam mthong
NK123(go)001:6904: sgom mthar lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i rig 'dzin bzhi
NK123(go)001:6906: mthong lam la blo'i nus stobs che chung gis rnam
NK123(go)001:6907: smin gyi lus dwangs ma'i lus su ma gyur pa
NK123(go)001:6909: dwangs ma'i lus su gyur pa lam mchog yongs rdzogs tshe dbang rig 'dzin gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:6911: nus pa thob dang ma thob pa'i //
NK123(go)001:6912: mthong lam gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK123(go)001:6915: lus rnam smin sha khrag gi phung po dang ma bral ba /
NK123(go)001:6916: yid 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin pa /
NK123(go)001:6917: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin lus rgya dang bral ma
NK123(go)001:6918: thag phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor nges
NK123(go)001:6919: pa ste / chos gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6921: bdag don du bkod pa dkyil 'khor gyi bya bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs par byed cing /
NK123(go)001:6922: phrin las bzhi'i sgo nas gzhan don rdzogs par byed /
NK123(go)001:6923: zag med lha'i spyan rnam par dag pa la sogs
NK123(go)001:6924: pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa gling bzhi pa'i 'jig
NK123(go)001:6925: rten tsam du sku'i don mdzad cing sprul gzugs ston
NK123(go)001:6926: tshul tshe dbang dang cha 'dra bas don mdzad do
NK123(go)001:6928: sems 'od gsal gyi lha skur smin cing phra yang
NK123(go)001:6929: la sogs pa'i 'ja' lus kyi yon tan khyad par
NK123(go)001:6930: can dang ldan pa'i rdo rje'i lus can te /
NK123(go)001:6931: spyir tshe dbang la sman gyi bcud len la brten pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:6932: thig le dbab bzung sogs la brten pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:6933: sgrol ma rlung la brten pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:6934: lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe dbang dang bzhi las 'di ni phyi ma ste /
NK123(go)001:6935: zag med mthong lam gyi ye shes ji lta ba bzhin mngon sum du mthong ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6937: bdag don du kun 'gro'i dri ma sbyang zhing /
NK123(go)001:6938: gzhan don du cho 'phrul bzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:6939: phrin las bzhi sogs kyi don mdzad /
NK123(go)001:6940: cha lugs mi dang 'dod lha'i gtso bo'i cha byad
NK123(go)001:6941: du yang ston mod lha mi gzhan las khyad par
NK123(go)001:6942: du 'phags pa'o // mngon shes kyi yul don yang /
NK123(go)001:6943: dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lngas gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgyar dus gcig tu don mdzad /
NK123(go)001:6944: sa lhag ma dgu sgom lam phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyis bsdus te /
NK123(go)001:6947: ye shes sku yi cha lugs can //
NK123(go)001:6948: 'byung ba rdo rje'i lus las gol //
NK123(go)001:6949: zhes pas sngar rang nyid kyis gang bsgoms kyi lhag
NK123(go)001:6950: pa'i lha rigs lnga gang yin gyi cha lugs 'dzin
NK123(go)001:6953: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK123(go)001:6955: zhes pas sa gnyis pa nas lnga pa'i bar rdo rje'i rig 'dzin zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:6956: rtogs pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bus rang sa'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6957: sa drug pa sher phyin la gtso bor spyod cing chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:6958: sa bdun pa'ang thabs la mkhas pa 'khor lo ltar gyur pas de gnyis la 'khor lo'i rig 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:6959: sa brgyad par mi rtog ye shes la dbang bsgyur bas rin po che'i rig 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:6960: sa dgu par chags pa med pas zhing sbyong zhing 'gro don mdzad pas pad+ma'i rig 'dzin /
NK123(go)001:6961: sa bcu pa phrin las phun sum tshogs pas sems
NK123(go)001:6962: can gyi don dpag med mdzad pa'i phyir ral gri'i
NK123(go)001:6964: cha byad zung 'jug gi lha sku mtshan dpe yongs
NK123(go)001:6965: su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid can bdag don du lhan
NK123(go)001:6966: cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa sbyong zhing /
NK123(go)001:6967: gzhan don du rngon pa dang smad 'tshong ma la
NK123(go)001:6968: sogs pa gang 'dul gyi sprul gzugs su ston par
NK123(go)001:6969: byed cing / mngon shes kyi yul don kyang /
NK123(go)001:6970: dbang shes nyi shu rtsa lnga'i yon tan tshe dbang dang 'dra na'ang /
NK123(go)001:6971: 'dir gsal brtan gyi khyad par du byas shing /
NK123(go)001:6972: longs sku'i zhing dang mnyam pa'i 'gro don mdzad do //
NK123(go)001:6973: de ltar sa gnyis pa nas bcu pa'i rnam grol lam tshun chad phyag chen du bsdus shing /
NK123(go)001:6974: sa bcu'i khyad par lam mam mthar lam ni lhun grub rig 'dzin te /
NK123(go)001:6975: yan lag bdun dang ldan pa'i ye shes gong ma'i gzhir gyur pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6977: sku lnga lhun grub rdo rje 'chang gi cha lugs 'dzin pa ste /
NK123(go)001:6978: drug pa'i rgyal tshab mdzad pa po gsang ba'i bdag po bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:6980: bdag don du rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK123(go)001:6981: zhes bya ba nang gi mngon byang gis shes sgrib
NK123(go)001:6982: phra ba snang gsum gyi dri ma sbyong zhing /
NK123(go)001:6983: gzhan don rjes thob la sangs rgyas dang cha 'dra bar 'gro ba'i don mdzad /
NK123(go)001:6984: sprul gzugs kyang mdzad pa bcu gnyis sogs mchog gi sprul sku dang phyogs mthun du ston /
NK123(go)001:6985: mngon shes kyi yul don ji snyed mkhyen pa'i yul rgyal ba nyid dang shas cher 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK123(go)001:6986: nam mkhas khyab tshad kyi don yang ci rigs par mdzad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:6987: de yang rgyu'i theg pa'i 'phags pa rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:6988: rnal 'byor chen po 'di nyid kyi rig pa 'dzin
NK123(go)001:6989: pa rnams mu tshod mtshungs kyang dgongs pa khyad par
NK123(go)001:6990: che ste / rgyu'i theg pa'i sa dang po dang rnam smin rig 'dzin gnyis dgongs pa mnyam la /
NK123(go)001:6991: rgyu'i sa brgyad pa dang tshe dbang /
NK123(go)001:6993: mi slob pa'i sa kun tu 'od dang lhun grub rig 'dzin gnyis dgongs pa mnyam pa'i phyir te /
NK123(go)001:6995: de yang dang po dang po dang //
NK123(go)001:6996: skal mnyam gnyis pa'i rig mchog de //
NK123(go)001:6997: brgyad pa'i sems dpar skal pa mnyam //
NK123(go)001:6998: gsum pa bcu dang skal mnyam mod //
NK123(go)001:6999: dgongs spyod rgya mtshos khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:7000: zhes gsungs te lam rang gi ngo bo thabs shes
NK123(go)001:7001: gnyis char nas 'og ma las khyad par du gyur
NK123(go)001:7002: pa'i phyir ro // 'di ni bka' sde zur pa'i bzhed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7003: kun mkhyen bla mas ni lam lnga ka rig 'dzin bzhis bsdus par bzhed do //
NK123(go)001:7004: gnyis pa rdzogs rim ni thabs kyi lam ste /
NK123(go)001:7006: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar ba'i thabs //
NK123(go)001:7008: gtso bor thabs kyi khyad par brtul zhugs kyi spyod
NK123(go)001:7009: pa rmad du byung ba'i sgo nas 'bras bu myur
NK123(go)001:7010: du 'grub par byed pas dug gsum ma spangs thog
NK123(go)001:7011: rdzis kyi spyod pa'i brtul zhugs gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:7012: lta ba'i gdeng dang ldan pas spyad na mi 'ching
NK123(go)001:7013: bar ma zad grol ba'i 'bras bu myur du thob
NK123(go)001:7014: la / de ltar ma yin pa zhig gis spyad
NK123(go)001:7015: na grol ba mi thob pa ma zad ngan song
NK123(go)001:7016: du ltung ba'i nyen chen po dang ldan pas mak+shi
NK123(go)001:7017: ga'i sbyor ba bzhin khe nyen che zhing /
NK123(go)001:7018: de lta bu'i thabs lam de la'ang dbye na /
NK123(go)001:7019: rim gsum las gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo /
NK123(go)001:7020: zhes pas steng sgo dang 'og sgo gnyis su yod pa las /
NK123(go)001:7021: dang po de la'ang thun khyad gnyis kyi /
NK123(go)001:7022: thun mong pa rang lus kyi dbus su rtsa ro
NK123(go)001:7023: rkyang dbu gsum srog shing gi tshul du gnas pa
NK123(go)001:7024: la / de las gyes pa'i rtsa 'khor spyi bor bde chen gyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab so gnyis /
NK123(go)001:7025: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug /
NK123(go)001:7026: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad /
NK123(go)001:7027: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab re bzhi /
NK123(go)001:7028: de'i 'og tu sbar bya me'i 'khor lo gru gsum ram gyis mtshan pa /
NK123(go)001:7029: de'i 'og tu sbar byed rlung gi gzhu'i dbyibs can
NK123(go)001:7030: yam gyi mtshan pa ste 'khor lo drug la brten
NK123(go)001:7031: nas srog rtsol gyi rkyen gyi a ham 'bar 'dzag
NK123(go)001:7032: gi sbyor bas spyi bo sogs rim bzhin 'khor lo
NK123(go)001:7033: bzhir bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa la bslab pa
NK123(go)001:7036: 'khor lo gsum gnyis srog shing gsum //
NK123(go)001:7037: me rlung 'gro bas nam mkha'i ba //
NK123(go)001:7038: bzho bas steng du rnam par grags //
NK123(go)001:7039: zhes pas bstan khyad par ba ni snying po'i rgyud
NK123(go)001:7040: le'u bcu gsum pa las gsungs pa ltar snying ga'i
NK123(go)001:7041: 'khor lo dwangs ma lnga 'dus la brten pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:7042: shes snying po thig le wam gyi dbyibs can la
NK123(go)001:7043: gnad du bsnun pa kun tu bzang po'i man ngag
NK123(go)001:7044: lte ba'i 'khor lo dbyings kyi yum lnga'i thig le
NK123(go)001:7045: a thung gi rnam pa la gnad du bsnun pa
NK123(go)001:7046: kun tu bzang mo'i man ngag /
NK123(go)001:7047: mgrin pa'i 'khor lo mkha' 'gro ma rngam ma'i thig
NK123(go)001:7048: le am gi rnam pa la gnad du bsnun pa
NK123(go)001:7049: sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag /
NK123(go)001:7050: spyi bo'i 'khor lo kun tu bzang po zla ba'i
NK123(go)001:7051: thig le ham gi rnam pa la gnad du bsnun
NK123(go)001:7052: pa khyab brdal chen po'i man ngag ste /
NK123(go)001:7054: snying ga'i 'khor lo bsgoms pa las byung ba'i ye
NK123(go)001:7055: shes spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ni chos
NK123(go)001:7056: sku / lte 'khor bsgoms pa'i ye shes rtog tshogs zhe gnyis ltar dag pa sprul sku /
NK123(go)001:7057: mgrin pa'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes ni longs sku /
NK123(go)001:7058: spyi bo'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes ni bde ba chen po'i sku ste /
NK123(go)001:7059: de'ang dwangs ma rnams 'khor lo bzhi'i lte ba'i dwangs
NK123(go)001:7060: ma g.yo byed dang bral ba'i 'od gsal la tshul
NK123(go)001:7061: thim pas bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK123(go)001:7062: shes chen po'i gcig dang du ma med pa'i chos
NK123(go)001:7063: nyid mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i 'od gsal 'char bar
NK123(go)001:7064: byed pa steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag go
NK123(go)001:7065: // de ltar bshad pa'i rtsa 'khor sogs ni rnal
NK123(go)001:7066: 'byor pa la nye bar mkho ba tsam zhig bstan
NK123(go)001:7067: // pa ste / gzhan du rags lus la gnas
NK123(go)001:7068: pa'i rtsa phran gyes pa ba spu'i grangs snyed yod
NK123(go)001:7069: // pa ste / pa gsungs shing / de rnams
NK123(go)001:7070: kyi chos nyid don dam ye shes kyi rtsa ni
NK123(go)001:7071: rang rig pa'i rnam par shar ba'i phyir tha mal
NK123(go)001:7072: gyi rtsa thams cad la khyab byed du bzhugs pas
NK123(go)001:7073: ye shes kyi dbu ma chen po zhes kyang grags
NK123(go)001:7074: // pa ste / pa gsungs shing / te /
NK123(go)001:7075: ye shes kyi rtsa de rnam pa thams cad pa
NK123(go)001:7076: yin pas kun rdzob kyi rtsa yang de'i rjes su
NK123(go)001:7077: // pa ste / pa gsungs shing / te /
NK123(go)001:7078: 'gro ba'i phyir / rnal 'byor pa'i sems kyi rnam
NK123(go)001:7079: pa gar gtad de dang 'dra bar tha mal pa'i
NK123(go)001:7080: rtsa rnams kyis kyang bya ba byed pas /
NK123(go)001:7081: gzhan rgyud sde tha dad las gsungs pa'i rtsa'i rnam
NK123(go)001:7082: bzhag mi 'dra ba rnams kyang mi 'gal ba'i gnad
NK123(go)001:7083: shes par bya'o // de bzhin du rlung gi rnam bzhag mi 'dra ba rnams kyang /
NK123(go)001:7084: ye shes kyi rlung rnam pa thams cad pa yin pas /
NK123(go)001:7085: de'i rjes su 'gro ba'i phyir gnad gcig tu 'du
NK123(go)001:7086: zhing thig le thams cad kyi rtsa ba chos nyid
NK123(go)001:7087: mi shig pa'i thig le ni rnam pa thams cad
NK123(go)001:7088: pa yin pas / thig le'i rnal 'byor ji snyed
NK123(go)001:7089: pa kun kyang dngos brgyud gang rung gi sgo nas
NK123(go)001:7090: yang dag pa'i lam du 'gro ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:7092: mkha' gsang gnyis la brten nas dbab bzung ldog khyab
NK123(go)001:7093: kyi sbyor bas skad cig la bde stong gnyis med
NK123(go)001:7094: kyi ye shes bskyed pa thabs lam cig car ba
NK123(go)001:7095: ste / de'ang sbyor ba'i dus kyi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:7096: dang po mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i yum brtsal ba
NK123(go)001:7097: rtsa brtags pa slong ba 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis
NK123(go)001:7098: bde ba rgyas pa sogs ni bsnyen pa'i yan lag
NK123(go)001:7099: / phan tshun brda' bzhis bskul te 'du shes gsum
NK123(go)001:7100: ldan gyi sgo nas phyag rgya bzhis gnyis med du
NK123(go)001:7101: rol ba nye bsnyen gyi yan lag /
NK123(go)001:7102: de ltar snyoms par zhugs nas rjes chags kyi rlung
NK123(go)001:7103: bskyed pas dmar cha 'bar ba des dkar cha zhu
NK123(go)001:7104: ba yas 'bab kyi 'gros kyi phyin pa las 'khor
NK123(go)001:7105: lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i rim pas rdo rje nor bu'i
NK123(go)001:7106: rtser 'dzag med du bzung bas dngos po lhan cig
NK123(go)001:7107: skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong ba sgrub pa'i
NK123(go)001:7108: yan lag / nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blangs te
NK123(go)001:7109: bzlog pa'i sbyor bas gyen du drangs te 'khor lo
NK123(go)001:7110: bzhi'i gnas so sor mas brten gyi dga' bzhi nyams
NK123(go)001:7111: su myong mthar byang sems rtsa gnas thams cad du
NK123(go)001:7112: dgram pa'i sbyor bas rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK123(go)001:7113: ye shes nyams su myong ba ni /
NK123(go)001:7114: sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag ste 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag go //
NK123(go)001:7116: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7117: lus ri rgyal ltar mi g.yo /
NK123(go)001:7118: ngag lkugs pa ltar mi brjod /
NK123(go)001:7119: sems nam mkha' ltar mi rtog pa chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du 'jog pas /
NK123(go)001:7120: gang yid la mi byed pa'i stong pa ni kun
NK123(go)001:7121: tu bzang mo chos nyid don gyi ye shes yin
NK123(go)001:7122: la / rang gsal rig pa gsal dwangs phyed pa'i
NK123(go)001:7123: snang cha ni kun tu bzang po chos sku gzhi
NK123(go)001:7124: la / ye shes te / de gnyis dbyer med
NK123(go)001:7125: pa rig pa phyi nang bar med du phyam gdal
NK123(go)001:7126: ba ni dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kun bzang
NK123(go)001:7127: yab yum zung 'jug gnyug ma'i sems rdzogs pa chen
NK123(go)001:7128: la / ye shes te / po zhes bya'o // spyod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7129: thabs la mkhas pa'i gdeng gis zin pas 'khor ba'i chos ci la'ang ma chags par spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7131: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK123(go)001:7132: ta na dang ni ga na dang /
NK123(go)001:7133: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga po la //
NK123(go)001:7134: thabs chen lta ba'i spyod pa spyad //
NK123(go)001:7137: spyir lus ngag yid gsum yongs su dag par bya ba yin la /
NK123(go)001:7138: de yang dus tshod dang 'brel bar bslab ste /
NK123(go)001:7139: las dang po pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin la
NK123(go)001:7140: brtan pa ma thob pas dge sbyong gzhon nu'i spyod
NK123(go)001:7141: pa ltar bag dang ldan pas gzab pa lhur len
NK123(go)001:7142: pa ste / rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK123(go)001:7143: brtan pa ma thob bar du ni //
NK123(go)001:7144: kha na ma tho rdul med cing //
NK123(go)001:7145: sdom pa gsum la gnas par bya //
NK123(go)001:7147: de'ang mnyam gzhag gi rtogs pa bag ldan du bsring
NK123(go)001:7148: zhing thun mtshams su rjes thob kyi bya ba chos
NK123(go)001:7149: spyod bcu la sogs pa sgrub pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7150: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa cung zad thob nas
NK123(go)001:7151: mnyam rjes bsre bar nus pa na rtog pa rkyen
NK123(go)001:7152: thub tu byed pa smyon pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod
NK123(go)001:7153: pa dang / brtan pa cher thob nas rtogs pa
NK123(go)001:7154: la bri gang med pa na gzhan phan kho na
NK123(go)001:7155: la bslab pa rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi spyod pa
NK123(go)001:7156: lta bu ste spyod tshul gsum mo //
NK123(go)001:7157: bye brag tu thabs lam brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7158: grol lam bag yod kyi spyod pa gnyis su bshad cing /
NK123(go)001:7160: dang po lta ba gtan 'bebs pa'i dus su dang brtson gyi spyod pa /
NK123(go)001:7161: stong chen gyi dus su shes rab dang mthun pa /
NK123(go)001:7162: snying rje sgyu ma'i skabs su thabs dang mthun pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7163: phyag rgya gcig pa'i skabs su phyogs cig pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7164: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi skabs su spros pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7165: tshogs sgrub kyi skabs su tshogs kyi spyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7166: zag med la bslab pa'i rig 'dzin bzhi'i skabs su
NK123(go)001:7167: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyod pa ste rim gyis pa'i spyod
NK123(go)001:7168: pa bdun dang / blang dor med pa rmad du
NK123(go)001:7169: byung ba cig car ba'i spyod pa dang brgyad do
NK123(go)001:7171: tshe 'adi'am bar dor sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid mngon du byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7173: 'di ni bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK123(go)001:7174: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK123(go)001:7175: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par brgyan //
NK123(go)001:7179: yang na lus ni spang ma thag /
NK123(go)001:7180: brtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub //
NK123(go)001:7182: de yang rgyu rgyud bde gshegs snying po zab gsal
NK123(go)001:7183: gnyis med kyi ye shes e wam zung 'jug lhan
NK123(go)001:7184: skyes bde ba chen po gdod ma nas rang chas
NK123(go)001:7185: su bzhugs pa dang de las shar ba'i snang spyod
NK123(go)001:7186: thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor chen
NK123(go)001:7187: por ye nas gnas pa'i sbyang gzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:7188: med snang glo bur gyi dri ma spyi dang khyad
NK123(go)001:7189: par 'pho sgrib phra ba dang bcas pa ni sbyang
NK123(go)001:7190: bya / rim gnyis kyi bsdus pa'i lam rnams ni sbyong byed /
NK123(go)001:7191: de ltar lam gyis dri ma mtha' dag sbyangs pa
NK123(go)001:7192: las gzhi la ji ltar yod pa'i yon tan rnams
NK123(go)001:7193: mngon gyur mthar thug pa ni sbyangs 'bras te /
NK123(go)001:7195: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur bzod //
NK123(go)001:7199: 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsung thugs //
NK123(go)001:7200: yon tan phrin las rnam pa lnga //
NK123(go)001:7201: de yang skabs kyi lnga lnga ste //
NK123(go)001:7203: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga re re
NK123(go)001:7204: la'ang lnga lngar phye bas 'bras chos nyi shu rtsa
NK123(go)001:7205: lngar 'gyur te / de la sku lnga ni /
NK123(go)001:7212: chos sku brjod med don gyi gsung //
NK123(go)001:7213: longs sku dgongs pa brda' yi gsungs //
NK123(go)001:7214: sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung //
NK123(go)001:7215: mngon byang rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung /
NK123(go)001:7216: dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung dang lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:7218: chos sku'i thugs chos dbyings ye shes /
NK123(go)001:7219: longs sku'i thugs mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK123(go)001:7220: sprul sku'i thugs bya grub ye shes /
NK123(go)001:7221: mngon byang thugs me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK123(go)001:7222: rdo rje'i thugs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:7224: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams /
NK123(go)001:7225: rgya tshad dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK123(go)001:7228: dgyes dgur spyod pa'i longs spyod lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:7229: phrin las lnga ni zhi ba /
NK123(go)001:7233: lhun gyis grub pa ste lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:7236: mdzad pa phrin las dang gsum du 'du ste /
NK123(go)001:7239: dbyings rnam dag gi thog tu rig pa'i ye shes
NK123(go)001:7240: sgrib pa med par grol bas zung 'jug sku gsum
NK123(go)001:7241: ye rdzogs mtshan 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad dang
NK123(go)001:7242: bral ba'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa chos sku /
NK123(go)001:7243: de las ma g.yos bzhin du sa bcu rgyun mtha'
NK123(go)001:7244: la bzhugs pa'i byang sems rnams la mtshan dpe'i rnam
NK123(go)001:7245: par snang ba'i gzugs brnyan longs sku /
NK123(go)001:7246: so skye rnams la so so'i mos pa dang mthun par mchog gi sprul sku dang /
NK123(go)001:7247: bzo dang skye ba sogs gang la gang mtshams par
NK123(go)001:7248: sangs rgyas kyi gzugs brnyan ci rigs su snang ba
NK123(go)001:7251: de'i steng du sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres par
NK123(go)001:7252: snang ba'i ldog cha nas mngon byang dang sku gsum
NK123(go)001:7253: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i
NK123(go)001:7254: sku ste gnyis po brnan pas sku lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:7256: de'i tshe tshogs brgyad gnas su dag pa'i ye shes lnga ste /
NK123(go)001:7257: kun gzhi 'byed pa med pa'i cha nas de nyid
NK123(go)001:7258: gnas su dag pa cir yang mi dmigs pas spros
NK123(go)001:7259: pa'i mtha' thams cad las 'das pa chos dbyings ye
NK123(go)001:7260: shes / kun gzhi'i rnam shes gsal la mi rtog
NK123(go)001:7261: pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag pa me
NK123(go)001:7262: long ngos gnyis pa ltar rang gzhan gyi chos rnams
NK123(go)001:7263: gsal la spu ris 'byed par mi mdzad pa me
NK123(go)001:7265: nyon yid kyis phyi nang gi chos rnams la blang
NK123(go)001:7266: dor byed pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag
NK123(go)001:7267: pa 'khor 'das bzang ngan med par mnyam nyid du
NK123(go)001:7268: gzigs pas srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa
NK123(go)001:7270: rnam shes drug 'gag ma thag pa'i yid kyis dpyad
NK123(go)001:7271: pa med par rtogs pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas
NK123(go)001:7272: su dag pa chos can ma lus pa mngon sum
NK123(go)001:7273: du ma 'dres par yongs su sa ler gzigs pa
NK123(go)001:7274: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK123(go)001:7275: sgo lnga'i rnam shes kyi bya ba thams cad sgrub
NK123(go)001:7276: pa'i cha nas de nyid gnas su dag pa 'gro
NK123(go)001:7277: ba'i don mdzad pa la thog pa med pa'i phrin
NK123(go)001:7278: las 'jug pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te
NK123(go)001:7279: lnga'o // de dag kyang chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK123(go)001:7280: phyi ma bzhi po ji snyed pa'i ye shes su 'du bas na ye shes gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:7282: de ltar nyon shes kyis bsdus pa'i med snang glo
NK123(go)001:7283: bur gyi sgrib gnyis bag chags snang gsum gyi dri
NK123(go)001:7284: ma dang bcas pa mtha' dag spangs shing /
NK123(go)001:7285: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis shes
NK123(go)001:7286: bya'i chos thams cad mngon sum du gzigs pa'i sgo
NK123(go)001:7287: nas spangs rtogs kyi yon tan thams cad mthar phyin
NK123(go)001:7288: zhing / de'i mthu las gdul bya so so'i skal
NK123(go)001:7289: ba dang mtshams par zhi sogs gang la gang gis
NK123(go)001:7290: ji ltar 'dul ba'i phrin las kyi sgo mtha' yas
NK123(go)001:7291: pa dus las yol ba med la 'bad rtsol med
NK123(go)001:7292: par lhun gyis grub pa ni nam mkha' ji srid
NK123(go)001:7293: pa de srid du rgya che zhing rgyun mi 'chad
NK123(go)001:7294: par 'byung ba ste zhib par gzhan du shes par
NK123(go)001:7295: zhing / bya la / zhar byung du mdo sngags
NK123(go)001:7296: gnyis kyi sangs rgyas khyad par yod med dpyad na
NK123(go)001:7297: zhing / bya la / / kun mkhyen chos kyi
NK123(go)001:7298: rgyal po sogs ni mthar thug rigs gcig dang theg
NK123(go)001:7299: pa gcig tu grub pa'i phyir de gnyis la khyad
NK123(go)001:7301: rgyal ba g.yung ston pa ni rgyu 'bras theg pa'i
NK123(go)001:7302: khyad par dang blo gros rnam 'byed kyi ched du
NK123(go)001:7303: de gnyis la khyad par 'di ltar mdzad de chos
NK123(go)001:7306: byin rlabs kyi khyad par dang gsum las /
NK123(go)001:7308: mtshan nyid theg pa'i chos sku spros pa dang bral ba'i stong nyid nam mkha' lta bu yin la /
NK123(go)001:7309: sngags kyi chos sku ni dbyings dang ye shes kyi rang bzhin snang stong zung du 'jug pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7311: mtshan nyid theg pa'i chos sku stong pa'i mthar lhung la /
NK123(go)001:7312: sngags kyi chos sku ni snang stong gnyis su med pas rtag chad kyi mthar ma lhung ba'o //
NK123(go)001:7314: mtshan nyid kyi chos sku las byin rlabs gzugs sku gnyis las mi 'char la /
NK123(go)001:7315: sngags kyi chos sku ni dbyings dang ye shes snang
NK123(go)001:7316: stong zung du 'jug pa'i byin rlabs las sku lnga
NK123(go)001:7317: la sogs pa ci rigs par 'char ro //
NK123(go)001:7318: gzugs sku gnyis kyi khyad par yang 'di ltar yod
NK123(go)001:7319: de rgyu mtshan nyid kyi gzugs sku gnyis rgyu rkyen
NK123(go)001:7321: sngags kyi gzugs sku ni rgyu dang rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7322: rgyu'i gzugs sku skye 'jigs can yin la /
NK123(go)001:7323: sngags kyi gzugs sku skye 'jigs dang bral ba'o //
NK123(go)001:7324: bye brag tu longs sku'i khyad par la'ang gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:7325: longs su spyod bya'i khyad par /
NK123(go)001:7326: mtshan nyid theg pa'i longs skus dkar phyogs la longs spyod pa las nag po'i phyogs la mi spyod /
NK123(go)001:7329: sbyong byed thabs kyi khyad par yang /
NK123(go)001:7330: mtshan nyid theg par nag po'i phyogs la longs spyod pa'i thabs med /
NK123(go)001:7331: sngags la dkar nag gnyis kar longs spyod pa'i thabs yod pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:7332: sprul sku la'ang khyad par gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:7333: gdul bya yul gyi khyad par ni /
NK123(go)001:7334: mtshan nyid theg pa'i sprul skus dkar phyogs kyi gdul
NK123(go)001:7335: bya 'dul ba las nag phyogs kyi gdul bya mi
NK123(go)001:7336: 'dul / sngags kyi sprul sku'i gdul bya la phyogs ris med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7337: 'dul byed thabs kyi khyad par yang /
NK123(go)001:7338: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi sprul sku la nag phyogs 'dul ba'i thabs med /
NK123(go)001:7340: gdul bya dkar nag gi phyogs gnyis ka 'dul ba'i thabs dang ldan pa rnams su bzhed /
NK123(go)001:7341: gzhan yang chos sku la mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i
NK123(go)001:7342: bde ba chen pos khyad par du byas pa dang
NK123(go)001:7343: / longs sku nges pa lnga ldan kyang zhi ba
NK123(go)001:7344: dang ston 'khor thams cad rang snang bzhi'i 'od gsal
NK123(go)001:7345: chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i snang cha las gzhan
NK123(go)001:7346: snang gi bsdus pa min pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7347: sprul sku yang 'dul ba rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas
NK123(go)001:7348: phrin las rnam pa bzhi rab 'byams ci yang rung
NK123(go)001:7349: ba la mnga' dbang bsgyur nas gdul bya'i don mdzad
NK123(go)001:7350: pa la dbang 'byor ba sogs khyar par gzhan yang
NK123(go)001:7351: yod par phyis kyi mkhas chen dag bzhed do //
NK123(go)001:7352: der ma zad kun mkhyen d+harma sh+r+ais /
NK123(go)001:7353: dbu ma'i lam gyis thob pa'i sa dang pos mthong lam gyi go chod mod /
NK123(go)001:7354: 'on kyang de rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes tsam yin pas /
NK123(go)001:7355: sngags bla med kyi rdzogs rim gyis thob pa'i mthong lam dang khyad che ste /
NK123(go)001:7356: 'di la sa dang po na kha sbyor yan lag
NK123(go)001:7357: bdun ldan rjes mthun pa zhig yod pa'i phyir ro
NK123(go)001:7359: gnyis pa gang zag dbang po rab kyi 'bring /
NK123(go)001:7360: 'dod chags shas che ba dang sems gnas pa la
NK123(go)001:7361: dga' ba la dgongs nas gsungs pa lung a nu
NK123(go)001:7364: lung a nu yo ga ni chos thams cad kyi lam lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:7365: zhes gsungs pas rnal 'byor chen po dang shin tu
NK123(go)001:7366: rnal 'byor gnyis mtshams sbyor bar byed pas lam lta
NK123(go)001:7373: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten
NK123(go)001:7374: pa'i sgo nas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK123(go)001:7375: pa'i don rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba thob
NK123(go)001:7378: a nu yo ga ste shes rab rjes chags kyi
NK123(go)001:7379: lam gtso bor ston pa'i phyir rjes su rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:7380: ro // dbye ba la drug las /
NK123(go)001:7382: a nu'i dkyil 'khor du phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bcu /
NK123(go)001:7383: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig /
NK123(go)001:7384: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bcu gsum /
NK123(go)001:7385: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis bcas phyi nang
NK123(go)001:7386: sgrub gsang bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang chog sum cu rtsa
NK123(go)001:7388: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK123(go)001:7389: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK123(go)001:7390: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK123(go)001:7391: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:7393: de la'ang rgyud dang man ngag ltar bskur tshul gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:7394: rang bzhin gyi snod du gyur pa zab mo'i don
NK123(go)001:7395: la mos pa'i slob ma khyad par can la mdo
NK123(go)001:7396: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du rgyud kyi dngos bstan ltar
NK123(go)001:7397: chu bo bzhi rdzogs kyi dbang sum cu rtsa drug
NK123(go)001:7398: bskur ba dang / sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa
NK123(go)001:7399: rgya che ba la mos pa'i slob ma thun mong
NK123(go)001:7400: pa la mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs yan lag gi
NK123(go)001:7401: dkyil 'khor so sor phye nas bde ba gsal mdzad
NK123(go)001:7402: kyi las tho ltar theg pa thams cad 'dus pa'i
NK123(go)001:7403: mdo dbang rtsa ba so drug las yan lag rags
NK123(go)001:7404: pa brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur ba
NK123(go)001:7405: bskur ba dang / gnyis las / chos kyi rgyal
NK123(go)001:7406: po smin gling pa yab sras sogs kyi phyag bzhes
NK123(go)001:7407: su rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gnyis 'dor len
NK123(go)001:7408: gyi gnad kyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba mdzad
NK123(go)001:7409: bskur ba dang / gnyis las / cing / de ltar mdzad pas gnas skabs su bya sla zhing /
NK123(go)001:7410: brgyud nas lugs gnyis gcig gis gcig mi nub par
NK123(go)001:7411: chabs gcig tu 'phel ba'i dgos pa khyad par can
NK123(go)001:7412: yod do // lugs de gnyis kas yo ga bzhi rdzogs dang /
NK123(go)001:7413: theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa la 'dra ba yin te /
NK123(go)001:7415: bcu yis byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:7416: bcu gcig gsang ba nang pa 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:7417: bcu gsum bla ma chen por grags //
NK123(go)001:7418: gnyis kyis theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7419: zhes gsungs la des na mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs
NK123(go)001:7420: de yang theg brgyad dgos kyi cho ga so so
NK123(go)001:7421: nas btus te spyi'i cho gar byas pa ni ma
NK123(go)001:7422: yin gyi / 'dir mdo rang lugs kyi sa dang
NK123(go)001:7423: po 'gyur ba ma nges pa nas sa bcu pa
NK123(go)001:7424: rdzogs pa ci chib kyi bar non par bya ba'i
NK123(go)001:7425: ched du lha mi nas brtsams te a nu rang
NK123(go)001:7426: lugs kyi rdzogs rim mthar thug pa a ti'i bar
NK123(go)001:7427: la bya spyod so sor bgrang bas dbang rim bcu
NK123(go)001:7428: byung ba de nyid bya spyod gcig tu bsdus nas
NK123(go)001:7429: theg dgu dang tshul 'dra bas theg dgu'i dbang zhes
NK123(go)001:7430: grags shing de lta bu'i lam stegs kyi theg pa
NK123(go)001:7431: rnams so so'i lam dang 'dra rung du byung kyang
NK123(go)001:7432: yin gyi / / don la sngags kyi thabs mkhas
NK123(go)001:7433: kyis zin pas theg pa rang rang gi spangs thob
NK123(go)001:7434: dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan de dang de skye ba'i
NK123(go)001:7435: myur lam du'ang 'gro ba yin zhes gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:7437: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:7439: a nu dbyer med sa 'dod pa //
NK123(go)001:7440: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK123(go)001:7443: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis te //
NK123(go)001:7445: skye med dbyings nyid ye shes te //
NK123(go)001:7446: ye shes rig pa dbyings nyid tshul //
NK123(go)001:7447: gnyis med rol pa bde ba che //
NK123(go)001:7448: rim par 'jug pa ma yin te //
NK123(go)001:7449: snang srid phyag rgya thams cad la //
NK123(go)001:7450: chu la nya ldang ji bzhin du //
NK123(go)001:7451: thugs phrad snang srid phyag rgya che //
NK123(go)001:7454: dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid
NK123(go)001:7455: can dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i rtsa ba
NK123(go)001:7456: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du chos thams cad
NK123(go)001:7457: ye gdod ma nas sangs rgyas pa nyid de /
NK123(go)001:7459: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang gi sems kyi rtsal snang du 'du zhing /
NK123(go)001:7460: sems de nyid skye med spros pa'i mtha' thams cad
NK123(go)001:7461: dang bral ba'i dbyings sam rang bzhin yum kun tu
NK123(go)001:7462: bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7463: ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:7465: sems las byung ba stong nyid pas /
NK123(go)001:7466: de las byung ba thams cad stong /
NK123(go)001:7468: skye med de nyid thams cad du ma 'gag par
NK123(go)001:7469: rang snang ris med kun khyab tu shar ba ni
NK123(go)001:7470: ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin lhun grub
NK123(go)001:7473: brtags na ma mthong cir yang snang ba nyid //
NK123(go)001:7475: de gnyis kyang ngo bo tha mi dad par zung 'jug tu gnas pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7476: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba chen po ste /
NK123(go)001:7477: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK123(go)001:7479: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK123(go)001:7480: snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa /
NK123(go)001:7481: gnyis kyi ngo bo las grol ba /
NK123(go)001:7482: dbu mar mi dmigs pa gang yin pa de kho na nyid do //
NK123(go)001:7485: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i
NK123(go)001:7486: rang bzhin rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK123(go)001:7487: du ye nas sangs rgyas par blta ba ste /
NK123(go)001:7489: thams cad de nyid ro gcig pas //
NK123(go)001:7490: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK123(go)001:7491: skye 'gags med pa'i snying po yin //
NK123(go)001:7492: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK123(go)001:7493: ye nas sgrub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK123(go)001:7496: snang srid bzang mo'i mkha' klong las //
NK123(go)001:7497: ma bskyed dkyil 'khor kun bzang shar //
NK123(go)001:7498: shar ba nyid na shar ba med //
NK123(go)001:7499: yab yum sras bcas bde chen mo //
NK123(go)001:7502: de'ang kun tu bzang po'i rol pa ma 'gags pa'i rtsal lha skur 'char ba 'dod de /
NK123(go)001:7504: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK123(go)001:7505: phyi nang gasalanga ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di //
NK123(go)001:7506: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK123(go)001:7509: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni /
NK123(go)001:7510: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK123(go)001:7511: lha dang lha mo'i dkyir 'khor du //
NK123(go)001:7512: ma skyes rdzogs pa'i tshul du 'dod //
NK123(go)001:7516: gzhi 'dzin pa ni dam tshig ste //
NK123(go)001:7517: sgo gsum sdom par gnas pa'i don //
NK123(go)001:7518: rtsa ba yan lag la sogs pa'i //
NK123(go)001:7519: bsrung dang sgrub pa de nyid do //
NK123(go)001:7520: zhes pas sgo gsum gyis rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK123(go)001:7521: la sogs pa'i dam tshig bsrung zhing bsgrub par bya
NK123(go)001:7522: ba rnams te / de'ang dbye na /
NK123(go)001:7523: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK123(go)001:7524: thun mong gi nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK123(go)001:7531: lta ba'i dam tshig ste rnam grangs dgu spyi mdo'i le'u re drug par gsungs te /
NK123(go)001:7532: de la dang po gal mdo nges pa'i gzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:7533: lus 1dang ngag 2dang yid 3dang spyod 4yul yongs su
NK123(go)001:7534: dag pa ste bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs dang sems
NK123(go)001:7535: can gyi yid kyis ma khrel bar bya'o //
NK123(go)001:7536: gnyis pa thun mong nyer brgyad ni /
NK123(go)001:7537: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i dam tshig gsum /
NK123(go)001:7543: gong bshad rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig nyer brgyad dang mthun no //
NK123(go)001:7544: gsum pa lhag pa'i bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:7545: don dam par dam tshig gi ngo bo la 'da' nyams dang bral bas bsrung mtshams med pa 1dang /
NK123(go)001:7546: rnam pa gzung 'dzin las 'das pas phyal 2ba ste phyal ler khyab pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7547: de dag sems nyid gcig 3pa'i dbyings su 'dus pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7548: chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang las ma
NK123(go)001:7549: g.yos na sdom pa dam tshig thams cad rang bzhin
NK123(go)001:7550: gyis rnam par dag cing lhun gyis grub pa ste
NK123(go)001:7551: gnas lugs rtogs pa rab kyi dam tshig go //
