NK123(go)001:7552: bzhi pa brtul zhugs nyer gsum ni /
NK123(go)001:7553: wa dang cang shes gyi ling sogs kyi dpes bstan
NK123(go)001:7554: pa'i don gnubs chen sogs kyis bkral ba ltar na
NK123(go)001:7555: / wa gal la zin na srog la mi lta bar lag pa bcad nas 'gro ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7556: rnal 'byor pas srog la babs kyang dam tshig bsrung ba ste /
NK123(go)001:7557: mi mthun phyogs brtul zhing dam tshig gi stobs la zhugs pa'i thabs so //
NK123(go)001:7558: cang 2shes rtas thams cad shes shing myur mgyogs kyis sa thams cad yud tsam gyis bskor ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7559: shes rab kyis shes bya spyi dang rang gi mtshan
NK123(go)001:7560: nyid thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7561: so // gyi ling rtsal 3che bas cir yang 'gyur
NK123(go)001:7562: ba ltar lus gus pas gar dang phyag rgya 'khrul
NK123(go)001:7563: 'khor la brtson pa le lo gzhom pa'i brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7564: so // so // glang 4chen chang gi myos pas
NK123(go)001:7565: dgra zin mi 'byed par gang snang gzhom pa ltar
NK123(go)001:7567: shes pas lta spyod kyi dgra bzhi bcom pa'i spyod
NK123(go)001:7568: so // so // / pa'o // stag 5dpa' brtul za byed kyi sems gtum rngam 'khrugs pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7569: gnas lugs rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dpa' bo'i brtul zhugs stobs dang ldan cing /
NK123(go)001:7570: spyod pa'i brtul zhugs kyis zhing bcu sgrol ba za
NK123(go)001:7571: byed gtum rngam 'khrugs pa'i tshul gdul bya dang mthun
NK123(go)001:7572: pa ste ru tra bsgral nas gnas spar ba lta
NK123(go)001:7573: bu'i spyod pa'o // khyung chen 6nam mkhar lding bas
NK123(go)001:7574: gnam 'phang rtsol med du gcod cing ma bltas par
NK123(go)001:7576: lta bas dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med du rtogs pas rtsol ba med pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7577: dom gyis gang 7la dmigs pa the tshom med par 'jig cing 'bral bar byed pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7578: rnal 'byor lta spyod kyi gdings dang ldan pas the
NK123(go)001:7579: tshom med par mngon spyod kyi las la sbyor ba'i
NK123(go)001:7580: brtul zhugs so // rgya mtsho'i 8gting gi gser 'gyur ba mang pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7581: zab don gsang thub cing nyams su len pa la blo mi ldog par brtan pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7582: lkug pa gti mug can gyis blang dor mi 'byed pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7583: 'khor 'das sogs ris su mi 'byed pa'i mnyam bzhag
NK123(go)001:7584: gis bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab mthar phyin pa'i
NK123(go)001:7585: brtul zhugs so // ri rab 10mi g.yo ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7586: bla ma dang grogs la dad gus mi 'gyur ba
NK123(go)001:7587: dang ting nge 'dzin bying rgod kyis mi g.yo ba'i
NK123(go)001:7588: gnyen po brten pa'i thabs kyi brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7589: nam mkha' 11yangs la rgya che bas spang len med par ci'ang shang ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7590: rnal 'byor pa mched kyi nang du shong yangs che
NK123(go)001:7591: ba dang bdag nyid chen po'i lta spyod 'di'i nang
NK123(go)001:7592: du 'khor 'das dang theg pa gang yang ma shong
NK123(go)001:7593: ba med par spyod pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7594: thog 12gang la bab kyang 'joms pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7595: rnal 'byor pa drag po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis dgra
NK123(go)001:7596: bgegs gang yang thogs med du 'joms pa'i brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7597: so // lag na rdo rjes log lta can thams cad 'joms pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7598: rnal 'byor pas khro bo bsgoms nas bar du gcod
NK123(go)001:7599: pa the tshom med par 'joms pa'i brtul zhugs so
NK123(go)001:7600: // bya rog gi dgra dang gzan gnyis dus gcig tu mig gis bsrung ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7601: phyi nang gi dam tshig 'di dag rgyun du spang
NK123(go)001:7602: len dus gcig tu brtson pa'i thabs kyi brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7603: so // glang 15chen chu rab bde ba dang mi
NK123(go)001:7604: bde ba la ltos pa med par 'jug pa ltar
NK123(go)001:7605: so // / bdag nyid chen po'i lta spyod gding
NK123(go)001:7606: dang ldan pas spang blang gnyis med du spyod pa'am
NK123(go)001:7607: so // / / gdul bya mi 'dam par phrin las bzhi'i las mdzad pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7608: seng ge grogs 16med gcig pur sdod pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7609: lta spyod mi mthun pa'i grogs spangs nas gcig pur
NK123(go)001:7610: dgon par gnas pas lta sgom skyod pa'i brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7611: so // ngang pa 17pho mo mi 'bral bar 'grogs pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7612: sems can la snying brtse bas thar pa'i bde ba
NK123(go)001:7613: la 'god pa'i thabs dang mi 'bral bar 'grogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:7614: brtul zhugs so // sgyu 18ma mkhan gyis byas pa'i gzugs brnyan ltar /
NK123(go)001:7615: phung khams skye mched rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sgyu ma
NK123(go)001:7616: lta bur yin par shes nas de ltar sgom zhing
NK123(go)001:7617: bstan pa ni thabs mkhas kyis 'drid pa'i brtul zhugs
NK123(go)001:7618: so // phag 19gis gtsang dme med par thams cad bza' ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7619: dam rdzas lnga blang dor med par mnyam pa nyid du spyod pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7620: ce spyang 20thogs pa med par gsod la dga' ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7621: lta spyod goms pa'i thugs rjes log lta can rtogs
NK123(go)001:7622: pas bsgral zhing rnam shes zag med la bkod pas
NK123(go)001:7623: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i thabs kyi brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7624: glog 21gis thams cad dus gcig myur du gsal ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7625: lam nyams su blang bas rang don myur du 'grub par brtson pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7626: bya 22rgod tshul khrims srog gcod la 'dzem pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:7627: barlangasa spyod kyi brtul zhugs theg pa gzhan la mi
NK123(go)001:7628: 'tshoms pa ltar snang yang 'dir bdag nyid chen po'i
NK123(go)001:7629: tshul du spyod na dam tshig sbyong zhing nyes pa
NK123(go)001:7631: rgyal 23po bag dang ldan pas rgyal sa gnon cing rang las 'khor gces par skyong ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:7632: dbyings ye shes dbyer med bde ba chen por rtogs
NK123(go)001:7633: goms kyi thabs la 'bad pa'i rnal 'byor pas brtul
NK123(go)001:7634: zhugs kyi rgyal sa gnon cing chos thams cad rang
NK123(go)001:7635: las mi gzhan par rtogs pas 'gro ba skyong zhing
NK123(go)001:7636: nyes pa rang sar dag pa'i brtul zhugs so //
NK123(go)001:7637: de rnams kyang bdag don dang gzhan don dang gnyis
NK123(go)001:7638: ka'i don blo rab cig char bas nyams su len
NK123(go)001:7639: byar gsungs so // lnga pa sgrub pa'i nyi shu ni /
NK123(go)001:7640: mi shig pa ni seng ge ste /
NK123(go)001:7641: gcan gzan rgyal po'i khri mi gzhig /
NK123(go)001:7642: ces sogs kyis bstan pa'i don /
NK123(go)001:7644: gcan gzan rgyal po'i khri mi gzhig /
NK123(go)001:7645: ces sogs brda yis bstan pa dang gnad gcig ste /
NK123(go)001:7646: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la mi 1bsdo /
NK123(go)001:7649: dkon mchog 4dang bla ma'i dkor la mi 'bag cing chang myos par mi 'thung /
NK123(go)001:7651: mtshan dang 6mi ldan pa'i gzung ma mi brten /
NK123(go)001:7652: mtshan nyid dang mi ldan 7pa'i dam rdzas mi brten /
NK123(go)001:7653: mkhas pa'i yon tan 8la mi smod /
NK123(go)001:7654: snod min la 9gsang chos mi ston /
NK123(go)001:7655: mtshan ldan gyi gzungs 10ma dang snod ldan gyi slob ma mi spang /
NK123(go)001:7656: don bde stong dang rtags 11yab yum mi 'bral /
NK123(go)001:7657: mched lcam la kyal 12kha tsam du'ang nang 'thab mi byed /
NK123(go)001:7658: gzhan gyis 13spyad pa'i lhag mi spyod /
NK123(go)001:7660: rang gzhan gyis sgrub 15pa'i mtshams mi 'bral /
NK123(go)001:7661: ting nge 'dzin bying rgod kyi dbang 16du mi gtong /
NK123(go)001:7662: bzlas pa 17dang cho ga mi tshig gis bar mi gcod /
NK123(go)001:7663: dbang rtags kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' 18zhing brda' mi brjed par bya ba /
NK123(go)001:7664: rnal 'byor pa'i dkyil 'khor mi dkrug 19cing skye bo'i mthu bzlog mi byed pa /
NK123(go)001:7665: slob dpon gtsug tu 'khur ba 20las nyams par mi bya ba rnams so //
NK123(go)001:7666: drug pa spyod lam rgyun gyi bzhi ni /
NK123(go)001:7667: rdo rje gor phur t+wam chen sogs kyis bstan pa'i don /
NK123(go)001:7668: bsam gtan gyi srog gcod pa gnyis spang 1ba dang /
NK123(go)001:7672: bdun pa bdud lnga spang ba ni /
NK123(go)001:7673: rnal 'byor spyod pa la rgyun gyi bar du gcod pa'i bdud rnam par rtog 1pa /
NK123(go)001:7678: brgyad pa dgra bzhi gzhom pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7679: lta sgom spyod gsum bcos ma rang gar 1shor ba'i dgra /
NK123(go)001:7680: lta ba dman la 2spyod pa rtsing ba 'chal ba'i dgra /
NK123(go)001:7681: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa ltung ba'i dgra /
NK123(go)001:7682: tshod yod le los 4'bras bu 'phrog pa'i dgra ste bzhi po de gzhom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7683: dgu pa lta ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK123(go)001:7684: snod rnam par dag pa 'og min gyi zhing /
NK123(go)001:7685: 'dod yon rnam par dag pa mchod pa'i yo byad /
NK123(go)001:7686: 'khor ba rnam par dag pa lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK123(go)001:7687: nyon mongs rnam par dag pa ye shes chen por rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7688: de dag kyang bsdu na bsrung mtshams med par chos nyid cig char ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK123(go)001:7689: bsrung mtshams yod pa snying rje'i dam tshig rim gyis pa'i sdom pa gnyis su 'du ste /
NK123(go)001:7691: bsrung bya bsrung du med pa ni //
NK123(go)001:7692: chos nyid dam tshig dam pa yin //
NK123(go)001:7694: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK123(go)001:7695: kun gyi thun mong ma yin phyir //
NK123(go)001:7696: mos pa chung ngu thams cad la //
NK123(go)001:7697: bsrung ba'i mtshams dag bzung bar byas //
NK123(go)001:7700: spyir rtogs bya gzhi dang rtogs byed kyi lam gnyis ka rnal 'byor gsum du bsdu nas bshad de /
NK123(go)001:7703: de bas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam pa gang zhe na /
NK123(go)001:7704: 'di ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad kyi rnam pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7705: rnal 'byor gsum gyis yongs su 'brel ba ste /
NK123(go)001:7708: bya ba byed pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK123(go)001:7709: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK123(go)001:7712: rkyen gyi rnal 'byor dang 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor gsum du rtsa rgyud thun 'dus rig par gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:7713: rtsa bshad kyi rgyud de gnyis kyi dgongs don gcig tu bsdus nas bstan pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7715: kun bzang thugs rjes 'gro don du //
NK123(go)001:7716: theg pa gsum snang 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK123(go)001:7717: don dam nges pa'i theg pa las //
NK123(go)001:7718: gsang sgo mtshon pa'i mdo rgyud don //
NK123(go)001:7719: rnam pa gsum du shes bya ste //
NK123(go)001:7720: bya ba rgyu dang byed pa rkyen //
NK123(go)001:7722: ji snyed chos kyi rtsa bar bshad //
NK123(go)001:7726: bya ba 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor te gsum las /
NK123(go)001:7728: chos thams cad kyi gshis lugs dkyil 'khor rnam pa
NK123(go)001:7729: gsum gyi rang bzhin du ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs
NK123(go)001:7730: par gnas pa nyid yin te /
NK123(go)001:7732: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK123(go)001:7733: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:7734: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pas //
NK123(go)001:7735: shes par bya ba rgyud don yin //
NK123(go)001:7738: lam gyi rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i byed pas srid pa las brgal te /
NK123(go)001:7739: zhi ba gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu la 'jug par
NK123(go)001:7740: byed pas nyan rang byang sems kyi theg pa gsum
NK123(go)001:7743: theg pa de ni bya byed rkyen //
NK123(go)001:7746: sems kyi chos nyid gdod ma nas rang bzhin gyis
NK123(go)001:7747: rnam par dag pas 'bras bu gzhan nas brtsal ba'i
NK123(go)001:7748: rtsol sgrub kyi re dogs dang bral ba sngags phyi
NK123(go)001:7751: gzhan du 'bras bu re rtsol med //
NK123(go)001:7752: bsgrub bya nyid la lam gnas pas //
NK123(go)001:7753: thabs chen theg 'di bya bral lo //
NK123(go)001:7755: de ltar rkyen 'bras kyi rnal 'byor phyi ma gnyis
NK123(go)001:7756: po de la thun mong spyi yi lam zhes bya
NK123(go)001:7757: zhing / de las rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa
NK123(go)001:7758: yo ga phyin gyi sgom rim thun mong pa ni
NK123(go)001:7760: thun min mdo rang lugs kyi man ngag dang sgom
NK123(go)001:7761: skor ni mdo dbang chen mo sogs las shes par
NK123(go)001:7762: bya dgos la / 'dir a nu'i rang lam khyad par ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK123(go)001:7764: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK123(go)001:7765: zhes pas thabs kyis nges pa'i lam dang /
NK123(go)001:7766: shes rab kyis rnam par grol ba'i lam gnyis su med pa las /
NK123(go)001:7768: sbyang gzhi mchog tu mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK123(go)001:7769: po gnyug ma lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes gnas
NK123(go)001:7770: lugs rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa chen po'i
NK123(go)001:7771: rang mdangs / shin tu phra ba'i sgo gsum rdo
NK123(go)001:7772: rje gsum du sgrub gzhi rang byung rdo rje'i lus
NK123(go)001:7773: la gnas pa'i rtsa rlung byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK123(go)001:7774: rang mdangs / chen por / sbyang bya snang gsum
NK123(go)001:7775: 'pho ba'i bag chags rkyen gyur gzung 'dzin kun rtog
NK123(go)001:7776: gi g.yo ba tha mal snang zhen gyi sgrib par
NK123(go)001:7777: rang mdangs / chen por / rags phra rnams /
NK123(go)001:7778: sbyong byed phyi spros rtsol gyi lam la mi ltos
NK123(go)001:7779: par nang rang lus rtsa rlung thig le la gnad
NK123(go)001:7780: du bsnun pa'i thabs gang zhig /
NK123(go)001:7781: zhu bde'i lam la brten nas rags pa'i 'gyur ba
NK123(go)001:7782: thams cad thog mar gang las byung ba 'gyur med
NK123(go)001:7783: ye shes kyi dbu ma'i dbyings su bstim pa las
NK123(go)001:7784: / dpe dang don gyi ye shes btsan thabs su
NK123(go)001:7785: 'dren par byed pa'i bde ba chen po'i man ngag
NK123(go)001:7786: / ste / de yang steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'am
NK123(go)001:7787: me rlung gnyis bsnan pa'i 'khor lo drug bsgom pa'i
NK123(go)001:7788: rnal 'byor gyis lhan skyes ye shes rim gyis 'dren
NK123(go)001:7790: 'og sgo las sam ye shes kyi phyag rgya gang
NK123(go)001:7791: rung la brten nas mkha' gsang snyoms 'jug gi thabs
NK123(go)001:7792: la brten nas 'bar 'dzag gi sbyor bas thig le
NK123(go)001:7793: 'dzag med du bcing nas yas bab dang mas brtan
NK123(go)001:7794: gyi dga' bas drangs pa'i 'pho med lhan cig skyes
NK123(go)001:7795: pa'i ye shes cig car du 'dren pa'i thabs gnyis
NK123(go)001:7796: te / de las rol pa'i ka ra la sogs pa /
NK123(go)001:7797: man ngag thabs kyis der 'jug dang /
NK123(go)001:7801: thos bsam sgom pa'i tshul 'gro ba'i //
NK123(go)001:7802: der ni 'jug pa rnam gsum ste //
NK123(go)001:7803: rtog dpyod don dang yi ge yid //
NK123(go)001:7805: dang po rtog dpyod kyi rjes su 'jug pa lta ba gtan la phab pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7806: lam gyi sngon du 'gros dgos te /
NK123(go)001:7807: de'ang chos can shes bya'i don la shes byed rig
NK123(go)001:7808: pa'i gtan tshigs rnams kyis so sor brtags pas chos
NK123(go)001:7809: thams cad kyi gnas lugs chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK123(go)001:7810: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin dbyer med sma bsam
NK123(go)001:7811: brjod bral du gtan la phebs pa ni /
NK123(go)001:7812: 'di nyid kyi grub mtha' ste gong du smos zin la /
NK123(go)001:7814: rtags kyi rol pa gnyis las /
NK123(go)001:7816: spros med rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7817: bsgom bya chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngang la sgom
NK123(go)001:7818: byed kyi blo yang de bzhin du ma bcos par
NK123(go)001:7820: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK123(go)001:7821: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag na //
NK123(go)001:7822: brjod pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK123(go)001:7823: ma yengs rgyun du dran pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7825: 'di la don gyi rjes su 'jug pa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:7827: spros bcas lha yi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7828: sa bon nam rten dang brten pa so so'i bskyed
NK123(go)001:7829: sngags brjod pa tsam gyis chu la nya ldang ba
NK123(go)001:7830: ltar / snod bcud thams cad lha'i gzhal yas khang
NK123(go)001:7831: dang dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor gsal la ma 'dres
NK123(go)001:7832: pa cig car du bsgom pa gtso bor byed pa'i
NK123(go)001:7833: ltar / nyams len te / bang mdzod 'phrul lde las /
NK123(go)001:7834: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni //
NK123(go)001:7835: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas nas //
NK123(go)001:7836: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i lha ru bsgom //
NK123(go)001:7838: 'di la yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:7839: de dag gi nges rdzogs bsgom pa'i dbang du byas na zag bcas dang /
NK123(go)001:7843: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:7844: de yang blo stobs che ba rnams rtog goms chig chod du byed pas mthar phyin pas na /
NK123(go)001:7845: sa lam rim bgrod kyi rtsol ba dang bral yang blo 'bring tha gnyis kyis ni /
NK123(go)001:7846: sa bcu pa'i slob lam bzhi rim gyis sam thod
NK123(go)001:7847: rgal gang rung gis bgrod nas mi slob pa'i lam
NK123(go)001:7848: mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor bar byed dgos
NK123(go)001:7849: pa yin pas / chos nyid snying po ji bzhin
NK123(go)001:7850: pa'i rjes su 'jug pa'i rang sa'i lam na 'phar
NK123(go)001:7851: ba'i rim pa ltar bsgom pas /
NK123(go)001:7852: dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa'i sa dang /
NK123(go)001:7853: gnyis pa brten pa gzhi'i sa gnyis ni tshogs lam 'dun pa sems dpa'i rnal 'byor gyis bsdus te /
NK123(go)001:7854: 'dis rkyen 'gyur las kyi bag chags rags phra gnyis dag nas mos spyod kyi lha sku grub /
NK123(go)001:7855: thun mong gi dngos grub spyan dang mngon shes sogs
NK123(go)001:7856: grub pas sangs rgyas sprul sku'i zhal mthong ba sogs
NK123(go)001:7857: tshogs lam gyi yon tan rnams 'char ro //
NK123(go)001:7858: gsum pa gal chen sbyong ba dang /
NK123(go)001:7859: bzhi pa bslab pa rgyun gyi sa lnga pa bsod
NK123(go)001:7860: nams rten gyi sa gsum ni sbyor lam rigs chen
NK123(go)001:7862: 'dir mngon du rgyu'i bag chags rags 'bring phra ba
NK123(go)001:7863: gsum dag nas rlung sems tsam gyi lha sku 'grub
NK123(go)001:7864: cing nyin snang dang mtshan snang gi bar mtshams med
NK123(go)001:7865: par thams cad sgyu ma ltar bur rtogs pa sogs
NK123(go)001:7866: sbyor lam gyi yon tan rnams 'char ro //
NK123(go)001:7868: dbugs chen 'byin pa dang lung chen thob pa dang /
NK123(go)001:7869: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:7870: de yang sbyor lam gyi rten de la tshogs kyi spyod pa'i nyer rgyu la brten nas /
NK123(go)001:7871: khu rdul rlung yid kyi 'gyu ba de rags pa bcoms te /
NK123(go)001:7872: 'jigs pa lnga dang bral zhing zag pa thams cad zad nas /
NK123(go)001:7873: drug pa brten pa khyad par du 'gro ba'i sa ni /
NK123(go)001:7874: mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor te /
NK123(go)001:7875: 'di'i kun 'gro'i sgrib pa dag cing chos nyid rang
NK123(go)001:7876: mtshan pa mngon sum du mthong ba'i stobs kyis bde
NK123(go)001:7877: stong 'od gsal gyi lha sku 'grub cing yon tan
NK123(go)001:7878: brgya phrag bcu gnyis la dbang thob /
NK123(go)001:7879: longs sku rigs lnga'i zhing bgrod nas chos nyan pa
NK123(go)001:7880: sogs mthong lam gyi yon tan thams cad 'char ro
NK123(go)001:7881: // de nas mthong lam 'od gsal las longs pa'i rjes la /
NK123(go)001:7882: bdun pa dmigs pa 'bras bu skye ba'i sa ni sgom lam lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor te /
NK123(go)001:7883: 'dis lhan cig gnas pa'i sgrib pa dag nas chos
NK123(go)001:7884: nyid rtogs pa'i ye shes dang dag pa lha sku'i
NK123(go)001:7885: snang ba rgyun mi 'chad pa spob pa'i zung 'jug
NK123(go)001:7886: gi sku 'grub / de nas brgyad pa gnas pa mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK123(go)001:7887: dgu pa gdal ba chos nyid kyi sa dang /
NK123(go)001:7888: bcu pa rdzogs pa spyir chub kyi sa gsum po
NK123(go)001:7889: mthar lam rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyis bsdus
NK123(go)001:7890: te / 'dis bag nyal rags 'bring phra gsum gyi sgrib pa rim par dag cing /
NK123(go)001:7891: de ltar sgom mthar gyi lam bzhi po de /
NK123(go)001:7892: thun mong ba ltar na sgom lam sa dgus bsdus pas na /
NK123(go)001:7893: de rnams su sngar mthong lam gyi yon tan brgya
NK123(go)001:7894: phrag bcu gnyis po de stong du 'gyur ba na
NK123(go)001:7895: / zhing khams brjod du med pa bye ba khrag
NK123(go)001:7896: khrig brgya stong phrag bcu'i rdul shin tu phra ba
NK123(go)001:7897: snyed dang mnyam pa'i bar du rim par 'phel zhing
NK123(go)001:7899: dbang bcu la sogs pa'i yon 'char ro //
NK123(go)001:7900: de'i mthar mi slob pa'i lam rgyun matha'i bar chad
NK123(go)001:7901: med lam la brten nas 'dod chags chen po'i lam
NK123(go)001:7902: gyis 'bras bu'i dbang bskur bas dga' bzhi'i lugs 'byung
NK123(go)001:7903: dang lugs ldog gi mthar snang gsum 'pho ba'i bag
NK123(go)001:7904: chags phra ba rten khu rdul rlung gsum gyi rgyu
NK123(go)001:7905: ba shin tu phra ba'ang rgyun chad pas /
NK123(go)001:7906: brten pa shes sgrib phra ba'ang dag ste /
NK123(go)001:7907: 'bras chos nyer lnga dbyer med lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK123(go)001:7908: bde ba chen po'i sku mi slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK123(go)001:7909: la mngon du sbyor bar byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:7910: de ltar sa bcu po re re dang sbyar ba'i gnas skabs bcur /
NK123(go)001:7911: rang sa'i lam na 'phar ba'i rim pa ltar bsgom pas /
NK123(go)001:7912: rkyen 'byung las kyi bag chags rags phra sogs gong
NK123(go)001:7913: smos rang sa'i sgrib pa bcu po rim par dag
NK123(go)001:7914: nas gong ma gong ma la sbyor ba'i tshul 'di
NK123(go)001:7915: ni / g.yo ba byang chub sems sogs sems bcu po /
NK123(go)001:7916: dpe skar ma phra mo lta bu la sogs pa
NK123(go)001:7917: bcu dang sbyar nas bgrod par rtsa rgyud kun 'dus
NK123(go)001:7918: kyi le'u gnyis pa sogs mdo'i rtsa bshad kyi rgyud
NK123(go)001:7919: dang man ngag las rgyas par gsungs zhes kun mkhyen
NK123(go)001:7921: de las sgrib pa bcu spong tshul gang du gsal la /
NK123(go)001:7922: sems bcu dang dpe bcu sbyar tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:7923: rnal 'byor chen po'i sa zhes thun min gyi lam ste /
NK123(go)001:7924: skye ba'i sa dang rgyu'i sa gang nas gsang sngags
NK123(go)001:7925: su sems skyes kyang 'dir gzhi las dang por 'gyur
NK123(go)001:7926: te / rnal 'byor lnga'i tshogs lam 'dun sems kyi skabs su /
NK123(go)001:7928: thogs mar sngags kyi bden gnyis spyi'i mtshan nyid tsam shes pa'i sems g.yo ba g.yo ba'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7929: dpe mun pa'i sprin rum nas skrar zer phra mor byung ba dang 'dra /
NK123(go)001:7930: blo mun pa lta bu las byang chub kyi sems rgyu rkyen gyis de tsam skyes pa'o //
NK123(go)001:7932: rgyu nges gsang sngags kyi 'bras bu'i don la slob cing rtogs par smon pa smon pa'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7933: dpe skarma 'bring po tsam ste da dung sngags kyi
NK123(go)001:7934: de kho na nyid la zhugs pa ni min te
NK123(go)001:7936: gnyis pa sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed pa'i skabs su gal chen sbyong ba'i sar /
NK123(go)001:7937: de gnyis kyi rgyus sngags la zhugs nas bslab pa'i mtha' bcu la slob pa'i tshe /
NK123(go)001:7938: 'og mar med pa'i lhag pa'i sems smon pa las gyen du ldang ba ldang ba'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7939: dpe mtshan mo'i skar chen lta bu /
NK123(go)001:7941: rgyu des sngags kyi don rtogs pa la sbyor ba sbyor ba'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7942: dpe 'gal me'i 'khor lo myur la rgyun mi chad pa'am zla ba tshes gcig pa lta bu /
NK123(go)001:7944: des mnyam nyid kyi don la shes rab kyis rtsal
NK123(go)001:7945: sbyang ste mthong lam la 'jug pa gnyis med don
NK123(go)001:7947: dpe sgron me'am zla ba tshes gnyis pa lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:7948: gsum pa mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'i skabs su brten par khyad par gyi sar /
NK123(go)001:7949: sngar gyi rgyu des chos nyid kyi ro myong zhing
NK123(go)001:7950: bden pa mthong ba 'i tshe sngar med kyi dga'
NK123(go)001:7951: ba skye ba shin tu dga' ba'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7952: dpe bum nang gi mar me'am zla ba tshes gsum pa lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:7954: bsgom lam lung chen thob pa'i skabs su /
NK123(go)001:7955: dmigs pa 'bras bu skye ba'i sar /
NK123(go)001:7956: rtogs zin sgom lam chos nyid la 'jug pa'i tshe /
NK123(go)001:7957: lta ba'i gdeng de las mi 'gyur ba mi 'gyur lhag pa'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7958: dpe tshes bzhi pa'i zla ba lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:7959: lnga pa thar lam rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skabs su /
NK123(go)001:7961: lam mthar phyin te chos thams cad bdag nyid chen
NK123(go)001:7962: po rig pa'i cho 'phrul du rtogs pa ci snang
NK123(go)001:7963: rang byung ye shes su gsal ba'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7964: dpe tshes lnga pa'i zla ba lta bu /
NK123(go)001:7965: gdal ba chos nyid kyi sar /
NK123(go)001:7966: shin tu goms pa gdengs su gyur pas rang rig
NK123(go)001:7967: pa mtha' dang bral ba'i don nyid dang dbyer med
NK123(go)001:7968: par 'bad med du gnas pa'i sems /
NK123(go)001:7969: dpe shin tu gsal ba'i sgron me ngam zla ba tshes brgyad pa lta bu /
NK123(go)001:7970: rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi par rgyu des sgom mi
NK123(go)001:7971: dgos par ting 'dzin las su rung ba'i tshe dbyings
NK123(go)001:7972: ye dbyer med ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su rtogs pa
NK123(go)001:7973: de las skyed byar du med pas rdzogs pa'i sems
NK123(go)001:7974: dpe tshes bcu drug gi zla ba lta bu gsal
NK123(go)001:7975: zhing rdzogs pa'o // des na 'gro ba'i sems ye nas chos skur yod kyang /
NK123(go)001:7976: btags pa'i sgrib pas bsgribs nas mthong ba de sems
NK123(go)001:7977: bcus bskyed pas 'bras bu grub cing de ltar mthar
NK123(go)001:7978: phyin pa yin zhes gnubs chen gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:7979: de ltar bshad pa'i rnal 'byor lnga dang /
NK123(go)001:7980: sa bcu pa de rnams kyi nges tshig ni /
NK123(go)001:7981: mdo rtsa bshad kyi rgyud dang man ngag gi las gsal bar bstan pa ma mthong yang /
NK123(go)001:7982: spyi tsam la dpag na rnal 'byor lnga'i dang po ni /
NK123(go)001:7983: tshogs lam gyi dus su 'od gsal dang lha sku
NK123(go)001:7984: gnyis 'dren pas drangs pa'i mos pa tsam gyis yul
NK123(go)001:7985: du byed pas 'dun pa sems pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:7986: gnyis pa ni sbyor lam thob pa'i tshe zag pa
NK123(go)001:7987: yod kyang ldog pa med pas rigs nges pa'i phyir
NK123(go)001:7989: gsum pa ni mthong lam du 'jigs pa lnga dang bral ba sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:7990: chos nyid mngon sum mthong bas 'jig rten gyi chos las 'das pas dbugs chen 'byin pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:7991: bzhi pa ni sgom lam du dus dang gnas sogs
NK123(go)001:7992: nges pa can gyi sgo nas lung bstan chen po
NK123(go)001:7993: thob pas lung chen thob pa'i dang /
NK123(go)001:7994: lnga pa ni mthar lam du slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK123(go)001:7995: gi yon tan gyi rtsal mthar thug pa rdzogs pa'i
NK123(go)001:7996: phyir rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK123(go)001:7997: sa yang rnam pa bcu las /
NK123(go)001:7999: zag ldog gnyis ka yod pas 'gyur ba ma nges pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8000: rnal 'byor dang po 'di'i skabs kyi mngon rtogs rnams
NK123(go)001:8001: brten pa sbyor lam sogs bskyed pa'i rten yin pas
NK123(go)001:8002: gnyis pa la brten pa gzhi yis zhes bya zhing
NK123(go)001:8004: mthong lam don gyi 'od gsal la bsgrib pa'i mngon
NK123(go)001:8005: gyur gyi bag chags thams cad sbyong bas gsum pa
NK123(go)001:8006: la gal chen sbyong ba'i sa dang /
NK123(go)001:8007: nyin mtshan med par sgyu ma lta bu'i tshul gyis
NK123(go)001:8008: zung 'jug gi rgyu la bslabs pas bzhi pa la
NK123(go)001:8009: bslab pa rgyun gyi sa dang /
NK123(go)001:8010: nye rgyu'i spyod pa'i bsod nams la brten nas zag
NK123(go)001:8011: med kyi ye shes la sbyor bas lnga pa la
NK123(go)001:8012: bsod nams rten gyi sa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:8013: mthong lam du don gyi 'od gsal la mngon du
NK123(go)001:8014: mthong bas de la brten nas zag med kyi yon
NK123(go)001:8015: tan thams cad gong nas gong du khyad par du
NK123(go)001:8016: 'gro bas drug pa la brten pas khyad par du
NK123(go)001:8018: sgom du slob pa'i zung 'jug gi don la dmigs
NK123(go)001:8019: shing goms pas 'bras bu mi slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK123(go)001:8020: gi sku 'grub pas bdun pa la dmigs pas 'bras
NK123(go)001:8021: bu skye ba'i sa zhes bya /
NK123(go)001:8022: mthar lam du dbyings ye dbyer med kyi dgongs pa
NK123(go)001:8023: la rtag tu gnas shing 'pho 'gyur med pas brgyad
NK123(go)001:8024: pa la gnas mi 'gyur ba'i sa dang /
NK123(go)001:8025: chos nyid don gyi 'od gsal dang chos can lha
NK123(go)001:8026: sku'i snang ba gnyis 'du 'bral med pa'i chos nyid
NK123(go)001:8027: kyi phyag rgyas snang spyod thams cad la khyab par
NK123(go)001:8028: brdal bas dgu pa la brdal ba chos nyid kyi
NK123(go)001:8029: sa dang / rtsal snang gzugs sku'i bkod pa'i thams
NK123(go)001:8030: cad skye ba med pa'i dbyings su 'ub chub par
NK123(go)001:8031: yongs su rdzogs shing mthar phyin pas rdzogs pa spyir
NK123(go)001:8033: sa 'di rnams phal cher lam nges pa zhes pa'i sgra sbyor ba ltar na /
NK123(go)001:8034: 'di dag slob pa'i sa yin pas rang rang gi
NK123(go)001:8035: gnas skabs kyi sgrib pa dag cing sa gong ma'i
NK123(go)001:8036: yon tan la sbyor du yod pas rang rang gi
NK123(go)001:8037: skabs su bzhag pa'i nges tshig de nyid sa dang
NK123(go)001:8038: ldan pa'i gang zag de la rnam pa kun tu
NK123(go)001:8039: ma nges so // yang sa phyi ma la mi
NK123(go)001:8040: slob pa'i sar bshad pa ltar na'ang dgra bcom zhugs
NK123(go)001:8041: pa'i sa bzhin btags pa ba yin gyi dngos ni
NK123(go)001:8042: min no zhes bdag gi mkhan po rje dpon mkhas
NK123(go)001:8043: pa chen po gu nas gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:8044: mdor na kun rdzob byang sems dang 'brel ba'i gdams
NK123(go)001:8045: pa steng sgo rlung dang 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag
NK123(go)001:8046: dang / 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag
NK123(go)001:8047: gnyis la brten nas 'dzag med bde stong gi ye
NK123(go)001:8048: shes bskyed pa la bslab pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8049: don dam byang chub sems dang 'brel ba'i gdams pa /
NK123(go)001:8050: rten can snying ga'i mi shigs pa'i theg le la
NK123(go)001:8051: rlung sems kyi dwangs ma thams cad thim ste dbyings
NK123(go)001:8052: rig gnyis med bde ba chen po'i ye shes 'char
NK123(go)001:8053: bas khams gsum bde ba chen por grol bar byed
NK123(go)001:8055: rten med mi g.yo gsum ldan gyi gnad kyis rnam
NK123(go)001:8056: par mi rtog pa'i ngang la bsal bzhag med par
NK123(go)001:8057: bskyang bas yul chos nyid don gyi ye shes dang
NK123(go)001:8058: / yul can chos sku gzhi'i ye shes dbyer med
NK123(go)001:8059: pa'i rig pa dbyings ye zung 'jug tu rtogs pas
NK123(go)001:8060: / / dkyil 'khor gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gtan la 'bebs par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:8061: spyod pa ni spyir mnyam pa nyid la gtso bor spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8063: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni /
NK123(go)001:8064: dbyings dang ye shes longs spyod rdzogs zhes so //
NK123(go)001:8068: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum ste /
NK123(go)001:8070: byin gyis rlabs kyi spyod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:8071: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi spyod pa ste //
NK123(go)001:8072: dper na nam mkha' rgyal po'am //
NK123(go)001:8073: ji ltar me dpung chu bo 'dra //
NK123(go)001:8074: zhes pas dbyings ye gnyis med rtogs pa'i byin rlabs kyi spyod pa nam mkha' lta bu /
NK123(go)001:8075: dug lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du dbang bsgyur
NK123(go)001:8076: ba'i spyod pa rgyal po'am me dpung gis shing bsregs
NK123(go)001:8077: pa lta bu / 'khor 'das gnyis med du rtogs
NK123(go)001:8078: pa'i thabs kyi spyod pa rgyun mi 'chad pa chu
NK123(go)001:8081: tshe gcig gis mo slob pa'i zung 'jug 'bras chos
NK123(go)001:8082: nyer lnga dbyer med lhun grub kyi ngo bo sku
NK123(go)001:8083: bzhi ye shes lnga yi bdag nyid bde ba chen
NK123(go)001:8084: po'i sku mngon du mdzad nas rtag khyab lhun gyis
NK123(go)001:8085: grub pa'i phrin las kyis gdul bya'i don mdzad pa
NK123(go)001:8086: ste / thig le mchog gi rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:8087: 'od gsal ba yi sems nyid ni //
NK123(go)001:8088: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med par //
NK123(go)001:8089: bde ba che de sus bsgoms pa //
NK123(go)001:8093: a nu yo ga'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:8094: bar ma chod pa tshe gcig gis //
NK123(go)001:8095: sangs rgyas sa la nges par 'gro //
NK123(go)001:8097: 'bras chos nyer lnga sogs ni gong du smos pa ltar la /
NK123(go)001:8098: de yang gzhi la yon tan lhun grub tu bzhugs pa nyid mngon du gyur pa tsam ste /
NK123(go)001:8100: gzhan las ma byung rang byung ba //
NK123(go)001:8103: tha ma yid bzhin nor bu ltar //
NK123(go)001:8104: ma bsags zad 'phel med pa'i sku //
NK123(go)001:8105: gdul bya'i don snang dngos gzhi med //
NK123(go)001:8106: lhun grub yon tan rang snang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:8108: gsum pa gang zag gti mug can nam dbang po
NK123(go)001:8109: rab kyi rab bya rtsol med par 'jug pa la
NK123(go)001:8110: dgongs nas gsungs pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti
NK123(go)001:8112: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga ni chos rnams kyi 'bras bu lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:8113: zhes gsungs pas ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis ka'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i skyel so ste /
NK123(go)001:8114: dbyings rang bzhin gyis dag pa'i sems nyid 'og gsal
NK123(go)001:8115: ba lhun grub rang gnas chen por bzhugs pa'i rang
NK123(go)001:8116: byung gi ye shes bcos bsgyur spang len dang bral
NK123(go)001:8117: bar lam du khyer bas theg pa 'og ma rnams
NK123(go)001:8119: theg pa 'og ma rnams bcos slad kyi rtsol sgrub
NK123(go)001:8120: kyis blang dor byas pas re dogs kyi sgrib pas
NK123(go)001:8121: rang byung gi ye shes bsgribs te /
NK123(go)001:8122: rnal ma'i don la reg pa'i skabs med pa nyid /
NK123(go)001:8124: nges pa thob pa'i theg pa drug /
NK123(go)001:8125: rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sar bstan //
NK123(go)001:8126: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:8127: 'dir ni rang byung gi ye shes rdzogs pa chen
NK123(go)001:8128: po nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i che ba'i yon
NK123(go)001:8129: tan lhun grub tu yod pas sku gsum rang chas
NK123(go)001:8130: su tshang ba'i phyir log nas btsal mi dgos pas
NK123(go)001:8131: / 'di nyid ma bcos ji bzhin pa'i ngang nas ma g.yos pas 'grub par bstan te /
NK123(go)001:8134: sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK123(go)001:8135: chos kyi sku ni byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:8136: byang chub sems las chos kyi sku //
NK123(go)001:8137: rdul tsam sus kyang bcos su med //
NK123(go)001:8138: de na sangs rgyas sems las med //
NK123(go)001:8139: longs spyod rdzogs sku byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:8140: byang chub sems las longs spyod sku //
NK123(go)001:8141: sems las byung ba'i gzugs rnams la //
NK123(go)001:8142: longs spyod rdzogs las sku gzhan med //
NK123(go)001:8143: sprul pa'i sku ni byang chub sems //
NK123(go)001:8144: byang chub sems kyi sprul pa las //
NK123(go)001:8145: 'gro ba'i don mdzod gzhan na med //
NK123(go)001:8146: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyang //
NK123(go)001:8147: byang chub sems las gzhan med de //
NK123(go)001:8148: snga rab 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK123(go)001:8149: rang sems ma bcos sngar mthong rtogs //
NK123(go)001:8150: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK123(go)001:8151: ma bcos pa yi rang sems de //
NK123(go)001:8152: ma bcos ji bzhin rtogs gyur pas //
NK123(go)001:8153: da ltar 'gro ba'i don yang mdzad //
NK123(go)001:8154: slad nas 'byon pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK123(go)001:8155: rang sems byang chub sems nyid 'di //
NK123(go)001:8156: snga ma bcos par lung ma bstan //
NK123(go)001:8158: ma bcos lam du zhugs nas byon //
NK123(go)001:8160: de'i phyir sems nyid g.yo ba med pa'i chos sku
NK123(go)001:8161: byang chub kyi sems ni bya rtsol las 'das pa
NK123(go)001:8162: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin te /
NK123(go)001:8164: sems ni ji bzhin pa yi dngos po ste //
NK123(go)001:8165: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin nyid du 'grub //
NK123(go)001:8166: ji bzhin pa la 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK123(go)001:8167: ngo bo nyid las gzhan du ma bsgrubs shig /
NK123(go)001:8168: brtsal na rgyal bas dbyings nas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK123(go)001:8169: sngar byas zin pas da ni byed mi dgos //
NK123(go)001:8170: sngar bsgrubs zin pas da sgrub ma byed par //
NK123(go)001:8171: mi rtog cir mi dgongs la mnyam par zhog /
NK123(go)001:8173: der ma zad rdzogs chen sde gsum gyi nang nas kyang /
NK123(go)001:8174: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po gsang ba man ngag
NK123(go)001:8175: gi sde snying thig gi skor rnams ni rang byung
NK123(go)001:8176: gi ye shes skad cig gis nang du 'char ba'i
NK123(go)001:8177: rtags rang bzhin gyi snang ba ye shes lnga la
NK123(go)001:8179: tshig dang yi ge dang rtog dpyod dang mi rtog
NK123(go)001:8180: pa'i ting nge 'dzin blos byas kyi sgom pa kun
NK123(go)001:8181: las khyad par du 'phags te nor sa dang 'dzol
NK123(go)001:8182: sa med cing / brtson 'grus bskyed na dbang po
NK123(go)001:8183: rno rtul med pas rtsol med ye shes kyi rang
NK123(go)001:8185: sku gsum lhun grub chen po'i zhing la tshe 'dir
NK123(go)001:8186: dngos su sbyor bas sems klong sogs las kyang ches
NK123(go)001:8187: 'phags te / gsang ba sgra'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:8188: dngos grub mchog rnams mthar thug pa //
NK123(go)001:8189: 'bad cing rtsol bas ma yin par //
NK123(go)001:8190: gang su 'phrad pas grol bar nges //
NK123(go)001:8191: des na rdzogs chen bya ba bral //
NK123(go)001:8192: gzhan 'bad pa las byung ba min //
NK123(go)001:8193: chos nyid mngon sum khyad par gyis //
NK123(go)001:8194: dbang po rno dang rtul med pas //
NK123(go)001:8195: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas las //
NK123(go)001:8196: gzhan du gnas pa ma yin no //
NK123(go)001:8198: tha na dbang bskur ba dang ngo sprad pa tsam yang chos nyid bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK123(go)001:8199: rang bzhin sprul bar dbugs 'byin la /
NK123(go)001:8200: cung zad nyams su blang nas 'das kyang bar dor
NK123(go)001:8201: grol ba'i rtags tshad mngon sum du snang ba dang
NK123(go)001:8202: / tshig rgyud kyi glegs bam bris te bcang pa
NK123(go)001:8203: tsam la'ang gzhan las phan yon che bar basngagasa pa
NK123(go)001:8204: sogs 'phags chos bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK123(go)001:8205: zhib par kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po'i gsung rab rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:8206: kun gzigs zhe chen ma h+aa pan+di tas mdzad pa'i
NK123(go)001:8207: thig le kun gsal chen mo'i rgyud kyi rgyab chos
NK123(go)001:8213: ye sangs rgyas pa'i don rang thog tu grol bar
NK123(go)001:8214: byed pa'i thabs spang blang re dogs dang bral ba'i
NK123(go)001:8218: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i rdzogs rim mthar thug pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK123(go)001:8219: theg pa thams cad kyi rtse mor gyur pas shin tu rnal 'byor ro //
NK123(go)001:8223: de yang dbang gsum pa'i dpe yi ye shes la
NK123(go)001:8224: ltos mi dgos par thog ma nas don dam byang
NK123(go)001:8225: chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug tu rung ba'i
NK123(go)001:8226: skal ldan la rdzogs pa chen po'i rig pa'i rtsal
NK123(go)001:8228: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i khog don las /
NK123(go)001:8229: zab pa don gyi dbang mchog ni //
NK123(go)001:8230: rig pa'i rtsal dbang thob pa ste //
NK123(go)001:8231: chos nyid rtogs pas dbang zhes bya //
NK123(go)001:8232: ye shes dbang bskur cod pan 'chang //
NK123(go)001:8234: khyad par man ngag gi sde ltar na /
NK123(go)001:8236: spros bcas spros pa med pa dang //
NK123(go)001:8237: shin tu spros med rab spros med //
NK123(go)001:8238: dbang ni rnam pa bzhi yis kyang //
NK123(go)001:8239: skal ba ldan la smin par bya //
NK123(go)001:8240: zhes pa'i dbang bzhis rim pa ltar /
NK123(go)001:8241: lus ngag yid dang shes bya la rmongs pa'i sgrib pa sbyong /
NK123(go)001:8242: sku gsung thugs dang rang byung 'od gsal ba'i nus pa 'jug /
NK123(go)001:8244: gtum mo sgom pa bde stong zung 'jug sgom zhing ka dag gi ye shes rtogs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8245: mngon sum lhun grub kyi don nyams su len pa bzhi la dbang ba yin no //
NK123(go)001:8246: 'di ni dbang gong ma nyid la dbang bzhir phye ba yin pas /
NK123(go)001:8247: bla med thun mong ba'i dbang bzhi dang grangs 'dra yang don mi 'dra ba shes dgos shing /
NK123(go)001:8248: der ma zad bla med thung mong ba'i dbang bzhi
NK123(go)001:8249: pa'i sngags sdoms rgyun ldan zhig gis 'di nyid thob
NK123(go)001:8250: na sdom pa sngar med gsar thob kyang 'dod dgos
NK123(go)001:8251: te / bla med kyi cho ga gzhan rnams rgyas
NK123(go)001:8252: bsdus dang rnam grangs mi 'dra ba tsam las phan
NK123(go)001:8253: tshun gcig gi dod gcig gis thub pas mtshungs pa'i
NK123(go)001:8254: te / phyir / de dag so so las thob
NK123(go)001:8255: pa'i sdom pa rnams kyang ngo bo gcig tu 'gyur
NK123(go)001:8256: te / phyir / mod / zhu bde lhan skyes
NK123(go)001:8257: kun rdzob pa dpe'i ye shes tsam la ngo sprad
NK123(go)001:8258: pa'i bzhi pa brtags pa ba des don dam lhan
NK123(go)001:8259: skyes zung 'jug gi ye shes la 'jug pa'i thabs
NK123(go)001:8260: bzhi pa mtshan nyid pa 'di'i dod mi thub pas
NK123(go)001:8261: mtshungs pa ma yin pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK123(go)001:8263: ci yang 'jug tu med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK123(go)001:8265: chos la bya rgyu med pa'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:8266: rtsol ba med pa'i sgo nas 'jug /
NK123(go)001:8269: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK123(go)001:8270: thig le chen po chos sku rang byung gi ye
NK123(go)001:8271: shes chen po'i ngo bor bya rtsol med par ye
NK123(go)001:8274: rang byung ye shes rtsol med la //
NK123(go)001:8275: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK123(go)001:8278: a ti bkod pa chen po las //
NK123(go)001:8279: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK123(go)001:8280: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK123(go)001:8281: rim rtsol bral la man ngag sde //
NK123(go)001:8282: zhes sems klong man ngag gi sde gsum las /
NK123(go)001:8284: chos thams cad sems nyid las gud na med pas
NK123(go)001:8285: spang bya'i mtha' las grol ba sems sde bas ni
NK123(go)001:8286: / ngo bo sna tshogs su snang yang sems nyid
NK123(go)001:8287: gcig gi rol pa las ma 'das pas sna tshogs
NK123(go)001:8288: su snang ba sems kyi snang ba yin la /
NK123(go)001:8289: don la ma grub cing gnyis su med pas sems
NK123(go)001:8290: kyi ngo bo 'od gsal ba rang byung gi ye
NK123(go)001:8293: dang po 'bras bu sems kyi byung sar 'dod pas ni /
NK123(go)001:8294: 'bras bu gdod ma'i dbyings la 'gyur ba med pas sems nyid la 'pho 'gyur med pa'i ngang las /
NK123(go)001:8295: grol gzhi'i lhun grub kyi snang cha las 'khor ba
NK123(go)001:8296: ltar shar kyang ngang las ma g.yos pas ma dag
NK123(go)001:8298: snang ba'i cha nas dbyings las byung zhing dbyings la gnas /
NK123(go)001:8299: dbyings su thim pa nam mkha'i cho 'phrul bzhin ye
NK123(go)001:8300: grol rang bzhag 'bad rtsol gnyen po med par la
NK123(go)001:8301: bzla ba'o // gnyis pa gol sgrib la bzla ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8302: a nu man chad kyi rim pa brgyad po rnams
NK123(go)001:8303: ni blos btags pas gzhi las gol ba yin la
NK123(go)001:8304: / 'dir ni rang byung gi ye shes blo dang
NK123(go)001:8305: bral bas rgyu rkyen las 'das par la bzla bas
NK123(go)001:8306: chos nyid ye stong chen po dran bsam phyogs 'dzin
NK123(go)001:8307: / dang bral bas / snang srid snod bcud ma dag pa ltar snang yang /
NK123(go)001:8308: gang las kyang ma byung gang du'ang mi gnas /
NK123(go)001:8310: 'khrul zhen ming med khams gsum gzhi grol spang gnyen gzhi med phyam gcig tu la bzla bar 'dod /
NK123(go)001:8311: gsum pa gtan tshigs khungs rdib pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8312: gzhi sems nyid la ngos bzung med pas las dang bag chags kyi rten med /
NK123(go)001:8313: gsog byed kyi sems ma grub pas las dang bag chags kyi byed mkhan stong /
NK123(go)001:8314: bsags pa'i las kyang brtags na ma grub pas rnam smin dang 'bras bus stong /
NK123(go)001:8315: des na 'khor ba ming med du grol la /
NK123(go)001:8316: sems nyid skye med rang byung gi ye shes las
NK123(go)001:8317: rol pa 'gag med phyogs yan du shar bas spang
NK123(go)001:8318: blang dgag sgrub med par yid ches te /
NK123(go)001:8319: chos nyid ye stong rang sangs /
NK123(go)001:8320: mtha' grol chen po'i gtan tshig khong nas shar bas 'khor 'das phyogs 'dzin las grol ba'o //
NK123(go)001:8321: bzhi pa rgya chad phyogs lhung med par 'dod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8322: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes kyi 'khor 'das kun la khyab kyang /
NK123(go)001:8323: snang ba dngos por rgya ma chad /
NK123(go)001:8324: stong pa dngos med du rgya ma chad /
NK123(go)001:8325: gnyis ka ma yinapasa zung 'jug gi phyogs su ma lhungs /
NK123(go)001:8326: ngo bo stong pas rtag pa'i mtha' las grol /
NK123(go)001:8327: rtsal ma 'gags pas chad mtha' las grol bas bya bral bde sdug las 'das pa'i chos nyid do //
NK123(go)001:8328: lnga pa phyogs 'dzin grub mtha' las 'das pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8329: sems kyi ngo bo gang du'ang mi gnas shing gang
NK123(go)001:8330: du'ang ma grub par cir yang snang la cir yang
NK123(go)001:8331: ma 'gag par 'char bas shar yang mi dgag mi
NK123(go)001:8333: drug pa blo bral phyogs 'dzin las 'das pas ni /
NK123(go)001:8334: rang byung gi ye shes blo dang bral bas ji
NK123(go)001:8335: ltar snang yang bden rdzun gang du'ang ma grub pas
NK123(go)001:8336: yod med mtha' grol chen po'i rol pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8337: bdun pa sems kyi phyogs yan du smra ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8338: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad sems kyi rol ba
NK123(go)001:8339: yin pas sna tshogs su snang yang sems nyid ngo
NK123(go)001:8340: bo med pas snang ba sna tshogs kyang ngo bo
NK123(go)001:8341: med pa'i phyir snang brtags kyi chos ma grub cing
NK123(go)001:8342: / gang shar sems kyi rnam pa 'dzin byed dang /
NK123(go)001:8343: snang ba gzung bar bya ba gnyis ka'ang snang ba tha dad du snang yang /
NK123(go)001:8344: yin gang yang ma yin pa'i chos nyid rang byung
NK123(go)001:8345: gi ye shes su dbyer med pas snang ba sems
NK123(go)001:8347: rang rtsal lhun grub kyi gdangs las 'khor 'das gnyis
NK123(go)001:8348: su shar yang shar mkhan la ngo bo med pas
NK123(go)001:8349: shar sar rang grol du 'gro ba 'di'i khyad par
NK123(go)001:8350: gyi chos so // gnyis pa chos can thams cad
NK123(go)001:8351: chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i klong du 'ub chub
NK123(go)001:8352: pas gnyen po'i mtha' las grol ba bya bral klong
NK123(go)001:8353: gyi chos so // gi sdes ni / rang byung
NK123(go)001:8354: gi ye shes chos nyid kun tu bzang po'i klong
NK123(go)001:8355: yangs bar chos can ji ltar snang ba thams cad
NK123(go)001:8356: rang snang bkod pa'i rgyan tsam las 'ching grol dang
NK123(go)001:8357: gyi chos so // gi sdes ni / / shar bya shar byed du ma grub pas /
NK123(go)001:8358: sems sde ltar rtsal dang rol par snang bar mi bzhed cing /
NK123(go)001:8359: ltos grub dang yod med dang /
NK123(go)001:8361: dag ma dag gang du'ang mi dpyod par ye grol phyogs 'byams chen por gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8362: de la bye brag tu dbye na bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:8363: dang po klong nag po rgyu med du smra ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8364: rang byung gnyug ma'i ye shes de nyid 'gyur med
NK123(go)001:8365: rgyu dang rkyen las 'das pa'i rang bzhin phyogs char
NK123(go)001:8366: med pas chos can dang chos nyid gnyis kar mi
NK123(go)001:8368: gnyis pa klong khra bo sna tshogs su smra ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8369: rang byung gi ye shes de nyid kyi rol par snang ba rnams /
NK123(go)001:8370: yin sna tshogs rang shar du snang ba chos nyid kyi rgyun dang rol pa la /
NK123(go)001:8371: min phyogs med kun khyab tu shar ba rol pa dgag sgrub las 'das par 'dod /
NK123(go)001:8372: gsum pa klong dkar po sems su smra ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8373: rang byung rig pa'i ngang las phyi snang ba dang /
NK123(go)001:8374: nang rig par shar pa thams cad sems kyi rol pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8375: snang ba dang rkyen rang sar grol bas byar med ka nas dag ste /
NK123(go)001:8376: gnas lugs la bsgrub tu med par 'dod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8377: bzhi pa klong rab 'byams rgyu 'bras la bzlo ba ni /
NK123(go)001:8378: rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngang las snang ba'i chos thams cad par sems kyis shes la /
NK123(go)001:8379: mi snang bar gnas lugs kyis shes par 'dod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8380: de dag la nang gses kyi dbye ba zhib tu byed na bcu gnyis yod kyang /
NK123(go)001:8381: de dag bsdu na rol ba /
NK123(go)001:8383: chos nyid bya bral gyi klong bzhir 'dus pa las /
NK123(go)001:8385: sems kyi rol ba 'gags med du shar ba'i ngag nas 'pho 'gyur med pas ci yang yin la /
NK123(go)001:8386: dngos med kyi rol pa mthar 'dzin du ma grub pas gang yang min la /
NK123(go)001:8387: phyogs yan nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8391: rang byung bcos bslad med pa'i rgyan du ye shar te /
NK123(go)001:8392: skye med kyi ngag las 'gag med du shar bas
NK123(go)001:8393: snang sems mi dgag mi sgrub rang 'gros rang bzhag
NK123(go)001:8394: rang gsal chen po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8396: skye 'gag dang bral ba'i chos nyid kyi rang las rol pa'am rtsal sna tshogs su snang yang /
NK123(go)001:8397: 'byung bzhi'i 'pho 'gyur nam mkha'i dbyings las ma g.yos pa bzhin du /
NK123(go)001:8398: chos nyid ye stong ye grol ye bzhag chen po'i
NK123(go)001:8399: ngang du spang blang re dogs dang bral bar phyam
NK123(go)001:8400: gadala'o // bya ba dang bral ba'i klong ni /
NK123(go)001:8401: chos gang la'ang ched du 'bad rtsol gyi blang dor mi dgos te /
NK123(go)001:8405: ma bsgrubs ye grub tu 'dus pa /
NK123(go)001:8406: nam mkha' ltar 'pho 'gyur bcos slad med par 'dod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8407: gsum pa don rang gi mtshan nyid yin lugs ltar
NK123(go)001:8408: gtan la 'bebs pas spang gnyen gnyis ka'i mtha' las
NK123(go)001:8409: grol bas snga ma gnyis las kyang khyad par du
NK123(go)001:8410: 'phags pa man ngag gi sde pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8411: gdod ma nyid nas grol zhing ka nas dag pa'i
NK123(go)001:8412: chos nyid la nyi tshe ba'i blta bya'i yul dang
NK123(go)001:8413: / lta byed kyi shes pa gnyis su ma chad pas 'khrul ma 'khrul dang /
NK123(go)001:8414: rtogs ma rtogs su sgrub pa'i ltos gzhi dang /
NK123(go)001:8415: ltos sa'i chos las log pas /
NK123(go)001:8416: rang gi ngo bo spros bral gyi cha nas shes
NK123(go)001:8417: bya shes byed kyi yul yul can gnyis ka yang
NK123(go)001:8418: dag pa ma yin par mnyam zhing /
NK123(go)001:8419: tha snyad tsam du btags pa las /
NK123(go)001:8420: der 'dzin gyi bsam brjod las yang dag par 'das pa na /
NK123(go)001:8421: blo dang yid dpyod las 'das pa'i don gnad thog tu 'bebs pa me btsa' lta bu ste /
NK123(go)001:8423: dang po kha 'thor ni ngo bo blo 'das rang
NK123(go)001:8424: byung gi ye shes gnad la brten nas skad cig
NK123(go)001:8427: ngo bo blo bral ma 'khrul ba /
NK123(go)001:8428: rang bzhin rnam rtog gi khung rdib pa /
NK123(go)001:8429: mtshan nyid gnyis med ngos bzung dang bral ba'o //
NK123(go)001:8430: gsum pa rgyud rang gzhung du bstan pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8431: ngo bo ka thams cad kyi byung sar gyur pa /
NK123(go)001:8432: rang bzhin 'khor 'das dang bral bas spang blang bya rtsol med pa /
NK123(go)001:8433: chos nyid sgra tshig tu mi gnas pas stong nyid rtsod gzhi dang bral ba'o //
NK123(go)001:8434: de dag la'ang nang gses kyi dbye ba mang yang
NK123(go)001:8435: gtso bor phyi ma'i bye brag bsnyan rgyud dang bshad
NK123(go)001:8436: rgyud du grags pa la skor bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:8440: thams cad rdzogs pa dang 'dra ba yang gsang bla na med pa'i skor te bzhi'o //
NK123(go)001:8441: dang po phyi skor gyi ngo bo la nyon mongs ma grub pas dug lnga lam du khyer /
NK123(go)001:8442: rang bzhin la rtsol sgrub med pas cir snang chos nyid du shar /
NK123(go)001:8443: mtshan nyid la phyogs cha med pas stong snang gang du'ang phye ba med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8444: nang skor gyi ngo bo gzugs can las 'das pas mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid /
NK123(go)001:8445: rang bzhin 'gro 'ong med pas rtag pa rgyun gyi ye shes /
NK123(go)001:8446: mtshan nyid 'khor 'das gnyis ka la zug pas rtsa ba lta bu /
NK123(go)001:8447: rang ngo tha dad du 'dril bas sdong bu lta bu /
NK123(go)001:8448: rtsal snang cir yang rgyas pas yal ga /
NK123(go)001:8449: gsal cha mi 'gag pas me tog /
NK123(go)001:8450: sna tshogs gcig tu smin pas 'bras bu lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:8451: gsang skor gyi ngo sprad pa dang rtogs pa dus mnyam pas shes rab gsum la ma ltos /
NK123(go)001:8452: rang bzhin dbugs chad pa dang grol ba dus mnyam pas gom stobs la ma ltos /
NK123(go)001:8453: mtshan nyid sangs rgyas pa dang thugs rje 'byung ba
NK123(go)001:8454: dus mnyam pas rgyu tshogs gnyis la mi ltos pa'o
NK123(go)001:8455: // yang gsang bla na med pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8456: ngo bo shes bya ma yin pas shes byed la mi ltos /
NK123(go)001:8457: rang bzhin mngon sum mthong bas chos nyid yid dpyod du mi gnas /
NK123(go)001:8458: mtshan nyid snang ba bzhis 'bras bu phyi dus la
NK123(go)001:8459: re mi 'cha' bar tshe 'di nyid kyis gdod ma'i
NK123(go)001:8461: 'di dag gi don zhib par ni kun mkhyen chos
NK123(go)001:8462: kyi rgyal pa'i gsang mdzod rnams las rtogs par bya'o
NK123(go)001:8463: // tshul khrims la gnyis kyi srung du yod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8464: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig re re la'ang dgu dgur phye ba'i nyer bdun te /
NK123(go)001:8466: sku dang gsung dang thugs dag las //
NK123(go)001:8467: re re la'ang dgu dgu ste //
NK123(go)001:8468: 'jug dang las kyi rnam pas shes //
NK123(go)001:8474: nang pha ma rdo rje spun sring dang rang lus la smod pa /
NK123(go)001:8475: chos dang gang zag la smod pa /
NK123(go)001:8476: rang lus la rdeg 'tshog dang dka' thub kyis brnyas shing gdung ba spong ba gsum /
NK123(go)001:8477: gsang ba rdo rje spun sring gi lus la rdeg par gzas shing rgyan la smod pa /
NK123(go)001:8478: rdo rje mched lcam la brdeg pa dang bla ma'i yum la gtses pa /
NK123(go)001:8479: bla ma'i grib mar 'gongs pa dang spyan sngar lus
NK123(go)001:8480: ngag gi bag med spong ba gsum ste sku yi
NK123(go)001:8481: dam tshig dgu / phyi rdzun phra ma tshig rtsub spong ba gsum /
NK123(go)001:8482: nang chos kyi tshig smra ba /
NK123(go)001:8484: gnas lugs sgom par byed pa rnams la gshe skur 'debs pa spong ba gsum /
NK123(go)001:8485: gsang ba rdo rje spun sring gi tshig /
NK123(go)001:8486: bla ma'i phyag rgya dang nye 'khor gyi tshig /
NK123(go)001:8487: bla ma'i gsung rnams la brnyas shing gcog par spong ba gsum bcas gsung gi dgu /
NK123(go)001:8488: phyi gnod sems rnab sems log lta spong ba gsum /
NK123(go)001:8489: nang spyod pa log pa bag med /
NK123(go)001:8490: sgom pa log pa bying rgod dang gol sgrib /
NK123(go)001:8491: lta ba log pa rtag chad mthar 'dzin rnams spong ba gsum /
NK123(go)001:8492: gsang ba nyin zhag gi thun re re bzhin lta sgom spyod gsum yid la ma byas pa /
NK123(go)001:8493: yi dam gyi lha yid la ma byas pa /
NK123(go)001:8494: bla ma'i rnal 'byor dang mched lcam la brtse gdung
NK123(go)001:8495: yid la ma byas pa gsum spong ba bcas thugs
NK123(go)001:8496: kyi dam tshig dgu ste nyi shu rtsa bdun no
NK123(go)001:8498: thig le kun gsal chen po'i rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:8499: nga yi dam tshig gsang ba ni //
NK123(go)001:8500: rang rig ye shes chen po la //
NK123(go)001:8501: bsrung bya bsrung byed gnyis med pas //
NK123(go)001:8502: nyams dang mi nyams gnyis su med //
NK123(go)001:8503: theg brgyad bcos pa'i dam tshig grangs //
NK123(go)001:8504: nga yis bsrung ba med ces bya //
NK123(go)001:8505: 'og ma'i dam tshig las grol zhing //
NK123(go)001:8506: rang gi sgo bsrung yangs pas na //
NK123(go)001:8507: phyal ba zhes su grags pa yin //
NK123(go)001:8508: bsrung du med pa'i dam tshig la //
NK123(go)001:8509: 'da' mi srid pa'i bsrung thabs ni //
NK123(go)001:8510: rang rig ye shes gcig pu bas //
NK123(go)001:8511: gcig pu zhes su btags pa yin //
NK123(go)001:8512: rang rig ye shes gcig pu la //
NK123(go)001:8513: bya rtsol med pa ye bsrung bas //
NK123(go)001:8514: lhun grub ces su btags pa yin //
NK123(go)001:8515: zhes pa ltar ka dag gi dam tshig med pa dang phyal ba /
NK123(go)001:8516: lhun grub kyi dam tshig gcig pu dang lhun grub ste /
NK123(go)001:8517: dam tshig gi spyi sdom chen po bzhi la sogs pa las /
NK123(go)001:8520: a ti yo ga'i dam tshig ni //
NK123(go)001:8521: med pa dang ni phyal ba dang //
NK123(go)001:8522: gcig pu dang ni lhun gyis grub //
NK123(go)001:8523: de yi don las 'da' mi bya //
NK123(go)001:8526: bstan bcos chen po shes bya kun khyab las /
NK123(go)001:8527: sgom pa sems bde rig stong chos kyi skur //
NK123(go)001:8528: klong sde chos nyid bya rtsol med pa'i ngang //
NK123(go)001:8529: man ngag ye grol spang blang bral bar 'dzeg /
NK123(go)001:8530: ces gsungs pa ltar rdzogs chen sde gsum las /
NK123(go)001:8531: dang po snang srid snod bcud kyi snang ba thams
NK123(go)001:8532: cad sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes brjod bral
NK123(go)001:8533: chos kyi skur gtan la phab nas rig stong chos
NK123(go)001:8534: sku'i ngang du bsal bzhag med par skyong ba sems
NK123(go)001:8535: sde bas ni / chos su ji ltar snang ba
NK123(go)001:8536: la chos nyid kyi phyag rgyas phar rgyas mi 'debs
NK123(go)001:8537: par chos can ji ltar snang ba 'di kun chos
NK123(go)001:8538: nyid byang chub kyi sems su rdzogs pas rtsal lam
NK123(go)001:8539: rol pa tsam du snang rig ngos bzung dang bral
NK123(go)001:8540: ba'i dbyings su skyol bar byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8541: snang ba thams cad sems kyi rang rtsal /
NK123(go)001:8542: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes yin pa la yin par shes nas /
NK123(go)001:8543: de'i ngo bor bzo bcos rtsis gdab med par rnal
NK123(go)001:8544: ma gzhi thog tu 'jog pas 'khrul pa'i snang ba
NK123(go)001:8545: ma spang rang thog tu grol /
NK123(go)001:8546: bsgom bya'i yul stong par rtogs pas sgom ma myong /
NK123(go)001:8547: 'khrul pa'i phug rdeb pas don dang 'bral ma myong
NK123(go)001:8548: ba'i phyir rang snang ris med rig stong chos sku'i
NK123(go)001:8549: ngang du bzhag bya 'jog byed dang bral ba lhun
NK123(go)001:8550: grub mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du 'jog pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8553: ji ltar snang ba de bzhin nyid du gcig /'di la sus kyang 'chos par ma byed cig /
NK123(go)001:8554: ma bcos mnyam pa'i rgyal po de la ni //
NK123(go)001:8555: mi rtog chos sku'i dgongs pa de la gnas //
NK123(go)001:8557: dran bsam yid la 'gyu ba ma lus kun //
NK123(go)001:8558: skye ba med pa'i ngag las ma yengs pas //
NK123(go)001:8559: gang ltar bsam kyang sgom pa yin shes na //
NK123(go)001:8560: ma bsgom gang ltar bzhag kyang yengs pa med //
NK123(go)001:8562: gnyis pa rang byung gi ye shes dang de las
NK123(go)001:8563: shar ba'i chos thams cad ye grol rang dag chos
NK123(go)001:8564: nyid kun tu bzang mo'i klong nas 'gro sa gzhan
NK123(go)001:8565: med par gtan la phab nas chos dmigs med bya
NK123(go)001:8566: rtsol dang bral ba'i ngang du skyong ba klong sde
NK123(go)001:8567: bas ni / da lta'i dus su smin grol gyi rgyun bzhugs rdo rje zam pa ltar na /
NK123(go)001:8571: 'bras bu blo dang bral ba bzhir gnad du 'du zhing /
NK123(go)001:8572: de yang gnad bzhi dang ldan pa'i tshul bzhis dbang bzhi'i don lam du byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8573: dbang po rang yan gsal ba'i gnad /
NK123(go)001:8574: sgron ma mi 'gul stong pa'i gnad /
NK123(go)001:8575: thung ser gyen 'then bde ba'i gnad /
NK123(go)001:8576: smra byed ma reg dbyer med pa'i gnad bzhis /
NK123(go)001:8580: chos nyid kyi tshul te rdo rje'i tshig rkang gis
NK123(go)001:8581: bstan pa'i brda' bzhi'am tshul bzhi gnang dang 'brel bar
NK123(go)001:8582: gzir te / dbang bzhi'i ye shes dang pos gsal ba bum dbang /
NK123(go)001:8583: gnyis pas stong pa gsang dbang /
NK123(go)001:8584: gsum pas bde ba shar dbang /
NK123(go)001:8585: bzhi pas chos nyid bzhi ba'i don dam du byed pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8587: ma nor ba yi chos nyid la //
NK123(go)001:8588: ma bcos gnas shing ma byas gsal //
NK123(go)001:8589: ma 'gags pa nyid ye shes klong //
NK123(go)001:8590: de bzhin nyid kyi gnas 'di la //
NK123(go)001:8591: yengs dang ma yengs med pa dang //
NK123(go)001:8592: g.yo dang mi g.yo med pa'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:8593: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'di las med //
NK123(go)001:8595: 'jog thabs kyi gnad mdor bsdu na /
NK123(go)001:8598: gces grol gsum du 'du zhing de dag gi don
NK123(go)001:8599: yang dmigs gtan la bral ba'i gnad zab mos chos
NK123(go)001:8600: nyid bya rtsol med pa'i ngang du 'jog pa la
NK123(go)001:8601: 'adu'o // gsum pa ye grol spang blang bral ba'i
NK123(go)001:8602: chos nyid kyi ngang du 'jog pa man ngag gi
NK123(go)001:8603: sde la phyi nang gsang ba yang gsang bzhi las
NK123(go)001:8604: 'adu'o // / 'dir yang gsang bla med kyi dbang du byas na /
NK123(go)001:8605: ye grol spang blang bral ba zung 'jug gnyis su
NK123(go)001:8606: med pa'i ye shes kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK123(go)001:8607: cad chos nyid stong 'dzin dang bral ba'i ngang du
NK123(go)001:8609: 'khor 'das gang du'ang ma phye ba'i rig pa chos nyid kyi yul la mngon sum du shar nas /
NK123(go)001:8610: rang rig lu gu rgyud kyi skur smin pas gnad
NK123(go)001:8611: thog tu grol bar byed pa gnad la theb pa
NK123(go)001:8613: de la'ang sems gzhi med rtsa bral ka dag tu gtan la phab nas /
NK123(go)001:8614: snang sems thams cad ye grol sor bzhag chen po khregs chod kyi nyams len dang /
NK123(go)001:8615: lhun grub lus kyi dkyil 'khor de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang mdzod sgo phye nas /
NK123(go)001:8616: rang gnas kyi ye shes 'od gsal lhun grub kyi
NK123(go)001:8617: dkyil 'khor du zhal lta ba thod rgal gyi nyams
NK123(go)001:8620: nyams blang khregs gcod thod rgal lo //
NK123(go)001:8621: zhes gsungs de las dang po khregs chod kyi nyams len ni /
NK123(go)001:8622: rang byung gzhir gnas kyi rig pa byang chub kyi
NK123(go)001:8623: sems rang gi ngo bo ye gdod ma nas 'khor
NK123(go)001:8624: ba'i chos gang gis kyang ma gos pas srid pa'i
NK123(go)001:8625: nyer len gyi rgyu zad pas ye grol /
NK123(go)001:8626: gnyen po gang gis kyang ma bcos par gang shar
NK123(go)001:8627: thams cad sbrul mdud rang zhig pa bzhin 'grol byed
NK123(go)001:8628: gzhan la ma ltos pas rang grol /
NK123(go)001:8629: tshogs brgyad kyi shes pa thams cad kyang yul yul
NK123(go)001:8630: can gnyis su med pa skad cig nyid la thog
NK123(go)001:8631: bab chen por rang bzhin gyis grol bas gcer grol
NK123(go)001:8632: / dus gsum dang shes bya gang du'ang mi gnas pas mtha' grol te /
NK123(go)001:8633: de ltar grol lugs chen po bzhi'i ngang du gnas
NK123(go)001:8634: pa ni lam 'di nyid kyi khyad par gyi chos
NK123(go)001:8636: kun tu bzang po ye shes zang thal gyi dgongs
NK123(go)001:8637: pa ye gdod ma'i ka dag gi gnas lugs ji
NK123(go)001:8638: lta ba de da lta mngon sum rang thog tu
NK123(go)001:8639: ngo shes pas ngo rang thog tu 'phrod /
NK123(go)001:8642: spang gnyen ma zhugs pa'i rig pa de nyid ji
NK123(go)001:8643: ltar 'dug kyang chos sku rang byung gi ye shes
NK123(go)001:8644: las ma 'das pas thag gcig thog tu chod /
NK123(go)001:8645: ci snang ci shar thams cad dang po chos nyid
NK123(go)001:8646: kyi rtsal du byung da lta chos nyid kyi ngang
NK123(go)001:8647: la gnas / mthar chos nyid kyi ngang du thims pas gdeng grol thog tu bca'/
NK123(go)001:8648: de dag gi bogs 'don du phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK123(go)001:8649: nam mkha' sum phrugs kyi gdams pa sogs la rnal
NK123(go)001:8651: mdor na ri bo cog bzhag gi lta bas rang
NK123(go)001:8652: byung gi ye shes rig stong chos sku'i ngo bor
NK123(go)001:8653: thag bcad / rgya mtsho cog bzhag gi sgom pas
NK123(go)001:8654: rang grol sor bzhag snang sems chig chod du grol
NK123(go)001:8655: ba du ma rol mnyam chen por 'gag bsdam /
NK123(go)001:8656: snang ba cog bzhag gi spyod pas skyes grol thugs phrad ris med du sbyang bas bog dbyung /
NK123(go)001:8657: rig pa cog bzhag gi 'bras bus rang rdzogs lhun
NK123(go)001:8658: grub chen po la re dogs kyi 'phrang mi bca'
NK123(go)001:8662: lhun gyis gnas pas bzhag pa yin /
NK123(go)001:8664: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK123(go)001:8665: sems kyi rang bzhin ye gnas bud+d+ha ste //
NK123(go)001:8666: sems la skye 'gag med pa nam mkha' 'dra //
NK123(go)001:8667: chos kun mnyam nyid yang dag don rtogs nas //
NK123(go)001:8668: de nyid ma btsal bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK123(go)001:8669: zhe a ti zab don snying por gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:8670: de ltar bsgoms pas nyams kyi skye rim yang bzhi ste /
NK123(go)001:8671: mnyam dang mi g.yo mnyam nyid lhun gyis grub //
NK123(go)001:8673: dang po gnas pa'i nyams shes pa yul phyir mi 'gro ba rtse gcig thun thub pa /
NK123(go)001:8674: gnyis pa mi g.yo ba'i nyams ting nge 'dzin la bying rgod la sogs pa'i rkyen dang bral ba /
NK123(go)001:8675: gsum pa mnyam pa nyid kyi nyams 'khor 'das ro
NK123(go)001:8676: mnyam pa'i mnyam bzhag nam mkha' lta bu dang rjes
NK123(go)001:8677: shes su sgyu ma lta bu khong du chud pas
NK123(go)001:8679: bzhi pa lhun gyi grub pa'i nyams ting nge 'dzin
NK123(go)001:8680: thun mtshams las 'das shing blo zad chos zad du
NK123(go)001:8681: song ba'o // gnyis pa lhun grub thod rgal gyi nyams len ni /
NK123(go)001:8682: thog mar sku gsum gyi sna khrid par byed pa 'byung bzhi'i sgra don la bslab pa /
NK123(go)001:8683: rig pa'i sna khrid par byed pa 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa /
NK123(go)001:8684: sems kyi sna khrid par byed pa sgo gsum gyi sngon 'gro rnams legs par 'byongs nas /
NK123(go)001:8686: rig pa mi gnas pa gnas par bya ba'i gdams ngag gi shes pa bag btsal bas /
NK123(go)001:8687: rig pa ma zin pa zin par bya ba'i gdams
NK123(go)001:8688: ngag gi gnad rnams pa gsum la mkhas par bya
NK123(go)001:8689: ba / rig pa mi brtan pa brtan pa brtan
NK123(go)001:8690: par bya ba'i gdams ngag gis yul dang shes pa
NK123(go)001:8691: ba / bsre ba / rig pa ma skyes pa
NK123(go)001:8692: skyes par bya ba'i gdams ngag gis snang ba'i tshad
NK123(go)001:8693: ba / bsre ba / bzung ba / rig pa
NK123(go)001:8694: ma shes pa shes par bya ba'i gdams ngag gis
NK123(go)001:8695: drod tshad gtan la dbab pa /
NK123(go)001:8696: rig pa ma grol ba grol bar bya ba'i gdams
NK123(go)001:8697: ngag gis sku gsum gyi sa la goms par bya
NK123(go)001:8698: ba ste gnad chen po drug gi sgrom du gzhug
NK123(go)001:8700: bca' ba lus kyi gnad gsum /
NK123(go)001:8702: snang ba yul gyi gnad gsum ste gnad gsum mam
NK123(go)001:8703: dgu la brten nas mngon sum rang thog tu phab
NK123(go)001:8704: ste nyams su blang bas snang bzhi rim gyis 'char
NK123(go)001:8705: te / shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma spros
NK123(go)001:8706: bral gnyug ma'i ye shes ka dag khregs chod kyi
NK123(go)001:8707: dgongs pa rig stong zang thal du rtogs pa de'i
NK123(go)001:8708: dbyings nas 'od gsal gyi snang ba dpag tu med
NK123(go)001:8710: rgyang zhags chu'i sgron ma 'od rtsa dar dkar gyi
NK123(go)001:8711: rkud pa lta bus rig gdangs 'char ba'i sgo phyes
NK123(go)001:8712: / dag pa dbyings kyi sgron ma 'od lnga 'ja'
NK123(go)001:8713: tshon gyi snang bas zhing khams dang gzhal yas kyi
NK123(go)001:8714: / rgyan bkram nas / thig le stong pa'i sgron
NK123(go)001:8715: ma 'od khyim zlum po'i rnam pa las zhi khro'i
NK123(go)001:8717: de yang dang po chos nyid mngon sum gyi skabs
NK123(go)001:8718: su rgyu yis ma bskyed pa'i 'od lnga 'ja' tshon
NK123(go)001:8719: gyi snang ba dbyings su shar nas zhing khams kyi
NK123(go)001:8720: sgo phye / de las cher mched de thig le
NK123(go)001:8721: sku ru smin du nye ba nyams gang 'phel sprul
NK123(go)001:8722: sgo phye / sku / rkyen gyis ma bskyed pa'i
NK123(go)001:8723: snang nyams rigs lnga'i tshom bu'i sku ru smin pa
NK123(go)001:8724: rig pa tshad phebs longs sku /
NK123(go)001:8725: de nas snang ba thams cad thig le gcig gi
NK123(go)001:8726: dkyil 'khor du dag nas blos btag pa'i chos so
NK123(go)001:8727: cog thams cad zad cing chos nyid du 'dzin pa
NK123(go)001:8728: tsam yang zad pas chos sku'i snang ba mthong ste
NK123(go)001:8730: chos nyid mngon sum mthong ba yis //
NK123(go)001:8732: nyams snang gang du 'phel ba yis //
NK123(go)001:8733: 'khrul pa'i snang ba nub pa dang //
NK123(go)001:8734: bar do'i ye shes mngon du byed //
NK123(go)001:8735: rig pa tshad 'phebs snang ba yis //
NK123(go)001:8736: sku gsum rtogs pa'i lam snang 'das //
NK123(go)001:8737: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba yis //
NK123(go)001:8738: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyun thag chad //
NK123(go)001:8740: rjes mtha' rten gyi man ngag mi 'gul ba gsum la gzhi bca'/
NK123(go)001:8741: sdod pa gsum gyi tshad bzung /
NK123(go)001:8742: thob pa gsum gyis gzer gdab gdeng bzhi'i grol tshad bstan pa dang bzhis mthar dbyung ba ste /
NK123(go)001:8743: de dag gi gnad zab mo rnams ni bla ma
NK123(go)001:8744: yang tig yid bzhin nor bu sogs gsang ba snying
NK123(go)001:8745: thig gi gzhung khrid rnams las shes par bya dgos
NK123(go)001:8746: la / 'dir mngon sum 'od gsal la lta ba'i
NK123(go)001:8747: rig pa skad cig de nyid la khams gsum pa'i
NK123(go)001:8748: sems sems byung kun gzhi dang bcas pa ldog tshul
NK123(go)001:8749: la / / ye shes kyi ngo bo la dgongs pa'i tshang tshul /
NK123(go)001:8750: 'og ma snying po gong mar 'du tshul gsum brtsi na /
NK123(go)001:8751: dang po mngon sum la bltas pas nang kun rtog gi 'phro 'du med pas 'dod pa'i sems log /
NK123(go)001:8752: gsal ba'i ngang la gsal bar 'jog byed kyi gnyen po med pas gzugs kyi sems log /
NK123(go)001:8753: rtog med rtse cig la chos nyid du zhen pa'i blo med pas gzugs med kyi sems log /
NK123(go)001:8754: dwangs la rig pa'i phyir kun gzhi las log /
NK123(go)001:8755: rang byung gi ye shes su thag chod pas kun gzhi'i rnam shes las log /
NK123(go)001:8756: snang ba 'od gsal gyi yul las tha mal gyi
NK123(go)001:8757: rdzas su snang ba med pas sgo lnga'i rnam shes
NK123(go)001:8758: las log / de'i tshe dpyod byed kyi rtog pa
NK123(go)001:8759: dang chags sdang gi kun rtog med pas yid shes
NK123(go)001:8760: dang nyon yid las ldog ste /
NK123(go)001:8761: mdor na khams gsum gyi sems dang sems byung thams
NK123(go)001:8762: cad las rnam par grol ba ni sangs rgyas kyi
NK123(go)001:8763: ye shes zhi ba nyid las gzhan ma yin pas
NK123(go)001:8765: de'i phyir dkon mchog brtsegs pa chen po'i chos kyi rnam grangs las /
NK123(go)001:8767: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi gsang ba 'di sems
NK123(go)001:8768: dang yid dang rnam par shes pa dang yang bral
NK123(go)001:8769: la / ting nge 'dzin gyi gnad kyang mi 'dor la /
NK123(go)001:8770: 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8772: gang dag sngags kyi grub mtha' rgyud sde 'og ma
NK123(go)001:8773: rnams su ro rkyang gi rlung dbu mar tshud pas
NK123(go)001:8774: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes la lhan cig
NK123(go)001:8775: skyes pa'i ye shes su 'dod pa gang zhig kun
NK123(go)001:8776: gzhi'i tshogs brgyad las ma log ste /
NK123(go)001:8777: tshor ba bde ba ni yid dang nyon yid kyis rjes su bskyed cing /
NK123(go)001:8778: dwangs ma phyed pa'i sems rtog med kun gzhi /
NK123(go)001:8779: cung zad gsal dwangs tsam kun gzhi'i rnam shes /
NK123(go)001:8780: gzugs sogs yul lnga rags pa dang dbang shes so
NK123(go)001:8781: so la snang ba sgo lnga'i rnam shes las ma
NK123(go)001:8782: 'das pas / de dag ma log na 'khor ba las mi grol te /
NK123(go)001:8783: 'khor ba'i sems las ma grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:8784: yang de dag rtsa rlung thig le ro gcig tu
NK123(go)001:8785: 'dres pa'i dga' ba rnal ma'i don du 'dod pas
NK123(go)001:8786: / rlung dang khams rnams ro rkyang nas dbu mar
NK123(go)001:8787: 'jug cing rtsa mdud re grol stobs kyis yon tan
NK123(go)001:8788: re 'char bar 'dod pas gegs mang la /
NK123(go)001:8789: 'gro drug gi rtsa 'dab tu rlung sems zhugs pas
NK123(go)001:8790: ma dag pa'i 'khrul snang mang po 'char ba'i phyir
NK123(go)001:8791: gol ma gol gyi gnad kyang de yin la /
NK123(go)001:8792: 'dir ni las rlung rnams rang zhir 'jog pa las
NK123(go)001:8793: dbu mar 'jug pa sogs kyi rtsol ba med la
NK123(go)001:8794: rtsa 'dab so so'i rlung rang dag la song dus
NK123(go)001:8795: / 'od rtsa'i ye shes kyi rlung rang sa na
NK123(go)001:8796: rang gsal bas dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba
NK123(go)001:8797: sku dang zhing khams dang 'od kyi rang bzhin las
NK123(go)001:8798: ma dag pa'i 'khrul snang 'char ba'i skabs med cing
NK123(go)001:8799: / / dbu ma'i 'od rtsa rnams 'phel bas rtsa
NK123(go)001:8800: mdud kyi rnam pa rnams rim gyis 'od du yal
NK123(go)001:8801: ba'i yon tan las sa'i mngon rtogs rnams rang snang
NK123(go)001:8802: / / du 'char ro // de yang rtsa mdud dang po gnyis 'od du grol bas /
NK123(go)001:8803: phyir snang 'od kyi nang du sangs rgyas kyi zhing
NK123(go)001:8804: khams brgya phrag 'char ba dang de dag tu 'od
NK123(go)001:8806: rang snang du 'dus pas bgrod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8807: lus 'gul bas zhing brgya g.yo ba dang /
NK123(go)001:8808: nang du chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK123(go)001:8809: brgya la snyoms par 'jug cing ldang ba sogs mthong
NK123(go)001:8810: lam gyi yon tan brgya phrag bcu gnyis po 'byung
NK123(go)001:8811: zhing / des mtshon te dbu ma'i 'dud pa gnyis
NK123(go)001:8812: gnyis grol ba las sa gong ma gong ma'i yon
NK123(go)001:8813: tan rnams rtsol ba med par snang ba'i phyir 'og
NK123(go)001:8814: ma rnams las ches khyad par du 'phags shing myur
NK123(go)001:8817: dus 'khor gyi stong gzugs sogs sgom pa las byung bas mchog la /
NK123(go)001:8818: rdzogs chen thod rgal bsgom pa la'ang 'char bas dman snyam pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8819: dus 'khor gyi bde stong zung 'jug bsgom pas skye la /
NK123(go)001:8820: rdzogs chen rig pa bsgom mi dgos par ngo sprad pas dman no snyam pa gyi na ste /
NK123(go)001:8821: dus 'khor dang rdzogs chen gnyis ka chos nyid lam du byed par 'dra yang /
NK123(go)001:8822: chos nyid ni gsar du bsgoms pas byas pa ma yin te /
NK123(go)001:8823: gal te yin na bcos ma glo bur bar gyur pas dman no //
NK123(go)001:8824: chos nyid gsar byung ma yin na ye nas yod pa nyid ngo sprad pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8825: bstan te lam du byas pas grol ba la rdzogs chen gyi lam mchog tu grub pa yin no //
NK123(go)001:8826: de la rdzogs chen gyi rig pa'ang ngo ma sprad na mi rtogs la /
NK123(go)001:8827: ma rtogs na de nyid bsgom mi shes /
NK123(go)001:8828: bsgom ma shes shing ma bsgom na mi grol bas bsgom pas grol ba gnyis ka 'dra yang /
NK123(go)001:8829: rdzogs chen khregs thod gnyis bsgom dgos pas rtsol ba'i lam du mi 'gro ste /
NK123(go)001:8830: rtsol ba'i lam gyis ye shes gzod tshol ba min par /
NK123(go)001:8831: rtsol med du ye shes la 'jug pa'i cha nas rtsol med ces brjod pa'i phyir ro //
NK123(go)001:8832: des na thod rgal mi snang ba 'di rtsol med
NK123(go)001:8833: du yod kyang lam du ma byas na mi rtogs
NK123(go)001:8834: la / byas na 'od gsal gyi rtags snang de
NK123(go)001:8835: nyid kyi mthus gdos bcas kyi phung po dbyings su
NK123(go)001:8836: 'gags nas don gyi lhan skyes bde chen rdo rje'i
NK123(go)001:8838: rlung nyi khri chig stong sogs ma dag pa'i rtsa
NK123(go)001:8839: rlung thig ler rags lus kyi steng du 'gag pa
NK123(go)001:8840: gtso bor mi byed par ma dag pa'i rtsa rlung
NK123(go)001:8841: thams cad rang 'gags su song nas don dam ye
NK123(go)001:8842: shes kyi sku 'grub pa de las lhag pa gzhan
NK123(go)001:8843: gsar rnying gi rgyud dang man ngag gang la'ang cung
NK123(go)001:8844: zad med pas gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde kun gyi
NK123(go)001:8845: rdzogs rim thams cad dus 'khor gyi rdzogs rim gyi
NK123(go)001:8847: de'i mtha' yang rdzogs pa chen po nyid la thug
NK123(go)001:8848: nas mthar phyin par byed pas na kun gyi bla
NK123(go)001:8850: 'di dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas pa ni gnyug sems
NK123(go)001:8851: 'od gsal gyi don la dpyod pa'i skabs sogs las
NK123(go)001:8852: shes par bya'o // gnyis pa ye shes kyi ngo bo la dgongs pa'i tshang tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:8853: de ltar gnad las mthong ba'i mngon sum la lta ba'i skad cig la /
NK123(go)001:8854: dwangs ma mi g.yo ba spro bsdu dang bral ba'i
NK123(go)001:8855: ye shes nang du shar ba ni khregs chod chos
NK123(go)001:8856: sku rang thog tu 'phebs pa yin la /
NK123(go)001:8857: phyi snang 'od gsal du snang ba'i thabs ni /
NK123(go)001:8858: thod rgal lhun grub tu shar ba'i gzugs sku lam du byed pas /
NK123(go)001:8859: phyir snang bskyed rim thabs su shar ba'i gnad las /
NK123(go)001:8860: nang gsal skye med spros kun zhi ba'i rdzogs rim
NK123(go)001:8861: mu mtha' dang bral ba'i shes rab mngon du gyur
NK123(go)001:8866: tshogs gnyis rnams khregs chod dang thod rgal sgom pa'i skad cig la rdzogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8867: de'i tshe sku lnga ye shes dang bcas pa'ang tshang ste /
NK123(go)001:8868: rtse gcig spros pa dang bral bas chos sku /
NK123(go)001:8869: rang gsal 'dzin pa med pas longs sku /
NK123(go)001:8870: sna tshogs yul la shar bas sprul sku /
NK123(go)001:8871: tshogs brgyad rnam shes log pas byang chub kyi sku /
NK123(go)001:8872: dbyings la 'pho 'gyur med pas rdo rje'i sku'o //
NK123(go)001:8874: dmigs bsam spros pa dang bral ba chos dbyings ye shes /
NK123(go)001:8875: gsal la 'grib pa med pa me long ye shes /
NK123(go)001:8876: ro mnyam ngang la gnas pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK123(go)001:8877: snang ba 'od lnga ma 'dres pa kun rtog ye shes /
NK123(go)001:8878: gzung 'dzin gnyis snang grol bas bya grub ye shes so //
NK123(go)001:8879: ye shes de dag mkha' 'gro lnga'i rang bzhin du'ang gnas shing /
NK123(go)001:8881: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i don skad cig la tshang bar gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8882: gzhan yang rig pa rang shar las /
NK123(go)001:8883: sa zhes bya ba gud na yod pa ma yin no //
NK123(go)001:8884: bden pa mthong ba'i gang zag gcig la sa rnams rdzogs nas yod de /
NK123(go)001:8885: de'ang ngo sprod pa bstan pa'i gang zag de /
NK123(go)001:8886: dang po bden pa mthong ba'i dus na de la
NK123(go)001:8887: dga' ba skyes pa ni sa dang po rab tu
NK123(go)001:8889: ka dag gi sa la ye shes lhug par shes
NK123(go)001:8890: nas de'i gong na gzhan med pa ni bcu drug
NK123(go)001:8891: ye shes bla ma'i sa thob pa'o //
NK123(go)001:8892: zhes pa'i bar gyis gsungs pa bzhin /
NK123(go)001:8893: mngon sum lam gyi bden pa mthong ba sogs sa
NK123(go)001:8894: dang po rab tu dga' ba nas kun 'od bar
NK123(go)001:8895: bcu gcig dang / khyad par gyi sa bcu gnyis
NK123(go)001:8896: ma chags pad+ma can nas bcu drug ye shes bla
NK123(go)001:8897: ma'i sa yi bar du sbyor bar mdzad do //
NK123(go)001:8898: gsum pa 'og ma'i snying po gong mar 'du tshul ni /
NK123(go)001:8899: 'od gsal gyi skad cig la gnas pa de'i tshe /
NK123(go)001:8900: gang zag dang chos kyi bdag tu 'dzin pa med
NK123(go)001:8901: pas nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' gsum
NK123(go)001:8902: gyi lta ba'i dgongs pa 'dus so //
NK123(go)001:8903: lus ngag yid gsum nyon mongs pa'i dri ma med
NK123(go)001:8904: pas gtsang sbra spyod pa k+r+ai ya u pa yo
NK123(go)001:8905: ga gsum gyi ye shes dri med gsum 'dus so
NK123(go)001:8906: // snang ba rig pa gnyis med gsum zung du
NK123(go)001:8907: chud de rtogs pa ting nge 'dzin khyad par can
NK123(go)001:8908: mngon du gyur pas ma h+aa a nu a ti
NK123(go)001:8910: de bzhin du gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang sa
NK123(go)001:8911: lam rnams kyang rig pa'i ye shes dri ma med
NK123(go)001:8912: pa la gnas pa'i chas bzhag pas de dag kyang
NK123(go)001:8913: 'du ste / theg pa 'og mar nyams su len
NK123(go)001:8914: pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang rtogs pa'i yon tan gyi
NK123(go)001:8916: skyon gyi cha rnams med pas ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK123(go)001:8917: zhes kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos gsungs so //
NK123(go)001:8919: cir snang chos nyid kyi rol par shar bas blang dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK123(go)001:8921: bya ba med pas las rnams zin //
NK123(go)001:8924: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni /
NK123(go)001:8925: lta sgom srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8926: shugs las byung ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK123(go)001:8927: ji ltar snyan pa'i spyod pa bzhin //
NK123(go)001:8928: gang la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK123(go)001:8932: rnal 'byor don la sus sbyor ba //
NK123(go)001:8933: spyod pa 'di rnams goms par bya //
NK123(go)001:8934: bung ba lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8935: chos rnams kun gyi ro myong bya //
NK123(go)001:8936: ri dwags lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8937: 'khrul ba'i rkyen gyur yul rnams spang //
NK123(go)001:8938: lkugs pa lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8939: 'khrul pa'i ngag rnams rnam par spangs //
NK123(go)001:8940: thi bya lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8941: gsang ba'i sngags kyi the tshom gcad //
NK123(go)001:8942: smyon pa lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8943: gcig tu gnas pa'i yul rnams spangs //
NK123(go)001:8944: seng ge lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8945: 'jigs pa'i sems spang dur khrod rgyu //
NK123(go)001:8946: khyi phag lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8947: gtsang dang sme ba'i rtog pa spangs //
NK123(go)001:8949: bu lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8950: dran bsam thog bab nyid du spyod //
NK123(go)001:8952: bu chung lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8953: 'khrul pa'i spyod pa rgyun ring spangs //
NK123(go)001:8954: ngang mo rdza bo yang snang /
NK123(go)001:8956: 'jig rten mthun pa'i tshig gis drangs //
NK123(go)001:8957: glang chen lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8958: 'khor ba'i g.yul rnams gting nas bzlog /
NK123(go)001:8959: ri sked ri dwags kyang snang /
NK123(go)001:8961: bu dang dgra yi 'du shes spangs //
NK123(go)001:8962: rgya mo lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8963: 'dod pa chog shes dus tshod gcad //
NK123(go)001:8964: dre'u lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8965: 'khor ba'i sa bon spel mi bya //
NK123(go)001:8966: bram ze lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8967: gzhan gyi longs spyod zas rnams spangs //
NK123(go)001:8968: dpa' bo lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8970: chu mig lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8971: dran pa'i rten nyid rang sar bzhag /
NK123(go)001:8972: nam mkha' mdung bskor spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8973: dngos po rnams la zang thal spyad //
NK123(go)001:8974: bar snang rlung 'dra'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8975: gzung dang 'dzin pa'i rtog pa spangs //
NK123(go)001:8976: bya khyung lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
