NK123(go)001:8977: g.yang sa rnams ni rlabs kyis gcod //
NK123(go)001:8978: ri bo lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8979: 'gyur med rang dag steng du spyod //
NK123(go)001:8980: thog chen lta bu'i spyod pa yis //
NK123(go)001:8981: snang ba phyir mi ldog par spyod //
NK123(go)001:8982: ces nyi shu rtsa gcig tu gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:8984: thog mar sgo kun nas bsdud pa bung ba tshang
NK123(go)001:8985: 'tshol ba lta bus shes rab gsum gyis phyi nang
NK123(go)001:8987: de'i grogs su the tshom med pa thi bya tshang
NK123(go)001:8988: du 'jug pa lta bus rang nyid gang la yid
NK123(go)001:8989: ches pa'i gdams pa de nyams su len /
NK123(go)001:8990: de'i grogs kun gyi spyod yul ma yin pa ri dwags lta bus rtag tu dben pa brten /
NK123(go)001:8991: de'i grogs lkug pa lta bus smra ba bcad de su dang yang gtam mi smra /
NK123(go)001:8992: de ltar byas pas dran pa rengs pas smyon pa lta bu'i spyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:8993: gtsang sme med pa khyi phag lta bu'i spyod pa shugs kyis 'byung la /
NK123(go)001:8994: de drug rdzogs pa las zil gyis mi gnon pas
NK123(go)001:8995: seng ge lta bu'i spyod pa 'byung ste rnal 'byor
NK123(go)001:8996: pa de su la'ang 'jigs pa dang bag tsha ba
NK123(go)001:8997: med par 'byung bzhi'i gnod pa sogs kyis mi bardzi
NK123(go)001:8998: zhing snang ba la dbang bsgyur bas snang ba dbang
NK123(go)001:8999: bsgyur gyi spyod pa zhes bya ste mthar phyin pa'o
NK123(go)001:9002: rdzogs chen a ti'i 'bras bu ni //
NK123(go)001:9003: gdod nas snying po byang chub tu //
NK123(go)001:9004: thob med 'bras bu rang la smin //
NK123(go)001:9006: lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i sa la da lta nyid nas gnas pa mthar phyin pa ste /
NK123(go)001:9007: gdeng bzhi tshad du phyin pas 'khor ba myang 'das su grol ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9010: mi 'gyur lta ba'i gdeng chen bzhis //
NK123(go)001:9011: mi ldog ye shes tshad kyang bzungs //
NK123(go)001:9013: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal dang tshe tshad la
NK123(go)001:9014: sogs pa thos kyang rang ngo gdod nas 'khrul mi
NK123(go)001:9015: shes pa'i thog tu bde sdug shes bya la mi
NK123(go)001:9016: srid par thag chod pas ngan song la bag mi
NK123(go)001:9017: tsha ba'i gdeng / rig pa gzhi thog tu pheb
NK123(go)001:9018: pa la 'khor ba'i ming tsam du'ang ma grub pas
NK123(go)001:9019: rgyu 'bras rnam smin la mi re ba'i gdeng /
NK123(go)001:9020: chos nyid kyi gshis la 'di ltar grol nas 'di
NK123(go)001:9021: tsam du bade'o snyam pa'i myang 'das rang mtshan pa
NK123(go)001:9022: med pas thob bya la re ba med pa'i gdeng
NK123(go)001:9023: / rgyal ba'i khams la yon tan tshad med par
NK123(go)001:9024: thob kyang rang ngo rig pa las tha dad pa'i
NK123(go)001:9025: sangs rgyas spu'i rtse mo tsam du'ang med pa gshis
NK123(go)001:9026: thog tu phebs pas dga' brod mnyam pa nyid du
NK123(go)001:9028: de ltar gdeng rnam pa bzhi'i tshad du skyol nas
NK123(go)001:9029: mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong khyer dam par 'jug
NK123(go)001:9030: par ni / rdo rje sems dpa'i snying gi me long gi rgyud las /
NK123(go)001:9031: mya ngan las 'das pa de yang gnyis te /
NK123(go)001:9032: yang dag par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK123(go)001:9033: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9034: de la yang dag par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK123(go)001:9035: phung po lhag ma med par sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9036: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i skyes bu de la 'od dang /
NK123(go)001:9040: sa g.yo ba la sogs par 'byung ngo //
NK123(go)001:9041: zhes gsungs pa'i snga ma lce btsun chen po sogs dang /
NK123(go)001:9042: phyi ma kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dri med
NK123(go)001:9043: 'od zer lta bu yin par rig 'dzin 'jigs med
NK123(go)001:9045: de yang ka dag khregs chod kyi nyams len mthar
NK123(go)001:9046: phyin pas lus rdul phran du deng ba nam mkha'
NK123(go)001:9047: dang mkha' 'gro lta bu'i 'chi lugs gnyis dang /
NK123(go)001:9048: lhun grub thod rgal gyi nyams len mthar phyin nas
NK123(go)001:9049: dwangs ma 'od phung du deng pa rig 'dzin dang
NK123(go)001:9050: me phung lta bu'i 'chi lugs gnyis te bzhir gsungs
NK123(go)001:9051: shing / de las snga ma gnyis ni /
NK123(go)001:9052: lus rdul phran dang sems chos nyid du dengs nas
NK123(go)001:9053: ka dag gi sar skad cig la grol ba spang
NK123(go)001:9054: mi pham mgon po bdun brgyud lta bu ste /
NK123(go)001:9055: 'di'i lugs la 'pho chen rdo rje'i skur bzhengs mi nus par gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:9056: phyi ma gnyis kyi dbang du byas na snang ba bzhi'i lam rdzogs nas /
NK123(go)001:9057: lus des gzhan don 'grub par gzigs na srid pa
NK123(go)001:9058: ji srid bzhugs par dgongs pa de srid du sku
NK123(go)001:9059: de nyid chu'i zla ba ltar /
NK123(go)001:9060: snang gzugs yod kyang reg gzugs med par bzhugs nas
NK123(go)001:9061: sems can gyi don mdzad pa 'pho ba chen po'i
NK123(go)001:9063: slob dpon chen po bi ma la dang pad+ma lta
NK123(go)001:9064: bu rdzu 'phrul dang chos kyi rnam grangs bsam gyis
NK123(go)001:9065: mi khyab pa skad cig gcig la ston pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9066: lus des gzhan don rgya chen mi 'grub par gzigs
NK123(go)001:9067: na 'od gsal du grol ba'i ngang de nyid dbyings
NK123(go)001:9068: gdod ma'i sar sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub
NK123(go)001:9069: pas / chos sku'i zhing na kun tu bzang por
NK123(go)001:9070: bzhugs bzhin du de'i ngang las longs sku'i zhing khams
NK123(go)001:9071: stug po bkod pa rang snang longs spyod rdzogs par
NK123(go)001:9073: dag pa'i zhing du rigs lngar snang bas sa la gnas pa'i sems dpa' rnams kyi don mdzod cing /
NK123(go)001:9074: 'gro ba drug gi gnas su rang rang gi ston
NK123(go)001:9075: par snang nas don mdzad pa mchog gi sprul pa
NK123(go)001:9076: dang / bzo dang skye ba sprul pa la sogs
NK123(go)001:9077: pa srid pa ji srid par 'phrin las rgyun mi
NK123(go)001:9078: 'chad par so so'i snang ba bzhin du 'byung ba
NK123(go)001:9079: dang / ste / zhib par dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi grol lugs dang /
NK123(go)001:9081: sku dang ye shes kyi rnam bzhag sogs rgyas par
NK123(go)001:9082: theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod sogs kun mkhyen chos
NK123(go)001:9083: kyi rgyal po'i gsung rab rnams las shes par bya
NK123(go)001:9085: mdor na sngags phyi rgyud rnams las sngags grub pa'i
NK123(go)001:9086: mthus 'dod gzugs kyi lha dang skal ba mnyam pa'i
NK123(go)001:9087: lus su gyur nas mkha' spyod kyi rig 'dzin grub
NK123(go)001:9088: pa sogs dang / gsang 'dus rim lnga sogs su
NK123(go)001:9089: phra ba'i rlung sems sgyu ma'i sku bsgrub tshul dang
NK123(go)001:9090: pa sogs dang / / 'od gsal thod rgal gyii snang bzhi mthar phyin nas /
NK123(go)001:9091: gdos bcas rags pa'i lus 'di yang 'od du yal te /
NK123(go)001:9092: rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal shin tu rnam dag
NK123(go)001:9093: gi ngang las rang shar ba'i zung 'jug gi lha
NK123(go)001:9094: sku nam mkha' dang mnyam par 'grub pa la rnying
NK123(go)001:9095: ma pas 'ja' lus 'od sku zhes btags pa 'di
NK123(go)001:9099: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i khyad par gnam sa
NK123(go)001:9100: ltar yod pa ni mdo tsam gong du smos zin
NK123(go)001:9101: la / zhib par gnyug sems 'od gsal la dbye
NK123(go)001:9102: ba'i skor sogs las kyang gsal bas der gzigs par
NK123(go)001:9103: la / mdzod cig / des dbang bsgyur thabs kyi
NK123(go)001:9104: theg pa ma h+aa a nu a ti gsum gyi
NK123(go)001:9105: theg pa mdo tsam bshad zin to //
NK123(go)001:9106: rtsa ba'i gsum pa lung gis zhabs bsdu ba ni /
NK123(go)001:9107: de ltar theg pa rim dgu'i rnam bzhag chos kyi
NK123(go)001:9108: rgyal po smin gling pa sku mched yab sras kyi
NK123(go)001:9110: gzhan kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po dang /
NK123(go)001:9111: kun gzigs kahthoga pa chen po dang zhe chen pan+di ta mthu stobs mtshan can yab sras dang /
NK123(go)001:9112: rigs bdag bka' drin mtshungs med 'jam mgon rnam gsum
NK123(go)001:9113: gyi gsung las btus te cung zad bshad zin nas
NK123(go)001:9114: / da ni de'i rgyab brten du rdzogs pa chen po rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud dang /
NK123(go)001:9115: bshad rgyud thig le kun gsal chen po'i rgyud las
NK123(go)001:9116: gsungs pa'i lung rnams kyang mdor bsdus te 'bri na
NK123(go)001:9120: nyan thos theg pa 'di lta ste /
NK123(go)001:9121: 'jug pa'i sgo ni bden pa bzhi //
NK123(go)001:9123: dbye ba rnam pa gnyis 'dod do //
NK123(go)001:9124: bye brag pa dang mdo sde pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9125: bye brag pa yi lta ba ni //
NK123(go)001:9126: phung po khams dang skye mched la //
NK123(go)001:9127: g.yag rnga ne'u gseng tshul du 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9128: rang gi blo yi ltas gyur na //
NK123(go)001:9129: rdul dang rdul phran dag tu 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9130: de bzhin rnam par gzhig nas ni //
NK123(go)001:9131: stong pa nyid du bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9132: mdo sde pa yi lta ba ni //
NK123(go)001:9133: kha don byas pa'i rang bzhin dang //
NK123(go)001:9134: thos pa bsams pa bsgom pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:9135: shes rab rnam gsum bsgom pa yis //
NK123(go)001:9137: nyan thos spyi yi rnam pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9138: bden pa rnam pa bzhi sgom zhing //
NK123(go)001:9140: de yang sgom lugs 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9145: mi chags gnas su zhugs nas ni //
NK123(go)001:9146: dang po zas la goms par byed //
NK123(go)001:9147: zas la goms par gyur pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9148: bsam gtan ting 'dzin sgom byed de //
NK123(go)001:9149: bsam gtan mi rtog chig tshugs sgom //
NK123(go)001:9150: rgyal ba byams pa'i bstan pa la //
NK123(go)001:9153: zas kyi 'du shes bral ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9155: de yang zhe sdang gnyen por sgom //
NK123(go)001:9156: nyon mongs thams cad spang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9157: sa lam sgom pa 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9158: 'dod chags gnyen por sgom pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9159: gti mug gnyen po sgom pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9160: de bzhin lam gyi sgom pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9162: lam gyi sgom lugs 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9163: 'dod chags dag gi gnyen po ru //
NK123(go)001:9164: rang gi dpral ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK123(go)001:9165: keng rus dkar po the bang tsam //
NK123(go)001:9166: dkar po 'od chags bsgoms pa las //
NK123(go)001:9167: de nas skye nas mgo bo tsam //
NK123(go)001:9168: de nas lus po tsam sgom ste //
NK123(go)001:9169: de nas rang gi tho yul tsam //
NK123(go)001:9170: de nas cir snang thams cad sgom //
NK123(go)001:9171: de ltar stong gsum dkar po ste //
NK123(go)001:9172: de ltar dkar po goms gyur nas //
NK123(go)001:9174: gti mug sdug bsngal spong ba ni //
NK123(go)001:9175: rang gi spyi bo'i gtsug tu yang //
NK123(go)001:9176: me dmar gsal la gdangs pa cig /
NK123(go)001:9177: bsgoms pas shes pa gsal ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9179: des ni gti mug sdug bsngal spongs //
NK123(go)001:9180: de ltar rnam bzhi bsgoms pa yis //
NK123(go)001:9181: 'bras bu rnam pa bzhi thob bo //
NK123(go)001:9182: 'bras bu bzhi po gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9184: rgyun du zhugs pa thob pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9185: rab tu dga' ba thob pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9186: de bzhin sa bdun man chad do //
NK123(go)001:9187: kun 'byung bsgoms pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK123(go)001:9188: lan cig phyir mi 'ong ba thob //
NK123(go)001:9189: sa brgyad man chad thob pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9190: lam bsgoms pa yi yon tan gyis //
NK123(go)001:9191: dgra bcom 'bras bu thob pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9192: sa bcu mthar phyin thob pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9193: sa dang lam la gnas pa'i tshe //
NK123(go)001:9194: nyan cing thos par byed pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9195: sa bdun man chad sems dpa' ni //
NK123(go)001:9196: rang rang dpon la nyan pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9197: sa brgyad yan chad sems dpa' ni //
NK123(go)001:9198: sprul pa'i sku las nyan par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9199: de yang dngos por mthong med do //
NK123(go)001:9200: byin gyi rlabs kyis thos pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9204: a ho gsang ba'i bdag po nyan //
NK123(go)001:9205: rang rgyal mdo sde'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9206: 'jug pa'i sgo ni rten 'brel bcu gnyis so //
NK123(go)001:9207: rtogs pa'i lta ba gang zag bdag med la //
NK123(go)001:9208: chos nyid bdag phyed yod par blta ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9209: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrung //
NK123(go)001:9210: sgom pa'i rim pa mi rtog chos nyid bsgom //
NK123(go)001:9211: phyi dang nang gi rten 'brel rnams //
NK123(go)001:9212: goms nas stobs su gyur pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9214: de yang dpe mtshon 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9215: dper na dur khrod ro bzhin te //
NK123(go)001:9216: dur khrod dag tu song nas ni //
NK123(go)001:9217: ro 'di dang po gang nas byung //
NK123(go)001:9218: da lta 'di yi dngos po ci //
NK123(go)001:9219: snyam du dpe yi mtshon par byed //
NK123(go)001:9220: de yang ma rig pa las byung //
NK123(go)001:9221: ma rig pa las 'du byed do //
NK123(go)001:9223: rnam par shes las ming 'byung zhing //
NK123(go)001:9224: ming las gzugs kyi rang bzhin 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9225: gzugs las skye mched rnam drug 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9226: skye mched drug las reg pa 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9229: sred pa las ni len pa 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9230: len pa las ni srid pa 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9231: srid pa las ni skye ba 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9232: skye ba las ni rgas pa 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9233: rgas pa las ni na ba 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9234: na ba las ni shi ba 'byung //
NK123(go)001:9235: de bzhin rten 'brel bcu gnyis bsgom //
NK123(go)001:9236: de ltar bsgom pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK123(go)001:9237: sa bcu gnyis kyi 'bras bu thob //
NK123(go)001:9238: mi sdug rnam pa brgyad bsgom ste //
NK123(go)001:9239: dur khrod phyogs su phyin nas ni //
NK123(go)001:9240: rang gi lus la 'di ltar rtog /
NK123(go)001:9241: dang po rnam par sngo bar 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9242: de nas rnam pa dmar ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9243: rnam par gnag pa dag dang ni //
NK123(go)001:9244: de bzhin rnam pa bam pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9245: de bzhin rnam par 'bu zhugs dang //
NK123(go)001:9246: rnam pa thor ba dag tu 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9247: de bzhin rnam par dgar ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9248: de bzhin 'dod chags gnyen po ru //
NK123(go)001:9249: mi sdug rnam pa brgyad bsgom pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9250: nyan dang thos pa med pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9251: de phyir rang rgyal theg par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9255: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9256: 'jug pa'i sgo ni bden pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9257: don dam dang ni kun rdzob bo //
NK123(go)001:9258: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims yan lag ni //
NK123(go)001:9259: sdom pa brgyad cu rtsa lnga'o //
NK123(go)001:9260: lta ba stong nyid ye shes so //
NK123(go)001:9261: don dam kun rdzob 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9262: kun rdzob rnam pa gnyis su 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9263: log pa dang ni yang dag go //
NK123(go)001:9264: log pa'i kun rdzob 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9265: brtags par snang ba thams cad kun //
NK123(go)001:9266: mthun par snang la don byed nus //
NK123(go)001:9267: brtags na ngo bo nyid kyis dben //
NK123(go)001:9268: don ni med pa ltar snang ngo //
NK123(go)001:9269: de ni log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NK123(go)001:9270: yang dag kun rdzob 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9271: dge ba bcu yi las rnams dang //
NK123(go)001:9272: dkar por gyur pa'i bsam pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9273: mos pa'i bsam pa ji snyed pa //
NK123(go)001:9274: yang dag kun rdzob chen por 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9275: sbyin pa la sogs tshul khrims dang //
NK123(go)001:9276: de bzhin ting 'dzin la sogs rnams //
NK123(go)001:9277: yang dag kun rdzob chen po'o //
NK123(go)001:9278: don dam la yang rnam pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9279: mtshan ma tshig gi don dam dang //
NK123(go)001:9280: yang dag sems kyi don dam mo //
NK123(go)001:9281: mtshan ma tshig gi don dam ni //
NK123(go)001:9283: de yang tshad ma'i rigs pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9284: gang de nyid la de ltar snang //
NK123(go)001:9285: tshig gi stong pa chen po la //
NK123(go)001:9286: don la stong zhing ma rtogs pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9287: mtshan ma tshig gi don dam mo //
NK123(go)001:9288: yang dag sems kyi don dam ni //
NK123(go)001:9289: stong pa cang med sgom par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9290: dper na nam mkha' stong pa bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9291: stong pa'i don nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK123(go)001:9292: stong nyid phyang chad mu med do //
NK123(go)001:9293: zhes ni spyod cing chags pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9296: de yang drod skye bzod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9297: rtse mo 'jig rten chos mchog go //
NK123(go)001:9298: drod la rnam pa gsum gyis bstan //
NK123(go)001:9299: phyi dang nang dang gnyis ka'o //
NK123(go)001:9300: phyi yi dro skye 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9301: gnyis po dri ma med pa la //
NK123(go)001:9302: dngos por snang ba stong par skye //
NK123(go)001:9303: de ni ting 'dzin nyams len te //
NK123(go)001:9304: sa gnyis dag la skye bar gsungs //
NK123(go)001:9305: nang gi drod ni drug pa la //
NK123(go)001:9306: stong pa rig byed dag tu rtogs //
NK123(go)001:9307: gnyis ka'i drod ni 'di ltar te //
NK123(go)001:9308: bdun pa dag las skye bar gsungs //
NK123(go)001:9309: brgyad pa bzod pa thob pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9310: dgu pa rtse mo mthar phyin no //
NK123(go)001:9311: bcu pa 'jig rten chos kyi mchog /
NK123(go)001:9312: de bzhin sa bcu thob par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9313: de ni byang chub theg pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9314: stong pa'i tshig med yi ge med //
NK123(go)001:9319: k+r+ai yi'i theg pa'i grub mtha' ni //
NK123(go)001:9320: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:9322: bsrung ba'i dam tshig 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9323: lung gcig chu la mi btung zhing //
NK123(go)001:9324: ma yengs ngang la spyod pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9325: bya ba dag pa rnam gsum byed //
NK123(go)001:9326: dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9327: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9328: rdzas dang longs spyod dag pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9330: rtogs pa'i lta ba 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9331: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9332: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du lta //
NK123(go)001:9333: spang ba'i rim pa 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9334: sha dang nya dang sgog pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9335: de bzhin chang la sogs pa spong //
NK123(go)001:9337: k+r+ai yi'i theg pa de bzhin no //
NK123(go)001:9341: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9342: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK123(go)001:9343: spyod pa k+r+ai yar spyad pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9344: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK123(go)001:9348: yo ga'i grub mtha' 'di ltar ste //
NK123(go)001:9349: 'jug pa'i sgo ni mngon par byang chub lnga //
NK123(go)001:9350: rtogs pa'i lta ba lha dang grogs po'i tshul //
NK123(go)001:9351: bsrung ba'i dam tshig ma khrol rnam gsum bsrung //
NK123(go)001:9352: spyod pa dag ni dgag sgrub med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9353: byang chub lnga po 'di lnga ste //
NK123(go)001:9354: gdan gyi sgo nas byang chub dang //
NK123(go)001:9355: sku yi sgo nas byang chub dang //
NK123(go)001:9356: phyag mtshan sgo nas byang chub dang //
NK123(go)001:9357: bskyed pa'i sgo nas byang chub dang //
NK123(go)001:9358: yig 'bru'i sgo nas byang chub bo //
NK123(go)001:9359: de ltar byang chub lnga po spyod //
NK123(go)001:9360: ma khrel gsum po gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9361: yi dam lha yi ma khrel dang //
NK123(go)001:9362: slob dpon mched kyis ma khrel dang //
NK123(go)001:9363: rang gi sems kyi ma khrel ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9364: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK123(go)001:9365: spun dang grogs po'i tshul du 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9366: lha yi dkyil 'khor bdag dang gnyis med bsgoms //
NK123(go)001:9367: lha yang bdag las byung zhing thim par 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9370: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK123(go)001:9372: kye ma gsang bdag nges par gzung //
NK123(go)001:9373: ma h+aa'i grub mtha' 'di ltar te //
NK123(go)001:9374: 'jug pa'i sgo ni ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:9375: rtogs pa'i lta ba cir snang lha ru rtogs //
NK123(go)001:9376: bsrung ba'i dam tshig rtsa ba sku gsung thugs //
NK123(go)001:9377: 'bras bu thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med //
NK123(go)001:9379: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin //
NK123(go)001:9380: rtog med sa le seng nge'o //
NK123(go)001:9381: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin //
NK123(go)001:9382: gsal la ma yengs tshul du bsgom //
NK123(go)001:9383: de bzhin rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin //
NK123(go)001:9384: h'u las sems dpa' sum brtsegs bsgom //
NK123(go)001:9385: bdag nyid dam tshig sems dpa' la //
NK123(go)001:9386: phun sum tshogs pa bzhi dang ldan //
NK123(go)001:9388: gsal ba rnam pa gsum dang ldan //
NK123(go)001:9389: ye shes sems dpa' rnam gnyis te //
NK123(go)001:9390: zhi ba dang ni khro bo'o //
NK123(go)001:9392: yam dang ram dang kham dang ni //
NK123(go)001:9393: ra dang sum dang kam dang ni //
NK123(go)001:9394: pam dang a dang ma dang ni //
NK123(go)001:9395: h'u dang phata la sogs pa yi //
NK123(go)001:9397: rab tu sprul nas nga rgyal ldan //
NK123(go)001:9398: rnam pa'i lha dang stong pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9400: dam tshig rnam gsum 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9401: sku yi sgo na srog gcod spang bar bya //
NK123(go)001:9402: ma byin len dang mi tshang spyod pa spang //
NK123(go)001:9403: gsung gi sgo nas rdzun dang phra ma spang //
NK123(go)001:9404: tshig rtsub dang ni de bzhin kyal ba spang //
NK123(go)001:9405: thugs kyi sgo nas brnab sems gnod sems spang //
NK123(go)001:9406: log par lta ba rab tu spang bar bya //
NK123(go)001:9407: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par rtogs //
NK123(go)001:9408: ma h+aa yo ga'i grub mtha' de bzhin 'dod //
NK123(go)001:9412: kye ma rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon //
NK123(go)001:9413: lung chen a nu'i theg pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9414: dbyings dang ye shes rnam pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9416: 'jug pa'i sgo ni cig char rim gyis so //
NK123(go)001:9417: rtogs pa'i lta ba 'du 'bral med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9418: cig char 'jug pa gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9419: lha rnams ma bskyed snying po dran pas rdzogs //
NK123(go)001:9420: rim gyis 'jug pa gang zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9421: dbyings dang ye shes rim gyis zhugs nas ni //
NK123(go)001:9422: rdo rje 'dzin gyi sa la 'bras bu thob //
NK123(go)001:9423: bsrung ba'i dam tshig 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9424: gsang sngags don ston rtag tu bkur bar byas //
NK123(go)001:9425: gsang sngags ston pa'i slob dpon la //
NK123(go)001:9427: slob dpon dang ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK123(go)001:9428: khyab med gcig gi ngo bor bsten //
NK123(go)001:9429: mdor bsdus dbyings dang ye shes so //
NK123(go)001:9430: lung chen a nu'i grub matha'o //
NK123(go)001:9432: man ngag rdzogs pa chen po ni //
NK123(go)001:9434: e ma gsang ba'i bdag po nyon //
NK123(go)001:9435: ngas bstan legs par yid la gzung //
NK123(go)001:9436: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK123(go)001:9437: gcig rdzogs gnyis rdzogs thams cad rdzogs //
NK123(go)001:9438: gcig byung gnyis byung thams cad byung //
NK123(go)001:9439: gcig skye gnyis skye thams cad skye //
NK123(go)001:9440: gcig med gnyis med thams cad med //
NK123(go)001:9441: de bzhin rdzogs chen a ti la //
NK123(go)001:9442: byas pa'i chos ni ka nas med //
NK123(go)001:9443: byas dang byed pa med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9444: rdzogs pa chen po'i don nyid la //
NK123(go)001:9445: dam tshig bsrung du med pas ye nas bsrung dang bral //
NK123(go)001:9446: med pa phyal ba lhun grub gcig pu nyid //
NK123(go)001:9447: gsang basngagasa kun gyi dgongs pa chen po yin //
NK123(go)001:9448: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga ni //
NK123(go)001:9449: dper na gcan gzan seng ge bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9450: gsang ba a ti yo ga ni //
NK123(go)001:9451: rang rig gtan la 'bebs shing theg dman zin gyis gnon //
NK123(go)001:9452: rang byung rang la thim pas sku gsum don //
NK123(go)001:9453: skye med dbyings las sgom med chen po yin //
NK123(go)001:9454: bsgom bya bsgom byed gnyis dang bral //
NK123(go)001:9455: 'dzin pa med pa'i rang grol ni //
NK123(go)001:9456: dper na sbrul gyi mdud pa bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9457: rang grol rang sangs chen po yin //
NK123(go)001:9458: de bzhin mtshan ma'i bsam pa rnams //
NK123(go)001:9459: rang grol rang sangs chen po'i //
NK123(go)001:9460: rdzogs chen a ti'i theg pa la //
NK123(go)001:9461: re dang dogs pa ga la yod //
NK123(go)001:9462: re dogs yod na lhung ba'i rgyu //
NK123(go)001:9463: de bzhin 'dzin med rang grol lo //
NK123(go)001:9464: chos can mtshan mar snang ba yang //
NK123(go)001:9465: rang las byung zhing rang la thim //
NK123(go)001:9466: de bzhin rdzogs chen a ti la //
NK123(go)001:9467: sgrub med bsgrub dang bral ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9468: byas med byung ba med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9471: chos med sangs rgyas chen po'o //
NK123(go)001:9472: gnas med ye shes med pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9473: sems med yid med sangs rgyas med //
NK123(go)001:9475: de ltar rig pa rang shar chen po'i rgyud kyi
NK123(go)001:9476: lung tshig rnams theg mchog mdzod du drangs pa ltar
NK123(go)001:9477: bsdus pa yin la lung gi don 'grel yang de
NK123(go)001:9479: gnyis pa bshad rgyud thig le kun gsal chen po'i rgyud kyi lung sbyor la /
NK123(go)001:9480: thog mar theg pa'i ngo bo dang nges tshig sogs spyir bstan pa ni /
NK123(go)001:9482: theg pa'i ngo bo shes rab snying rje yin //
NK123(go)001:9483: de gnyis che chung theg pa mtho dman snang //
NK123(go)001:9484: theg pa'i nges tshig 'degs dang skyob pa yin //
NK123(go)001:9485: dbye na mang po'ang bsdu na gnyis las med //
NK123(go)001:9486: rgyu rkyen lam khyer mtshan nyid theg pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9487: 'bras bu lam khyer gsang sngags theg pa gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9488: rkyal pa gru gzings mtshan nyid theg pa'i dpe //
NK123(go)001:9489: zam pa sa gzhi gsang sngags theg pa'i dpe //
NK123(go)001:9491: bye brag so so'i ngo bo yang //
NK123(go)001:9493: snang ba'i ngo bo nges tshig dang //
NK123(go)001:9494: dbye ba so so'i dpe ru bshad //
NK123(go)001:9495: dang po dbye ba rgyas bsdus gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9496: rgyas pa la yang rnam pa bzhi //
NK123(go)001:9497: 'gro drug zhen pa'i snang ba drug /
NK123(go)001:9498: rgyu 'bras blo yi snang ba bcu //
NK123(go)001:9499: rtogs ldan don gyi snang ba gcig /
NK123(go)001:9500: dbyer med kun bzang snang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9501: bsdus pas snang ba rnam pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:9502: ma dag 'khrul ba'i snang ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9503: dag pa 'jig rten snang ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9504: yang dag ye shes snang ba'o //
NK123(go)001:9505: dang po rgyas par bshad bya ba //
NK123(go)001:9506: 'gro drug zhen pa'i snang ba drug /
NK123(go)001:9508: snang ba'i dngos po 'di nyid la //
NK123(go)001:9509: dmyal ba tsha grangs gnyis su mthong //
NK123(go)001:9510: yi dwags gsum la snang ba gsum //
NK123(go)001:9511: phyi nang spyi mthun snang ba gsum //
NK123(go)001:9512: phyi ni zas la rnag khrag dang //
NK123(go)001:9513: gos la tsher ma lta bu'o //
NK123(go)001:9514: phyi la zas snang srung mas bsrungs //
NK123(go)001:9515: nang ni srung med zos pas dug /
NK123(go)001:9516: de ni yi dwags gsum la snang //
NK123(go)001:9517: byol song gnyis la snang ba gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9518: bying na gnas pa mun pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9519: kha thor rnams la gyen thur dang //
NK123(go)001:9520: bza' btung ma 'gags thad kar snang //
NK123(go)001:9521: mi la snang ba 'di nyid de //
NK123(go)001:9522: yul dang sa phyogs khyim la sogs //
NK123(go)001:9523: lha ma yin la go mtshan snang //
NK123(go)001:9524: lha la rin chen bdud rtsi snang //
NK123(go)001:9525: blo snang zhen pa'i bag chags yin //
NK123(go)001:9526: rgyu 'bras blo yi snang ba bcu //
NK123(go)001:9527: mu stegs rtag pa'i snang ba yang //
NK123(go)001:9528: rtag pa'i dngos las gzhan mi snang //
NK123(go)001:9529: mu stegs chad pa'i snang ba yang //
NK123(go)001:9530: 'di yod phyi ma med pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9531: 'di snang glo bur byung ba la //
NK123(go)001:9532: zhig pas 'byung lnga'i ngang du zhi //
NK123(go)001:9533: med char snang la gzhan mi snang //
NK123(go)001:9534: nyan thos g.yag rnga ne'u seng dang //
NK123(go)001:9535: gong bu cha shas med par blta //
NK123(go)001:9536: gzung 'dzin chos kyi bdag tu mthong //
NK123(go)001:9537: rang rgyal gong mthun phyogs gcig stong //
NK123(go)001:9538: phung po khams la bdag med stong //
NK123(go)001:9539: mdo sde'i don dam stong pa nyid //
NK123(go)001:9540: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du snang //
NK123(go)001:9541: gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis po dang //
NK123(go)001:9542: don dam mdo sde mthun pa la //
NK123(go)001:9543: kun rdzob snang ba so sor mthong //
NK123(go)001:9544: k+r+ai yas rigs gsum rje 'khor mthong //
NK123(go)001:9545: u pas lha dang dpon g.yog mthong //
NK123(go)001:9546: yo gas spun dang grogs po mthong //
NK123(go)001:9547: ma h+aas phung po lhar snang mthong //
NK123(go)001:9548: a nus dbyings dang ye shes mthong //
NK123(go)001:9549: kun gyi rgyu 'bras ma spangs shing //
NK123(go)001:9550: dngos por mi ldan blo la snang //
NK123(go)001:9551: rgyu 'bras blo yi snang ba yin //
NK123(go)001:9552: rtogs ldan don gyi snang ba ni //
NK123(go)001:9553: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i snang ba yin //
NK123(go)001:9554: thams cad chos sku'i ngo bor mthong //
NK123(go)001:9555: kun tu bzang po'i snang ba ni //
NK123(go)001:9556: gong ma dang mtshungs gnyis med snang //
NK123(go)001:9557: thog ma'i gzhi snang 'du tshul ni //
NK123(go)001:9558: bsdus pas snang ba rnam pa gsum //
NK123(go)001:9559: ma dag 'khrul pa'i snang ba rigs drug yin //
NK123(go)001:9560: dag pa 'jig rten sa bcu'i byang sems yin //
NK123(go)001:9561: yang dag ye shes gzhi snang gong dang mthun //
NK123(go)001:9562: snang ba'i dbye ba rgyas bsdus bstan pa'o //
NK123(go)001:9566: so so'i ming gi nges tshig ni //
NK123(go)001:9567: ngas bstan khyod kyis legs par zung //
NK123(go)001:9568: ston pas gsungs pa'i tshig don rnams //
NK123(go)001:9569: rna bas nyan cing yid kyis thos //
NK123(go)001:9570: rang rig khong nas mi 'char bar //
NK123(go)001:9571: ston pa'i gsung la rag las pas //
NK123(go)001:9572: nyan thos ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9573: ston pas gzhan la mi ltos par //
NK123(go)001:9574: rang gi mthu yis rang sangs rgyas //
NK123(go)001:9575: rang rgyal ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9576: spang dang ye shes thugs rje dang //
NK123(go)001:9577: phrin las phun sum tshogs pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9578: de don gzhan la sgrogs byed pa //
NK123(go)001:9579: byang sems ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9580: khrus dang gtsang sbra gtsor bstan pas //
NK123(go)001:9581: kri y+aa zhes su bstan pa yin //
NK123(go)001:9582: spyod pa mas 'dzegs lta ba yas //
NK123(go)001:9583: u pa'i ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9584: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas sku rnams la //
NK123(go)001:9585: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum sbyor //
NK123(go)001:9586: yo ga'i ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9587: ting 'dzin gsum dang thabs shes gtsor bstan pa'i //
NK123(go)001:9588: don la 'jug pa ma h+aa'i nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9589: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i don la 'jug pa'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:9590: rdzogs pa a nu'i ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9591: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK123(go)001:9592: lhun grub chos skur ye nas rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK123(go)001:9593: gnas lugs gnyis med tshul gyis 'jug pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9594: rnal 'byor rdzogs chen ming gi nges tshig yin //
NK123(go)001:9596: dbye na chung 'bring che gsum la gsum gsum du dbye ba theg rim dgu las /
NK123(go)001:9598: ldem po'i lta ba 'di lta ste //
NK123(go)001:9599: nyan thos rang rgyal sems dpa' dang //
NK123(go)001:9600: kri yog sde gsum bskyed rdzogs gnyis //
NK123(go)001:9601: bden par phyogs re ngos bzung nas //
NK123(go)001:9602: gza' gtad bcas pa'i lta ba brgyad //
NK123(go)001:9603: blo yul gnyis kyi mur 'dzin pas //
NK123(go)001:9604: rang rig ye shes la ma bzlos //
NK123(go)001:9605: de bas phyin ci log pa yin //
NK123(go)001:9606: don la nyams dang gol ba'i phyir //
NK123(go)001:9607: zhe 'dod blo yi lta ba yin //
NK123(go)001:9608: zhes sogs lta ba brgyad dang /
NK123(go)001:9609: dmigs gtad bcas pa'i sgom pa brgyad //
NK123(go)001:9610: rtsol ba blo yi yul bzung bas //
NK123(go)001:9611: rtsol bral blo las grol ma rtogs //
NK123(go)001:9612: de bsgoms ma shes 'dod pa bsgoms //
NK123(go)001:9613: zhes sogs sgom pa brgyad dang /
NK123(go)001:9614: theg brgyad rang gi spyod pa brgyad //
NK123(go)001:9615: sdug bsngal rtsol sgrub bcas pas spyod //
NK123(go)001:9616: blang dor med pa ma rtogs pas //
NK123(go)001:9617: thun mong ma gyur blang dor spyod //
NK123(go)001:9618: ces sogs spyod pa brgyad dang /
NK123(go)001:9619: theg pa so so'i 'bras bu ni //
NK123(go)001:9620: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK123(go)001:9621: nyan thos dag gi 'bras bu ni //
NK123(go)001:9622: lta sgom spyod pa mthar phyin pas //
NK123(go)001:9623: 'bras bu zung bzhi ya brgyad smin //
NK123(go)001:9624: zhes sogs 'bras bu brgyad bcas so so phye ste /
NK123(go)001:9627: bltar med lta ba'i don bstan pa //
NK123(go)001:9628: a ti'i lta ba gzab gtad bral //
NK123(go)001:9629: dngos med ye shes zang thal bas //
NK123(go)001:9630: rang rig ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NK123(go)001:9631: de las ma gtogs gzhan med pas //
NK123(go)001:9632: so so rang rig ye shes la //
NK123(go)001:9633: cir snang ye shes chen po'i gdangs //
NK123(go)001:9634: ye nyid bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK123(go)001:9635: zhes sogs yang dag nges pa'i lta ba dang /
NK123(go)001:9636: ngas bstan gnyis med bde chen la //
NK123(go)001:9637: sgom du yod med tha snyad rnam par dag /
NK123(go)001:9638: shes rab stobs can rang rig don rtogs pas //
NK123(go)001:9639: gnyis med bde chen ngang du 'du 'bral med //
NK123(go)001:9640: ma btsal bzhag pas ngang las ma g.yos gsal //
NK123(go)001:9641: rgyun chad med pas chu bo g+aang+ga bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9642: zhes sogs dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi sgom thabs dang /
NK123(go)001:9643: blang dor med pa'i spyod pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9644: spyad rgyu med pa spyod pa'i mchog /
NK123(go)001:9645: chos nyid don gyi spyod pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9646: mtshan ma med pas nam mkha' bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9647: chos can mtshan ma mi lta bar //
NK123(go)001:9648: rnal 'byor zag med shes rab kyis //
NK123(go)001:9649: dngos med nam mkha' bzhin du spyod //
NK123(go)001:9650: zhes sogs a ti'i spyod pa dang /
NK123(go)001:9651: 'bras bu lta ba mngon du gyur pa ste //
NK123(go)001:9652: de yi gnas lugs bstan pa ni //
NK123(go)001:9653: chos nyid phyi nang med par gsal //
NK123(go)001:9654: rig pa phyi nang med par khyab //
NK123(go)001:9655: gnyis med chos sku rdo rje'i lus //
NK123(go)001:9656: rang gsal 'dzin med ngang du gnas //
NK123(go)001:9657: zhes sogs yang dag don gyi 'bras bu'i bar /
NK123(go)001:9658: le'u dgus bstan pa rgyud rang las shes par bya'o //
NK123(go)001:9659: theg pa 'og ma rnams las gong ma rnams khyad du 'phags tshul yang /
NK123(go)001:9661: ma rtogs log par rtogs las nyan thos khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9662: de yang ji ltar 'phags zhe na //
NK123(go)001:9663: gang zag bdag med rtogs pas lta ba khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9664: dge bcu rang don la spyad pas spyod pa khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9665: bden bzhi'i sgo nas bsgrubs pas khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9666: zung bzhi ya brgyad thob pas 'bras bu khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9667: nyan thos dag las rang rgyal 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:9668: gzugs kyi phung po chos kyi khams dag la //
NK123(go)001:9669: phyogs gcig bdag med rtogs pas lta ba khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9670: dge bcu rdzu 'phrul spyod pas spyod pa khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9671: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mi brten par //
NK123(go)001:9672: goms pa'i shugs kyis sgrubs pas sgrub pa khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9673: ne tso bse ru ltar gnas 'bras bu khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9674: rang rgyal dag las byang sems 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:9675: bdag med rnam gnyis rtogs pas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9676: tshad med bsdu bzhi'i don mdzad spyod par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9677: pha rol phyin bcu bsgrub pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9678: kun tu 'od kyi sa gnon 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9679: byang sems dag las kri y+aa bzhis 'phags te //
NK123(go)001:9680: don dam skye ba med pa rab rtogs shing //
NK123(go)001:9681: kun rdzob bdag dang ye shes sems pa'i lha //
NK123(go)001:9682: rje dang bran du lta bas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9683: dag pa rnam gsum spyod pas spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9684: sgom rgyud byin rlabs bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9685: rigs gsum 'bras bu gnon pas 'bras bu khyad par 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9686: kri y+aa dag las u pa 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:9687: lha bdag dpon g.yog lta bas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9688: mtshan ma yod med spyod pas spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9689: kho na nyid bzhi bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9690: rigs bzhi'i go 'phang thob pas 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9691: u pa dag las yo ga 'phags pa yang //
NK123(go)001:9692: kun rdzob lha dang grogs su lta bas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9693: phrin las rnam bzhi spyod pas spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9694: phyag rgya rnam bzhi bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9695: rigs bzhi sangs rgyas 'grub pas 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9696: yo ga dag las ma h+aa bzhis 'phags te //
NK123(go)001:9697: rang lus dkyil 'khor lta bas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9698: sbyor sgrol gnyis med spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9699: thabs shes gnyis med bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9700: stug po bkod pa'i sa thob 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9701: ma h+aa dag las a nu bzhis 'phags te //
NK123(go)001:9702: dbyings dang ye shes rtogs pas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9703: dbyings dang ye shes dag las spyod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9704: ye shes dbyings la spyod pas spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9705: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba rnam pa lnga //
NK123(go)001:9706: rigs lnga yab yum bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9707: pad+ma can gyi sa thob 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9708: a nu dag las a ti bzhis 'phags te //
NK123(go)001:9709: snang srid chos skur sangs rgyas lta ba 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9710: chos sku 'gro don spyod pas spyod pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9711: bya rtsol med par bsgrubs pas sgrub pa 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9712: bcu drug 'khor lo tshogs chen yan chad nas //
NK123(go)001:9713: nyi shu rtsa gcig man chad 'bras bu 'phags //
NK123(go)001:9715: khyad par gyi che ba yang /
NK123(go)001:9717: gnas skabs 'gyur ba'i che ba rnams //
NK123(go)001:9718: theg pa so so'i che ba yin //
NK123(go)001:9719: mthar thug che ba rnam pa lnga //
NK123(go)001:9721: phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lngas //
NK123(go)001:9722: mngon par sangs rgyas che ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9723: bzhugs gnas dbyings kyi mtshan nyid lngas //
NK123(go)001:9724: chos dbyings sangs rgyas che ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9725: bdag nyid chen po rang rdzogs lngas //
NK123(go)001:9726: bdag nyid sangs rgyas che ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9727: gtan la 'bebs pa'i thabs chen lngas //
NK123(go)001:9728: sangs rgyas yin pa che ba dang //
NK123(go)001:9729: dri med rnam dag mngon 'phags pas //
NK123(go)001:9730: thams cad sangs rgyas che ba lnga //
NK123(go)001:9731: mthar thug che ba rnam lnga yin //
NK123(go)001:9732: zhes de dag gi don dkrol nas rgyas par gsungs pa dang /
NK123(go)001:9733: a nu man chod yid dpyod dang 'dres pas gol sar bstan nas /
NK123(go)001:9734: a ti rang byung gi ye shes la gol sgrib sogs med par bstan pa yang /
NK123(go)001:9735: rdzogs chen thig le nyag gcig la //
NK123(go)001:9736: gol dang ma gol gnyis su med //
NK123(go)001:9737: gol sa rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK123(go)001:9738: kun bral nyag gcig cir ma spangs //
NK123(go)001:9739: a ti'i lta sgom spyod pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9740: 'bras bu ye nas gnyis med pas //
NK123(go)001:9741: gnyis su snang ba'i gol sgrib med //
NK123(go)001:9742: lta sgom spyod pa 'bras bu bzhi //
NK123(go)001:9743: ye nas rang byung ye shes pas //
NK123(go)001:9744: rgyu rkyen 'dus pa'i gol sgrib med //
NK123(go)001:9745: rdzogs chen lta ba bsgom pa dang //
NK123(go)001:9746: spyod pa 'bras bu lhun grub pas //
NK123(go)001:9747: sgom sgrub re dogs rtsol ba yin //
NK123(go)001:9748: gol sa sgrib pa rnam par dag /
NK123(go)001:9749: nga yi gong na gzhan med pas //
NK123(go)001:9750: sgrib med gsal ba'i ye shes yin //
NK123(go)001:9751: theg brgyad 'og ma snang ba yang //
NK123(go)001:9752: nga yi thugs rje'i mdzad spyod yin //
NK123(go)001:9753: dbyer med shes rab rang la gnas //
NK123(go)001:9754: ma 'dres rdzogs pa'i ye shes pas //
NK123(go)001:9755: lhung ba'i gol sa rnam par dag /
NK123(go)001:9756: dbyer med shes rab rang gsal la //
NK123(go)001:9757: gol sgrib gnyis su 'byed med gsal //
NK123(go)001:9759: mtshon tshig sogs rgyas par gsungs shing /
NK123(go)001:9760: gzhan yang rdzogs chen gyi rgyud rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:9761: mdo dgongs 'dus sogs snga 'gyur gyi rgyud gzhung rnams dang /
NK123(go)001:9763: kahdama pa rin po ches mdzad pa'i theg dgu'i spyi chings dang /
NK123(go)001:9764: de'i 'grel ba mkhas grub ye shes rgya mtshos mdzad
NK123(go)001:9765: pa sogs mang du bzhugs pa de dag 'dir bsdu
NK123(go)001:9766: ma long bas de dang der gzigs par mdzod cig
NK123(go)001:9768: bkra shis yon tan bye ba'i dpal gyis mngon 'phags thub dbang lha yi lha'i //
NK123(go)001:9769: dpal gyi mgul las legs 'ong zab dang rgya che'i chos mchog nor bu'i sgrom //
NK123(go)001:9770: tshang la ma nor snga 'gyur rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i zhal gyi lung bzang po //
NK123(go)001:9771: deng yang ma nyams spyod yod e ma sngon goms dge ba'i dpal las so //
NK123(go)001:9772: mkhyen brtse'i sprin bzang las thon 'phags lam yan lag brgyad ldan bdud rtsa'i char //
NK123(go)001:9773: gnas skabs gdul bya'i snod kyi dbye bas dman 'bring mchog tshul cir snang yang //
NK123(go)001:9774: mthar thug 'od gsal snying po'i klong du ro mnyam chu bran rgya mtshor bzhin //
NK123(go)001:9775: mthar thug theg gcig 'bras bu'i tshul la nges don mdo rgyud dgongs pa mthun //
NK123(go)001:9776: lha mi'i theg pa'i sa gzhi la brten mtshan nyid sde gsum gser ri'i skor //
NK123(go)001:9777: rgyud sde bzhi yi bang rim legs mdzes bskyed rdzogs nyi zla'i rna cha can //
NK123(go)001:9778: 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i lhun po srid zhi'i bla na mngon 'phags pa //
NK123(go)001:9779: brgyud gsum bla ma rig 'dzin lha dbang bye bas nye bar brten byar gyur //
NK123(go)001:9780: de slad bdag blo dman yang tshul 'dir gcig tu gus pas nyer len gyis //
NK123(go)001:9781: zla bral mkhas grub du ma'i gsungs las cung zad 'di ru bsdu bar byas //
NK123(go)001:9782: legs bshad gsar du spro ba'i nus pa bdag lta'i skal bar gyur min yang //
NK123(go)001:9783: dam pa'i gsungs la rang bzos bcos shing bslad pa'i dri ma med snyam bgyid //
NK123(go)001:9784: 'on kyang skyes thob sbyong brtson dman dang brjed ngas bag med gyur sogs kyis //
NK123(go)001:9785: nongs par gyur na snying nas bshags bgyi 'phags pa rnams kyis tshangs par rtsol //
NK123(go)001:9786: lhag bsam mthu dang cung zad ngal ba bgyis las bsod nams gang thob pa //
NK123(go)001:9787: de yang bdag gzhan skye kun yang dag lam gyi snang ba thob phyir bsngo //
NK123(go)001:9788: rmad byung 'khor lo bzhi yi ba dan legs mdzes dal 'byor gru bo mchog /
NK123(go)001:9789: yang dag lam gyi ded dpon gyis bskul theg mchog nor bu'i gling bgrod nas //
NK123(go)001:9790: zab dang rgya che'i 'byor bas brgyan byas gzhan 'phan lhag bsam brtson pa'i mthus //
NK123(go)001:9791: ma lus 'gro la chos mchog 'dod dgu'i char chen rtag par 'bebs byed shog /
NK123(go)001:9792: srid zhi'i phun tshogs kun gyi 'byung gnas ris bral thub bstan ba dan rtser //
NK123(go)001:9793: grol ba drug ldan snga 'gyur bstan mchog dgos 'byung nor bu'i tog 'bar bas //
NK123(go)001:9794: bstan la 'tshe byed lha min kla klo gdug pa'i g.yul las rnam rgyal zhing //
NK123(go)001:9795: chos ltar bcos pa'i mun sprul kun zhi bkra shis bde legs 'phel gyur cig //
NK123(go)001:9796: ces pa'ang rang nyid kyi dran pa'i gsos tsam du
NK123(go)001:9797: sngar bris pa las cung zad rgyas par phyes te
NK123(go)001:9798: / gdod ma'i mgon po dang zhabs mi gnyis pa
NK123(go)001:9799: rdzogs chen rab 'byams lnga pa'i zhabs rdul la spyi
NK123(go)001:9800: bos reg pa'i rig 'dzin gyi btsun pa rdo rje
NK123(go)001:9801: thugs mchog rtsal lam ming gzhan 'jam dbyangs blo gros
NK123(go)001:9803: rang lo zhe drug pa me 'brug sa ga zla
NK123(go)001:9804: ba'i tshes bcu nyi ma me bzhi'i 'gru sbyor gyi
NK123(go)001:9805: snga char / rang gnas dpal zhe chen bstan gnyis
NK123(go)001:9806: dar rgyas gling gi dben spyi la bkra shis 'chi
NK123(go)001:9807: med 'od snang du grub par bgyis pa las /
NK123(go)001:9808: yi ge gnyis par spel ba po ni sdom brtson
NK123(go)001:9809: sde snod smra ba tshul khrims rnam dag gis mdzad
NK123(go)001:9810: pa ste / 'dis kyang bstan pa rin po che yun du gnas pa'i rgyur gyur cig //
NK123(go)001:9811: sarba th+aa mang+ga lam b+ha wa tu //
